#: Convo.dgn_challenge_sdmnt_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_challenge_sdmnt_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
