"Ха! На відміну від тих панцирів, я не тріскаюся під тиском."

#: Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "I'm guessing you've got a second challenge up your feathery sleeve for me?"
msgstr "Гадаю, ти приготувала для мене друге випробування у своєму пернатому рукаві?"

#: Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "Okay... I'll try my best."
msgstr "Добре... я спробую зробити все можливе."

#: Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_challenge_thtchr_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END_ALT"
msgid "<#RED>{condition_2}</> before reaching the end?\n"
"What, are you going easy on me, {name.shop_magpie}?"
msgstr "<#RED>{condition_2}</> перш ніж дійти до кінця?\n"
"Що, ти зменшуєш рівень складності для мене, {Name.shop_magpie}?"

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REALLY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REALLY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>Bwe-heu-heu!</i> Of course not! Supping on any form of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> is madness!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WHATDO
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WHATDO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Why I doth eat them. To prompt psychedlic visions for new pieces..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_YEAHRIGHT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_YEAHRIGHT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\t\t\t\t\n"
" I doth use them to fuel mine forge to maketh more pieces.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" My craft... is my life. <z 0.7>*Single Tear* *So Humble*</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "Right, right... Well, back to browsing."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь, голубе."

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REALLY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REALLY"
msgid "Whoa! Really?!"
msgstr "Ого! Справді?!"

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WHATDO
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WHATDO"
msgid "I'm curious: What do you do with all the {name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser} I give you?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_YEAHRIGHT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_corestones_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_YEAHRIGHT"
msgid "Pfft, yeah right. What do you <i>really</> do with them?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Because I think it's adorable how you gallivant about the forest playing \"hero\".\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" I suppose I shouldn't encourage your delusion by selling you my pieces, but--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I can't help it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Бо я думаю, це мило, як ви ганяєтеся по лісі, граючи в \"героя\".\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!eyeroll\n"
"Припускаю, не варто підтримувати ваші ілюзії, продаючи вам мої речі, але...\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Я не можу втриматися."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Yes!\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Oh, cometh on. Don't pretend you don't like it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Так!\n"
"!eyeroll\n"
"Ой, ну ж бо. Не прикидайтесь, що вам це не подобається."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Bless your heart."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!closedeyes\n"
"Благословляю ваше серце."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Fare thee well, little culver!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!wink\n"
"Прощавай, маленький голубе!"

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh my. \n"
" !point\n"
" You. <i>You're</> a culver. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Or, if pressed, one might relent and deign to admit it signifies a dove."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "Thanks, but I'd better shop and back on the Hunt."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь, голубе."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I've been meaning to ask: why do you call me \"culver\"?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Oh. You've been patronizing me."
msgstr "Ох. Ти мене підколюєш."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "...I've taken down {name_multiple.rot_boss}, you know."
msgstr "...Я вже не раз перемагав {2:{name_multiple.rot_boss}}, ти це знаєш."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "I'm leaving now."
msgstr "Я вже йду."

#: Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_culver_nickname_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Oh, one more thing. What even <i>is</> a \"culver\"?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" HEAVENSSS, no.\n"
" !point\n"
" Don't lump me in with the rabble that hangs around these woods!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>I</> went to businesss ssschool."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"О, НЕБЕСCCА, ні.\n"
"!point\n"
"Не рівняйте мене до того наброду, що тиняється цими лісами!\n"
"!gesture\n"
"<i>Я</> вчився у бізнеccс-школі."

#: Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" And you still don't!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"І ви досі не знаєте!"

#: Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I was wondering... do you live out here?"
msgstr "Я хотів запитати... ти живеш тут?"

#: Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_do_you_live_here_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "I didn't know you had a degree."
msgstr "Я не знав, що у тебе є диплом."

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Often enough to inspire me, I suppose."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 'Tis not swords and sworcery alone that may fell a <#RED>{name.rot}</>, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> hath <i>very</> skilled impressions. A defenseless baby... an arrogant elderly person...\n"
" !wink\n"
" ...a sobbing novice Hunter, perhaps?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" She throws her voice, luring the <#RED>{name.rot}</> into my sights, and BAM!\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> art easy to fool."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "Intrepid! Excuse me, I think I'll get back to browsing."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь, голубе."

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "{name.npc_market_merchant}, how ofted do you run into {name_multiple.rot} out here?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_encounter_rots_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "You're not a Hunter, so how is it that you and {name.shop_magpie} aren't {name.rot}-food?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_explain_shipping1_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_explain_shipping1_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Shy are we? I vow not to look whilst thou art changing... \n"
" !wink\n"
" I jest. My associate <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> doth provide a delivery service, free of charge.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Simply choose \"<#RED>Ship</>\" when you purchase any Chateau d'Alphonse-exclusive piece.\n"
" !point\n"
" It shall be uponst your <#RED>Armour Rack</> by the time you returnst home.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Whereupon you can disrobe in whatever company you prefer. \n"
" !wink\n"
" Didst thou see my wink? I art being coy, little culver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_explain_shipping1_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_explain_shipping1_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Yeah, hi. Question: what happens if I don't wear what I buy straightaway?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_explain_shipping2_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_explain_shipping2_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ...It's <i>simple</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Just choose \"<#RED>Ship</>\" whenst you buy a piece.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}'ll</> ensure it's waiting on your <#RED>Armour Rack</> once you returnst home.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Now ship or get off the pot."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_explain_shipping2_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_explain_shipping2_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Canst thou--argh, now <i>I'm</> doing it. Can you remind me how shipping works?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Caa-caa-caa-caa.</>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <z 0.8>Kwee chwee quaw quaw. Queep.</>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Каа-каа-каа-каа.</>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <z 0.8>кві чвіі кву кву. Квіп.</>"

#: Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Kwee quee!</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Квіі кві!</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Alright, alright, I get it, I failed.\n"
"No need to rub it in."
msgstr "Добре, добре, я зрозумів, я не впорався.\n"
"Не треба це підкреслювати."

#: Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_failed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "I'll beat your challenge next time!"
msgstr "Наступного разу я виконаю твоє випробування!"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Quee, quee quee!</>\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Caa-caa-caa-caa.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Кві, кві кві!</>\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Каа-каа-каа-каа.</>"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Quaw, quaw.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Caa-caa-caa-caa.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Кву, кву.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Каа-каа-каа-каа.</>"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" <z 0.8>Queep!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" <z 0.8>Квіп!</>"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Oh, um. Nice to meet you too?"
msgstr "О, гм. Мені теж приємно познайомитися з тобою?"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_END"
msgid "Yeah. Err. See you around!"
msgstr "Так. Емм... Побачимося!"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "<i>What did you just say to me?</i>"
msgstr "<i>Що ти щойно сказала?</i>"

#: Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_first_meeting_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B_END"
msgid "Sorry, I musta misheard. See you around?"
msgstr "Вибач, я, мабуть, не розчув. Ще побачимося?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Yes, yes, <i>everyone</> likes my face."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Так, так, <i>усім</> подобається моє обличчя."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Could it be... a little birdie told me you were coming?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Um... I hath eyes."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Гм... У мене є очі."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" But you doth not already have a <i>me,</> little culver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I offer luxurious, hand-forged pieces of exclusive <#RED>Armour</> and <#RED>Weapons</>, both.\n"
" !point\n"
" And before you ask: all my materials are sourced--semi-ethically--from the local region's <#RED>{name.rot}</> populations. \n"
" !agree\n"
" So do expect my stock to change should we meet again in another land."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>? Ohh, y'know, odds and ends.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" <#RED>Potions</>, <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>, anything she finds lying about that's shiny, verily.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" She's quite proud of her collection.\n"
" !neutral"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.shop_magpie}</>? Ох, ви ж знаєте, різне дріб'язкове.\n"
" !neutral\n"
"!eyeroll\n"
" <#RED>Зілля</>, <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>, все, що вона знаходить на підлозі і що блищить, чесно кажучи.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Вона дуже пишається своєю колекцією.\n"
" !neutral"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "I'll look around. Thanks."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_ALT"
msgid "Okay, thanks. I'll take a look around."
msgstr "Гаразд, дякую. Я оглянуся."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Always nice to see a friendly face out here."
msgstr "Завжди приємно бачити тут знайоме обличчя."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "You always seem to be waiting for me..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Uh, wow. I'm flattered? But what makes you think I'm in the market?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_ALT"
msgid "Why do you think I'm in the market for gear?"
msgstr "Чому ти думаєш, що я шукаю спорядження?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "But the {name_multiple.foxtails} already have an {name.job_armorsmith}, and a {name.job_blacksmith}."
msgstr "Але {Name_multiple.foxtails} вже мають {3:{name.job_armorsmith}} і {2:{name.job_blacksmith}}."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Well, what sort of gear do you sell?"
msgstr "Яке спорядження ти продаєш?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "What's the bird sell?"
msgstr "Що продає птах?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wink\n"
" 'Tis time for a proper introduction.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The name's <#BLUE>{name.shop_armorsmith}</>. Yes. THE <#BLUE>{name.shop_armorsmith}</>.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7>...hold for applause...</>\n"
" !agree\n"
" And I am quite pleased to inform you:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The latest season's |<i>CHATEAU d'ALPHONSE</>|collection is HERE!\n"
" !point\n"
" And you--yes, YOU!--shall be permitted to gaze uponst it, purchase fromst it, and display it uponst thine very body!\n"
" <i><z 0.7>All sales art final. Wash only in a stream burbling through a glade frolicked by faeries singing a song in a forgotten tongue.</></> \n"
" <i><z 0.7>But if thou art not privy to such a glade, dry cleaning would honestly be just fine.</></>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7>...hold for applause...</>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You art welcome."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoyyy, culver.\n"
" !happy"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь, голубе.\n"
" !happy"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" --Now, you seem like someone who could use a bit of a pick-me-up. A refreshing <i>punch</i> of vim and vigour! A bit of insurance, you might say, in an unsssure w--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!dubious\n"
"...Тепер ви виглядаєте тим, кому знадобиться трохи підбадьоритися. Освіжаючий <i>поштовх</i> енергії та бадьорості! Трохи страховки, можна сказати, в невизначеному місці..."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Why, forgive my manners!\n"
" !clap\n"
" The name's <#BLUE>{name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>, illussstrious post-apocalypse entrepreneur, ssscholar of medicine and beloved young heir to the {name.npc_doc_lastname} family fortune!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" At your mid-hunt convenience."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ай-ай-ай, вибачте за мої манери!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Мене звати <#BLUE>{Name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>, видатний підприємець після апокаліпсису, вчений-медик і улюблений юний спадкоємець родини {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Зручно для вас під час полювання."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" My, what a dissscerning eye you have! Why yes, my good chum!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Allow me to introduce you to my patented {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health Potion</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!shocked\n"
"О, який у вас споссстережливий погляд! Так, мій любий друже!\n"
"!clap\n"
"Дозвольте представити вам моє запатентоване <#RED>зілля здоров'я</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" --Now, you seem like a savvy <#BLUE>{player.species}</> who could use a bit of a pick-me-up. A refreshing <i>punch</i> of vim and vigour... a bit of, err...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Now wait just a moment!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>I barely sssmell any <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> on you</i>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Що ж, здається, ви розумний <#BLUE>{player.species}</>, якому може знадобитися трохи підбадьоритися. Освіжаючий <i>удар</ i> енергії та бадьорості... трохи, е-е...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Зачекайте хвилинку!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>Я ледве відчуваю <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> на тобі</i>."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2"
msgid "!think\n"
" My, what an awkward predicament we find ourselvesss in!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I can't show you the wonder of my {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</> without appropriate compensssation!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sssuch is the fickle nature of the market, I suppose.\n"
" !point\n"
" Do come back for a <#RED>{name.potion}</> when you have <#KONJUR><p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {name.konjur}</>, won't you?"
msgstr "!think\n"
" Жах, у якому незручному становищі ми опинилися!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я не можу показати вам чудеса моїх <#RED>лікувальних зіллів</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname} без належної компенсації!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Такааа непостійна природа ринку, як би там не було.\n"
" !point\n"
" Повернетесь за <#RED>{name.potion}м</>, коли матимете <#KONJUR><p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> {konjur_cost} {2:{name.konjur}}</>, чи не так?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ta-ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!greet\n"
"Па-па!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Agreed!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!greet\n"
"Згода!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Woah, hold on a sec. Who are--"
msgstr "Вау, зачекай секундочку. Хто..."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "--SORRY! To interrupt. Who <i>are</i> you?"
msgstr "...ВИБАЧ! Що перервав. Хто ти <i>такий</i>?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "--Skip the pitch. Are those {name_multiple.potion}?"
msgstr "...Досить переконань. Це {name_multiple.potion}?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Woah, hold on a sec. Who are--"
msgstr "Вау, зачекай секундочку. Хто..."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "Oh, yeah. I'm a bit broke right now."
msgstr "О, так. Зараз я трохи розбитий."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "Yeah? So?"
msgstr "Так? І що?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "Okay, sorry about that. See ya!"
msgstr "Добре, вибач за це. Побачимось!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "Well that was a waste of time."
msgstr "Ну, це була марна трата часу."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" One sip with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>'s guaranteed to <#RED>Heal</> your woundsss, clear your skin, and leave your breath minty fresh for that <i>ssspecial someone</i> back home.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] And all for only a modessst sum of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!agree\n"
"Один ковток натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK> і воно гарантовано <#RED>зцілить</> ваші рани, очистить шкіру і залишить свіже дихання для когось <i>особливого</i> вдома.\n"
"!shocked\n"
"[recipe:admission_recipe] І все це лише за скромну суму <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</>!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !notebook_stop\n"
" A Hunter, huh? Interesting.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'm a <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>. The name's {name.npc_konjurist}.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wait a minute... have you been <i>consuming</> <#RED>Teffra Crystals</>?!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !notebook_stop\n"
" Мисливець, так? Цікаво.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>. Мене звати {Name.npc_konjurist}.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Постривайте... ви що, <i>споживали</> <#RED>кристали конжуру</>?!"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" <i>Fascinating</i>. I wonder...\n"
" !point\n"
" Wanna try a little experiment? With my <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist} Equipment</>, I could <#RED>Upgrade</> one of your <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'd be very interested in seeing the results."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" <i>Цікаво</i>. Я думаю...\n"
" !point\n"
" Хочете провести невеликий експеримент? За допомогою <#KONJUR>обладнання {2:{name.job_konjurist}}</> я можу <#RED>покращити</> ваші <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>, але тільки одну.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Мені було б дуже цікаво побачити результати."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Weeelllll... Look. It takes some <#KONJUR>Teffra</> to <#RED>Upgrade</> <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I don't mind using a <i>bit</> of my own supply for the sake of research, but if you want more than one <#RED>Upgrade</>, you'll have to chip in.\n"
" !point\n"
" The bigger the <#RED>Upgrade</>, the more <#KONJUR>Teffra</> it's gonna take.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" What do you say, Hunter?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Нууу... Слухайте. Для <#RED>покращення</> <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> потрібно трохи <#KONJUR>конжуру</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я не проти використати <i>трохи</> власних запасів заради дослідження, але якщо хочете більше одного <#RED>покращення</>, доведеться докинути.\n"
" !point\n"
" Чим краще <#RED>покращення</>, тим більше <#KONJUR>конжуру</> знадобиться.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" То як, Мисливцю?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm a Hunter. Who are you?"
msgstr "Я Мисливець. А ти хто?"

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "You mean the crystals that give me powers? Sure have."
msgstr "Ти про кристали, що дають мені сили? Так, звісно."

#: Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_firstmeeting_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Only one? Can't you upgrade more?"
msgstr "Тільки одну? Хіба ти не можеш покращити більше?"

#: Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wow. That's surprisingly insightful. For a Hunter from the <#RED>Brinks</>, anyway.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Yeah. <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> state changes are all shifted down the temperature scale compared to, say, regular water.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Woah. I hadn't thought of it before, but <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> might have uses as an antifreeze additive in industrial machinery.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Gotta write that down."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ого. Це несподівано прозорливе зауваження. Як для Мисливця з <#RED>Брінкс</>, у всякому разі.\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Так. Зміни стану <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> зміщені по температурній шкалі вниз, порівняно, скажімо, зі звичайною водою.\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Ого. Раніше я не замислювався про це, але <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> можна застосувати як антифриз у промислових машинах.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Треба це записати."

#: Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" See ya."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Побачимось."

#: Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I've seen {name.konjur} as a gas before."
msgstr "Я бачив {name.konjur} у газоподібному стані."

#: Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_freezing_temp_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "'Kay, I'm gettin' cold. Gonna keep moving."
msgstr "Гаразд, я замерзаю. Піду далі."

#: Convo.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RAISED_PRICE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RAISED_PRICE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I say! What's with that tone? Do you know how dangerousss this place has gotten?\n"
" !angry\n"
" I'm out here risking life and <z 0.7><i>metaphorical</i></> limb, all to provide my dear cussstomers with high quality {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand products!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And all I ask in return is a measssly bit of extra {name.c_konjur} for my troubles.\n"
" player:\n"
" Well, I guess when you put it that way...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'll happily accept your apology in the form of a purchase."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Слухайте! Що це за тон? Ви взагалі розумієте, нассскільки небезпечним стало це місце?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Я тут ризикую життям і <z 0.7><i>метафоричними</i></> кінцівками, лише щоб поссставляти моїм дорогим клієнтам продукцію під маркою {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" І все, чого я прошу взамін — це малесссенька дрібка додаткового {2:{name.c_konjur}} за мої старання.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ну, якщо вже так сказати...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я із задоволенням прийму ваші вибачення у вигляді покупки."

#: Convo.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RAISED_PRICE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_frenzy_price_increase_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RAISED_PRICE"
msgid "Am I imagining things, or did the price of your {name_multiple.potion} go up?"
msgstr "Мені здалося, чи ціна на твої {name_multiple.potion} зросла?"

#: Convo.dgn_grove_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_grove_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Your whirlybird is very conspicuous, my friend!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And you know what they say--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Location, location, location!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ваша пташка дуже помітна, мій друже!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" І знаєте, як кажуть...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Пошук, пошук, пошук!"

#: Convo.dgn_grove_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_grove_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How'd you find this grove anyway?"
msgstr "Як ти знайшов цю галявину?"

