#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.OPT_NEXT_TIME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.OPT_NEXT_TIME"
msgid "You got it!"
msgstr "У тебе вийде!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CHAT_ONLY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT0.chat_only.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CHAT_ONLY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" He! He! He!\n"
" I came across something interesting!\n"
" !point\n"
" Let me know if you come across something interesting!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Хе! Хе! Хе!\n"
" Я натрапив на дещо цікаве!\n"
" !point\n"
" Дайте знати, якщо знайдете щось цікаве!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.OPT_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.OPT_EXIT"
msgid "...Yep."
msgstr "...Так."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT1.done.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He!\n"
" 'til we meet!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!clap\n"
"Хе! Хе! Хе!\n"
"До нових зустрічей!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_BOMB_GAME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT10.bomb_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_BOMB_GAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [BOMB_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Dodge a series of flying explosives.\n"
" TIP: When getting knocked down, tap <#RED>Dodge</> just as you hit the ground to <#RED>Quick Rise</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [BOMB_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ухиляйтеся від серії летючих вибухівок.\n"
" ПОРАДА: Коли вас збивають з ніг, клацніть <#RED>ухилення</> в той момент, коли ви торкаєтесь землі, щоб <#RED>швидко піднятися</>!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DODGE_GAME
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT11.dodge_game.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DODGE_GAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DODGE_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Run through a field of <#RED>Spike Traps</> without getting hit.\n"
" TIP: You can't be hit at the start of a <#RED>Dodge</>. Keep moving!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DODGE_GAME]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Пробіжіть через поле <#RED>Колосових рослин</>, не отримавши пошкоджень.\n"
" ПІДКАЗКА: Вас не можуть атакувати в самому початку <#RED>ухиляння</>. Рухайтесь!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DPS_CHECK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT12.dps_check.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DPS_CHECK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [DPS_CHECK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Deal a lot of <#RED>Damage</> to one target within a time limit.\n"
" TIP: Find an attack pattern that deals the most <#RED>Damage</> possible!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"[DPS_CHECK]\n"
"!clap\n"
"Нанесіть багато <#RED>{2:{name.concept_damage}}</> одній цілі протягом обмеження часу.\n"
"ПОРАДКА: знайдіть тип атаки, яка завдає найбільш можливий <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</>!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HIT_STREAK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT13.hit_streak.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HIT_STREAK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [HIT_STREAK]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Get a high <#RED>Hit Streak</> by attacking a pair of alternating dummies.\n"
" TIP: Focus on the timing and choose the right time to switch sides!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"[HIT_STREAK]\n"
"!clap\n"
"Отримайте високу <#RED>серію влучань</>, атакуючи пару манекенів, що чергуються.\n"
"ПІДКАЗКА: Зосередьтеся на часі та виберіть правильний час для зміни сторони!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.TALK_MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT14.mini_cabbage_swarm.giver.STATE_0.TALK_MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Kill as many tiny <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</> as possible. Lose points when you get hit.\n"
" TIP: You can't be hit at the start of a <#RED>Dodge</>. Keep moving!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [MINI_CABBAGE_SWARM]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Убийте якомога більше крихітних <#RED>{2:{Name_multiple.cabbageroll}}</>. Втрачайте очки, коли вас вдарять.\n"
" ПІДКАЗКА: Вас не можуть атакувати на самому початку <#RED>ухиляння</>. Рухайтесь!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr "Ні в якому разі!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_HEADS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_HEADS"
msgid "Heads."
msgstr "Голови."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_TAILS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.OPT_TAILS"
msgid "Tails."
msgstr "Хвости."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.TALK_COIN_FLIP_MAX_HEALTH_OR_DAMAGE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT2.coin_flip_max_health_or_damage.giver.STATE_0.TALK_COIN_FLIP_MAX_HEALTH_OR_DAMAGE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" He! He! He! Care to flip a coin?\n"
" Call it right, I'll help you out.\n"
" If not, I'll have to help your enemies! He! He! He!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" Хе! Хе! Хе! Хочеш підкинути монету?\n"
" Вгадаєш, я тобі допоможу.\n"
" Якщо ні, мені доведеться допомогти твоїм ворогам! Хе! Хе! Хе!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Ooh! Free gift!"
msgstr "Оох! Безплатний подарунок!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "Uh, I'll pass, thanks."
msgstr "Ум, я піду, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_EPIC
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT3.free_power_epic.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_EPIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm!\n"
" We live inside a dream.\n"
" !point\n"
" But who is dreaming?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And who is dreaming the dream <i>they're</> in? He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * He extends a hand. In it, a gift gleams."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Хм!\n"
" Ми живемо уві сні.\n"
" !point\n"
" Але хто його бачить?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" І хто бачить сон, у якому <i>він</> є? Хе! Хе! Хе!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * Він простягає руку. У ній виблискує дарунок."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Thanks, I think?"
msgstr "Дякую, напевно?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "Uh, no?"
msgstr "Гей, ні?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_LEGENDARY
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT4.free_power_legendary.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FREE_POWER_LEGENDARY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Craving craves only to crave!\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you want?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What you want?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * He extends a hand. In it, a gift offered."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Жага жадає лише жадати!\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви хочете?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Того, чого хочете?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * Він простягає руку. У ній - запропонований дарунок."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Yes..."
msgstr "Так..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No."
msgstr "Ні."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT5.potion_refill.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Temperance!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I knew a thirsty ghost who carried an infinite potion.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Her throat was swollen, and she could never drink enough.\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you thirst?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Спокійно!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я знав спраглого привида, який ніс нескінченне зілля.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Її горло розпухло, і вона ніколи не могла випити достатньо.\n"
" !think\n"
" Ти відчуваєш спрагу?"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> Sure..."
msgstr "<#RED>[Вибрати {2:{name.concept_relic}}...]</> Звісно..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.TALK_LOSE_POWER_GAIN_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT6.lose_power_gain_health.giver.STATE_0.TALK_LOSE_POWER_GAIN_HEALTH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He! I've got an idea!\n"
" Give me a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> of yours...\n"
" !think\n"
" And I'll give you some <#RED>Health</> of mine! He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Choose and lose a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> to gain <#RED>Health</>, depending on its <#RED>Rarity</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Хе! Хе! Хе! У мене є ідея!\n"
" Дайте мені <#RED>{2:{name.concept_relic}}</>...\n"
" !think\n"
" А я дам вам трохи <#RED>здоров'я</>! Хе! Хе! Хе!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Виберіть і втратьте <#RED>{2:{name.concept_relic}}</>, щоб отримати <#RED>здоров'я</> залежно від її <#RED>рідкості</>."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Select a {name.concept_relic}...]</> Sure..."
msgstr "<#RED>[Вибрати {2:{name.concept_relic}}...]</> Звісно..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_TRANSMUTE_POWER
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT7.transmute_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_TRANSMUTE_POWER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" He! He! He! Transmutation!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Transmutation! Transmutation! Transmutation!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lead into gold! What do you say?\n"
" !think\n"
" Choose and lose a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</>. But gain a random <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> of one <#RED>Rarity</> higher."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Хе! Хе! Хе! Трансмутація!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Трансмутація! Трансмутація! Трансмутація!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Свинець у золото! Що скажете?\n"
" Виберіть і втратьте <#RED>{2:{name.concept_relic}}</>. Але отримайте випадкову <#RED>{2:{name.concept_relic}}</> на одну <#RED>рідкість</> вище."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "Yeesh. But okay..."
msgstr "Ну гаразд..."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr "Ні в якому разі!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_UPGRADE_RANDOM_POWER
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT8.upgrade_random_power.giver.STATE_0.TALK_UPGRADE_RANDOM_POWER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" He! He! He! I'm feeling generous!\n"
" I'll <#RED>Upgrade A Random {name.concept_relic}</> for free.\n"
" !think\n"
" All it will cost is a slice of your finger! He! He! He!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Accept: Random <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> upgrade. <#RED>Take 250 Damage</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Хе! Хе! Хе! Я відчуваю себе щедрим!\n"
" Я безплатно <#RED>покращу випадкову {2:{name.concept_relic}}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Це коштуватиме, — шматок вашого пальця! ! Хе! Хе! Хе!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Прийняти: випадкова <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> покращиться. <#RED>Отримаєте 250 шкоди</>."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_ACCEPT"
msgid "<#RED>[Start Minigame]</> Let's go!"
msgstr "<#RED>[Почати міні гру]</> Починай!"

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.OPT_BACK"
msgid "No thanks."
msgstr "Ні, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.TALK_EVENT_PROTOTYPE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_mystery.ATTRACT9.event_prototype.giver.STATE_0.TALK_EVENT_PROTOTYPE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's prototype an event!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Start?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Створімо прототип події!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Починаємо?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"And whatever.\" Feh!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'll have you know I maketh my pieces from <i>locally</>-sourced monsters, and this locale is home to some particularly robust <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Why, I had to develop an entirely new forging technique to work their materials--and the result? \n"
" !wink\n"
" Only the most <i>majestically</> powerful gear thou hast ever laid eyes on. Very avant-garde--\"and whatever\"--hm?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(*sputter*)</> My <i>\"bangs\"?!</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" First of all, I doth not have <i>\"bangs\"</>, I hath a... a <i>cascade</> of silky locks that crasheth roguishly upon mine chiseled visage.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Second, I was talking about my new works of art. <i>Obviously.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Then I guess you'll have to come findeth me again over there."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" No."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Ні."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>No!</i>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>Ні!</i>"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" ... Fine.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmmm... Yep, I art <i>definitely</i> looking. This is me, \"looking in the back\". O! What a fine back it is, and...\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" No, we don't have it. Now begone."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ANNOYING_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ANNOYING_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !angry\n"
" \"Call around\"?! I am the ONLY store--!!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Thou art joking. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> <z 0.7>How I loathe interacting with the clientele.</z>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EARLY_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EARLY_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Make sure to tell your Hunter friends about me once thou returnst home."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Не забудьте розповісти своїм друзям-мисливцям про мене, як тільки повернетеся додому."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LATE_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LATE_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh. What a relief it is to have that settled. Hurrah.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Thou art free to continue browsing now, little culver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Hm... Same condescending look... Oh! Your stock's all different and whatever!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ALT"
msgid "Hey, you're right! Your stock's totally different and whatever!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Um... did you trim your own bangs?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Er, but I wanted something you had at the old market."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Can't you look in the back to see if you have it?"
msgstr "Хіба ти не можеш зазирнути назад і подивитись, чи є це у тебе?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "Pleeeeease?"
msgstr "Будь ла-а-а-а-а-а-аска?"

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5"
msgid "C'moonnn..."
msgstr "Давайте..."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ANNOYING_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ANNOYING_END"
msgid "Could you call around to other stores?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_END"
msgid "Okay. Good to know."
msgstr "Добре. Корисно знати."

#: Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LATE_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_new_biome_meeting_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LATE_END"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr "Добре."

#: Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ugh! Do I look like a bedraggled bard, hat upturnt, kicked-in concertina slung o'er my shoulder? \n"
" player:\n"
" I'm not sure what any of that meant, but the vibe is \"no\". \n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I. Do. Not. Take. <i>Requests.</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" I am a visionary! A luminary! A... A biggeth deal!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And thou art lucky to hath the <i>opportunity</> to even glance at my original works.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Fortunately for you I am also merciful, so I shall allow you to purchase said works, despite the insultations."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Hey, 'Phonsey, can I put in orders for specific items?"
msgstr "Привіт, Фонсі, можна замовити конкретні товари?"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Sssplendid, sssplendid!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then without further ado, allow me to introduce you to my patented {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" One sip with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>'s guaranteed to <#RED>Heal</> your woundsss, clear your skin, and leave your breath minty fresh for that <i>ssspecial someone</i> back home.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] This veritable panacea <#RED>Health {name.potion}</> can be <i>yours</i> for only a modessst sum of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Блиссскуче, блиссскуче!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Тоді без зайвих слів, дозвольте представити вам моє патентоване <#RED>{name.potion} здоров'я</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Один ковток <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK> гарантовано <#RED>зцілить</> ваші рани, очистить вашу шкіру і залишить ваше дихання м'ятно-свіжим для <i>когось осссобливого</i> вдома.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] Ця справжня панацея, <#RED>{name.potion} здоров'я</> може бути <i>вашим</i> лише за помірну суму <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</>!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Why, forgive my manners!\n"
" !clap\n"
" The name's <#BLUE>{name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>, illussstrious post-apocalypse entrepreneur, ssscholar of medicine, and beloved young heir to the {name.npc_doc_lastname} family fortune!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] At your mid-hunt convenience."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ай-ай-ай, вибачте за мої манери!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Мене звати <#BLUE>{Name.npc_potionmaker_dungeon}</>, видатний підприємець після апокаліпсису, вчений-медик і улюблений юний спадкоємець родини {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] Зручно для вас під час полювання."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Now hold on just a sssecond there!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'll let you in on a little secret. These woods are <i>danger</i>-ous.\n"
" !think\n"
" I'd hate to see fine folks like yourself in a pinch... so what sssay you buy one of these <#RED>Potions</> for the road, hm?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Зачекайте сссекунду!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я відкрию вам маленький секрет. Ці ліси <i>небезпечні</i>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Я б не хотів, щоб такі як ви опинилися в скрутному становищі... То що ви ссскажете про купівлю одного з цих <#RED>зіллів</> в дорогу, га?"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha-ha! You had me on the ropes, but I knew from the start you were a smart <#BLUE>{player.species}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Enjoy your {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}</>, and may we deal again soon!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ха-ха! Ви майже мене впіймали, але я з самого початку знав, що ви розумний <#BLUE>{player.species}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь своїм <#RED>лікувальним {name.potion}м</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}, і можливо, ми ще знову зустрінемося!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HAS_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" A tough customer. I <i>do</i> love a challenge.\n"
" !greet\n"
" Well, fair play, my friend. I'll get you next time!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"Важкий клієнт. Я <i>дуже</i> люблю виклики.\n"
"!greet\n"
"Що ж, чесна гра, мій друже. Наступного разу я вас впіймаю!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>--Now,</i> as I was sssaying last time, you seem like one savvy <#BLUE>{player.species}</> who could--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>Hold your horses!</i> Did you just say you're ssstill broke?\n"
" !angry\n"
" How'sss that even possible?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Err, I mean, no hard feelings. Why don't you go give some monsters the what-for, then come back in a flash with some cold hard (actually gooey) <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" My gen-u-ine <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</> will be waiting!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>...Тепер,</i> як я казав минулого разу, ви виглядаєте як кмітливий <#BLUE>{player.species}</>, який міг би...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>Постривайте!</i> Ви щойно сказали, що всссе ще на мілині?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Як це взагалі можливо?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Е-е, я мав на увазі, без образ. Чому б вам не піти й не надавати монстрам прочуханки, а тоді повернутися з (насправді липкий) <#KONJUR>{3:{name.i_konjur}}</>?\n"
" !agree\n"
" Мої справжні <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</> будуть чекати на вас!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_RESOURCES_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ta-ta!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>(Good grief.)</z>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Та-та!\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>(Благословляю.)</z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" --Now, as I was sssaying last time, you seem like a savvy <#BLUE>{player.species}</> who could--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" WAIT! You already have a <#RED>{name.potion}</>?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Bouncing <#RED>{name_multiple.cabbageroll}</> on a pogo stick, this just won't do!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I can't sell you my <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</> if you have nothing to carry them in."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Тепер, як я говорив минулого разу, ви здається розумний <#BLUE>{player.species}</>, хто може...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ПОЧЕКАЙТЕ! У вас вже є <#RED>{name.potion}</>?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Підкидати <#RED>{Name_multiple.cabbageroll}</> на палиці-поприщі, це просто не підходить!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я не можу продати вам свої <#RED>{name_multiple.potion}</>, якщо у вас немає в чому їх нести."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1_MISSING_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_1_MISSING_HEALTH"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" Tell you what, why don't you take a moment to empty that flask of yours out with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>?\n"
" !clap\n"
" Then I can top you up with some bonafide {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health Potion</> instead!"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
"Скажу вам більше, чому б вам не спорожнити цю флягу натиснувши <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK>?\n"
"!clap\n"
"Потім я зможу заповнити її справжнім <#RED>Зіллям здоров'я</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2A"
msgid "Most certainly!"
msgstr "Безперечно!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2B"
msgid "Don't think <i>too</i> long now! It's bad for your health!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" I'm counting on it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!greet\n"
"Я на це розраховую!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Yeah! And I have funds this time."
msgstr "Так! Цього разу у мене є кошти."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "Why should I buy your {name_multiple.potion}? I don't even know you."
msgstr "Чому я маю купувати твої {name_multiple.potion}? Я навіть не знаю тебе."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "I think I'll pass, thanks."
msgstr "Думаю, я піду, дякую."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3A"
msgid "Fine, you talked me into it."
msgstr "Добре, ти вмовив мене на це."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HAS_RESOURCES_3B"
msgid "No, I'm really okay."
msgstr "Ні, я дійсно в порядку."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_1"
msgid "Err, yeah, but I'm still a bit low on {name.i_konjur}."
msgstr "Е-е, так, але мені все ще трохи не вистачає {2:{name.i_konjur}}."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2A"
msgid "Okay! I'll go bash some {name_multiple.rot}!"
msgstr "Добре! Я піду поб'ю трохи {2:{name_multiple.rot}}!"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_RESOURCES_2B"
msgid "Eh, we'll see how I do."
msgstr "Ех, побачимо, як я вчиню."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_1"
msgid "Err, yeah, but I have a {name.potion} already."
msgstr "Еее, так, але я вже маю {name.potion}."

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2A"
msgid "Wowee! Thanks!\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "Ого! Дякую!\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Зілля вже повне)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2B"
msgid "Lemme think it over.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "Дайте мені подумати.\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Зілля вже повне)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_secondmeeting_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_NO_SPACE_2_FULL_HEALTH"
msgid "Err, sorry. Catch ya next time?\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Potion already full)</></i></z>"
msgstr "Оуу, вибач. Зустрінемось наступного разу?\n"
"<i><#RED><z 0.7>(Зілля вже повне)</></i></z>"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" \"Another\"--?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I don't know if you hath noticed, but there is no \"another\" like <i>me.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Mayhaps if thou <i>describe</> this hobbyist... ? \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Even though I hardly hath time to pay heed to mere <i>window-shoppers</> passing through."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Didst thou say--\n"
" !cough\n"
" --hair in a \"bun\"? UGH. Who would gaze upon such an outdated hair arrangement? Not I. Surely.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Now, if you'll excuse me. I have cultures to revolutionize."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Oh, I always try, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" О, я завжди стараюся, голубе."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm looking for my missing crew--have you seen another Armoursmith out here?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Well... she's a {name.species_ogre} with red hair in a bun, goes by {name.npc_armorsmith}--"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Forget it. I don't think you could've been less helpful if you'd tried."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Missing crew? I hope they're Hunters like you, or they're not gonna last long out here.\n"
" !think\n"
" Come to think of it, I did spot some footprints a little while ago.\n"
" !point\n"
" They were headed deeper into the forest."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Зникла команда? Сподіваюся, вони такі ж Мисливці, як і ви, інакше їм тут довго не протриматися.\n"
" !think\n"
" Але, якщо задуматися, я бачив кілька слідів деякий час тому.\n"
" !point\n"
" Вони вели глибше в ліс."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I'd be quick about finding them if I were you...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" They're gonna run right into the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> if they keep heading that way."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Я б не зволікав з їхнім пошуком, якби був на вашому місці...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Вони прямо на шляху до <#RED>{2:{Name.megatreemon}}</>, якщо продовжать рухатися туди."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm looking for my missing crew-- have you seen anyone else out here?"
msgstr "Я шукаю свою зниклу команду... ти бачив тут ще когось?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Thanks!"
msgstr "Дякую!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hath we not been over this, my little culver? Unless they art a patron...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I. Doth. Not. Care."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Хіба ми не обговорювали це, мій маленький голубе? Якщо вони не клієнти...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Мені. Все. Одно."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" No. It wasn't."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Ні. Це не так."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Mm. I recall a gentlecat of the sort padding through <i>le Chateau d'Alphonse</> most recent...\n"
" !wink\n"
" Try as I might, the brute could not be coerced onto my leash. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" You should find him elsewhere, mayhaps closeby, mayhaps not. \n"
" !greet\n"
" See you soon, culver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm still looking for a member of my crew. Have you seen another Blacksmith out here?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "<i>(sigh)</> It was worth a try."
msgstr "<i>(зітхає)</> Варто було спробувати."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "He's a {name.species_canine}, distinctive shoulder tattoo, steel collar..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sorry, I just got here a little while ago. Haven't seen anyone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Did you find your other friend... in one piece?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Вибачте, я тут нещодавно. Нікого не бачив.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви знайшли свою подругу... цілою та неушкодженою?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well that's a load off my mind.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I hate running into corpses."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ну, це велике полегшення.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ненавиджу натрапляти на трупи."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I'm still looking for a member of my crew. Have you seen them?"
msgstr "Я все ще шукаю члена своєї команди. Ти його не бачив?"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_blacksmith_powerupgrade.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "I did. She's safe at our camp."
msgstr "Так. Вона в безпеці в нашому таборі."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!greet\n"
"Дякую!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Thank you!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Well, I'm afraid I haven't ssseen or heard anything.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Good luck on your search my friend!\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ta!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!clap\n"
"Дякую!\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Ну, боюся, я нічого не бачив і не чув.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Удачі вам у пошуках, друже!\n"
"!greet\n"
"Дякую!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" That's your choice, no harm no foul!\n"
" !point\n"
" Good luck on your sssearch, kid!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Це ваш вибір, без шкоди для здоров'я!\n"
"!point\n"
"Удачі у пошуках, друже!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ARMOURSMITH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_ARMOURSMITH"
msgid "Actually, have you seen our {name.job_armorsmith}? She's lost somewhere in these woods!"
msgstr "До речі, ти бачили нашого {3:{name.job_armorsmith}}? Вона загубилася десь у цих лісах!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_BLACKSMITH
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_BLACKSMITH"
msgid "Actually, have you seen our {name.job_blacksmith}? He's lost somewhere in these woods!"
msgstr "До речі, ти бачили нашого {2:{name.job_blacksmith}}? Він загубився десь у цих лісах!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_TWOFRIENDS
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A_TWOFRIENDS"
msgid "Hey-- Have you seen our {name.job_blacksmith} and {name.job_armorsmith}? They're lost in these woods!"
msgstr "Гей... Ти бачив нашого {3:{name.job_blacksmith}} і {2:{name.job_armorsmith}}? Вони загубилися в цих лісах!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Hm. Well, see you around, {name.npc_doc_firstname}."
msgstr "Хм. Що ж, побачимося, {name.npc_doc_firstname}."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "<#RED>[<p img='images/hud_images/hud_konjur_drops_currency.tex'> 2 {name.konjur}]</> Uh, okay... Here you go."
