" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:admission_recipe] Лише жменька <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</> за раз!"

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_RESOURCES
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_RESOURCES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But you don't have enough <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Але у вас недостатньо <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</>."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_SPACE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2_NO_SPACE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But your flask's still full. I'm afraid this is a bring-your-own container sort of operation.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I care deeply about the environment, you know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Але ваша фляга ще повна. Боюся, що це операція типу \"принеси свій контейнер\".\n"
" !agree\n"
" Знаєте, я дуже дбаю про навколишнє середовище."

#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_potion.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" My word! How terrible! Truly awful!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [recipe:hoggins_tip_recipe] For a sssmall fee, I'd be happy to tell you everything I know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Боже мій! Який жах! Справді жахливо!\n"
"!happy\n"
"!agree\n"
" [recipe:hoggins_tip_recipe] За невелику плату я буду радий розповісти вам все, що знаю."

#: Convo.dgn_shop_powerupgrade.HUB0.shop.giver.STATE_0.OPT_UPGRADE
