#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I beat another one of your challenges, {name.shop_magpie}!"
msgstr "Я пройшов ще одне твоє випробування, {name.shop_magpie}!"

#: Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_succeed_generic_magpie.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "Haha. Thanks for opening the chest, bud.\n"
"See ya next time!"
msgstr "Ха-ха. Дякую, що відкрила скриню, крихітка.\n"
"Побачимося наступного разу!"

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Good. Than canst thou report to me if she sayeth anything about mine...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...about mine <z 0.7>hair thinnery?</>\n"
" player:\n"
" \"Hair...thinnery\"? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Keepeth it down! I hath a reputation to uphold. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> told me that upon a recent landing, she espied the top of my head...\n"
" !angry\n"
" And that false feathered fiend said my famously lushious locks were... <z 0.7>thinning!</> Revealing more of my.... <z 0.7>bare pate!</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" This is of course libelous slander and I shall not have it spreading about willy and, god forbid, nilly."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ch-check <i>what?</> Bwe-heu-heu! I should check YOU, for...for...\n"
" ...\n"
" Begone! <z 0.7>But please do report back should <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> speak such things to you! I beseech thee!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END"
msgid "Y'know, I'd better shop and back on the Hunt."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_END_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь, голубе."

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Understand what she's saying? Or understand her soul? <z0.7>(It's a 'yes' to both.)</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Of course! Wait--is this a chance for <i>me</> to be snide toward <i>you??</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1C"
msgid "Am I not supposed to? Does that make me...the BIRDMASTER? FLOCK TO ME, MY FEATHERED FRIENDS!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_understand_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "I could check for you, {name.npc_market_merchant}..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Woe, woe, and more woe! 'Tis a most tragic tale.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" She was once a beautiful <#BLUE>{name.species_mer}</> maiden, 'til one day she was cursed by the prick of a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-poisoned thorn."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>Bwe-heu-heu</i>! You're so gullible!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>Бве-хеу-хеу</i>! Ви такий довірливий!"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Bwe-heu-heu, indeed, I didst cut that tale of whole cloth."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" I hath no clue.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But I'm thankful nonetheless. She is the most stalwart of squires a <#BLUE>{name.species_ogre}</> could ask for. And a shrewd businessbird, in truth."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_EXIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" All's well that ends well. <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> taught me that expression.\n"
" !wink\n"
" 'Til next time, little culver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "So... what <i>is</i> {name.shop_magpie} exactly?"
msgstr "Отже... хто <i>така</i> {Name.shop_magpie}?"

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "I knew it! She just had that princess-turned-talking-bird vibe about her."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Wait--{name.konjur} can do that?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Pfft. Yeah right. I may be pretty, but I'm also brain-pretty."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "If that's right, why didn't she become a {name.rot}?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_EARLY_EXIT"
msgid "Oops, sorry, I've actually gotta run."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REGULAR_EXIT
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REGULAR_EXIT"
msgid "Well. Good for you guys."
msgstr "Ну. Радий за вас."

#: Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_whats_nimble_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</> was just normal wild magpie when <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> <i>did</i> turn her into, well, an abnormal wild magpie with a shoppe."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BEATEN
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BEATEN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hey, we're up against some pretty major forces and learning as we go.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" If it was easy, someone would have already done it, y'know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Гей, ми протистоїмо досить серйозним силам і вчимося на ходу.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Якби це було легко, хтось би це вже зробив, розумієш?"

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REVVED
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REVVED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ... You can be a little intense sometimes, Hunter. You know that?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" But that's probably why you're so good at what you do. I know you'll get her next time!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BEATEN
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BEATEN"
msgid "Ugh. <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> really whupped my behind..."
msgstr "Тьху. <#RED>{Name.megatreemon}</> реально вдарило мене по спині..."

#: Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REVVED
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_boss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REVVED"
msgid "When I'm done with <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, they'll <i>beg</> to be my toothpick."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Uh yeah, and <i>by a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</>!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Bigger <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> tend to hang out around <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>, y'know. That must mean you're getting close to the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'm sure <#RED>{name.megatreemon}'s</> just around the corner."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!clap\n"
"Я впевнений, що <#RED>{Name.megatreemon}</> не за горами."

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I just got my butt kicked."
msgstr "Я щойно отримав під зад."

#: Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "That's... reassuring?"
msgstr "Це... заспокоює?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LOCAL
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LOCAL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Really?! Was it on a dare? <#BLUE>{name.bandi_swamp}</>'s odor will curl the stiffest of nose hairs.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Regardless, plug your nose and stay on your toes, Hunter. The smell isn't the only nasty thing lingering in this swamp."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TOURIST
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TOURIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Welcome. Though it was never exactly a tourist destination--and the <#KONJUR>Eruption</> <i>certainly</> didn't improve things.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Plug your nose and stay on your toes, Hunter. The smell isn't the only nasty thing lingering in this swamp."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LOCAL
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LOCAL"
msgid "Oh, my 'nobe' has been here before, but before the Eruption."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TOURIST
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TOURIST"
msgid "Nope. It smells like {name.npc_dojo_master}'s socks but full of expired shrimp."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_ABANDONED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_ABANDONED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Exactly. It's why I can't shake this nagging feeling...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just keep your eyes peeled for anything unusual."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_EMPTY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1_EMPTY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" M-maybe he escaped? Took refuge somewhere down here?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I don't know, Hunter. Just watch out for anything unusual."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2_OKGO
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2_OKGO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" !point\n"
" Touché.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Be careful out there, Hunter. I'll be right behind you.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <z 0.7>We're coming, <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. Hold on. We're coming.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_ABANDONED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_ABANDONED"
msgid "Abandoning prime real estate like this? Madness!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_EMPTY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1_EMPTY"
msgid "So... it's empty? Then your Grandpa's in here... alone?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2_OKGO
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2_OKGO"
msgid "More unusual than usual, you mean?"
msgstr "Більш незвичними, ніж зазвичай, ти маєш на увазі?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> We can fix the past, but only by fighting for the future. <i><z 0.7>(Flicks toothpick in a cool way.)</></>\n"
" !point\n"
" <z 0.7>Oops, dropped my toothpick.</> Anyway, stay on your toes, Hunter. Seems the city's old <#RED>Security Systems</> are still online after all this time.\n"
" !think\n"
" Best to avoid them... unless you can figure out a way to use them against the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" We'll get our home back, Hunter. One way or another."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GRANDPA"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I... I don't know. What he said in the <#RED>Diary Pages</> we recovered... \n"
" !gesture\n"
" There <i>must</> be an explanation for it. Something... <i>(Sigh)</>\n"
" !point\n"
" Until then, stay on your toes. Seems the city's old <#RED>Security Systems</> are still online after all this time.\n"
" !think\n"
" Best to avoid them... unless you can figure out a way to use them against the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Hard to imagine this was home, once..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Security systems. Got it."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GRANDPA"
msgid "When we find your Grandpa, what are you going to say?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WIND
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_WIND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, did I forget to mention?\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>{name.owlitzer_forest}'s</> full of <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> with <#RED>Wind</> abilities.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you've got <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} Class</> gear it won't bother you much, but anything lighter and you might find it hard to keep your footing."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" О, я забув згадати?\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#RED>{Name.owlitzer_forest}</> повний <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</> зі здібностями <#RED>вітру</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Якщо у вас є спорядження класу <#RED>{name.heavy_weight}</>, це вас не дуже турбуватиме, але будь-що легше, і вам може бути важко втриматися."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Good luck out there, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" Удачі вам, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WIND
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_WIND"
msgid "Uh, what was that about wind?"
msgstr "Ух, що там було про вітер?"

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.CLOTHED
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.CLOTHED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, yes. It was my G-Grandpa's. <i>Is</> his, I g-guess. I wonder if he'll w-want it back...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> here are a-a-adapted to the cold, so th-th-they'll use it against you!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_QUICK
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_QUICK"
msgid "You bet. Now let's go save your still-alive Grandpa!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.FINISH"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" The t-t-temperature's so l-low that it won't take m-much to <#RED>freeze</> you solid!\n"
" I-I'm certain my Grandpa's being held c-captive here, so keep moving--we're all counting on y-y-you!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.NUDE
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.NUDE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Yeah... m-maybe you should have worn more a-armour. The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> will be ready for the c-c-cold... and might use it against you."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_SCARF
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_SCARF"
msgid "Good thing you've got that cozy scarf, huh?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DOIT
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DOIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Alright. Let's go. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" But be careful, Hunter--this is <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> Lab, his home turf. Who knows what's waiting for us..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I am, but only because I have the best team, lead by the best Hunter I've ever known. \n"
" player:\n"
" Me? Lead who? I've been following <i>you</> this whole time, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Then it's a miracle we haven't been going in circles! \n"
" !point\n"
" Speaking of miracles: you came to us in an ugly brown cloak--\n"
" player:\n"
" It's <i>minimalist!</> Its understatement <i>is</> the statement. And also: you're stalling.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Maybe. <i>(sigh)</> Definitely. Alright. Let's go. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" But be careful--this is <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> home turf. Who knows what's waiting for us..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DOIT
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DOIT"
msgid "Who are we to keep the old fox waiting?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY"
msgid "That's the plan. Are you ready to face him?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARMUSIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARMUSIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Strange... Maybe a guitar got stuck in some talented vines? \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway, as I was saying--I couldn't spot a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, but I did see a big bug carcass. It could be that <i>was</> the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> and \"natural causes\" have done your job for you.\n"
" !point\n"
" Whatever the case, we should check it out. There could be a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> ripe for the picking."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARNOTHING
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HEARNOTHING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Yes, I guess I must've imagined it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" As I was saying--I couldn't spot a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>, but I did see a big bug carcass. It could be that <i>was</> the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> and \"natural causes\" have done your job for you.\n"
" !point\n"
" Either way, we should check it out. There might be a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> ripe for the picking."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARMUSIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARMUSIC"
msgid "Those wickedly sinister guitar licks? Yep."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARNOTHING
msgctxt "Convo.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HEARNOTHING"
msgid "Maybe it was the wind?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CAUTIOUS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CAUTIOUS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Of course not!\n"
" !think\n"
" Well... I don't <i>think</> so. Not to be \"that guy,\" as they say, but the whole point of an experiment is that you're not sure what will happen...\n"
" !point\n"
" But I am <i>somewhat-mostly-reasonably certain</> you'll be in no danger, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" All you need to do is put that {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> I set up over there.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" And stand back."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OK
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Perfect. Now, just put that {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> I set up over there."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" It's the big machine in the center of our camp--you can't miss it.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Once you've done that, come back and tell me exactly what happened!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CAUTIOUS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CAUTIOUS"
msgid "Wait, is this experiment... <i>dangerous?</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OK
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OK"
msgid "Sure!"
msgstr "Звісно!"

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLERGY
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLERGY"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Erm, Hunter? You don't happen to have any {name.c_konjur} on you, do you? Or a hanky?\n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the Shard]</> No hanky, but I picked <i>this</> up on my Hunt. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egads! You found a {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.7>A real {name.c_konjur_heart_shard}! Just as his notes described! Then my calculations must be <i>mostly</> correct...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ah, Hunter, please, indulge me in a little experiment, would you?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HAS_BERNA_OR_HAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_HAS_BERNA_OR_HAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" It's so fun to watch you fight, Hunter! You're like a--a--aaahh--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" AH-CHOO!\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm like... a sneeze? Sudden. Violent. Involuntary.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ha, no... pardon me. I was saying, you're like a--ah... ah-CHOO! Ah-<i>CHOO!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_WITHOUTBERNAHAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT0.holding_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_WITHOUTBERNAHAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Poor Berna and Hamish. They're out there, all alone, and surrounded by <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>! \n"
" !scared\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, Hunter! They're like a ah--aaahh--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" AH-CHOO!\n"
" player:\n"
" They're like a sneeze? Loud. Wet. Involuntary. I can see it.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What? No, ah, sorry, I'm just worried about--ahb... ah-CHOO! Ah-<i>CHOO!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" YES! With so little <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>, I could never properly test our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>. But you just showed that our plan could work!\n"
" player:\n"
" The plan... right... Remind me again? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Well, I salvaged a defunct <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>, which used to provide people with <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> via the old <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>, you see.\n"
" !point\n"
" And then I modified it to <z 0.7>theoretically</> generate a <#RED>{name.rot}</>-repelling <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>! A shimmering <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> dome of safety...\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Imagine it, Hunter! This could be our home again! No more scrounging without <#KONJUR>Teffra</> in <#BLUE>The Brinks</>. A <i>real</> home...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" But the {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} wasn't enough power. I expect we'll need a much more concentrated <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> source to get it going...\n"
" player:\n"
" Point me in its direction, and I'll get it, Boss.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" Hah! \"Boss.\" Not me, surely. But you're not far off the mark...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" See, over time, the {name.c_konjur} in <#RED>Rots'</> bodies crystallizes to form {name_multiple.c_konjur_heart_shard} like the one you found.\n"
" !think\n"
" Now, if a <#RED>Rot</> grew large and powerful enough, it stands to reason that the crystallized {name.c_konjur} in their body would be extremely potent."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CONTEXT
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_CONTEXT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? What happened when you put the {name.c_konjur_heart_shard} into the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>? Tell me everything!\n"
" player:\n"
" It definitely reacted to the {name.konjur_heart_shard}. Maybe even powered up a little?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_NOCONTEXT
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TALK_NOCONTEXT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? What happened? Tell me everything!\n"
" player:\n"
" The {name.i_town_grid_cryst} definitely reacted to the {name.konjur_heart_shard}. Maybe it even powered up a little?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_GENERIC
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_GENERIC"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> like that are pretty rare--and elusive. But the <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</> certainly has its fair share!\n"
" player:\n"
" They wouldn't happen to offer their hearts up on request, would they?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh no no no! They'll fight to the death! Viciously! And without mercy! It'll be absolute carnage!\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oops--my apologies, Hunter. <z 0.7>Got carried away.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_TREEMON
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.TARGET_TREEMON"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> like that are pretty rare--and elusive--but we already know where one is: right here in the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest}</>...\n"
" player:\n"
" Let me guess: the {name.megatreemon} that knocked us out of the sky?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Bingo, bango, bongo! <z 0.7>Sorry, I'm getting a bit excited.</> Gosh, aren't we lucky she revealed her location so quickly?\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Err--well, not so lucky considering it meant we crash-landed and lost our friends, but..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_HAS_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_HAS_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !clap\n"
" Chin up! Our team's back together, and the mission's back on track!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Soon, we'll have our home back, just like it was. Go <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_MISSING_BERNA_OR_HAMISH
msgctxt "Convo.first_heart_shard_scout.ATTRACT1.deposited_shard.giver.STATE_0.WRAPUP_MISSING_BERNA_OR_HAMISH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Actually, just forget I said anything. Let's just focus on finding the rest of the crew, then we'll worry about the <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GONE
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" No! He couldn't have known--!\n"
" player:\n"
" He was an adult, playing with a substance he didn't fully understand, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" You're... You're right, Hunter. I know you are. But I also know he loved me, and never meant to hurt me...\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Perhaps he let his ambition get the better of him. Perhaps he... he <i>should</> have known better. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" But now, today, for me--it's enough that he knows he did wrong. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" And I want him to know that despite it all, I'm happy. And that I forgive him, that old fox.\n"
" player:\n"
" Then let's go save him so you have a chance to tell him so. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hm. Well said, Hunter. The <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> shows he's up ahead."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAME
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SAME"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Right... Like, if <i>I</> did it, then <i>I</> can undo it. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" But in reality, some things just <i>can't</> be undone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Even if we rebuilt this house--stone by stone, board by board--exactly as it was...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It'd never be the same. \n"
" player:\n"
" Because <i>we've</> changed. The world's changed.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Our mission's goal was to put things back to how they were...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" But if we never could in the first place, what was the point?\n"
" player:\n"
" To make something new, {name.npc_scout}. Something better. Now, let's go save your Grandpa.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You know, you're right! Well said, Hunter. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> shows he's up ahead."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GONE
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GONE"
msgid "Maybe your Grandpa took fault because it <i>is</> his fault?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAME
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SAME"
msgid "Maybe it gives us a false sense of control over random events?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON0.post_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No doubt about it. I found pieces of my old <#RED>{name.damselfly}</> toy here in the rubble.  \n"
" !agree\n"
" This is the house my <#BLUE>Granpda</> spoke of in the <#RED>Diary Pages</>. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" Or it <i>was</> the house. The one he moved me to after I developed my <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> sickness...\n"
" player:\n"
" You say that like it's something YOU did...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Did I? Huh. But I suppose, deep down, I <i>do</> believe it's my fault. \n"
" player:\n"
" Your Grandpa thought it was his fault, too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" And it was <i>neither</> of our faults. It was an accident! Why do we do that..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" You head out, Hunter. I... I need a moment alone."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scout_rummage\n"
" I'll... I'll follow in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> in a minute..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" I think I'll take one last look. You go on."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Don't wait for me, Hunter. I'll just be a moment."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Convo.grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.CHAT_DUNGEON1.wait_for_exit_room.giver.QUIP.post_chat:[in_convo_grandpa_house_scout_grimhollow.chat_dungeon1.wait_for_exit_room.giver,role_scout].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You don't mind if I stay here a bit longer, do you?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "See ya, Toot!"
msgstr "До зустрічі, Тут!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADD_TROUBLEMAKER
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADD_TROUBLEMAKER"
msgid "Smell ya later, 'teach."
msgstr "Зустрінемось пізніше, вчителю."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Tell me. Whatcha know about <#RED>Dodging</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Скажіть мені. Що ви знаєте про <#RED>ухилення</>?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Were you sleepin' during Hunter training?\n"
" !point\n"
" Right then, LISTEN UP--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough} Ви спали під час тренувань Мисливців?\n"
" !point\n"
" Тоді СЛУХАЙТЕ..."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>CORRECT!</></i>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>A+</>, kid. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
"<i><z 2>ПРАВИЛЬНО!</></i>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>5+</>, друже. {Name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" An acceptable answer. At least we're not starting from zero.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Now, look--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Прийнятна відповідь. Принаймні ми не починаємо з нуля.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough} А тепер слухайте..."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i><z 2>INCORRECT!</></i>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Someone's lookin' to get detention. {name.dojo_cough} Now LISTEN UP--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
"<i><z 2>НЕПРАВИЛЬНО!</></i>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Хтось хоче залишитися після уроків. {Name.dojo_cough} А тепер слухайте..."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Remember, it's easy to regret a swing, but you'll never regret a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!agree\n"
"Пам'ятайте, легко шкодувати про удар, але ви ніколи не пошкодуєте про <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's easy to regret a swing, but you'll never regret a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!agree\n"
"Легко шкодувати про удар, але ви ніколи не пошкодуєте про <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" The more familiar you can get with their patterns, the easier you'll stay alive."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!agree\n"
"Чим краще ви розумієте їхні рухи, тим легше вам буде залишатися живим."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Are you a teacher, Hunter? 'Cause you sure are testing me.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Y'know, I <i>was</i> gonna give you a <#KONJUR>Treat</>, but now I'm not sure if you deserve it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!angry\n"
"Ви вчитель, Мисливцю? Бо ви точно випробовуєте моє терпіння.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Знаєте, я <i>мав</i> намір дати вам <#KONJUR>смаколик</>, але тепер я не впевнений, що ви на нього заслуговуєте."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Sigh. Just take it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But try not to get clobbered out there, okay? Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dejected\n"
"Охх. Просто візьміть це.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Але постарайтеся не потрапити під удар, гаразд? Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph. {name.dojo_cough} Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Хмпф. {Name.dojo_cough} Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "POP QUIZ!!"
msgstr "ПОП ВІКТОРИНА!!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Oh. Um. Nothing?"
msgstr "О. Ем. Нічого?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "It's more important than Attacking."
msgstr "Це важливіше, ніж атака."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "You do it with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>."
msgstr "Це можна зробити натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "It's for wimps."
msgstr "Це для слабаків."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Gotcha... I'll Dodge with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!"
msgstr "Зрозуміло... Я буду ухилятися натискаючи <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Prioritize Dodging over Attacking. Okay!"
msgstr "Пріоритет — ухилятися, а не атакувати. Гаразд!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "Watch foes' movements closely. Can do."
msgstr "Уважно стежити за рухами ворогів. Зможу."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D"
msgid "I still think Dodging's for wimps."
msgstr "Я все ще думаю, що ухилення для слабаків."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "<z 0.92>Treat?? <i>(Ahem)</> I love dodging with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!</>"
msgstr "<z 0.92>Смаколик?? <i>(Кхм)</> Я обожнюю ухилятися натискаючи <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>!</>"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "You can't bribe <i>me!</i>"
msgstr "Ти не можеш підкупити <i>мене!</i>"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" If you charge into a fight swinging blindly, you'll get knocked on yer tail in no time flat.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Instead, watch your foes for clues they're about to strike, then <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> out of the way with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> when they do.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Foes leave themselves wide open after they <#RED>{name.concept_attack}</>, but you won't be able to capitalize if you're reelin' from a hit."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"Якщо ви кидаєтеся в бій наосліп, то в найкоротші терміни отримаєте удар під хвіст.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Натомість спостерігайте за ворогами, щоб вгадати момент, коли вони збираються атакувати, і <#RED>{3:{name.concept_dodge}}</> від них натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>, коли вони атакують.\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Вороги залишаються вразливими після <#RED>{2:{name.concept_attack}}</>, але ви не зможете скористатися цим, якщо будете оговтуватися від удару."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_dodge.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Here, have a <#KONJUR>Treat</>. Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"...Ось, візьміть <#KONJUR>смаколик</>. Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "Thanks for the quiz, Toot."
msgstr "Дякую за вікторину, Тут."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_TROUBLEMAKER
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_TROUBLEMAKER"
msgid "Smell ya later, nerd!"
msgstr "Понюхаємось пізніше, ботаніку!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tell me... Whatcha know about <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Скажіть мені... Що ви знаєте про <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, at least you've taken the 101 course.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> deal waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ну принаймні ви пройшли курс 101.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> завдають набагато більше <#RED>{2:{name.concept_damage}}</>, ніж звичайні <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" True! <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> do waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, so it's important to learn them.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You'll know you've done one right if you see <#BLUE>Blue Damage</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Точно! <#BLUE>{Name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> завдають набагато більше <#RED>{2:{name.concept_damage}}</>, ніж звичайні <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, тому важливо їх вивчити.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ви дізнаєтесь, що зробили все правильно, якщо побачите <#BLUE>шкоду синього кольору</>."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" CORRECT! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> deal waaay more <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> than regular <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, and show up as <#BLUE>Blue Damage</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ПРАВИЛЬНО! <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> завдають набагато більше <#RED>{2:{name.concept_damage}}</>, ніж звичайні <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_attack}</>, і відображаються як <#BLUE>шкода синього кольору</>!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, yer gonna get out-<#RED>{name.concept_damage}d</> by nerds, then.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" But what do I know. I'm just your {name.job_dojo}."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Що ж, тоді ботаніки вас переплюнуть у нанесенні <#RED>{2:{name.concept_damage}}</>.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Але що я знаю. Я ж лише ваш {name.job_dojo}."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Do you want your <#KONJUR>Treat</> or not?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
"Ви хочете свій <#KONJUR>смаколик</> чи ні?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just take it.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Просто візьміть це.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" You can lead a horse to <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ви можете привести коня до <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</>...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "POP QUIZ!!"
msgstr "ПОП ВІКТОРИНА!!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Err, their Damage appears in blue?"
msgstr "Е-е, їх пошкодження відображаються синім кольором?"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Each Weapon type has its own conditions!"
msgstr "Для кожного типу зброї діють свої умови!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "I can't do reliable Damage without them."
msgstr "Без них я не зможу завдати надійної шкоди."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2D"
msgid "They're for nerds."
msgstr "Вони для ботаніків."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} for more Damage. Got it."
msgstr "Зробити {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}, щоб завдати більше шкоди. Зрозумів."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "{name.concept_focus_hit} Damage appears blue. Gotcha."
msgstr "Шкода {2:{name.concept_focus_hit}} відображається синім кольором. Зрозумів."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3D"
msgid "Wow, that was a long and nerdy lecture."
msgstr "Вау, це була довга та нудна лекція."

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "<i>Sigh</>. I love doing extra Damage with {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}!"
msgstr "<i>Зітхання</>. Мені подобається коли {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} завдають додаткової шкоди!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "My brain can't be bought, pencil-pusher!"
msgstr "Мій розум не купити, канцелярський щуре!"

#: Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.pop_quiz_focus_hit.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yep. Feel free to practice your <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> on the dummies around town.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Now have a <#KONJUR>Treat</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Class dismissed."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Так. Не соромтеся практикувати свої <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> на манекенах у місті.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Тепер <#KONJUR>пригощайтеся</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Заняття закінчено."

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" He left me... again..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT0.grandpa_cutscene.giver.QUIP.scout_post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient0.grandpa_cutscene.giver,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...I just need a moment, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie.QUIP.post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Convo.post_fight_grandpa_scout.AMBIENT1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie.QUIP.post_grandpa:[in_convo_post_fight_grandpa_scout.ambient1.grandpa_cutscene.lottie,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Gotta say, Hunter, you really live up to the hype."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASHION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASHION"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh, absolutely! <i>Le Chateau d'Alphonse</> pieces absolutely STINK of power!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Though that could be due to the innovative use of <#RED>{name.rot}</> parts... \n"
" !think\n"
" That said... And I can't believe I'm about to say this but...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I <i>think</> <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I could make it even better?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I bet we can upgrade it more than your old armour--probably up to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Oh! Promise me you won't tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> I touched his work--much less made it BETTER!\n"
" player: \n"
" Promise.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Y'hear that, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? We're gonna work alongside--or at a little distance from--a fashion legend! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I never thought I'd get to upgrade <i>Chateau d'Alphonse</> {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour... Thank you, Hunter! From the both of us."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASHION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASHION"
msgid "Yeah! Does it make me look more powerful?"
msgstr "Так! Вона виглядає так, ніби я став могутнішим?"

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. I'll admit it's... creative. An' surprisin'ly sturdy... <z 0.7>an' <i>could</> hold under the pressure...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" It's given me an idear or two, Hunter... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I reckon I can upgrade it further than yer old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} weapons. Up ta <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>, even.\n"
" !point\n"
" The forge is roarin'. Just bring this here {name.i_item_rarity_rare} weapon to a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I can get started, ay?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Doesn't it just?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Yep! What do you think? Pret-ty sweet, eh?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "That sounds just swell!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADVICE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ADVICE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" From what <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> told me, seems like those old <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> have learned some new tricks.\n"
" !point\n"
" You won't be able to use the same tactics you used before to take 'em down, so watch 'em carefully before you attack.\n"
" !think\n"
" Also... with everything going all topsy-turvy like this, I've got a nasty feeling those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> will have found a way to revive themselves.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" At least that means another <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> for us. Ha!\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" If you feel like you need some extra training, I'm always happy to oblige."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Судячи з того, що розповів <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</>, схоже, що старі <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> навчилися новим трюкам.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви не зможете використати ті ж тактики, що й раніше, аби їх перемогти, тож уважно спостерігайте за ними перед тим, як атакувати.\n"
" !think\n"
" До того ж… із усіма цими переворотами в мене погане передчуття, що ті <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</> знайшли спосіб відроджуватися.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Принаймні це означає ще одне <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> для нас. Ха!\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Якщо відчуєте, що потребуєте додаткових тренувань, я завжди радий допомогти."

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CONFIDENT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CONFIDENT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Heh. You're doin' us all proud. Just make sure <i>you're</> not too proud to ask for advice when you need it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Хе. Ви робите нам усім честь. Лише подбайте, щоб <i>ви</> не були занадто горді, аби просити поради, коли вона знадобиться."

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ADVICE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ADVICE"
msgid "The {name_multiple.rot} have gone into a <#RED>Frenzy</>! Do you have any battle tips?"
msgstr "{Name_multiple.rot} стали <#RED>божевільними</>! Чи маєш якісь поради для бою?"

#: Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CONFIDENT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ascensions_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CONFIDENT"
msgid "Nothing I can't handle."
msgstr "Мені це під силу."

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Er--well... no. That is...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I kind of... sort of... thought they might make me look rugged. Like a rugged leader type.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Um, haha. A-anyway..!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "{name.npc_scout}, I've been wondering--what's with all the bandages you wear? Are you hurt?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_bandages_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Hiya, {name.npc_scout}. See ya, {name.npc_scout}."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" You think so? Gosh, I hope you're right, for the sake of those who come after us.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'd like to think that as long as you're breathing, it's never too late to start making things better."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" You're right. We can't undo what's happened, but that doesn't mean we can't build something new.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There's still room for beauty in change."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!agree\n"
"Ви маєте рацію. Ми не можемо скасувати те, що сталося, але це не означає, що ми не можемо створити щось нове.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"У змінах все ще є місце для краси."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "It'll be just as we remembered as kids."
msgstr "Це буде так, як ми пам'ятали в дитинстві."

#: Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_beautiful_future_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "It'll never be the same, but we can make it beautiful."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Of course! <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> our <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith}</> has a big, pink hair bun, and carries a leatherworking tool.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" She's a bit... eccentric. It'll be hard to miss her.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> our <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</> on the other hand, is a stoic kind of guy. Oh! And he has a distinctive tattoo on his arm.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We really need them both for this expedition to have any hope of success--you won't be able to <#RED>Upgrade</> any of your gear without their expertise.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" And besides all that, their safety... it's my responsibility. I still can't believe I lost them...\n"
" player:\n"
" Don't worry, we'll find them!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_READY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>'s ready to go."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS"
msgid "Could you tell me a bit about the missing folks first?"
msgstr "Можеш розказати трохи про тих хто зник?"

#: Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_READY"
msgid "I sure am!"
msgstr "Звісно!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND"
msgid "Bye, {name.npc_dojo_master}! Blam blam!"
msgstr "Бувай, {Name.npc_dojo_master}! Бам-бам!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ADDEND_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" I said be careful with that <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!angry\n"
"Я ж сказав бути обережним з <#RED>{4:{name.weapon_cannon}}</>!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" What d'ya wanna know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Що ви хочете знати?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Hm, yeah. So, <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> have two firing modes.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can shoot small <#RED>Projectiles</> in a wide spread.\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>Attack</> also doubles as your <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> and pushes you backwards.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can shoot a big ol' <#RED>Projectile</> that'll do more <#RED>Damage</>, but is also more concentrated."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!agree\n"
"Угу, так. <#RED>{Name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> мають два режими стрільби.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> ви можете стріляти малими <#RED>снарядами</> у широкому діапазоні.\n"
"!point\n"
"Ваша <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>атака</> також виконує роль <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> і відкидає вас назад.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> ви можете стріляти великим <#RED>снарядом</>, який завдає більше <#RED>шкоди</>, але є більш сконцентрованим."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FIRING_MODES_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Sure, but LISTEN UP this time.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> have two firing modes.\n"
" !point\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> you can launch yourself backwards and shoot a bunch of small <#RED>Projectiles</> in a big spread.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> you'll shoot a big ol' <#RED>Projectile</> that does more <#RED>Damage</>, but it'll also have less spread."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Добре, але СЛУХАЙТЕ уважно цього разу.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{Name_multiple.weapon_cannon}</> мають два режими стрільби.\n"
" !point\n"
" Натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> ви можете відштовхнути себе назад і випустити купу маленьких <#RED>снарядів</> у великому радіусі.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Натиснув <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK> вистрелите великим <#RED>снарядом</>, який завдає більше <#RED>шкоди</>, але більш концентрований."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Hm...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Right, yes. You can initiate a <#RED>Mortar</> volley by hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
" !point\n"
" But you gotta time hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to actually fire it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" But 'ey, then the last half of your <#RED>Mortar Projectiles</> will all be <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" That'll really hit'm where it hurts."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!think\n"
"{Name.dojo_cough} Хм...\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Так, звичайно. Ви можете зробити <#RED>мінометний</> обстріл, натиснувши <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
"!point\n"
"Але потрібно вчасно натиснути <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>, коли ваша <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> торкається землі, щоб здійснити постріл.\n"
"!laugh\n"
"Але, з іншого боку, остання половина ваших <#RED>мінометних снарядів</> нанесе <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>!\n"
"!agree\n"
"Це точно влучить у найболючіше місце."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MORTAR_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Heh. I like the enthusiasm.\n"
" !point\n"
" Okay. Hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> will initiate a <#RED>Mortar</> volley.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hitting <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground will fire the volley.\n"
" !agree\n"
" The last half of a <#RED>Mortar</> volley will all be <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Хм. Мені подобається ваш ентузіазм.\n"
"!point\n"
"Гаразд. Натискання <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> розпочне <#RED>мінометний</> обстріл.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Натискання <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK> в момент, коли ваша <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> торкається землі, здійснить постріл.\n"
"!agree\n"
"Остання половина обойми <#RED>мінометного</> обстрілу нанесе <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Reloading can be fiddly if you're new to this puppy.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> to start a reload, then hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> just as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to finish'r off.\n"
" !point\n"
" You can practice on the <#RED>Training Dummies</> while you're in camp if you need to."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RELOADING_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Okay. {name.dojo_cough} But LISTEN UP now.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Just hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>, then hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> as your <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> touches the ground to reload."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I wouldn't mind some {name.weapon_cannon} tips."
msgstr "Я б не відмовився від кількох порад про {2:{name.weapon_cannon}}."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES"
msgid "Firing modes."
msgstr "Режими стрільби."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FIRING_MODES_ALT"
msgid "Firing modes, again?"
msgstr "Режими стрільби, знову?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR"
msgid "Does it do anything cool?"
msgstr "Чи є ще якісь цікаві функції?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MORTAR_ALT"
msgid "Tell me about the mortar again!"
msgstr "Розкажи мені ще раз про міномет!"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING"
msgid "How do I reload?"
msgstr "Як перезарядитись?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RELOADING_ALT"
msgid "Re-explain reloading for me?"
msgstr "Поясни ще раз про перезаряджання?"

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO"
msgid "Ah nevermind, I can figure it out."
msgstr "А, забудь, я розберуся."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SKIPINFO_ALT"
msgid "Okay, I think I get the gist."
msgstr "Гаразд, думаю, я розумію суть."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.SKIPINFO_RESPONSE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.SKIPINFO_RESPONSE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just you don't blow yourself sky high and I'm happy. Anyway--"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Лише б ви не підірвалися, і я буду радий. В будь-якому разі..."

#: Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLDONE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_cannon_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK_ALLDONE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Play around, get a knack for it. I'm sure you'll be s'plodin' <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in no time."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Спробуйте, наберіться досвіду. Я впевнений, що ви скоро будете підривати <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>."

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEPOSIT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEPOSIT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Um... that's very kind of you Hunter, but I'm afraid I'll have to pass.\n"
" player:\n"
" You sure? It's pretty fun...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Yes, well, it's... erm, it's a little embarrassing... I have an extremely rare <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Allergy</>. I've had it since I was a kit.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Minor exposure causes sneezing, congestion, hives. Direct contact? Well, it's... rather cataclysmic.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I shudder to imagine what'd happen were I to hold a highly-concentrated <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HIGHFIVE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HIGHFIVE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ha... yes. Sorry about that.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm happy to give you a high-five anytime, Hunter... <i>after</> you wash off the {name.c_konjur}.\n"
" !cough\n"
" And <#RED>{name.rot}</> viscera."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RISKY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_RISKY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It would be if I was the one fighting.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But luckily, we have you! And I'll watch your back from the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>, far above any errant splashes of {name.c_konjur}."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEPOSIT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEPOSIT"
msgid "Do you wanna put the {name.konjur_heart} in the {name.town_grid_cryst} next time?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HIGHFIVE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HIGHFIVE"
msgid "At least now I know why you've been avoiding my victory high-fives."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RISKY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_RISKY"
msgid "Isn't this whole expedition a little risky for you, then?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKPEDAL
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BACKPEDAL"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Smart kid."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Розумний малий."

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_COUGH
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_COUGH"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ghe-heh-heh... ha-ha... GAH-HAW-HAW-HAW!\n"
" player:\n"
" What's so funny?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Hooo-- just thinkin' about all the laps I'm gonna make you run... we'll see who's \"up to this\" then, won't we?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ге-хе-хе... ха-ха... ГА-ГА-ГА-ГА!\n"
" player:\n"
" А що таке смішне?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Хооо... просто подумав про всі кола, які я змушу вас пробігти... тоді й побачимо, хто \"готовий до цього\", га?"

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKPEDAL
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BACKPEDAL"
msgid "Er-- n-no reason!"
msgstr "Е-е... н-нема причини!"

#: Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_COUGH
msgctxt "Convo.twn_dojo_cough.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_COUGH"
msgid "That cough sounds bad. Are you sure you're up to this?"
msgstr "Той кашель звучить тривожно. Ти впевнений, що справді готовий до цього?"

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CATBAG
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_CATBAG"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Now what's THAT supposed ta mean??\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Ah! Nothi-- I just-- It was--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" What--cat got yer tongue?\n"
" player:\n"
" Touché. <z 0.7>Which better not be a cat thing.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'll talk ta <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>. Let them know I hold nothin' against 'em. \n"
" !point\n"
" Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FEELBAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FEELBAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> I came along to try 'n' set right me wrongs. I dinnae want ta put <i>more</> pressure on the kid. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know them. They'd've taken that across their wee shoulders along with the rest o' the bloody world."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOBYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GOBYEBYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" Off ye go, Hunter. I'll talk ta <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OKBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_OKBYE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !greet\n"
" I'll do just that. Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_REMIND"
msgid "agent: \n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's true. I smithied the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> at the behest of <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> himself. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> couldn't be contained. Leaks sprung all over, creatin' what we now call the <#RED>{name.rot}</>.\n"
" !angry\n"
" When I told <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> that he needed ta shut it all down, he refused! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Called it a \"scientific opportunity.\" I called it a \"bloody disaster\" and him a \"bloody fool.\"\n"
" !angry\n"
" In a huff, I up and left fer <#BLUE>The Brinks</>. But... I shoulda stayed. Shoulda pushed back.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I didn't, though, did I, Hunter? No. I tucked tail and left. Haunts me ta this very day.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Weren't me intention ta have it haunt <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>, now, too!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CATBAG
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_CATBAG"
msgid "I can understand that. Still, cat's out of the bag now."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FEELBAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FEELBAD"
msgid "{name.npc_scout}? They feel bad for what happened, but also for not knowing."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOBYEBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GOBYEBYE"
msgid "Sorry, but could you ask them yourself? I have to run."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OKBYE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_OKBYE"
msgid "It's okay, but just talk to them. I'd better run."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_REMIND"
msgid "Remind me again what happened?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wait. <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>? Like, THE <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</>?? Why didn't you say so??\n"
" player:\n"
" I thought I <i>did</> ...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" He's just kind of, like, THE name in fashion??\n"
" !point\n"
" And you MET him. Did he insult you? Talk down to you? Make you feel \"less than\"?\n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. Maybe that sounds familiar...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Lucky!! If I stare, don't worry. I'm admiring the clothing--not you."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I LOVE it! The stitching? So meticulous! The darting? So inventive! \n"
" !shocked\n"
" And how they incorporated not just <#RED>{name.rot}</> materials but the whole VIBE of the area??\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It's... transcendent!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And I <i>never</> use that word (unless it's about <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> singing voice).\n"
" !think\n"
" What kind of lunatic could've made this?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_DESC
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_DESC"
msgid "Well, he's a pink-haired {name.species_ogre} with a serious attitude problem."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_SWOON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT_SWOON"
msgid "He's broody, mysterious, talks like a medieval knight... <i>(sigh)</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_armor.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE"
msgid "Oh, just this little place I know. 'Le Chateau d'Alphonse.' Do you like it?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MARKET
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MARKET"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A market. Out there. \n"
" player:\n"
" Yeah. Run by this floppy-haired guy with a <i>real</> affected way of talking.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Floppy hair? An' an affected manner o' speech, ye said?\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmph. <z 0.7>Wonder if <#BLUE>Berna</> knows...</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TEASE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !point\n"
" No.\n"
" player:\n"
" Fine, I bought it at a market out in the wilds, from this floppy-haired guy with a <i>real</> affected way of talking."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MARKET
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MARKET"
msgid "I bought it at a cute little market out in the wilds. Buy local, I say."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_alphonse_weapon_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TEASE"
msgid "Why? Is somebody <i>jeeeaalous</>?"
msgstr "А що? Хтось <i>за-а-здрить</>?"

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GG_EASY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GG_EASY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ha! That's what I like to hear!\n"
" !point\n"
" You keep puttin' those moves I taught you to good use, and we'll have that <#RED>Bubble Shield</> up and running in no time flat."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ха! Оце мені й подобається чути!\n"
" !point\n"
" Продовжуйте добре використовувати ті прийоми, що я вас навчив, і ми піднімемо та активуємо той <#RED>Бульбашковий щит</> за лічені хвилини."

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TERRIFIED
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_TERRIFIED"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Didn't think you were gonna make it?\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm. Sounds like I haven't been pushin' you hard enough. Starting now, I'm beefin' up yer training regimen!\n"
" !point\n"
" We'll start at the crack of dawn with a ten mile run, then push-ups until breakfast, and then--\n"
" player:\n"
" You know-- suddenly I'm a lot less scared of the {name_multiple.rot_boss}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That's the spirit!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Не думали, що впораєтесь?\n"
" !think\n"
" Хмм. Схоже, я ще не достатньо вас тренував. Відтепер я посилю вашу тренувальну програму!\n"
" !point\n"
" Почнемо на світанку з десятимильної пробіжки, потім віджимання до сніданку, а тоді...\n"
" player:\n"
" Знаєш... я раптово почав менше боюся {2:{name_multiple.rot_boss}}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Оце настрій!"

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GG_EASY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GG_EASY"
msgid "And I made it look easy, too."
msgstr "І я зробив це доволі легко."

#: Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TERRIFIED
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_boss_kill_dojo.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_TERRIFIED"
msgid "I-I'm still shaking... I didn't think I was gonna make it..."
msgstr "Я-я досі тремчу... Не думав, що впораюсь..."

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_DEAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Of course not! C'mon, I'm better at rescues than that.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ... You <i>did</> get a teensy bit totally knocked out, though. Luckily, I snagged you with the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> rope claw before things got <i>too</> dicey."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASTER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FASTER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I mean, I'd love to, but predicting the future is a, uh, a <i>bit</> beyond me.\n"
" !point\n"
" Remember, if you need to end your Hunt early and regroup, you can signal for me to take you back to camp at any time. No judgement.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" From me, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SQUAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SQUAD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Of course! It's the <#RED>{name.foxtails}</> way. So, you could have a look around, Hunter, or we could head back out. Just let me know."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_DEAD"
msgid "Back up. Did... did I die?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASTER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FASTER"
msgid "Next time, could you grab me <i>before</> I get knocked out?"
msgstr "Наступного разу не міг би ти мене схопити <i>перш ніж</> я опинюся в нокдауні?"

#: Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SQUAD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_first_death_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SQUAD"
msgid "I'm glad to know you have my back."
msgstr "Приємно знати, що ти за моєю спиною."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'd know the smell of those tools anywhere. <i>(sniff sniiiiiiff)</>\n"
" !think\n"
" They're still lost somewhere in the <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Wow. Good nose. Don't worry, I'll find them!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Wh-- how did you know?!"
msgstr "Щ.. звідки ти знаєш?!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT0.farmtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" Haven't found my <#RED>{name.farmtools}</> yet?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" Ви ще не знайшли мої <#RED>{name.farmtools}</>, так?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} ...Ick. Still covered in <#RED>{name.totolili}</> glop.\n"
" !think\n"
" Okay. Use my tools to take care of your garden. Pick a <#RED>Plot</> and start planting <#RED>Seeds</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" I got rid of the weeds. Everyone gets their own <#RED>Plot</>. Don't be greedy. Keep to your own. Simpler that way. \n"
" player:\n"
" Noted, I'll keep my paws off of other folks' plots.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Good. Take these <#RED>Seeds</> I found in my shoe. There's lots more out in the wilds."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Oh, okay. Thanks, {name.npc_apothecary}!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I found your {name.farmtools}!"
msgstr "Я знайшов твої {name.farmtools}!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT1.farmtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're back?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви повернулися?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...<#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" So. 'Hunter'. You hunt the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You don't... <i>eat</> them, do you?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh. Where do you get your food?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" О. А де ви берете їжу?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I <i>knew</> it. That's why you smell weird. Don't you have any normal food?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я так і <i>знала</>. Ось чому від вас дивно пахне. У вас що, немає нормальної їжі?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" 'Stale'? That's gross. You need a garden. Fresh food is best. It'd clear up your skin, too.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" If I had my <#RED>{name.farmtools}</>, I'd teach you to grow plants. But a <#RED>{name.totolili}</> took them. You know. Dangly arms? Big leaf hat they toss around? Jerks?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was looking for them when you found me. Probably still in the <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp_r2}</> somewhere...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.farmtools}, huh? I'll keep an eye out for them!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "You came! Welcome! Say, I forgot to ask, what's your name?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "What?! No!!"
msgstr "Що?! Ні!!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "Oh, I might've taken a nibble once or twice..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "We brought some food from the Brinks. It's a little stale, but there's enough to go around."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_apothecary.ATTRACT2.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Oh. It's you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Ох. Це ви."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm glad to see you're in one piece.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And I really wanna make sure you stay that way with some <#RED>Armour Upgrades</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Thing is... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>... he's got some trust issues.\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:dummy] I'll work on him, but in the meantime, change up your equipment with the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> over there!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BESTFRIEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_BESTFRIEND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" It's <i>what?</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_IMPORTANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_IMPORTANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Agreed! You'd be surprised how many people are rude about it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
"Погоджуюсь! Ви б здивувалися, скільки людей буває грубими щодо цього."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_WEIRD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FRIEND_WEIRD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe. But I'd rather be weird with my best buddy than normal without him!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Можливо. Але я краще буду дивною зі своїм найкращим другом, ніж нормальною без нього!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HOLDINGYOUBACK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_HOLDINGYOUBACK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>You</> try <#RED>upgrading armour</> without your number one friend/slashing tool!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And it's nothing personal! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> just not great with new people...\n"
" !think\n"
" But maybe gifting him a little <#RED>souvenir</> from your Hunts would help? To show you care and the like.\n"
" !neutral"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LUNN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_LUNN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" My leather cutter, obviously. He's my best buddy."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Мій різак для шкіри, очевидно. Він мій найкращий приятель."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_OPT"
msgid "Uhh... It was nice to meet you properly!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_EARLY_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" You too!\n"
" !think\n"
" ...I hope I didn't miss anything juicy while I was away."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Мені теж!\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Сподіваюся, я не пропустила нічого смачного, поки мене не було."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "No problem. It was nice to meet you--both!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" You too! Say bye, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>!\n"
" ...\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Did you lose your <i>manners</> in the wilds, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? Yeesh..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Glad to see you settling in!"
msgstr "Радий бачити, що ти облаштувалася!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BESTFRIEND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_BESTFRIEND"
msgid "Your best friend is a leatherworking tool? That's--"
msgstr "Твій найкращий друг - інструмент для обробки шкіри? Це..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_IMPORTANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_IMPORTANT"
msgid "It's great! Friends are important."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_WEIRD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FRIEND_WEIRD"
msgid "Um... It's a <i>little</> weird?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HOLDINGYOUBACK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_HOLDINGYOUBACK"
msgid "So it's {name.npc_lunn} who won't let <i>you</> upgrade my armour?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LUNN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_LUNN"
msgid "Wait, who's {name.npc_lunn}?"
msgstr "Зачекай, хто такий {Name.npc_lunn}?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Heya, Hunter! Thanks for the ride to camp."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Dressing for Battle"
msgstr "Одяг для бою"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ye know ye scream with yer eyes, don't ye? Yer doin' it right now."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" ...\"tough,\" ay?\n"
" !point\n"
" I see ye've got the {name.weapon_polearm} an' the {name.weapon_hammer}. Fine weapons, both. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" But, with a bit o' <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</> for th'forge, I'll smithy whatever prototype ye fancy in the <#RED>Weapon Racks</> o'er there. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</> fer new weapons. Deal? Deal."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_UPGRADES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_UPGRADES"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, that service there's reserved for <i>true</> Hunters.  \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ye've got ta convince me ye'll do more than drown the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in yer salty tears.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ... Been taken advantage of by unworthy types before, see. \n"
" !point\t\t\n"
" So fetch me a <#RED>souvenir</> from yer Hunt--proof of yer bona fides--an' I'll start upgradin' yer weapons.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Deal? Deal."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT"
msgid "Your personality is A+, {name.npc_blacksmith}."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Did you notice? I didn't scream <i>once</> on the ride back. I'm brave."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Nuh-uh. They're shouting about how tough I am."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_UPGRADES
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_UPGRADES"
msgid "What about <i>upgrading</> my weapons?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Hmph..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Гмпф..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Hammer Home"
msgstr "Коваль удома"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Howdy Hunter!\n"
" [recipe:unlock_recipe] Aw shucks, looks like you still haven't found everythin' I need to get cookin'. Oh well!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Привіт, Мисливцю!\n"
" [recipe:unlock_recipe] Ох, халепа, схоже, ви ще не знайшли все, що мені потрібно для готування. Ну, нічого!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT0.gather_ingredients.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well howdy, Hunter! What's got you so excited?\n"
" player:\n"
" I brought all the ingredients you asked for!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" W-well so you have! I can hardly believe my eyes!\n"
" player:\n"
" So, what's on the menu?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, see now here's the thing--um... it's a mite embarrassin', but I lost somethin' out there in the wilds while foragin' fer ingredients, as we {name.job_cook}s do.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" My... lucky <#RED>{name.cookingtools}</>. My dear old Ma gave it to me--it's a treasured family heirloom, passed down through generations.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Without it, I just don't know that I've got the heart for cookin' anything.\n"
" player:\n"
" Don't worry, I'll find it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh what a sweetheart you are, Hunter! I'd be much obliged!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Aww, that's a darn shame!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'm <i>sure</> it's out there somewhere, though. Not like I'd make somethin' like that up! Ha-ha!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Ох, яка прикрість!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Але я <i>впевнена</>, що вона десь там є. Не могла ж я таке вигадати! Ха-ха!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll keep looking!"
msgstr "Не хвилюйся, я шукатиму далі!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "I still haven't found your lucky {name.cookingtools}..."
msgstr "Я ще не знайшов твою щасливу {2:{name.cookingtools}}..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT1.cookingtools_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Howdy Hunter! Why the long face?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Привіт, Мисливцю! Чому такі сумні?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Eggs? Oh! Well, y'know what they say! Um... if yer eggs ain't, um, when danger's not eggs... That ain't it... hold on... \n"
" !think\n"
" If you ain't got your eggs while in peril, you might as well cook 'em...fer...yer Aunt Carol. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Hoo-whee! That's the sayin'! No further questions 'bout it!\n"
" !point\n"
" Now if you wanna go over by that there cookin' pot, I'll getcha a menu! <z 0.7>I'm <i>pretty</> sure I saw a menu around here somewhere...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just point at what you want and I'll get it packed up in yer <#RED>{name.lunchbox}</> all nice for your Hunt!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Eggs? O-oh! Don't trouble your pretty little head none, hun! I'm over eggs. Over easy! I'm easy. I don't need eggs is what I mean.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Now if you wanna go over by that there cookin' pot, I'll getcha a menu! <z 0.7>I'm <i>pretty</> sure I saw a menu around here somewhere...</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just point out what you want and I'll get it packed up all nice for your Hunt!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_cook}!"
msgstr "Дякую, {Name.npc_cook}!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Found it in {name.eggzy}'s lair! Dangerous place to forage for eggs, {name.npc_cook}..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Found it in {name.eggzy}'s lair! Sorry, I didn't bring any eggs back."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT2.cookingtools_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh! Howdy Hunter, back already?\n"
" player:\n"
" I found your {name.cookingtools}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" What?! How did you-- \n"
" !bliss\n"
" Erm, I mean, <i>hoo-whee!</> I can't scarcely believe it! Like, at all!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh just swell, don't you worry your little head about me!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ой, все чудово, не турбуйтесь про мене своєю маленькою голівкою!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ah... well, y'see, here's the thing... I can't cook if I don't have some ingredients to work with.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Why, to make anythin' decent I'd need, um... a <#RED>Squash</>, some <#RED>Berries</>, maybe some <#RED>Beans</>, and... let's see, um... some sorta <#RED>Fruit</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now if I had those, I could whip up somethin' great! Doubt you'll find anythin' like that way out here, though."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ну... справа в тому, що я не можу готувати, якщо не маю інгредієнтів.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Щоб приготувати щось путнє, мені потрібен <#RED>гарбуз</>, трохи <#RED>ягід</>, <#RED>боби</> і... хм... якийсь <#RED>фрукт</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Якби у мене це було, я б приготувала щось чудове! Але сумніваюся, що ви знайдете таке в цих краях."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Really? Err, great!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Справді? Еуф, чудово!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wh-what?! That's--! Um... w-well I can hardly believe my eyes!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Щ-що?! Це...! Ум... я просто не вірю власним очам!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, see now here's the thing--um... it's a mite embarrassin', but I realized I lost somethin' out there in the wilds.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" My... lucky <#RED>Cooking Spoon</>. My dear old Ma gave it to me--it's a treasured family heirloom, passed down through generations.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Without it, I just don't know that I've got the heart for cookin' anything."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_5"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh what a sweetheart you are, Hunter! I'd be much obliged!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ой, яке ж ви золотко, Мисливцю! Я вам буду дуже вдячна!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How are you settling in?"
msgstr "Як тобі тут живеться?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "I can't wait to try your cooking!"
msgstr "Не можу дочекатися, щоб скуштувати твої страви!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3"
msgid "I don't have it now, but I have an idea..."
msgstr "Зараз у мене її немає, але я маю ідею..."

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Actually, I have those exact things on me now!"
msgstr "Власне, у мене є ці продукти!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4"
msgid "So, what's on the menu?"
msgstr "То що сьогодні в меню?"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_5"
msgid "Don't worry, I'll find it!"
msgstr "Не хвилюйся, я її знайду!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You've sure got a nice little setup here, real homey!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" У вас тут гарненьке місце, дуже затишне!"

#: Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fn_unlocked_cook.ATTRACT3.convo.giver.STATE_0.TITLE"
msgid "Get Cooking"
msgstr "Приступаємо до готування"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" Want me to make an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Put the materials in the <#RED>Armoury</> and I'll get started."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooooh, that's gotta be the most beautiful <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</> I've ever seen!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, but um... could you hold onto it while I'm not doing upgrades?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I think <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> might be a little jealous... I don't want him to feel like he's getting replaced!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ооооо, це повинен бути найкрасивіший <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>, що я коли-небудь бачила!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" О, але... не могли б ви потримати їх у себе, поки я почну робити покращення?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Я думаю, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> може трохи заздрити... не хочу, щоб він відчував, що його замінили!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" I checked the <#RED>Armoury</>, but you haven't dropped off my materials.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] I need these to make the <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" Я перевірила <#RED>манекен для обладунків</>, але ви ще не залишили мені матеріали.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Вони потрібні мені, щоб зробити <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ah!! Look at that <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>-- isn't it just <i>everything?!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" But uhh, do you think you could you hold onto it between upgrades?\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> is still feeling a bit sensitive about the whole 'new tools' thing."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Anyways! If you want those upgrades, I'm gonna need an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Which means you've gotta bring back the stuff I need to make it.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Then I'll be able to upgrade <i>all</> of your armour to <#RED>Level {max_upgrade}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Отже! Якщо хочете ті покращення, мені потрібний <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] А це означає, що ви маєте принести мені необхідні матеріали.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Тоді я зможу покращити <i>всі</> ваші обладунки до <#RED>{max_upgrade} рівня</>!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Bring back materials. Okay!"
msgstr "Принести матеріали? Добре!"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_armorsmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "Чим я можу допомогти?"

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did ye get me the goods for them <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Put 'em in a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I'll get ta hammerin'."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви дістали для мене матеріали на <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Покладіть їх у <#RED>стійку для зброї</>, і я візьмуся до кування."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.fortify_1.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye. A fine set o' <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>, indeed.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well. Enough bletherin'.\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's get yer weapons up ta snuff, ay?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Got all the goods already?\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Put 'em in a <#RED>Weapon Rack</> and I'll make the <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Усі матеріали вже є?\n"
" !point\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] Покладіть їх у <#RED>стійку для зброї</>, і я зроблю <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>."

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith.ATTRACT3.fortify_2.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DONE_FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ah. Those <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</> are a thing o' beauty.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Let's get ta work on those weapons o' yers, ay?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" [recipe:fortify_recipe] I'll need materials. Which means you'll have ta source the goods.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I get new tools, and ye'll be able ta upgrade all yer weapons ta <#RED>Level {max_upgrade}</>. Seems like a good deal ta me."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fortify_blacksmith_1_ready.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOPPING_LIST"
msgid "How can I help?"
msgstr "Чим я можу допомогти?"

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" No, no, no. It's my Grandpa's notes, his discoveries...\n"
" !point\n"
" But all of that is just theory without <i>you!</> You made this all <i>real,</> Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thank you. Truly... this means everything."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You're one-of-a-kind. No doubt about it.\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, we've all waited long enough! Go put that last <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in our modified <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> and let's get our home back!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2A"
msgid "Thanks, Flitt, but I did it for everyone back in the Brinks."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_2B"
msgid "Y'know what? Yeah! I <i>am</> all that, Flitteroonie! Booyow!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "All thanks to that big brain of yours."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_MERCHANT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" EEEP! Were--were <i>you</> just eavesdropping on <i>me</>...?\n"
" !think\n"
" Huh. It's really not so fun being on the other side of that.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Fine, yes, I was fan girling about <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> a <i>little</> bit.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So like, if you find yourself on a <#RED>{name.run_ascension}</>, you might as well swing by the <#BLUE>Marketplace</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Make sure he's still alive or whatever.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Or don't. It doesn't really matter to me!\n"
" !scared\n"
" Please don't tell him I care so much but please check because I care SO much.\n"
" player:\n"
" Okay...?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_frenzy_hint_buy_from_alphonse_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_MERCHANT"
msgid "Are you talking about {name.npc_market_merchant}?"
msgstr "Ти говорила про {Name.npc_market_merchant}а?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} What are you carrying? It smells like the wilds. It doesn't <i>look</> like the wilds.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a souvenir from my Hunt! Wrapped up all nice-like. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Sou-ve-nir...? Hm. Do I--? What is--? I don't know--\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry, I didn't mean to make you uncomfortable. Should I take it back?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} Smelly box in paper, mine!\n"
" !think\n"
" You can use the <#RED>{name.i_seed_grinder}</>. If you want. I just fixed it up. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I'm done talking now. Bye."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}  'Souvenir'... 'Wrapped up all nice-like'...\n"
" !think\n"
" Six sides. Red petals on top. It's like a square flower. \n"
" !agree\n"
" It's pretty. I'll keep it.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're... welcome?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Okay."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 'Souvenir'! Gimme!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Another square flower. I will add it to the others.\n"
" player:\n"
" 'Others'? You haven't opened any of wrapped presents?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<i>'Opened'?</>\n"
" player:\n"
" You know, tear off the paper and see what's inside? I'll help--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} Don't touch my square flower!\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's weird. It smells like home. I like it.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, that's... nice. But the <i>intent</> is for the gift to be opened. It's what's inside that matters.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I don't live in tents. \n"
" !think\n"
" ... but I'll think about it."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Hee-hee... weird."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Then why are you sweating so much?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} And why does it smell like <i>that?</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...I've decided. This one will be opened. NOW!\n"
" !angry\n"
" GRR-AAAAAH!!\n"
" player:\n"
" That's impressive--I've never seen someone unwrap a box with their teeth.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ... Was I weird?\n"
" player:\n"
" There's nothing wrong with a little weirdness. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Are <i>you</> weird?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, sure! <z 0.7>Y'know, sometimes, when no one's looking, I'll lick a {name.konjur} crystals. They taste <i>tingly</>.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Why, I've never done a single weird thing in my life!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Granny taught me that. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" She was glad to return her life to the Wilds so new life could take root.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I like the bird house. Take this. I found it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" She was glad to return her life to the Wilds so new life could take root.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" When I'm there, she's all around me. The wind, the leaves, the birdsong...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I like the bird house. Take this. I found it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} I know what this is. \n"
" player:\n"
" Even without unwrapping it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's a bird house. Granny and I, we hung them in the trees around our hut.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" We'd watch the birds come and go for hours.\n"
" player:\n"
" I didn't know you have a Granny! Is she okay by herself? We could go check up on her.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I don't see why. She's been dead a couple years now.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Sorry, I didn't realize...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't be sad. Things are born. Then they die. Then new things are born. Nothing to be sad about."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Hm. I guess that's true."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "That seems a little cold..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I know. Hunters use weird magic. Doesn't work on you.\n"
" player:\n"
" Why are you practicing becoming invisible?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Even more so because it worked on you. \n"
" !point\n"
" Hunters use weird magic. Hard to fool you. Taken a lot of practice.\n"
" player:\n"
" Why are you practicing becoming invisible?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... {name.npc_apothecary}? I brought you a souvenir...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter! I'm right here.\n"
" player:\n"
" What... were you doing just now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I was practicing being invisible. I'm getting better at it."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Camouflage. For when I'm under threat.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're safe here, though. Unless there's something at camp that scares you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... no. Back to practicing. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7>And I'm gone.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "But you weren't invisible. I could see you the whole time."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Oh, uh, wow! That's... impressive!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The squareness of this gift... reminds me of something.. Oh.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" My hut in the wilds.  \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you feel like telling me about it? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Granny built it. So she could live far from everyone else. She liked to be alone.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then someone left me on her doorstep. As a baby. \n"
" player:\n"
" Wow, really?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss} No interrupting with disbelief!\n"
" player:\n"
" U-understood. Please. Go on.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" She taught me about the Wilds. How to garden. How to deal with <#RED>{name.rot}</>. How to everything. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" One day, there was a rumbling, and after that, more <#RED>{name.rot}</>. <i>Meaner</> <#RED>{name.rot}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" A few years later, we met an old Hunter--like you, but good skin. Told us about the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>. The evacuation. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" The old Hunter stayed, helped with the <#RED>{name.rot}</> problem. I was mad. Didn't think we needed her. Or anyone. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Then we lost her.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Then I lost Granny.\n"
" !point\n"
" Then you found me.\n"
" ...\n"
" You can talk now.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow, {name.npc_apothecary}. You've been alone for so long. <z 0.7>And I don't think my skin is <i>that</> bad...</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Before the <#KONJUR>Eruption</>, Granny said I should have 'friends' my age. Talked about a school in town...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I didn't want to go. I ran away. She found me. She didn't make me go.\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Maybe I should've been braver.\n"
" Okay, bye.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Квадратність цього подарунка... нагадує мені дещо... Ох.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Мою хатину в диких землях.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти хочеш розповісти мені про це?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Бабуся її збудувала. Щоб жити подалі від усіх. Вона любила самотність.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" А потім хтось залишив мене на її порозі. Немовлям.\n"
"player:\n"
" Воу, серйозно?!\n"
"agent:\n"
" {Name.apothecary_hiss} Не перебивайте з недовірою!\n"
"player:\n"
" З-зрозуміло. Будь ласка, продовжуй.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Вона розповіла мені про Дикі землі. Як вирощувати рослини. Як мати справу з <#RED>{3:{name.rot}}</>. Як робити все.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Одного дня стався гуркіт, а після цього - більше <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>. <i>Зліші</> <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Через кілька років ми зустріли стару мисливицю - як ви, але зі шкірою краще. Вона розповіла нам про <#KONJUR>Виверження</>. Евакуацію.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Та мисливиця залишилася, допомагала вирішити проблему з <#RED>{3:{name.rot}}</>. Я злилася. Думала, нам не потрібна вона. Чи хтось узагалі.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Потім ми її втратили.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Потім я втратила бабусю.\n"
" !point\n"
" А потім ви знайшли мене.\n"
" ...\n"
" Тепер можете говорити.\n"
"player:\n"
" Воу, {Name.npc_apothecary}. Ти була сама так довго. <z 0.7>І я не думаю, що моя шкіра <i>настільки</> погана...</>\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" До <#KONJUR>Виверження</> бабуся казала, що в мене мають бути \"друзі\" мого віку. Говорила про школу в місті...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я не хотіла йти. Я втекла. Вона мене знайшла. Вона не змусила мене йти.\n"
" !think\n"
" ... Можливо, мені варто було бути сміливішою.\n"
" Гаразд, бувайте.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Oh. Weird question, I guess. \n"
" player:\n"
" I was just joking, {name.npc_apothecary}. You know that <i>you're</> my friend, right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I am?? \n"
" player:\n"
" Of course! We share stories, you taught me to garden... You're a tough nut to crack, maybe, but inside--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --is a seed! That grows into a me-plant!\n"
" player:\n"
" Eeeeexactly what I was going to say! And who doesn't want a you-plant?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Someone who likes <i>stale</> people. And stale food. Gross.\n"
" player:\n"
" Gross! Stale people? Pee-ew!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Because I'm rude. Because I'm weird. Because I don't give square flowers. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh I was just kidding, {name.npc_apothecary}. You're a tough nut to crack, maybe, but inside--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --is a seed! That grows into a me-plant!\n"
" player:\n"
" Eeeeexactly what I was going to say! And who doesn't want a you-plant?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Someone who likes <i>stale</> people. And stale food. Gross.\n"
" player:\n"
" Gross! Stale people? Pee-ew!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you have any friends?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" But still... what if I do or say something wrong?\n"
" !scared\n"
" What if... <z 0.7>What if I get left behind again?</>\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I'm just going invisible for a bit. Bye.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "A Hunter's only friends are their weapon and their friends--YES I have friends!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Rude. And to answer you: I'd like to think so. Why do you ask?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Um... what <i>is</> this?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's an Ancient Hunter Friendship Charm!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...<#RED>\"Ancient Hunter Friendship\" Charm</>? \n"
" player:\n"
" Hold it tight, and you'll always have a friend. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" A stick with a pinecone and a dead fly stuck to it with sap is my ugly friend? \n"
" player: \n"
" What? <z 0.7>I worked really hard on that...</> No! It's magic! It will bring you friendship, okay? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...\n"
" !agree\n"
" Actually. I won't go invisible right now."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_apothecary.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I'm going to keep this one a square flower. \n"
" player:\n"
" Hah, sounds good, {name.npc_apothecary}. <z 0.7>Just a beautiful rock I spent ages polishing. But keep it wrapped! What do I care!</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh. And \"thank you.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Hah. You're very welcome! Manners! <i>That's</> new...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> taught me.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> showed me the best eavesdropping spots around camp. And I helped <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> with the flowers he's growing behind the forge...\n"
" player:\n"
" Whoa! Really? Who is this {name.npc_apothecary}? No invisibility or anything!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" It was the <#RED>Ancient Hunter Friendship Charm</>. It really worked. \"Thank you.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" About that... the Charm isn't magic. It was a <i>nice</> \"trick\" to make you be brave. <i>You're welcome.</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" ... Duh.\n"
" player:\n"
" You knew??\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I didn't go to \"school\" but I'm not dumb. You gave me forest trash and said it was magic. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" But thinking about you making it, thinking it was good and it would help me, I knew... I'd already made a friend.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>That's</> what made me feel brave. Knowing you're as weird as me, if not more weird. If anything, I'd abandon you for being too weird.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Just joking! I learned that from you. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" And just like you said, when I hold this charm, I know I'll always have a friend.\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm glad we became friends, {name.npc_apothecary}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Me too. So I made this \"Ancient Forest Baby Friendship Charm\" to help <i>you</> feel brave. <i>You're welcome.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я залишу цю квітку квадратною.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ха, звучить добре, {Name.npc_apothecary}. <z 0.7>Просто гарний камінь, який я довго полірував. Але тримай його загорнутим! Мені яка різниця!</>\n"
"agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" О. І \"дякую\".\n"
"player:\n"
" О! Ха. Будь ласка! Манери! <i>Оце</> щось новеньке...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> навчив мене.\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> показала мені найкращі місця для підслуховування в таборі. А я допомогла <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> з квітами, які він вирощує за кузнею...\n"
"player:\n"
" Ого! Справді? Хто ти така, {Name.npc_apothecary}? І без жодної невидимості!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Це був <#RED>Стародавній талісман дружби мисливця</>. Він справді спрацював. \"Дякую.\"\n"
"player:\n"
" До речі... талісман не магічний. Це був <i>гарний</> \"трюк\", щоб ти стала сміливіше. <i>Будь ласка.</>\n"
"agent:\n"
" ... Та ну.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти знала??\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я не ходила до \"школи\", але я не дурна. Ви дали мені лісове сміття і сказали, що це магія.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Але думаючи про те, як ви це зробили, думаючи, що це добре і допоможе мені, я зрозуміла... у мене вже є друг.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>Це</> і зробило мене сміливішою. Те, що ви такі ж дивні, як і я, якщо не дивніше. Хоча, може, я б покинула вас за те, що ви надто дивні.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ей!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Жартую! Я навчилася цього від вас.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" І як ви казали, коли я тримаю цей талісман, я знаю, що в мене завжди є друг.\n"
"player:\n"
" Я радий, що ми стали друзями, {Name.npc_apothecary}.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Я теж. Тож я зробила цей \"Стародавній дитячий талісман дружби лісу\", щоб допомогти <i>вам</> бути сміливішим. <i>Будь ласка.</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A present? For <i>me?!</> It's even got wrapping paper, and a real bow and <i>everything!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, it's actually for {name.npc_lunn}! Y'know, so that he trusts me...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, that's right! Well he sure does appreciate it. Don't you, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>? \n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha ha ha! Oh <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, their head DOES look like that!\n"
" player:\n"
" My head looks like what now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Haha! Don't worry about it! Here, take this <#RED>{name.armourtools0}</>. With it, I can make your <#RED>armour</> even better than it is now!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" Great! But again: my head looks like what now? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Haha! Don't worry about it! <i>Head</> on over to the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>. There, we can put our extra sparkle on anything!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What are you hiding behind your back, Hunter? You <i>know</> you can't keep a secret from me!\n"
" player:\n"
" You caught me-- I brought you another souvenir from my Hunt!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>Oooooooooh--</> a scarf pin! It looks <i>just</> like the one I lost fending off a <#RED>{name.groak}</> that tried to swallow me whole!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Actually, wait a minute... I think this <i>is</> the scarf pin I jabbed into that <#RED>{name.groak}'s</> gullet! Hilda! You've come back to me!\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait, it's <i>yours?!</> I guess this isn't much of a gift after all...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Are you kidding?! Being reunited with an old friend is the best gift <i>ever!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" You know, I've actually been working on something for you too. Now seems like the perfect time to give it to you!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Що це ви там ховаєте за спиною, Мисливцю? Ви ж <i>знаєте</> — від мене таємниць не сховаєш!\n"
" player:\n"
" Ти мене спіймала... я приніс тобі ще одну дрібничку з полювання!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <i>Оооооох,</> шпилька для шарфа! Виглядає <i>точнісінько</> як моя, яку я встромила в <#RED>{2:{Name.groak}}</>, коли той намагався мене проковтнути!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Хвилиночку... мені здається, це <i>саме</> та шпилька для шарфа, яку я встромила в горло того <#RED>{2:{Name.groak}}</>! Хільдо! Ти повернулася до мене!\n"
" player:\n"
" Що, вона <i>твоя</>?! Виходить, дарунок так собі...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Та ви що! Зустрітися зі старим другом — найкращий подарунок у <i>світі!</>\n"
" !think\n"
" А знаєте... у мене якраз теж щось є для вас. Час подарувати!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Eeeeeeeee! A present!! What do you think it is, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Funny you should mention {name.npc_lunn}-- it's kinda for him, too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" A whetstone! Aww Hunter, you're so sweet! Look <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, it's a whetstone just for you!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" ...Oh. Don't take it like that, I'm sure they weren't trying to imply anything about your sharpness.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Err... sorry, Hunter. I think you're gonna be in <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> bad books for a while.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh?! But I-- all I meant--!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Don't worry, he'll come around. <i>I</> thought it was a lovely gift."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Віііііііі! Це подарунок!! Як думаєш, що це, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Власне, він і для тебе, і для {2:{Name.npc_lunn}}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Точильний камінь! О, Мисливцю, яка ж ви душка! Дивись, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>, точильний камінь — спеціально для тебе!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" ...Ой. Тільки не думай, ніби він натякає на твою тупість...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Е-е, вибачте, Мисливцю. Схоже, ви трохи підпадеше у немилість <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_lunn}}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" Що?! Але я... ж тільки...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Не хвилюйтесь, він відтане. <i>Я</> вважаю, це був чудовий подарунок."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You know, you've done so much for me, Hunter. For all of us, really. You deserve something special every once in a while too!\n"
" !netural\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I had a look at that armour you're getting from {name.npc_market_merchant}. It's great. Too great.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I can upgrade that new {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour all the way to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>, but I can't get your old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} stuff beyond <#RED>Level {max_level_uncommon}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" What can we do?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Weeelllll... I've got an idea! If you help me beef up my sewing kit, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I could really give your armour some pizzazz!\n"
" !think\n"
" With an <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</>, I could upgrade your old armour to {name.i_item_rarity_rare}. I just need some materials.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Lemme put together a list of stuff we'll need!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви стільки для всіх нас зробили, Мисливцю... ви теж заслуговуєте на щось особливе!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я бачила ті обладунки, що ви купили в {2:{Name.npc_market_merchant}}. Вони шикарна. Навіть занадто.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я можу підняти ваші нові {2:{name.i_item_rarity_rare}} обладунки аж до <#RED>{max_level_rare} рівня</>, але старі {2:{name.i_item_rarity_uncommon}} далі <#RED>{max_level_uncommon} рівня</> не витягну.\n"
" player:\n"
" І що робити?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Нууу... є одна ідея! Якщо допоможете мені прокачати мій набір для шиття, ми з <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_lunn}}</> зможемо насправді додати вашим обладункам трішки шарму!\n"
" !think\n"
" Маючи <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</> я б могла зробити зі старих обладунків {2:{name.i_item_rarity_rare}}. Потрібні лише матеріали.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Складу вам списочок речей, які нам знадобляться!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ohmygosh, a back-scratcher! I've always wanted one of these!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> offered to help a few times, <z 0.7>but between you and me, I didn't think that would end well...</> Anyway, I'm gonna call him Balki!\n"
" player:\n"
" You're naming the back-scratcher, too?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Of course! Why not?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(gasp)</> Does he already have a name? How totally inconsiderate of me not to ask!\n"
" player:\n"
" Nope, never mind. Balki's a great name.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Whew-- I was worried for a second there. Thanks Hunter!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" О боже, дряпка для спини! Я завжди мріяла про такий!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> кілька разів пропонував допомогти, <z 0.7>але між нами, я уявила, чим би це закінчилося...</> Отже, назву його Балкі!\n"
" player:\n"
" Ти навіть йому ім'я дала?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" А чому б і ні?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>(зітхає)</> Хоча... може, в нього вже було ім'я? Ох, яка ж я нечемна!\n"
" player:\n"
" Ні-ні, все гаразд. Балкі — чудове ім'я.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Фух, аж камінь з душі. Дякую, Мисливцю!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I suuuuuper recommend it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Я дууууже це рекомендую!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Pretty great, right?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Круто, га?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Ohmygosh, for me? How are you both a totally fearsome Hunter <i>and</> a super sweetie?\n"
" player:\n"
" What about you? You're always so cheerful and confident. How do you do it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh! Well, I just take every bad thing that's happened to me and pack it up into a little box in my brain.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then I take that box, and hide it deep, deep, <i>deeeeep</> down, where I can't think about it anymore. It's like, super easy once you get the hang of it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!bliss\n"
"Ой, це мені? Як ви примудряєтесь бути і грізним Мисливцем, <i>і</> такою душкою?\n"
"player:\n"
"А ти як? Ти завжди така весела й упевнена. Як у тебе це виходить?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!think\n"
"О! Я просто беру всі погані речі, що зі мною траплялись, і складаю їх у маленьку коробочку в голові.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Потім беру ту коробочку і ховаю її глибоко-глибоко, <i>дууууже</> глибоко, щоб більше про це не думати. Воно, знаєте, дуже легко, коли звикнеш!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Neat trick! I'll give it a try!"
msgstr "Класний трюк! Я спробую!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "That's... um..."
msgstr "Це... е-е..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooooh, thanks Hunter! I'll have to open this later, I'm a little busy right now.\n"
" player:\n"
" What's going on?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" We're playing hide and seek! I found <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> here in a snap, but Balki's <i>really</> good at hiding.\n"
" player:\n"
" Balki?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" The back-scratcher you gave me! You didn't forget, did you?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyways, he and <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> have really been getting along. I think it's safe to say you've been forgiven for the whetstone incident.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ha... glad to hear it!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!clap\n"
"Оооо, дякую, Мисливцю! Відкрию пізніше, я зараз трішки зайнята.\n"
"player:\n"
"Що відбувається?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!wavelunn\n"
"Граємо в хованки! Я знайшла <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_lunn}}</> миттєво, а от Балкі ховається <i>просто</> майстерно.\n"
"player:\n"
"Балкі?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Та дряпка для спини, що ви мені подарували! Ви ж не забули?\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Взагалі, вона із <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_lunn}}</> останнім часом чудово ладнають. Думаю, інцидент із точильним каменем вам пробачено.\n"
"player:\n"
"Ха... радий це чути!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I know! I'm really happy for them-- I <i>am!</> But... if <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki start spending all their time together...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Will I become a <i>third wheel?!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!angry\n"
"Знаю! Я дуже рада за них... <i>справді!</> Але... якщо <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> і Балкі почнуть проводити весь час разом...\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Хіба я не стану <i>третьою зайвою?!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ugh, I can't believe I'm saying this, but now isn't the time for gossiping! This is serious!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" If <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki start spending all their time together... Where does that leave me? Will I become a <i>third wheel?!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!angry\n"
"Уф, не вірю, що це кажу, але не час пліткувати! Це серйозно!\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Якщо <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> і Балкі весь час будуть разом... то що буде зі мною? Хіба я не стану <i>третьою зайвою?!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" That {name.i_item_rarity_epic} armour you're getting from {name.npc_market_merchant} is impressive. Like, upgrade to <#RED>Level {max_level_epic}</> impressive.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" With this sewing kit I can only get your old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} stuff to <#RED>Level {max_level_rare}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" What if I made a <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>? With that, I could upgrade your old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} armour to {name.i_item_rarity_epic} <#RED>Level {max_level_epic}</> armour!\n"
" !point\n"
" I'll need a few things... But you can grab them for me!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oooh! I'll write up a list in the <#RED>Armoury</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!dejected\n"
"Ті {2:{name.i_item_rarity_epic}} обладунки від {2:{Name.npc_market_merchant}} — вражають. Прям от до <#RED>{max_level_epic} рівня</> вражають.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"З цим швейним набором я можу підтягти ваші старі {2:{name.i_item_rarity_rare}} лише до <#RED>{max_level_rare} рівня</>.\n"
"!think\n"
"А що як зробити <#RED>{name.armourtools2}</>? Тоді я зможу підняти ваші старі {2:{name.i_item_rarity_rare}} до {4:{name.i_item_rarity_epic}}, аж до <#RED>{max_level_epic} рівня</>!\n"
"!point\n"
"Мені знадобиться кілька речей... Але ви ж їх мені й дістанете!\n"
"!clap\n"
"Ооо! Напишу список в <#RED>манекені для обладунків</>!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh. Thanks Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" Is something wrong? You seem kinda down.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" N-nothing, it's just... it's <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki... they've been getting <i>really</> close. Then just this morning, I saw them...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>Canoodling!</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"О. Дякую, Мисливцю.\n"
"player:\n"
"Щось не так? Ти геть засмучена.\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Н-нічого, просто... це <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> і Балкі... вони стали <i>дуже</> близькими. А сьогодні зранку я бачила як вони...\n"
"!shocked\n"
"<i>Цілувалися!</>"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... I don't think that's possible.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" How can you say that? You don't <i>know!</> What if they get tired of me, and go off on their own? Just like... just like...\n"
" player:\n"
" Just like who?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Oh-- ha ha. What was I saying? Umm, sorry Hunter, I should focus on your armour."
msgstr "player:\n"
"{Name.npc_armorsmith}... не думаю, що це можливо.\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!angry\n"
"Як ви можете так казати? Ви ж <i>не знаєте!</> А раптом вони втомляться від мене й підуть собі удвох? Так само, як... як...\n"
"player:\n"
"Як хто?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!disagree\n"
"Ой... ха-ха. Що це я? Ем, даруйте, Мисливцю, мені слід зосередитись на ваших обладунках."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Your leather cutter and the back-scratcher? Um... good for them?"
msgstr "Твій шкіряний різак і дряпка для спини? Е-е-е... добре для них?"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Ooooh this is <i>juicy!</> Tell me more!"
msgstr "Оооо, це <i>соковито</>! Розкажи мені більше!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks, Hunter. Sorry for acting toootally weird before, I don't know what got into me! But don't worry, I'm feeling all back to normal now!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}... did someone leave you all alone, once?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Wh-what do you mean? I've never been alone, I've <i>always</> had someone by my side.\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean {name.npc_lunn}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" What's so wrong with that? I know people think it's weird-- I've heard the things some folks whisper about me. But you know what? My <i>things</> are always there for me when I need them.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Even you-- it seems like we're friends now, but what happens when this expedition's over? You'll go off to your next adventure and you'll never think about me again.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But all the souvenirs you gave me? <i>Those</> will stay with me. That's the way it always is.\n"
" player:\n"
" I wouldn't do that!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" That's what <i>everyone</> says to your <i>face</>, but they never mean it.\n"
" player:\n"
" So {name.npc_lunn} and Hilda... were they from people who left you behind?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I... th-they... they said they'd be right back... what did I do wrong?\n"
" !angry\n"
" No, I don't wanna think about this stuff! La-la-la-la-- not thinking about it!\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_armorsmith}--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" La-la-la-- sorry, can't hear yooouuuu!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <i>(sniffle)</> Hi Hunter. Thanks for the present.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey. Last time we talked... I'm sorry I stirred up bad memories for you.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No, it's... it's okay. Well, I mean it's <i>not</>, but... maybe it's okay if I don't always pretend I'm okay. You know?\n"
" player:\n"
" I think so. Wanna talk about it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ha. Not really. I think... I need to let myself have these feelings first, before I let them out to anyone else. Maybe one day I'll be ready to talk about it with someone, but... not today.\n"
" player:\n"
" If that day ever comes, I'll be there.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Yeah... I actually think you will."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"<i>(схлип)</> Привіт, Мисливцю. Дякую за подарунок.\n"
"player:\n"
"Привіт. Востаннє... хочу вибачитись за ті погані спогади.\n"
"agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!disagree\n"
"Ні, все... все гаразд. Тобто <i>не все</>, але... мабуть, це нормально... не завжди удавати, що все гаразд. Розумієте?\n"
"player:\n"
"Гадаю, так. Хочеш поговорити?\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Ха. Поки ні. Думаю... спершу мені треба дозволити собі це відчути, перш ніж комусь розповідати. Може, колись я буду готова поговорити з кимось, але... не сьогодні.\n"
"player:\n"
"Якщо настане той день — я буду поруч.\n"
"agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Так... Мені справді здається, що будете."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_armorsmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I appreciate the thought Hunter, but you know... I've started to realize that maybe I don't need <i>things</> as much as I thought I did...\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Oh-- haha, don't worry <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, of <i>course</> I wasn't talking about <i>you!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" Heh... I guess some things never change.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Yeah. You know, I was thinking about it... even the best of friends can't be with each other <i>all</> the time. So I had a great idea-- I made a souvenir for <i>you!</>\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Your own loveable, huggable, travel-sized <#BLUE>mini-Berna</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(gasp!)</> What's that, mini-Berna? I'm the coolest, best-looking Hunter you've ever met?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ohmygosh mini-Berna, you can't just <i>say</> stuff like that! People are gonna <i>talk!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Throw yer own trash out. \n"
" player:\n"
" \"Trash\"?! What? No! It's a souvenir from my Hunt!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" A souvenir? What are ye givin' it ta me for?\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... You said it would prove me worthy of your weapon upgrading skills?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, that <i>does</> have me ring to it...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Fine. Me <#RED>smithing tools</> an' forge'll give extra <i>oompf</i> to yer weapons.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" All ye've gotta do is go out into the wilds an' get the materials I need.\n"
" !point\n"
" Cannae upgrade squat with faerie wishes an' unicorn promises, can I? \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Of ye go... Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this s'posed ta be? Some wee scrap o' fabric?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a bookmark! {name.npc_armorsmith} tells me you're something of a reader? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Err... not sure where she got that from. <z 0.7><i>Wish she'd sew her darn mouth shut that one.</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. But wasn't it your novel she found? With two hammers kissing on the cover--?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...Let's stop talking. Aye?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph. Must've cleared all the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> out o' the <#BLUE>Rotwood</> if ye've got time ta pester me with this.\n"
" player:\n"
" Aw c'mon! I think deep down you like when I bring you souvenirs.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Bah. Ye dinnae know a thing about me.\n"
" player:\n"
" Now why do you think that is, Mr. Doesn't-Open-Up?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Feh. Mind yer own forge. That's what I always say. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" To meself."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hmph. Dinnae mean ta... Y'know I'm not a talker and the like, but...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Look. If ye ever need ta sit in silence with someone... ye know where I am."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Yer made of harder steel than I thought.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But if ye ever need ta sit in silence with someone... ye know where I am."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.FORTIFY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" ...Aye. There's work ta be done.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Trouble is, I left a lot o' me <#RED>smithing tools</> behind when we set out for this expedition. \n"
" !point\n"
" If'n ye help me make a new set of <#RED>{name.weapontools1}</>, I could reforge yer old {name.i_item_rarity_uncommon} weapons ta be {name.i_item_rarity_rare}.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I'll need more materials to make 'em. Check the <#RED>Weapon Racks</> fer a list.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ooh, sounds great... but why'd you leave those tools behind in the first place?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I had ta leave in a bit of a... hurry, ye see. Let's leave it at that."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Awright. Give <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}'s</> weapon here.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Y'know, Hunter. Ye can tell me if'n me weapons are failin' ye out in the wilds...  \n"
" player:\n"
" What?! They're great, {name.npc_blacksmith}. Why do you ask?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, ye've got that thousand-yard stare goin'. Somethin's weighin' on ye... \n"
" player:\n"
" Well, well, well... Look who's prying <i>now</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hmph. Mindin' yer own forge... I gotta respect that. \n"
" !think\n"
" Just figured... the pressure ye've been under... what with the whole <#BLUE>Rotwood</> dependin' on ye 'n' all...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Och, never ye mind."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, right, the pressure. I'd <i>almost</> forgotten. THANKS."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Pressure? Heh. I eat pressure for breakfast."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter... why do ye keep doin' this?\n"
" player:\n"
" What, don't you like cool souvenirs from my adventures?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What are ye hopin' ta get out of it? With the type I ran with back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>, nothing came without strings attached.\n"
" player:\n"
" Err... what 'type' did you run with, exactly?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Before joinin' <i>this</> merry crew?  Hmph... I s'pose there's no harm in tellin' ye that much...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was a member o' the Blacksmith's Guild. If ye wanna set up shop in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>, 'tis all but required.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" The Guild looks out fer its own. If a member has a pesky 'problem', the Guild sees it... 'taken care of'.\n"
" !point\n"
" But ye always have ta pay yer dues. If ye don't, ye might find <i>yerself</> becoming a 'problem'.\n"
" player:\n"
" That sounds ominous...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" They're a rough bunch, to be sure. But if ye've got wits enough ta keep yer head down and trust no one, ye can do alright for yerself.\n"
" player:\n"
" So what made you leave?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I s'pose I let me wits dull a bit over time. A mistake.\n"
" Hmph. S'enough chat fer now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"  !neutral\n"
"  !gesture\n"
"  Мисливцю... Чому ви все це робите?\n"
"player:\n"
"  Що, тобі не подобаються круті сувеніри з моїх пригод?\n"
"agent:\n"
"  !neutral\n"
"  !think\n"
"  А чого ви сподіваєтесь цим досягти? З тими, з ким я працював в <#BLUE>Брінкс</>, всі мали подвійне дно.\n"
"player:\n"
"  Е-е... з яким 'типом' ти водився?\n"
"agent:\n"
"  !neutral\n"
"  !think\n"
"  До того, як приєднався до <i>цієї</> веселої компанії? Хм... Думаю, не буде шкоди, якщо скажу...\n"
"  !gesture\n"
"  Я був у Гільдії ковалів. Якщо хочеш мати кузню в <#BLUE>Брінкс</>, це практично обов'язково.\n"
"  !gruffnod\n"
"  Гільдія піклується про своїх. Якщо в когось виникає 'проблема', Гільдія її... 'вирішує'.\n"
"  !point\n"
"  Але завжди треба платити внески. Якщо ні — можеш <i>сам</> стати 'проблемою'.\n"
"player:\n"
"  Звучить моторошно...\n"
"agent:\n"
"  !neutral\n"
"  !point\n"
"  Вони, звісно, груба компанія. Але якщо маєш розум, щоб тримати голову низько і нікому не довіряти — проживеш.\n"
"player:\n"
"  То чому ти пішов?\n"
"agent:\n"
"  !neutral\n"
"  !closedeyes\n"
"  ...Гадаю, з часом я розслабився й втратив пильність. Помилка.\n"
"  Гмпф. Досить балачок на сьогодні."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hmph. Ye should be thinkin' less about bringin' me souvenirs, and more about keepin' yerself safe out there.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye were lookin' a mite banged-up last time <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> dragged ye back ta camp.\n"
" player:\n"
" Aww, have you been worrying about me?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt}... No. Maybe. <z 0.7>A little...</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Bring a good {name.i_item_rarity_epic} weapon when ye go out there, ye ken? And armour, too! Don't want ye bein' a meal for the worms.\n"
" player:\n"
" I knew you had a soft side under that grumpy exterior!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...Don't ye go tellin' anyone. I mean it.\n"
" player:\n"
" I promise, your secret's safe with me!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. It'd better be. Ye know I dinnae take givin' away me secrets lightly.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Hunter... Somethin' you <i>could</i> fetch me...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" With some <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</>, I could upgrade yer old {name.i_item_rarity_rare} gear so it's not so laggard.\n"
" !agree\n"
" All I need from ye are a few raw materials. A win-win, aye?\n"
" player:\n"
" Thanks for thinking of me {name.npc_blacksmith}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Aye, err... Doing what's best for the {name_multiple.foxtails}, is all."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Хм. Вам слід менше думати про сувеніри для мене, і більше про власну безпеку.\n"
" !point\n"
" Востаннє <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> ледве притягнув вас назад у табір.\n"
"player:\n"
" Оу, ти що, хвилювався за мене?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt}... Ні. Може. <z 0.7>Трохи...</>\n"
" !angry\n"
" Беріть добру {3:{name.i_item_rarity_epic}} зброю коли підете, гаразд? І обладунки теж! Не хочу, щоб ви стали обідом для черв'яків.\n"
"player:\n"
" Я знав, що під цією буркотливою зовнішністю ти добрий!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...Тільки нікому не кажіть. Я серйозно.\n"
"player:\n"
" Обіцяю, твій секрет у безпеці зі мною!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хм. Так і має бути. Я не люблю роздавати свої секрети.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Мисливцю... Є щось, що ви <i>могли б</i> для мене дістати...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Отримавши <#RED>{name.weapontools2}</> я зможу покращити вашу стару {3:{name.i_item_rarity_rare}} зброю, щоб вона не відставала.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Все, що треба — трохи матеріалів. Обоє виграємо, га?\n"
"player:\n"
" Дякую, що дбаєш про мене, {Name.npc_blacksmith}.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Та-а... Я ж тільки заради {Name_multiple.foxtails} стараюсь."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Och, another-- wait... is this...?\n"
" player:\n"
" A new book! Well, not 'new' exactly, I found it on my Hunt.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>'A Royal Welding'</>, fourth book in the Forged Bonds Saga... this hasnae been in print since the eruption...!\n"
" player:\n"
" A-are you okay? Are you mad? If you don't like it--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" No! {name.blacksmith_grunt} Err, no. It's... actually... one o' me favourites...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Erm... Thanks, Hunter. This is... very thoughtful of ye.\n"
" player:\n"
" I gotta say, you have unexpected tastes in books.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmph. Well. I wasn't the one reading 'em ta start with-- but she'd leave 'em around the shop, and one day I got curious...\n"
" player:\n"
" 'She'?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! Slip o' the tongue. Just forget it, aye?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I have work that needs doin'. See ye round, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ох, ще один... почекай... Це що...?\n"
"player:\n"
" Нова книга! Ну, не зовсім 'нова', я знайшов її на полюванні.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <i>'Королівське зварювання'</>, четверта книга з саги 'Ковані Узи'... її ж не друкують відтоді, як сталося виверження...!\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти... ти впорядку? Ти не злишся? Якщо тобі не подобається...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ні! {name.blacksmith_grunt} Тобто, ні. Це... насправді... одна з моїх улюблених...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ем... Дякую, Мисливцю. Це... дуже уважно з твого боку.\n"
"player:\n"
" Не чекав від тебе таких літературних смаків.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Хм. Ну... Спершу це була не моя книжка... але вона залишала їх у кузні, і одного дня я зацікавився...\n"
"player:\n"
" 'Вона'?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ах! Обмовився. Просто забудь, гаразд?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...У мене робота. Побачимось, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Aren't ye?!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Хіба ні?!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Do I?!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Та невже?!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this here-- an oil lamp? Haven't seen one o' these since the old days.\n"
" player:\n"
" I know you like to read at night. I thought this would help!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Aye. It will. Thanks, Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey {name.npc_blacksmith}... who is the 'she' you mentioned before?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...I thought I told ye ta forget about that.\n"
" player:\n"
" I know, but--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ye just can't keep yerself from pryin' into me business, can ye?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I know what yer tryin' ta do, Hunter. Butterin' me up, hopin' I'll let something slip-- somethin' ye can use against me..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" А це що... лампа? Давненько я таких не бачив.\n"
"player:\n"
" Я знаю, ти любиш читати вночі. Думав, що це допоможе!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Ага. Допоможе. Дякую, Мисливцю.\n"
"player:\n"
" Гей, {Name.npc_blacksmith}... а хто та 'вона', про яку ти згадував?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...Я ж казав забути про це.\n"
"player:\n"
" Я знаю, але...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ви ніяк не можеш не лізти в мої справи, га?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Я знаю, що ви задумали, Мисливцю. Підлещуєтесь, сподіваєтесь, що я щось бовкну... щось, що можна використати проти мене..."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...No. Yer right. Sorry, Hunter. Went a bit off me head there.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's okay. Maybe instead of talking, we could... share the silence?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" Heh. Aye. I'd like that.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "W-wait, that's not what I'm trying to do at all!"
msgstr "П-почекай, я зовсім не це мав на увазі!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Come on, you know that's not true."
msgstr "Та годі, ти ж знаєш, що це неправда."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks, Hunter. I've been thinkin', maybe it's time I fessed up.\n"
" !think\n"
" Ye know... ye remind me of her sometimes. My Billie. Brave as a lion, and stubborn as an ox.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We weren't related by blood-- I took her on as an apprentice when I was settin' up me forge out in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. But she was the closest thing ta family I ever had.\n"
" player:\n"
" What happened to her?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Och. Sold me out to the Blacksmith's Guild, the wee bampot!\n"
" player:\n"
" WHAT?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye. Business had started ta pick up. She'd started showin' an interest in organizin' the ledgers. Fool that I am, I thought nothin' of it.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, one day the Guild comes a-knockin'. Turns out <i>someone</> had been doctorin' the books, cheatin' the Guild out of their cut o' me forge's profits. And the paper trail all led back ta me.\n"
" player:\n"
" So what did you do?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I high-tailed it out o' there as fast as me legs would carry me!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lucky fer me, I found this little expedition plannin' on flying out ta <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> was lookin' fer a blacksmith, and I figured it was the perfect way ta lie low while I waited for the heat ta die down.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow... I'm starting to get why you don't open up easily.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Aye. 'Tis a funny thing, though... when I think about Billie, cheatin' the Guild, doctorin' the ledger right under me nose, takin' over the forge fer herself, I can't help but feel--\n"
" player:\n"
" Angry? Betrayed? Hungry for vengeance?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Proud.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh?!?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Don't get me wrong, I'm also hoppin' mad about it! But at the end o' the day, my Billie knew what she wanted, and outsmarted the lot of us ta get it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" T'was ruthless, aye-- but that's exactly what ye need ta survive in the Guild. She's gonna go far, that one.\n"
" player:\n"
" That's one way to look at it, I guess.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. I dinnae expect ye ta fully understand. It was good bein' able ta talk about her again, though. Thanks, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Дякую, Мисливцю. Я подумав... мабуть, час зізнатися.\n"
" !think\n"
" Знаєте... ви інколи нагадуєте мені її. Мою Біллі. Хоробра, як лев, і вперта, як віл.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ми не були ріднею... я взяв її в учні, коли відкрив кузню в <#BLUE>Брінкс</>. Але вона була найріднішею мені душею, яку я коли-небудь мав.\n"
"player:\n"
" Що з нею сталося?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Ох. Продала мене Гільдії ковалів, ця дрібна зрадниця!\n"
"player:\n"
" ЩО?!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ага. Бізнес почав іти вгору. Вона зацікавилась бухгалтерією. Дурний я, нічого не підозрював.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" І от якось прийшла Гільдія. Виявилось, <i>хтось</> підробляв книги, недоплачував їхню частку прибутку. І вся паперова доріжка вела до мене.\n"
"player:\n"
" І що ти зробив?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Вислизнув звідти, як тільки міг!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" На щастя, ця експедиція саме збиралась у <#BLUE>Ротвуд</>. <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> шукав коваля, і я подумав, що це гарна нагода залягти на дно, поки не стихне шум.\n"
"player:\n"
" Вау... Тепер я розумію, чому ти не любиш відкриватися.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ага. Хоча... кумедна річ. Думаючи про Біллі, як вона обдурила Гільдію, підробляла книги в мене під носом, відібрала кузню собі, я не можу не відчувати...\n"
"player:\n"
" Злість? Зраду? Жагу помсти?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Гордість.\n"
"player:\n"
" Що?!?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Не зрозумій мене неправильно — я й досі злюсь! Але врешті-решт, моя Біллі знала, чого хотіла, і перехитрила нас усіх, щоб того досягти.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Безжально, так. Але саме це й треба, щоб вижити в Гільдії. Вона далеко піде.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ну... це своєрідний погляд.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Хе. Не очікую, що ви зрозумієте. Але добре було знову поговорити про неї. Дякую, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Aye. <i>Sure</> ye are. Careful as a bull in a china shop."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ага. <i>Звісно</>. Обережні, як бик у крамниці з порцеляною."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> I'm gonna go gray at this rate, mark me words."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <i>(зітхає)</> Посивію я з вами, от побачите."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hunter... I know yer heart's in the right place, but I'm runnin' outta space ta put all these souvenirs.\n"
" !point\n"
" Just keep yer wits about ye while out on yer Hunts, and come back safe. That's the best gift ye could give me."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Мисливцю... Я знаю, ваші наміри добрі, але в мене вже не лишається місця для всіх цих сувенірів.\n"
" !point\n"
" Просто повертайся живим зі своїх полювань. Це найкращий подарунок для мене."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well, anyway... I'd best get back ta the forge--\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait a minute, what's that you're hiding behind your back?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Urk--! Ah. Well... 'tis a silly thing, really, pay no mind...\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Och, <i>fine</>, take it! Just don't go showin' it around, ye ken?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Who me? I'm <i>always</> careful!"
msgstr "Хто, я? Я ж <i>завжди</> обережний!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_blacksmith.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Aw, come on! Life-threatening danger makes Hunts fun!"
msgstr "Та ну! Небезпека для життя робить полювання цікавим!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Aw shucks! A gift for this old bag of bones some thought to leave in the cold? That's mighty thoughtful of you, Hunter.\n"
" player:\n"
" I've been meaning to ask: what happened before we found you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ah well, I had a crew--or group or what have you--I was cookin' for, sendin' what I could back to my poor ailin' ma, all alone in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. \n"
" !angry\n"
" Well, I guess my compatriots got to figurin' they could enrich themselves if'n they cut me loose and kept my share of the findings!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Tsk. Stabbed me in the back, they did. Horrible. Terrible! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" (sniffle) And to think of my poor ma, alone--and sick--as she was! And she bein' the one who fostered my love of cookery and some such, too! Oh!\n"
" player:\n"
" That's awful, {name.npc_cook}! I'm so glad we found you when we did.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" As am I, sure as sugar! Say... You've been so welcomin', Hunter, I'm gonna whip up a batch of new, extra <#RED>Special</> recipes for ya!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'll even rotate through new <#RED>Specials</> to keep things fresh. So if you see somethin' you want, get it while it's hot, y'hear? Hoo-whee!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yup! Her joints would make this poppin' sound, uh, when she danced! Oh, and how 'pops' loved to dance. Joint's a-poppin' away into the night...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well anyways, you've probably got lots of important Hunter stuff to do. I'll let you mosey on on to it, then."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I swear on my family cookbook, it's the honest truth! She had these poppin' joints! 'Pop-pop-pop' they'd go, as she danced the night away...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyways, you've probably got lots of important Hunter stuff to do. I'll let you mosey on on to it, then."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Well gosh if it ain't my favourite Hunter, swingin' by with another thoughtful souvenir!\n"
" !wave\n"
" Thank ya kindly! Take care now!\n"
" player:\n"
" Actually, I was curious... what was your favourite recipe to make growing up?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm... um... that sure is a toughie... y'know, good ol' pops taught me so many tasty family recipes I don't reckon I can pick a favourite!\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait, I thought you said your <i>ma</> taught you how to cook? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Did I... ? I mean, I did, but, uh, 'pops' was just, er... a fun nickname we used to call her!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Oh, that makes perfect sense!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Riiigghhtt..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-another souvenir? Wow. You're really makin' a habit of this 'bein' nice' thing, huh?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Matter of fact, this whole camp is awfully friendly... The other day that <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> just <i>gave</> me a fire-retardant hair net she'd made... \n"
" !think\n"
" Then that <#BLUE>{name.job_dojo}</> guy fixed a wheel on my cart without me askin'! And <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> lit my grill! <z 0.7> Not like <i>that</>. Not sayin' he couldn't, though...</> \n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's with you guys? What's your angle, huh, bub? \n"
" player:\n"
" No angle. You're part of the team. We help one another like that!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oookaaaay... Hm. I won't let my guard down, so don't think of trying anything, alright, bub?\n"
" player:\n"
" O-of course. We weren't going to 'try anything.' Also--is your voice different all of a sudden?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Well now, who's a-gettin' a-suspicious of a-who, now? I reckon' you oughta get your listenin' holes checked!\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry! Must be hard to trust again, with your old team betraying you...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Yup! That's exactly what's happenin' here. \n"
" player:\n"
" I'll do all I can to make sure you know you can feel safe and secure here.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Really? Er, I mean, aw, shucks, don't you worry your pretty little head none, hun."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Aw now Hunter, don't be embarrassed! I love every souvenir you bring me--even the defective ones!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't you worry your little head about it, Hunter. I love every souvenir you bring me--even the defective ones!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Boy howdy! What a lovely... um...\n"
" player:\n"
" Colander?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" --Colander! Was on the tip of my tongue, ha ha!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Shame it's got all these little holes, though. It woulda made a mighty fine soup bowl."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I think it's actually <i>supposed</> to have those holes."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Oh no!! How did I not notice?!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" SUNNUVAGUN THAT SMARTS--! Oh, ah, sorry Hunter, just things get so dang hot when you take them outta the hot hole place!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Another gift? Why you shouldn't have--a mitten? Uh, I don't mean to be an Ungrateful Uma, but my problem is with the <i>heat,</> not the cold.\n"
" player:\n"
" It's an <i>oven mitt!</> For taking hot things out of the oven? Y'know... your exact problem? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Uh, right. O-of course. \"Oven mitt\"...\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}... you don't actually know anything about cooking, do you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Well I <i>never!</> Just cuz I don't know the names of fancy cookin' tools, or what ingredients are, or how recipes work...\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh! This is because I didn't go to yer fancy cookin' college, isn't it? It's because I learnt all I learnt from my pops--er, who is my ma--is that right?? <z 0.7>(<i>Is</> that right?)\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}. If you're not a {name.job_cook}, you can tell me. I won't be mad. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (sigh) Ya got me. I ain't a {name.job_cook}. I figured y'all would leave me in the cold if'n I didn't have no use in your Camp, Hunter.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" It's why I was left behind by my old crew, in fact. I was just gettin' too old to keep up. \n"
" player:\n"
" That's not how we do things here, {name.npc_cook}. I promise you that.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wow. You really mean it, don't you?\n"
" !think\n"
" Well, in thanks, I'd like to stay on and keep cookin' for ya. I really think I'm gettin' the hang of it! \n"
" !point\n"
" Matter o' fact, I just heard about this new thing called \"oven mitt.\" Gonna change the game, I reckon! Hoo-whee! \n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Oh, and I know it ain't much, but... here. Consider it a thank-you present for bein' so legitimately, actually, and truly kind-hearted, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ЧОРТ ЗАБЕРИ, ЯК БОЛЯЧЕ...! Ой, е-е, перепрошую, Мисливцю, просто вони так страшенно розігріваються, коли ви дістаєте їх із тієї гарячої дірки!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ще один подарунок? Вам не слід було… рукавиця? Ем, я не хочу бути невдячною, але моя проблема — це <i>жар</>, а не холод.\n"
"player:\n"
" Це ж <i>кухонна рукавиця!</> Для того, щоб діставати гаряче з духовки? Ну… у тебе ж саме така проблема?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" А! Ем, так. Звісно. \"Кухонна рукавиця\"…\n"
"player:\n"
" {Name.npc_cook}… ти взагалі не знаєш нічого про готування, так?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ну, я <i>ніколи б не подумала!</> Просто тому, що я не знаю назв цих ваших модних кухонних штук, або що таке інгредієнти, або як працюють рецепти…\n"
" !point\n"
" О! Це тому, що я не ходила у ваше елітне кулінарне училище, так?! Це тому, що я навчилась усьому від свого тата... ем, який насправді моя мама... чи як це?!\n"
" <z 0.7>(<i>Як</> це сказати вірно?)</>\n"
"player:\n"
" {Name.npc_cook}. Якщо ти не {name.job_cook}, ти можеш сказати мені. Я не буду злий.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (зітхає) Ви мене викрили. Я не {name.job_cook}. Я думала, що ви залишите мене, якщо я не матиму користі у вашому таборі, Мисливцю.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Мене колись так само залишила моя стара команда. Я просто стала занадто старою, щоб встигати за ними.\n"
"player:\n"
" Це не так у нас. Я тобі це обіцяю.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ого. Ви справді це серйозно, так?\n"
" !think\n"
" Що ж, на подяку я хочу залишитися й готувати для вас. Думаю, я вже починаю розумітися!\n"
" !point\n"
" Ба більше - я щойно дізналася про цю штуку під назвою \"кухонна рукавиця\". Це змінить гру, от побачите! Ху-ху!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" О, і хоч це небагато… ось. Вважайте це подарунком за те, що ви справді, по-справжньому добрі, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Well... it was a long time ago. When ya grow up, ya come to see there's only one kinda 'worth' what means anythin'. Especially in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sentiment won't keep ya fed."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yeah. When ya grow up, ya come to see there's only one kinda 'worth' what means anythin'. Especially in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sentiment won't keep ya fed."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Howdy, Hunter! Another gift? And it's a little wooden carvin' of a blimp!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Gosh, now this takes me back... Reminds of my family--my <i>actual</> family, mind you. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" You wouldn't mind if an old woman yammered on about her past fer a bit?\n"
" player:\n"
" Of course not!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" (Noticed ya didn't object to the \"old\" part but okay) I had a ma <i>and</> a pa, as well as five sisters, back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Poor as the dirt we clawed our livin' from, we were. Ma 'n' pa worked fer well-to-dos who did business with folks in <#BLUE>the Capital</>. \n"
" !laugh\n"
" Sisters 'n' me dreamt of seein' it one day. \"By blimp!\" the youngest, Marigold, would chirp. Heh. <z 0.7>Silly little goose.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Anyway, this reminds me of those innocent times, Hunter. Times of silly little dreams. Hm. I appreciate it."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I think that's really sweet."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's harsh but we've all gotta grow up sometime."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Is this--?\n"
" player:\n"
" A dried marigold flower! I remembered you said you had a sister named 'Marigold' so I thought...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hunter... I never... I never got somethin' so kind before. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" My ma and pa worked for a fancy family in the kitchen, and they'd bring home leftovers--that was all we had to eat. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" From a young age, my sisters 'n' me learnt we had to work to earn our food. Whoever brought in the most, ate the most. \"Thems <#BLUE>the Brinks</>,\" pa'd say. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" We were ruthless with each other. Cheatin'. Stealin'. Sabotagin'. I'm ashamed to say it now but... I was the best. So I ate the best. \n"
" !agree\n"
" But I <i>always</> split my take with the youngest, Marigold. She couldn't earn much, y'know? She was too little, the silly goose.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" (sniffle) Thank ya, Hunter. I... I don't know what to say. Truly.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Take this. It ain't much, I know, but, I ain't used to such kindness, Hunter. \n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-another gift? Sheesh, Hunter. I'm just plum embarrassed at this point.\n"
" player:\n"
" What? Don't be! You give us so much! Your spirit, your energy...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !\n"
" My food...\n"
" player:\n"
" ... Yeah. That... too.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" When I was younger, my ma and pa got fired for \"stealin'\" leftovers--food the fancy-pants people weren't even gonna eat! \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Then it was up to me 'n' my sisters to provide entirely. \n"
" !think\n"
" Dreamin' of <#BLUE>The Capital</>, Marigold 'n' me took up venturin' into <#BLUE>The Rotwood</> fer <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Not a bad racket if'n ya can hack it. Marigold 'n' me, we hacked it pretty good, mind. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" But as the years went on, we lost a sister here, a sister there... pretty soon, it was down to just Marigold 'n' me to provide. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, {name.npc_cook}. I'm so sorry. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Aw, s'alright. Some was natural. Some brought it on themselves. It's the nature of the world, Hunter. Cruelty and loss... \n"
" !point\n"
" ... Though <i>you</> have me thinkin' otherwise these days, heh. Warmin' an old gal's frozen heart. Thanks, Hunter.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" This souvenir... is it a wolf's tooth? How \"ay-pro-pow,\" as the fancy pants say it.\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'see, more recently, it came down to my sister Marigold 'n' I to provide for our aged ma and pa. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But to make enough fer our family, we couldn't just accept our fair share of the hauls. We, uh, we had to resort to some of our 'old ways'...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Don't like tellin' ya this, but we was dishonest to folks we ventured into <#BLUE>The Rotwood</> with. We'd tell fibs, sow discord--create chaos, 'n' the like...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" We'd have the group tearin' each other apart with suspicion and anger, while we made off with the haul.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Gosh, I shouldn't laugh. Old habits, y'know. Well, this last expedition, it was supposed to go the same. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But Marigold, that silly goose, she turned into a vicious wolf overnight. Seems I was becomin' a burden myself, at my age. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" She saw her opportunity and by gum she took it! She left me in the cold, and took the haul fer herself. \n"
" player:\n"
" Marigold?? No!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I taught her good, seems to me. Good as I knew how, then. \n"
" player:\n"
" But aren't you mad? She stabbed you in the back and left you for dead!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Mad? No, no, no. Well, actually, yes. But your kindness has shown me somethin': I can't be mad at a wolf for huntin' a little old rabbit, now can I? \n"
" !think\n"
" When it's in its nature to do so? When that's all it's been taught? The only way it knows how to be safe? \n"
" player:\n"
" Hm. I suppose not. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm just grateful I got a chance to learn a different way, Hunter. From you. Thanks... fer takin' a chance on a wolf in old lady's clothin'."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Цей сувенір... це ікло вовка? Як це там кажуть розумники - \"якраз доречно\".\n"
" !think\n"
" Бачите, останнім часом ми з моєю сестрою Маріґолд мусили забезпечувати наших стареньких батьків.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Але щоб прогодувати сім’ю, нам було мало просто брати свою чесну частку здобичі. Ми, е-е, вдалися до наших \"старих методів\"...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Не дуже хочу вам це казати, але ми були нечесними з іншими, з якими ходили в <#BLUE>Ротвуд</>. Брехали, сіяли розбрат - створювали хаос і все таке...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ми змушували групу розриватися від підозр і злості, поки самі тікали зі здобиччю.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ой, не варто було сміятися. Старі звички, знаєте. Отже, остання вилазка мала пройти так само.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Але Маріґолд, та дурненька гуска, за ніч обернулася на лютого вовка. Схоже, я й сама стала для неї тягарем у моєму віці.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Вона побачила свій шанс і, чорт забирай, скористалася ним! Вона кинула мене напризволяще і забрала всю здобич собі.\n"
"player:\n"
" Маріґолд?? Не може бути!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я її добре навчила, виходить. Як уміла на той час.\n"
"player:\n"
" Але ти не злишся? Вона зрадила тебе і кинула помирати!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Злюся? Ні-ні-ні. Хоча, якщо чесно, так. Але твоя доброта показала мені дещо: я не можу злитися на вовка за те, що він полює на старого кролика, правда?\n"
" !think\n"
" Коли це його природа? Коли його так навчили? Коли це єдиний спосіб для нього вижити?\n"
"player:\n"
" Хм. Гадаю, що так.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я просто вдячна, що отримала шанс навчитися іншого, Мисливцю. Від тебе. Дякую... що ризикнули і повірили у вовка в одежі старої жінки."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_cook.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thanks fer the souvenir, Hunter, but I'll open it on the road. I don't rightly belong here with y'all nice folk. \n"
" player:\n"
" But <i>you're</> nice folk! You're done with the bad stuff... right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm done with the backstabbin' 'n' treachery, that's true. However, there's one final thing I've yet to come clean with...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I've been poisonin' your food, Hunter!\n"
" player:\n"
" Aw, c'mon! That's a harsh way to talk about your... \"unique\" flavour profiles!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Huh? That's not--what'dya mean--??\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Nevermind all that--No! Since I started cookin' for ya, I've been addin' bits o' <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> to yer meals!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I been tryin' ta give ya <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-poisonin' so I could incapacitate ya and make off with yer haul!\n"
" !think\n"
" But as we got ta know one another, and I got ta know the folks you surround yourself with, well...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Guess I've gone soft. Like the plates o' veggies I leave in the sun until they're nice 'n' gooey 'n' stinky 'n' ready ta be served...\n"
" player:\n"
" Ew, what?! Now <i>that</> will poison me...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" You've changed me fer the better, Hunter, <i>and</> given me a new passion for cookery! \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Y'see, cookery is the <i>opposite</> of backstabbin'--why, it's front-stuffin'! So I'm hittin' the road to make good with what time I got left.\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_cook}, please stay! The {name.konjur} you've \"poisoned\" my meals with gives me powers!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" R-really? Ya mean it? Aw, Hunter! You're a saint, I tell ya! A \"bone-a-fined\" saint, as they say! \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here--I was gonna sell this to buy a weapon for revengin' on Marigold, but I'm over all that. \n"
" !laugh\n"
" It's yours, Hunter, along with my pledge to keep poisonin' yer food--just how you like it!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Дякую за сувенір, Мисливцю, але відкрию його в дорозі. Я тут не дуже вписуюсь серед таких хороших істот, як ви.\n"
"player:\n"
" Та ти ж <i>і є</> хороша істота! Ти ж покінчила з усім поганим... правда?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" З підступами й зрадою - так, покінчила. Але є ще одна річ, у якій я не зізналася...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Я труїла твою їжу, Мисливцю!\n"
"player:\n"
" Та годі! Це жорстко сказано про твої... \"унікальні\" смаки!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Що? Це не... що ви маєте на увазі...??\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Та забудьте... ні! Відтоді як я почала готувати для вас, я додавала трохи <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</> у ваші страви!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я намагалася викликати у вас отруєння <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</>, щоб знешкодити вас і утекти з вашою здобиччю!\n"
" !think\n"
" Але коли ми краще познайомилися, і я побачила інших поруч із вами, то...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Схоже, я розм'якшала. Як ті тарілки з овочами, які я лишаю на сонці, поки вони не стануть м’які, смердючі й готові до подачі...\n"
"player:\n"
" Фу, що?! Ось <i>це</> мене точно отруїть...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви змінили мене на краще, Мисливцю, <i>і</> дали мені нову пристрасть до кулінарії!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Бачите, кулінарія - це <i>протилежність</> підступам: це ж нагодовування! Тож я вирушаю в дорогу, щоб виправити все, поки маю час.\n"
"player:\n"
" {Name.npc_cook}, будь ласка, залишайся! Той {name.konjur}, яким ти \"отруювала\" мою їжу, дає мені сили!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" С-справді? Ви серйозно? Ох, Мисливцю! Та ви святі, кажу вам! Як то кажуть, \"справжнісінький\" святий!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ось... я хотіла продати це, щоб купити зброю для помсти Маріголд, але з цим покінчено.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Воно ваше, Мисливцю, разом із моєю обіцянкою й далі \"отруювати\" вашу їжу... саме так, як вам подобається!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Better luck next time, kid. Tell you what, here's a little consolation prize for ya."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" Is that so? Sounds like I've been going easy on you. I'll keep that in mind!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" In the meantime, here's a little something to keep you motivated."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's this? An apple for the teacher?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's a souvenir from my Hunt. I thought you'd like it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, now! Trying to get on my good side, are you?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You know that's not gonna get you out of running drills, right?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "<i>(sigh)</> It was worth a shot, at least."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Please. I'm not afraid of anything you throw at me."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" An idealist, huh? Well, I guess I was young and full of fire once. I won't hold it against ya."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" So how about you focus on your job, and I'll focus on mine?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks kid, you shouldn't have--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... are you sure you're okay?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I'm fine! Don't go worrying about me.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" In fact, you should be grateful I've got this old cough. Otherwise I'd be out there taking down the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> myself, and you'd be out of a job."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "'Job'? I volunteered to come here!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Fair point."
msgstr "Справедливо."

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. All these souvenirs are almost makin' me miss being out there myself. I wonder how much it's changed since the early days...\n"
" player: \n"
" I've heard rumours... were you really part of the first Hunting party after the eruption?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Kid, I <i>led</> that Hunting party.\n"
" player:\n"
" What?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hey, don't sound so surprised! I was <#BLUE>the Rotwood's</> top Hunter back in the day. Heck, I bet I could still fight out there as good as any--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" player:\n"
" Err... riiiight.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You know what? I think I'm gonna add fifty more pushups to your training regimen."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well, what have we got here? Another fine--\n"
" !very sick\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(cough cough cough <i>HACK</> cough)</z></i></> Ugh...\n"
" player:\n"
" Okay, that sounded <i>really</> bad. Have you ever seen a doctor about that cough?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Heh. What, one of those old sawbones working out of a shack in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>? Not on your life.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Besides, there's plenty of other folks who need the help more than me. No sense wasting resources on an old {name.species_ogre} who's well past his prime.\n"
" player:\n"
" Hold up, making sure you're okay is <i>not</> a waste!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Don't get your bloomers in a bunch, kid. Truth is, with the kind of life I've lived, it's a miracle I've lasted this long. If you think this silly little cough would be enough to do me in, well--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" ...You can forget it!\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm not just going to forget it. I'm worried about you!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...Sheesh, kid. You've got it all backwards. I'm your teacher--I'm the one supposed to be worrying about <i>you</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>(grumble)</>... Alright, fine. I'll get checked out next time we're back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. Happy?\n"
" player:\n"
" I'll be happy as long as you take better care of yourself.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Pffft. If you're happy, I ain't doin' my job. Addin' a hunnert more squats to your training regimen!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Look at this souvenir. What do you see?\n"
" player:\n"
" Um. I see it's still wrapped. Aren't you going to open it?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No! The point IS the wrapping, kid! Today's lesson: camouflage!\n"
" !point\n"
" You think how you look out there doesn't impact your survival? \n"
" !angry\n"
" WRONG!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Wear armour that makes you look a fool? Those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}'ll</> be laughin' at ya! They'll have the confidence and you won't!\n"
" !angry\n"
" And out there, an edge is an edge, dagnabbit! \n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !think\n"
" So! We old Hunters developed a trick to change our appearance to suit our needs. We'd grind up some <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> into <#KONJUR>{name.gem_dust}</>, y'see?\n"
" !agree\n"
" Then, by sprinkling it around us just so, we could create an illusion of a completely different armour set!\n"
" !point\n"
" I give to you: The <#RED>{name.i_vanity_screen}</>!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Use your <#KONJUR>{name.i_gem_dust}</> to make your armour look how you want it so you don't just survive, you slay. \n"
" player: \n"
" Wow! Thanks, {name.npc_dojo_master}! ...So, I'm just gonna open your souvenir <i>for</> you...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Fourty burpees added to your training regimen."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Another souvenir, huh? I just hope you're not letting yourself get distracted-- you're out there to hunt <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, not look for shiny trinkets.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Maybe I should up the intensity of your training, just to be on the safe side.\n"
" player:\n"
" Come on, give me a break! Is training all you think about?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You bet it is! And it should be all you think about too. The moment you let up, the <i>second</> you let your guard down, it's over. I'm not seein' another Hunter go down on my watch.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait... did you just say, 'another'?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...I'm givin' you an extra hour of target practice, first thing tomorrow."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Kid... where did you find this?\n"
" player:\n"
" Out in the wilds, where I found all my other souvenirs. Why?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" These bracers... belonged to a Hunter named Pike. Bravest Amphibee I ever met, and outright deadly with a spear. Saved my hide more than once.\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh. Why would they have left their bracers lying out in the wilds?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...I need to get to work on your training regimen. One session a day isn't enough--I'd better double it.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for the gift, kid. How are those hammies of yours? You were looking a little stiff in our last sparring match.\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, I'm sore <i>all over</>, but that's not what's bugging me. I want to know about Pike.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Pike...?\n"
" player:\n"
" You seemed upset when you saw those bracers. Did something happen?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Last time I saw Pike... I'd just taken a bad slash to the eye, and he was coverin' our retreat. One moment he was there, and the next... and the next, he wasn't.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" That <#RED>Rusty Skewer</> was all I was ever able to find. Until you brought me those bracers, anyway.\n"
" player: \n"
" You mean... the Rusty Skewer on the weapons rack...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yeah.\n"
" player:\n"
" And the Bammer? The Striker? Were they <i>all</>...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" They don't look like much now, but every one of those old weapons used to belong to a great Hunter... and a dear friend. It's up to us now, to carry on where they left off.\n"
" player:\n"
" I... had no idea...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. 'Course you didn't! It's not something I was too keen to bring up.\n"
" !point\n"
" Well, no need to get all mopey now--we've got your training to focus on. I'm makin' sure you're the strongest Hunter <#BLUE>the Rotwood</> has ever seen! \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You've gotta be unbeatable! Nothin' less will do, got it?\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Heh. A real checkers set! Why, let's throw down, junior!\n"
" player:\n"
" Right now?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Live in the moment! If ya ain't gonna do somethin' now, when are ya, huh?\n"
" player:\n"
" I actually wanted to talk to you about why you're so tough on me. I figured it out.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" That so? I didn't think I was being tough at all--who doesn't like wakin' up to a surprise round of combat practice from time to time?\n"
" player:\n"
" Most sane people. But I realized it's how you show you care.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...'Course I care. That's the whole problem. If anything happened to you out there... I don't know how I'd live with myself.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You gotta understand... I've lost a lot of things I cared about over the years. My home, an eye, my team... no, my <i>friends</>...\n"
" !point\n"
" But if I can prepare you enough, if I can make sure you're the best of the best--maybe this time things can turn out different. I won't let you down like I let down the others.\n"
" player:\n"
" You didn't let them down. Even you can't control everything that happens.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" But if I'd just done things differently...\n"
" player:\n"
" You told me to 'live in the moment'. So why are you keeping yourself locked in the past?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" That's...!\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Usin' my own lessons against me, huh? Tricky move there, kid..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_dojo.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Thanks, kid. Been meaning to talk to you...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I've been thinking about what you said. About blaming myself for what happened back then.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. I'm always harpin' on folks thinking so far into the future that it freezes them up. Then there I was, stuck in the past.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe it's time for this old trainer to learn some new tricks. Stop wallowin' in guilt and start looking ahead.\n"
" player:\n"
" I think that's what your friends would've wanted.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yeah. And I think it's what I want too. Time to start takin' better care of myself, and showin' a better example.\n"
" player:\n"
" Does this mean you'll start going easier on me in training?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Ha! Far from it! I'm all fired up now--time to kick things into high gear!\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Why am I not surprised.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Though maybe it wouldn't hurt to take some breaks in-between. It's important to take care of yourself, you know!\n"
" player:\n"
" Sounds like some pretty good advice to me.\n"
" agent:\n"
" Well, anyway... <i>(ahem)</>... I, er... got this for you. As a thanks. For everything.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_refiner.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_refiner.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Is this the <#RED>Souvenir</> I asked for? Nice. I can read its <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature from here!\n"
" player:\n"
" Really! It's just a little button pin with \"Go Rot Yourself!\" written on it...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" \"Go Rot Yourself!\" He he he! Love it. Just pure attitude. A preemptive finger in the eye of The Man tryin' to keep you down. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" I totally would've worn this back when I worked for <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>. \n"
" !think\n"
" Did you know my research was in how to imbue <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} crystals</> with energy, or \"<#KONJUR>Teffressence</>\"?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" When I saw <#BLUE>Doc's</> Mech, its crystals <i>imbued</> with <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>... My jaw hit the floor.\n"
" !angry\n"
" He turned my research into WEAPONS! Weapons that almost ended the WORLD! I felt so much shame. Like it was my fault. But no more.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Time for an attitude adjustment, Hunter. Take this <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" You're giving me a NEW WEAPON?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yep. I liberated it from Doc's Lab to keep it from being used at all. But it needs to be used--for good. \n"
" !point\n"
" Now--before I give it to you, there's a method to its madness...\n"
" !angry\n"
" First: it's very fragile. If you fail a {name.run} with this equipped, it'll <#RED>break</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> <i>can</> repair it, with enough <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" But with risk comes reward. \n"
" !think\n"
" Use it to beat an <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</>, and it'll get charged with their <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</>! Kinda like this button pin!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" While a <#RED>Charged {name.weapon_crystal}</> is powerful--it's still <#RED>breakable</>. \n"
" !shocked\n"
" Once you Charge it, take it back to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>! \n"
" !point\n"
" He can then <i>re-forge</> it into a permanently-charged, <i>unbreakable</> <#RED>{name.weapon_boss}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh! And until you charge <i>this</> <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> for the first time, <i>I'll</> cover its repair costs. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" After that, the cost is on you. So be careful, alright? I'm not made of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}</> over here.\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now take the <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>! And may your enemies GO ROT THEMSELVES!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Це той <#RED>сувенір</>, про який я просила? Клас. Я вже звідси відчуваю його <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-сигнатуру!\n"
"player:\n"
" Справді? Це ж просто маленький значок із написом \"Іди до гнилі!\"...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" \"Іди до гнилі!\" Хе-хе-хе! Обожнюю. Чистий характер. Завчасний ляпас системі, що намагається вас пригнітити.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я б точно носила таке, коли працювала на <#BLUE>доктора {2:{Name.flitt_lastname}}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви знали, що мої дослідження були про надання енергії <#KONJUR>кристалам {2:{name.konjur}}</>, або \"<#KONJUR>Конжуросенції</>\"?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Коли я побачила Меха <#BLUE>доктора</>, його кристали, <i>насичені</> <#KONJUR>Першоджерелом {2:{name.konjur}}</>... у мене щелепа відпала.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Він перетворив мої дослідження на ЗБРОЮ! Зброю, що ледь не знищила СВІТ! Мені було так соромно. Наче це моя вина. Але більше ні.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Час підкоригувати настрій, Мисливцю. Візьміть цю <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_crystal}}</>.\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти даєш мені НОВУ ЗБРОЮ?!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Так. Я \"позичила\" її з лабораторії доктора, щоб її взагалі не використали. Але її потрібно використати... на благо.\n"
" !point\n"
" Тепер... перш ніж віддати її вам, є нюанс...\n"
" !angry\n"
" По-перше: вона дуже крихка. Якщо ви провалите {name.run} з нею, вона <#RED>зламається</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> <i>може</> її полагодити, якщо буде достатньо <#KONJUR>{2:{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Але де ризик - там і нагорода.\n"
" !think\n"
" Використайте її, щоб перемогти <#RED>{2:{name.rot_sf_boss}}</>, і вона зарядиться їхньою <#KONJUR>Першоджерельною конжуросенцією</>! Як цей значок!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Хоч <#RED>заряджена {name.weapon_crystal}</> і потужна — вона усе ще <#RED>ламається</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Після зарядження віднесіть її до <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Він зможе <i>перекувати</> її в постійно заряджену, <i>міцну</> <#RED>{3:{name.weapon_boss}}</>!\n"
" !agree\n"
" О! І поки ви не зарядите <i>цю</> <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_crystal}}</> уперше, <i>я</> покрию витрати на ремонт.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Після цього платите ви. Тож будьте обережні, гаразд? Я тут не купаюся в <#KONJUR>{3:{name_multiple.i_konjur_soul_lesser}}</>.\n"
" !happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" А тепер беріть <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_crystal}}</>! І нехай ваші вороги САМІ ІДУТЬ ДО ГНИЛІ!"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT0.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Some leader I turned out to be. I got knocked out of the sky, lost half the team...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hm? What's this, Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" A souvenir from my Hunt! I thought it would cheer you up.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" F-for me? I-I don't know what to say... thank you, Hunter. It <i>is</> cheering me up.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We could use more of that around here--some <i>personal touches</> to make this place feel like home.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know what? I'm feeling inspired! I'll draft up some designs. Then we can start decorating!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" OH, really? Grandpa always thought it was silly. Or \"superfluous,\" as he put it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for the encouragement, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! It's alright. I know it's a bit superfluous, but it makes me happy, so to heck with it!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But don't worry, I won't let it get in the way of our expedition!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Another souvenir? I'll have to find the perfect place to put it...\n"
" player:\n"
" I had no idea you liked decorating so much.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Oh, well, it's just something I've liked since I was a kit.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" There's something about it, investing a place with some thought and care... it makes it feel more like a home.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Like magic! Well, not <i>magic</>-magic, like what {name.c_konjur} can do, but...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" A-anyways... sorry, I'm rambling..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "No, no, I completely agree."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT1.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's a bit 'woo-woo' for me, but I respect your passion."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT2.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I-is this a <i>real</> ceramic coffee mug? And it's barely even chipped! Wow. This is quite the find, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" It's a shame someone seems to have scribbled on it.\n"
" player:\n"
" That was me. Go ahead and read it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Apologies! Let's see here, it says... um... <i>'#1 Skort'?</> <z 0.7>Uh, wow... so thoughtful...</>\n"
" player:\n"
" What the--?! It's <i>supposed</> to say '#1 Scout'! I guess my handwriting isn't the best...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <i>(snrk!)</> Ahem--Actually, I think it's perfect this way. Thank you, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT3.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What's that you're hiding, Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, just another souvenir for my \"#1 Skort\"!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm sure you say that to all the skorts--Oh! \n"
" !dubious\n"
" It's <i>another</> mug with \"#1 Skort\" written on it instead of \"#1 Scout\"! Er, thanks! \n"
" player:\n"
" So... am I your favourite Hunter?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh! Oh, sure, yes, absolutely! Top fi--top ten, at least.\n"
" player:\n"
" Top ten?! C'mon!!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Sorry Hunter, I couldn't resist!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT4.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh, what's this? It looks like a little dancing <#RED>{name.rot}</> on a spring...\n"
" player:\n"
" I thought it'd look good on the {name.i_damselfly}'s dashboard.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I think you're right! You know, I haven't done much to decorate the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> since I first built it--this will be a long-overdue upgrade.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" You've been so thoughtful, bringing back all these souvenirs. I... might've picked up a little something for you, too. Hope you like it, b-but if not, feel free to give it away!\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ah, well--I wouldn't say my engine's perfect, it's not nearly as powerful as a {name.c_konjur} engine. It'll do fine for now, though.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks again for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That was my Grandpa's dream. He believed {name.c_konjur} would make everyone's lives better. Maybe we can get back there.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks again for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Oh, this lightcatcher will go splendidly with the little dancing <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> figurine you gave me, Hunter. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> has never looked better!\n"
" player:\n"
" Did you really build the {name.i_damselfly} yourself?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yep. The biggest challenge was designing an engine that didn't rely on {name.c_konjur} for fuel.\n"
" player:\n"
" It doesn't?! I thought <i>everything</> ran on {name.konjur}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>Most</> things do, but you know how hard it is to get your hands on {name.c_konjur} in <#BLUE>the Brinks.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Plus, I didn't want to rely on those shady scavengers who sell corroded old {name.c_konjur} batteries, and whatever else manages to wash up on shore.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" On top of all that, my allergy makes it pretty much impossible for me to work with a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-powered</> engine, so I had to get creative."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "Maybe we don't need to rely on {name.konjur} as much as we think."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT5.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "It's impressive, but <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}'s</> so powerful--I hope we can use it like we did before."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I remember those! Oh, the crust alone! So flaky... so buttery...\n"
" !think\n"
" But my favourite part was the dancing. I was too young to join in, but I'd imagine myself out there, dancing with a partner...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I never got the chance. After the eruption... well, there's hasn't been much to celebrate in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !shrug \n"
" Things like festivals sort of fall by the wayside when you're just trying to survive.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Still... I like to think that one day, when this is all over, we'll have things like the Spring Festival again.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Maybe I'll even get that dance. Hm.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... But I'm getting ahead of myself. Thank you for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I understand. It can be painful to dwell on the past. Especially with so much ahead of us to think about.\n"
" !think\n"
" Even if our expedition is successful, the eruption caused so much damage to <#BLUE>the Rotwood</>... I wonder if we'll be able to plant again like we used to...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ... No sense in worrying about that now. Thank you for the gift, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Thanks for the souvenir, Hunter. I was just thinking...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Do you remember the Spring Festivals back before the eruption?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Folks used to gather from far and wide to celebrate the planting season, with food, music, and dancing--"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I remember! There was a stall that sold the BEST mixed berry pie."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT6.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "I try to stay focused on the future, not the past."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT7.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thanks for the souvenir, Hunter! I wish I had something to give you...\n"
" player:\n"
" How about some insight into what was it like growing up with <i>the</> {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, sure! Grandpa and I, we were thick as thieves. Whatever experiment he was doing, I was front row center. To me, he was larger than life. He knew everything, could do anything.  \n"
" !agree\n"
" And it wasn't just me. Grandpa's devotion {name.c_konjur}, using it to make <#BLUE>the Rotwood</> a better place, it inspired <i>everyone.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Sometimes... sometimes I worried that having me around slowed him down... particularly after I developed my allergy. I think that was really hard on him.\n"
" player:\n"
" So you didn't always have a {name.konjur} allergy?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" At first, I was around {name.c_konjur} all the time with Grandpa--zero issue. But over time, symptoms began to crop up.\n"
" !think\n"
" No one had heard such an allergy, but I think my Grandpa worried about how it might affect folks' view of {name.c_konjur} and his <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> system.\n"
" player:\n"
" He was worried about the {name.i_town_grid_cryst} system? What about <i>you?</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" That's... that's beside the point. <i>I</> was the one causing problems for <i>him.</>\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_scout}...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I have some calculations that need calculating. I'll see you on your next Hunt.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Дякую за сувенір, Мисливцю! Шкода, що в мене немає нічого для вас...\n"
"player:\n"
" А як щодо того, щоб розповісти, як це, зростати поруч із <i>самим</> {3:{Name.npc_grandpa}} {3:{Name.flitt_lastname}}?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" О, звісно! Ми з дідусем були нерозлийвода. Який би експеримент він не проводив, я завжди був в першому ряду. Для мене він був більшим за життя. Він знав усе, міг усе.\n"
" !agree\n"
" І не тільки для мене. Відданість дідуся {2:{name.c_konjur}}, те, як він використовував це, щоб зробити <#BLUE>Ротвуд</> кращим місцем, надихало <i>всіх.</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Іноді... іноді я переживав, що через мене він рухався повільніше... особливо після того, як у мене з’явилася алергія. Думаю, йому це давалося дуже важко.\n"
"player:\n"
" Тобто в тебе не завжди була алергія на {name.konjur}?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Спочатку я постійно був поруч із  {3:{name.c_konjur}} разом із дідусем... і жодних проблем. Але з часом почали з’являтися симптоми.\n"
" !think\n"
" Ніхто не чув про таку алергію, але думаю, дідусь хвилювався, як це вплине на ставлення людей до  {2:{name.c_konjur}} і його системи <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_town_grid_cryst}}</>.\n"
"player:\n"
" Його хвилювала система {2:{name.i_town_grid_cryst}}? А як же <i>ти?</>\n"
"agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Це... це не має значення. <i>Я</> був тим, хто створював проблеми для <i>нього.</>\n"
"player:\n"
" {Name.npc_scout}...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" У мене є розрахунки, які треба порахувати. Побачимось на наступному полюванні.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]"

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" And I didn't mean to get so defensive. Asking why my Grandpa wasn't more concerned about my allergy... it hit a nerve, I guess."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" A-asking why my Grandpa wasn't more concerned about my allergy... it hit a nerve, I guess."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" This... this is for me? I kind of thought... after our last talk...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I'm sorry, Hunter. You were just trying to be kind, and I... didn't respond well."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" If... If I'm really being honest with myself, I'm not sure I was as important to him as <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> was.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" He was a... complicated fox. He could be so warm and wonderful--with the best hugs, and the biggest laugh... but other times, it was like I was invisible...\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm so sorry. That must have been tough.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I've... never really acknowledged that side of him before. I suppose I'd always rationalized that it was a necessary function of his devotion to his duty...\n"
" !think\n"
" He took me in when my parents passed, and I'll always be grateful for that, but... it was hard sometimes, never knowing what version of my Grandpa I'd be getting day-to-day.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" After losing him in the eruption, it was easier to remember all the good times, and try to forget the bad.\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm glad you told me.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks Hunter... I am too."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "That's okay, I didn't mean to pry."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT8.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "Yeah... what was up with that, anyway?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, I was <i>terrified.</> I'd never led a team before, never mind an important and <i>dangerous</> expedition.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Then in walks this neophyte Hunter, looking almost as scared as I was and <i>still</> volunteering to help. It made me feel a little braver."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GIFT_B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! Who could forget? You challenged <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> to an arm-wrestle. I'd never seen him laugh so hard. \n"
" !point\n"
" Even when he launched you over the table, your confidence was contagious--I remember thinking that if we had you on our side, we'd be able to take on the world!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.GIVE_GIFT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're so generous, Hunter, but so you know, I'm always happy to talk to you, even if you don't have something to give me.\n"
" !think\n"
" I was just thinking about the first time we met, at my old <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> base in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>. Do you remember?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.JOIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's hard to believe that was only a few weeks ago. We've been through so much since then.\n"
" player:\n"
" I hope we can stick together through a whole lot more.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Well, I wouldn't mind if in the future there's a <i>bit</> less fighting for our survival... but even so, I'd like nothing more. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You have a friend for life in me, Hunter. Whether it's watching your back in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> or just keeping you company on a gloomy day.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" In fact--I, um... made this for you. O-open it later though, I'll get too embarrassed if you open it now.\n"
" [notify:reward_def]\n"
" player:\n"
" I'm <i>definitely</> your favourite Hunter now, right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh, you've moved up to be at <i>least</> in the top three.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha ha! I'm kidding, I'm kidding! The look on your face!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_A"
msgid "I was so nervous. I thought I'd get laughed out of there."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_friend_give_gift_scout.FRIEND_GIFT9.give_gift.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GIFT_B"
msgid "I was so cocky. It's a bit embarrassing to reflect on, now..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOWGEM
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_SHOWGEM"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith} rummages around in the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}\n"
" !think\n"
" Och, wouldya look at <i>that</> beauty!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" * {name.npc_blacksmith} pulls a <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</> from the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}\n"
" !happy\n"
" Lookat you, little <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</>. What were ya doin' in there? Alright then, let's get us a better look atcha.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hrmm... <z 0.7>seems like... and the clarity... aye... should have enough power... t'would do nicely...</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "<i>You're</> a gem, {name.npc_blacksmith}!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMSMITHING
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMSMITHING"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Och. Alright then.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I <i>may</> dabble a wee bit in <#RED>Gemsmithing</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Folks think it's just fer soft-handed folk makin' frivolous baubles, but it's not, awright! ...It's fer everyone.\n"
" !think\n"
" Now. That <#KONJUR>{name.gem}</> ye have there, 'tis a curious thing indeed.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Crystallized Teffra, that is. Similar to a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</>-- but if ye take a good look at the colour, 'n the clarity... aye, this didn't form the way most crystals do.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And unlike most Teffra crystals ye come across, this one seems <i>stable</>. A wee bit less powerful I'd wager, but from the look of it, should last ye a lifetime.\n"
" player:\n"
" That's amazing! I had no idea you were so into {name_multiple.gem}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph. <z 0.7>Who wouldnae want ta get lost lookin' into wee <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>? Sparkly precious things hid inside o' rocks... <i>(sigh...)</></>\n"
" !disagree\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ....Eh. I've picked up a few things here 'n there.\n"
" !think\n"
" 'Course, I could <i>really</> get inta it if I had me <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But I lost 'em when we fell. So.\n"
" player:\n"
" Do you have any idea where they might be?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMTOOLS_LOCATION
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.GEMTOOLS_LOCATION"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Probably still somewhere out in th' <#BLUE>trees</> ye first found me in. 'Tis all frenzied now, though. \n"
" player:\n"
" Say I find your tools. You'd help me identify these {name_multiple.gem}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...I s'pose that'd be fair.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Alright, now. Off with ye then!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.PRY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.PRY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" [notify:gem_unidentified]\n"
" Well, tha's all I wanted ta see. Be gone with ye!\n"
" player:\n"
" C'mon! You know something. Why are you acting so weird?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Am not--!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Fine. I'll tell ye.\n"
" !point\n"
" But don't go bletherin' to everyone in camp about this. 'Specially not that wee nosy <#RED>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>. Ye ken?\n"
" player:\n"
" Of course! I'm Ken all the live long day. Now spill it!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "No promises..."
msgstr "Не обіцяю..."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B_A"
msgid "...Alright, FINE. I'm Ken. Now will you tell me, please?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOWGEM
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_SHOWGEM"
msgid "<#RED>[Show {name.npc_blacksmith} the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}]</> I don't see why not."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.gems_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tha <#RED>{name.teffrometer_unidentified}</> ye got there--can I have a look at it?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Och.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well. Innae that important, anyway.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmph."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "I'll find them, {name.npc_blacksmith}. Don't you worry."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Sorry, not yet."
msgstr "Вибач, ще ні."

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT1.gems_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Have ye happened to spot them? Ye know...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Me <#RED>{name.gemtools}</>?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ye really did! Ye found me babies--!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ahem...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" ...Thank ye, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Aye.\n"
" !point\n"
" Go on. Try out the <#RED>{name.i_station_gems}</> on yer own. I learned by gettin' me hands dirty--with {name_multiple.gem}!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "{name.i_station_gems}, got it."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "What has two thumbs and found your {name.gemtools}?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "What's say we put 'em to use identifying these {name_multiple.gem} I got?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_gems_intro_blacksmith.ATTRACT2.gems_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hmph. Ye seem awful pleased about somethin'.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wait--dunnae tell me...?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Uhh--the font is too flowery for me to read, but there's a picture of two hammers kissing on the front?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Anyway, I'll keep it safe until we bring him home. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Good idea."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "What book is it?"
msgstr "Що це за книга?"

#: Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hamishs_book_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Then I'd better get back to searching for him."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.REMIND"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter! On second thought: actually <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</> from one of your hunts, will ya?  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" A <#RED>Souvenir's</> <i>sure</> to be imbued with this funky-bad <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> energy... \n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's for a top secret thing. You'll see. Just <#RED>bring me a Souvenir</>, alright?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT0.hint_unlock_boss_weapon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Sheesh. One year since the craziness in Doc's lab. Time flies, huh? \n"
" player:\n"
" When you're having fun. Or living under a dome of pure {name.konjur} energy.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I <i>am</> proud of it. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Proud of <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, proud it's protecting the people here... \n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I can't get comfortable. Spent years under a volcano, but an energy dome? I'm nuts, aren't I?\n"
" player:\n"
" Or maybe you can't shake that your dad's outside it, still wandering the <#BLUE>{name.rotwood}</>...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hm. I do <i>not</> like you knowing personal details about me, Hunter. THAT makes me claustrophobic. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Time for an abrupt subject change unrelated to my discomfort with being seen!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" My <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> picked up some funky <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> spikes in <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> habitats... \n"
" player:\n"
" Funky... <i>bad?</>\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A scientist never assumes, but... yeah, funky-bad. Funky-tough. Funky-absolutely-funkin'-brutal. \n"
" !notebook\n"
" So if you could go check 'em out, that'd be great.\n"
" player:\n"
" Check out some funky-bad {name.rot_boss}'s lairs? Oh, sure! Sounds peachy!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" You're the best, Hunter. \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you think Doc {name.flitt_lastname} linked to these funky spikes? He's still out there...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... No. We knocked enough sense into Doc, he wouldn't try anything. <z 0.7>Pretty sure.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, and if you pick up any <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>-imbued stuff--bring it my way. \n"
" !point\n"
" I'm keen to study some up close. \n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" UGH. Did I just say, \"keen\"? Leave me to mourn the death of my coolness, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ого. Вже рік минув від тієї халепи в лабораторії Дока. Час летить, га?\n"
"player:\n"
" Коли тобі весело. Або коли ти живеш під куполом чистої енергії {2:{name.konjur}}.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я <i>пишаюся</> цим.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Пишаюся <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_scout}}</> і <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>, пишаюся тим, що він захищає всіх тут…\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Але я не можу розслабитися. Я роками жила під вулканом, а тепер ще й енергетичний купол? Я ж ненормальна, так?\n"
"player:\n"
" Або, може, ти не можеш позбутися думки, що твій батько за його межами й досі блукає <#BLUE>{2:{Name.rotwood}}…\n"
"agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Гм. Мені <i>дуже</> не подобається, що ви знаєте особисті деталі про мене, Мисливцю. Це викликає у мене клаустрофобію.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(зітхає)</> Час різко змінити тему, яка не має нічого спільного з моїм небажанням, щоб мене бачили!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Мій <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> зафіксував дивні сплески <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</> у лігвах <#RED>{2:{name.rot_boss}}</>…\n"
"player:\n"
" Дивні… <i>це погано?</>\n"
"agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Учений ніколи не припускає, але… так, погано. Дивно-небезпечні. Дивно-жорсткі. Дивно-абсолютно-пекельно-руйнівні.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Тож якщо зможете... перевірте це, добре?\n"
"player:\n"
" Перевірити лігва якихось дивно-поганих {name_multiple.rot_boss}? Авжеж, звучить чудово.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ви найкращі, Мисливцю.\n"
"player:\n"
" Як думаєш, док {Name.flitt_lastname} може бути пов’язаний із цими сплесками? Він же все ще десь там…\n"
"agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... Ні. Ми достатньо вибили з нього дурниць, він би такого не зробив. <z 0.7>Майже певно.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" О, і якщо знайдете щось просочене <#KONJUR>Першоджерельним {3:{name.konjur}} </> - принесіть мені.\n"
" !point\n"
" Мені дуже хочеться розглянути його зблизька.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" УФ. Я що, щойно сказала \"дуже хочеться\"? Дай мені посумувати за втратою моєї крутості, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.REMIND
msgctxt "Convo.twn_hint_unlock_boss_weapon.ATTRACT1.remind_about_gift.giver.STATE_0.REMIND"
