"agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... Ні. Ми достатньо вибили з нього дурниць, він би такого не зробив. <z 0.7>Майже певно.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" О, і якщо знайдете щось просочене <#KONJUR>Першоджерельним {3:{name.konjur}} </> - принесіть мені.\n"
" !point\n"
" Мені дуже хочеться розглянути його зблизька.\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" УФ. Я що, щойно сказала \"дуже хочеться\"? Дай мені посумувати за втратою моєї крутості, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Omigosh, you actually have a <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>! Where did you get it??"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" О, Боже мій, у вас справді є <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>! Де ви його взяли??"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i><z 0.7>(whisper whisper)</z></i>\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Hm. So... <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> doesn't believe you, I do, but Scarfanie (my scarf) has the tie-breaking vote, and she voted, 'Believe You!'\n"
" !happy\n"
" So we're usin' the <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</>!\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ooooh, this is going to be so fun!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did a <#RED>{name.gnarlic}</> poke your eyes out? It's a metal <#RED>Ingot</>! From the Before Times!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" How it ended up here is a preeetty juicy tidbit. A nice bit of tid. A... <z 0.7>seeeeecret.</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But whatever! You already have it, we might as well use it.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ooooh, this is going to be so fun!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" With that <#RED>Ingot</> I can fortify a piece of your <#RED>Armour</> and, like, take it to the next <#RED>Level</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" And I <i>guess</i> <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> could also improve a <#RED>Weapon</> with it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" But why would you fortify <i><#RED>Weapons</></i> when you could fortify <#RED>Armour</>??? Right??? It would make NO sense!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ugh, this is different!\n"
" !think\n"
" So like, imagine you become bestest friends with a piece of <#RED>Armour</> you got in an early Hunt.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now as your Hunts get tougher, that old <#RED>Armour</> won't keep you safe, BUT you don't want to ditch your bestest friend (the armour)!\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Now, if you used a <#RED>{name.upgrade_ingot}</> to raise your bestest friend's <#RED>Level</>, you could keep adventuring together without getting your butt kicked!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Same as how you always alter gear, with that adorable little <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> over there.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, but you'll have to <#RED>Upgrade</> your gear a few times first.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Once the gear's good and sturdy from regular <#RED>Upgrading</>, then <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I can work an <#RED>Ingot</> into it and raise its <#RED>Level</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Так само, як ви завжди змінюєте спорядження, через отой чарівний маленький <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" О, але спершу вам доведеться кілька разів <#RED>покращити</> своє спорядження.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Коли спорядження стане хорошим і міцним після звичайного <#RED>покращення</>, тоді <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>, і я вставити в нього <#RED>злиток</> і підвищити його <#RED>рівень</>."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Um. I guess it soaked up some personality from wherever you got it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Nothing wrong with a little personality! I can still use it.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" The <#RED>Ingot</>, not personality. I got plenty of that! \n"
" !agree\n"
" Heck, crud aside, some <#RED>Ingots</> might be more powerful than others."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You better!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Вам краще!"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Uh...? <z 0.7><#RED>(Show her a {name.upgrade_ingot})</></z>"
msgstr "Е...? <z 0.7><#RED>(Показати їй {name.upgrade_ingot})</></z>"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Something dropped it on one of my Hunts."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "Why, what is it? Is it bad? <z 0.7>Is it...poop??</>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "So what does it do?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3C"
msgid "Sorry, I gotta go, but I'll bring you any Ingots I find!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "It's for Upgrades? But you and {name.npc_blacksmith} already do that."
msgstr "Це лише для покращення? Але ти та {Name.npc_blacksmith} вже це робите."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A_ALT"
msgid "You and {name.npc_blacksmith} already give me Upgrades though."
msgstr "Ти та {Name.npc_blacksmith} вже дали мені покращення."

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "How do I use it?"
msgstr "Як це використовувати?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B_ALT"
msgid "Okay. So how do I use it?"
msgstr "Гаразд. Отже, як мені це використовувати?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4C"
msgid "How come it's covered in crud and stuff?"
msgstr "Чому він вкритий брудом і таким іншим?"

#: Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_ingot_armorsmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4D"
msgid "Gotta run, but I'll bring you any Ingots I find!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_PLAYER
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_PLAYER"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] If you ever forget the assignment, check the <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> over there behind you.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] Якщо раптом забудете завдання, перевірте <#RED>{2:{name.i_masteries_station}}</> он там позаду вас.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_TOOT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.POINT_BEHIND_TOOT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] If you ever forget the assignment, check the <#RED>{name.i_masteries_station}</> over there.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" [face:masteries_station] Якщо раптом забудете завдання, перевірте <#RED>{2:{name.i_masteries_station}}</> он там.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_mastery_explainer.ATTRACT0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Eyy, is that our new Hunter I see?\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_dojo_master}, right? Glad to see you made it here in one piece.\n"
" agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'd have no business bein' yer <#RED>{name.job_dojo}</> if I couldn't.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Well, this expedition's already off to a bumpy start, so let's get right to it. What d'ya say we jump right into yer <#RED>Masteries</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Masteries?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>Masteries</> are challenges I made to sharpen yer skills. It's real simple-- go on a {name.run} and complete a challenge, then come back for a nice reward.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I always make sure to give my students a <#KONJUR>Treat</> for finishing their homework!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ейй, це ж наш новий Мисливець, чи не так?\n"
" player:\n"
" {Name.npc_dojo_master}, так? Радий бачити, що ти дістався сюди цілими й неушкодженими.\n"
" agent:\n"
" [title:SPEAKER]\n"
" [sound:Event.joinedTheParty] 0.5\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Якби я не зміг, то не був би вашим <#RED>{2:{name.job_dojo}}</>.\n"
" [title:CLEAR]\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Ну, ця експедиція вже почалася не дуже гладко, тож перейдімо прямо до справи. Що скажете, якщо ми надолужимо згаяний час і перейдемо одразу до <#RED>Майстерностей</>?\n"
" player:\n"
" Майстерності?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>Майстерності</> — це виклики, які я створив, щоб загострити ваші навички. Усе просто... вирушайте на {name.run} і виконайте завдання, а потім повертайтеся за гарною винагородою.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Я завжди дбаю, щоб мої учні отримували <#KONJUR>смаколик</> за виконане домашнє завдання!"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> tips...? That better not be a pun.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Whatcha need to know?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Може порад про <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</>...? Сподіваюсь це не жарт.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Що вам потрібно знати?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Well, yer {name.tutorial_attack_light} is a simple forward jab. Reliable.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_heavy} launches you forward with a jumping thrust.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And heck, since you're takin' the time to learn, I'll give you a <#RED>Combo</> that's not in the tooltip.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Three {name_multiple.tutorial_attack_light} followed by one {name.tutorial_attack_heavy}. Have fun."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Отже, ваша {Name.tutorial_attack_light} — це простий прямий удар. Надійно.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Ваша {Name.tutorial_attack_heavy} — це стрибок уперед.\n"
"!shrug\n"
"І, якщо ви витрачаєте час на навчання, я розкажу вам про <#RED>комбо</>, якого немає в підказках.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Три {Name_multiple.tutorial_attack_light} і одна {Name.tutorial_attack_heavy}. Успіхів."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_light} is a forward jab.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Yer {name.tutorial_attack_heavy} launches you forward with a jumping thrust."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ваша {Name.tutorial_attack_light} — це удар вперед.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ваша {Name.tutorial_attack_heavy} — це стрибок з поштовхом уперед."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The most crucial lesson is this: <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_polearm}</> is mid-range <#RED>Weapons</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Near any <#RED>Attack</> can be a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if you land it at arm's length.\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <#RED>Spinning Drill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' color=BTNICON_DARK scale=0.4> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) will also <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if ya smack <#RED>2+ Enemies</> with it at once.\n"
" !point\n"
" Try practicin' on our <#RED>Training Dummies</> if you need."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Найважливіший урок: <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_polearm}</> — це <#RED>зброя</> середньої дальності.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Будь-який <#RED>удар</> може нанести <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>, якщо влучити на відстані витягнутої руки.\n"
"!point\n"
"Ваше <#RED>Закручене свердло</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' color=BTNICON_DARK scale=0.4> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) теж нанесе <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>, якщо одночасно вдарити <#RED>2+ ворогів</>.\n"
"!point\n"
"Практикуйтесь на наших <#RED>Тренувальних манекенах</>, якщо потрібно."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Yer <#RED>Spinning Drill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' scale=0.4 color=BTNICON_DARK> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) will <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</> if ya smack <#RED>2+ Enemies</> with it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You can also get <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> with most <#RED>Attacks</> if you hit with just the tip of yer <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Ваше <#RED>Закручене свердло</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <p img='images/ui_ftf/arrow_right.tex' color=BTNICON_DARK scale=0.4> <p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_LIGHT' color=BTNICON_DARK>) теж нанесе <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>, якщо одночасно вдарити <#RED>2+ ворогів</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви також можете отримати <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> більшістю <#RED>атак</>, якщо вдарите лише кінчиком свого <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_polearm}}</>."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Eh, that's a standard issue <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> from the Expedition <#RED>Rack</>, yeah?\n"
" !point\n"
" Then yer <#RED>Skill</> must be a melee <#RED>Crosscheck</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If an <#RED>Enemy</> gets too close, hit <p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK> to shove'em back and make some space."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Е, це стандартний <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> з експедиційної <#RED>стійки</>, так?\n"
" !point\n"
" Тоді ваша <#RED>навичка</> має бути ближнім боєм: <#RED>перехресна перевірка</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Якщо <#RED>ворог</> підходить занадто близько, натисніть <p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>, щоб відштовхнути його та створити трохи простору."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2C_ALT"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" LISTEN UP. Yer <#RED>Skill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>) is a close-range shove.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Use it to push <#RED>Enemies</> back and make some space."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" СЛУХАЙТЕ УВАЖНО. Ваша <#RED>навичка</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>) — це близький удар.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Використовуйте його, щоб відштовхнути <#RED>ворогів</> і звільнити трохи місця."

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2D"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Yer doin' that on purpose, aren't you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ви ж навмисно це робите, чи не так?"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_END"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Alright, alright, get gone with ya. {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!angry\n"
"Гаразд, гаразд, ідіть вже. {Name.dojo_cough}"

#: Convo.twn_polearm_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
