#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DIFFERENT_CRAFT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_DIFFERENT_CRAFT"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Indecisive, are we?\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye need to charge the weapon with the <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</> of the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> yer after.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Dunnae worry if the weapon's already charged up with another <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</>. The new one'll wipe the ol' one out."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shop_blacksmith.HUB0.corestone_crafting.giver.STATE_0.TALK_REPAIR_CORESTONE_WEAPON"
