msgstr "Добре, але, як я взагалі можу їх використовувати?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_ALT"
msgid "Can you cover the basics again? I wasn't paying attention."
msgstr "Можеш ще раз повторити основи? Я все прослухав."

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C"
msgid "Can these do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}?"
msgstr "Чи можуть вони завдавати {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2C_ALT"
msgid "Uh, how do I do {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} again?"
msgstr "Ух, як зробити {name_multiple.concept_focus_hit} знову?"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_END"
msgid "See ya {name.npc_dojo_master}, thanks for the explainer!"
msgstr "До зустрічі, {Name.npc_dojo_master}, дякую за пояснення!"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_dojo_master}!"
msgstr "Дякую, {Name.npc_dojo_master}!"

#: Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP_ALT
msgctxt "Convo.twn_shotput_explainer.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ENDLOOP_ALT"
msgid "But seriously. Thanks {name.npc_dojo_master}."
msgstr "Якщо серйозно. Дякую, {Name.npc_dojo_master}."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh, that's a funny story!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" And a bit of a long one, do you have the time?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" О, це смішна історія!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" І трохи довга, маєте час?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_STORY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A_STORY"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Sure, well... after the disaster I probably spent about a year bouncing from place to place in <#BLUE>the Brinks.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I got <i>really</> good at pickpocketing during that time."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_SKIP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B_SKIP"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh! Yes, well, I'm busy too, so...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" See ya!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Don't judge, Hunter. Hunger's a powerful motivator..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" True, true. Especially in those days."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Where were you back then?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_4B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hah! <i>Maybe</i> today... if he was asleep. And in a different room from his pockets."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_6"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Actually, no. One squint and he knew my story instantly.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I wasn't a bad kit. Just in a bad situation.\n"
" !agree\n"
" He took me in. And even though I didn't make a good Hunter, I was safe, warm, and fed.\n"
" !point\n"
" I want everyone in <#BLUE>the Brinks</> to have that, too."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anytime. I'm an open book."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Будь-коли. Я відкрита книга."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_7B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well, you can't say I didn't warn you!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5A"
msgid "Woah! {name.npc_dojo_master} was fast!"
msgstr "Вау! {Name.npc_dojo_master} був швидким!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.OPT_5B"
msgid "Woah! {name.npc_dojo_master} was strong!"
msgstr "Вау! {Name.npc_dojo_master} був сильним!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "How do you and {name.npc_dojo_master} know each other?"
msgstr "Як ти й {Name.npc_dojo_master} познайомилися?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_STORY
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A_STORY"
msgid "Sure, why not?"
msgstr "Авжеж, чому ні?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_SKIP
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B_SKIP"
msgid "Ah, maybe another time actually."
msgstr "Ах, можливо іншим разом."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "Wait, <i>you</> were a thief??"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3B"
msgid "Gotta do whatcha gotta do."
msgstr "Треба робити те, що треба."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4A"
msgid "Well that was a mistake."
msgstr "Ну це була помилка."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_4B"
msgid "Pfft, you could take him."
msgstr "Пфф, ви могли б його здолати."

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_6
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_6"
msgid "Was he mad?"
msgstr "Він був злий?"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7A"
msgid "Thanks for the glimpse into your past, {name.npc_scout}."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_7B"
msgid "You're right, that was a long story!"
msgstr "Ти правий, це була довга історія!"

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Still, not my proudest era, but hey--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I wouldn't be an expert <#RED>{name.job_scout}</> if not for all that sneaking around. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <i>Meanwhile</i> around that time, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> was kicking off the very first Hunter Academy.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" And my under-developed brain made the mistake of thinking he'd be an easy mark."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway, while he was distracted at the registration table I snuck up... reached into his pocket, and...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <z 3.0><i>BAM!</i></z>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Next thing I know, I'm dangling by my ankle two feet off the ground, my meagre pickings for the day falling out of my own pockets."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK4
msgctxt "Convo.twn_toot_and_flitt_origin_scout.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.TALK4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Haha! Yeah, he got a ton of new students after that display! <z 0.7><i>Some of whose pockets I'd picked.</></>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" What do ye know about <#RED>Weapon Weight</>?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Aye, then. Ahem. <#RED>Heavy Weapons</>?\n"
" !point\n"
" Hefty. They do more <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>Light Weapons</>? Less <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Fast though. Less risky ta commit ta an <#RED>Attack</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>Normal Weapon</>? Eh. Balanced."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Так. Гм. <#RED>Важка зброя</>?\n"
" !point\n"
" Сильна. Вона завдає більше <#RED>шкоди</>. \n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>Легка зброя</>? Менше <#RED>шкоди</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Але має менш ризикові <#RED>атаки</>. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>Звичайна зброя</>? Ех. Збалансована."

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Correct. But no cookie. Never cookie.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" As ye were."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_A"
msgid "More...less...balanced. Got it. Love you, Hamish!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_OPT_B"
msgid "Thanks, Hamish. You're my best friend."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.END_TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "<z 0.7><i>(In a cool gruff voice)</></> ...{name.npc_blacksmith}."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Nothing. Take me to school, Hamish."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weapon_weight_blacksmith.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
msgid "<z 0.9>It affects Attack Speed and Damage.</> Do I get a cookie?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Unfortunately not...\n"
" !think\n"
" That fourth <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> should have jump-started the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>, but the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> levels plummeted just as it got going!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'm so sorry. I-I must've missed something... some unknown variable..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I-it doesn't work like that, Hunter... \n"
" !dejected\n"
" After 10 years of calculations... I followed Grandpa's notes to the letter... Where could the <#KONJUR>Teffra</> have gone?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <z 0.7><i>Grandpa... if you can hear me... give me a sign...</></>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "Please tell me the shield is up, but it's just invisible..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2"
msgid "Why don't we just stuff this thing with {name_multiple.i_konjur_heart} until it works?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT0.town_weather_intro_before_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What... <z 0.7><i>I-I don't understand... the fourth <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> was supposed to... what did I miss?</></>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! Hunter! Y-you startled me."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Що... <z 0.7><i>Я-я не розумію... четверте <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> і його мало... що я проґавив?</></>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ой! Мисливцю! В-ви мене налякали."

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ONWARD
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.ONWARD"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" To the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" До <#BLUE>{2:{Name.treemon_forest_r1}}</>!"

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT1.town_weather_intro_after_cutscene.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Are you okay?!\n"
" player:\n"
" Yeah! What was that?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The missing <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>! It must have overloaded the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> and... burst out? B-but that shouldn't be possible!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" My stupid plan just made things worse! What was I thinking?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Pretending to be a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> scientist, risking lives to what? \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Impress my Grandpa? Who I foolishly hoped might somehow be--\n"
" player:\n"
" Snap out of it! The {name_multiple.foxtails} need a leader, so lead!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Y-you're right. <i>(deep breath)</> Okay. One moment...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <z 0.7>That... account for the... carry the zero...</>\n"
" !think\n"
" Right. The epicenter of that quake looks to be the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Our missing <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> should be there!\n"
" player:\n"
" Lead the way, Flitt!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GHOST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_GHOST"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Heard one, perhaps. I'm <i>positive</> I heard a melody... a melody I've known since I as a young kit... coming from these woods...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter... it was the lullaby sung to me by my <#BLUE>Grandpa</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" Your Grandpa? Famous {name.konjur} science guy? Who <i>died</> in the eruption?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Strange way to sum him up but yes! We were separated in the chaos of the eruption, and I assumed--like everyone--that he'd died. But maybe, just maybe...\n"
" player:\n"
" That's incredible! And what I mean by that is, it's not credible.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !scared\n"
" Please, Hunter. Only he and I know that song. If there's a chance my <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> alive somewhere out there, alone, afraid...\n"
" player:\n"
" ... And whistling a lullaby...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hunter. Please.\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry. One rescue, comin' up!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Thank you.\n"
" !point\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in the <#BLUE>{name.treemon_forest_r1}</> seem in a frenzy, so move fast!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GHOST
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_GHOST"
msgid "You okay, {name.npc_scout}? You look like you've seen a ghost."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT2.weather_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh... <z 0.7><i>Please be okay...</></>"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Y-yes...\n"
" !point\n"
" We just have to keep looking. M-maybe I heard something else, like the wind whistling through a tree with very specific holes?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I don't know..."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "It's okay. We'll keep looking. Or listening."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1"
msgid "No sign of that mystery song you heard, though."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT3.weather_indungeon.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well, that last excursion was a doozy. We barely made it out of there in one piece."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.END
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.END"
msgid "Then let's bundle up and save your <z 0.7>Grandpa</>."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.EXPLAIN
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.EXPLAIN"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" To put it in layneander's terms, it's a machine that locks in on the particular <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> radiological signatures of rare items...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" ... <i>OR</> rare people!\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean <z 0.7>Grandpa</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Precisely!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Anyone who's worked with as much <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> as <z 0.7><#BLUE>Grandpa</></> will have a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature through the roof--\n"
" !clap\n"
" --Found him! He's in <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Hunter. If we rescue my <z 0.7><#BLUE>Grandpa</></>, I'm positive he'd not only fix our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, he'd make it even better!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" He's the key to salvaging our whole mission."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_weather_intro_scout.ATTRACT4.weather_finish.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'm grateful <i>we</> made it out safe, but are you sure you looked everywhere?\n"
" player:\n"
" Sorry, {name.npc_scout}, I didn't see your Grandpa.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Please, Hunter, keep your voice down! People will think I've lost it, searching for my <z 0.7><i>long-thought-dead-and-probably-is-dead <#BLUE>Grandpa</></></> to fix everything...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ... M-maybe I just heard the wind, whistling through a tree with very specific, flute-like holes? \n"
" player:\n"
" <#RED>[Show them the {name.teffrometer_unidentified}]</> I <i>did</> find signs of a struggle, and this weird doo-hickey. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" \"Signs of a struggle\"? Oh dear--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egads! I've never seen a machine like that. Especialy not dropped by a flute-tree...\n"
" !think\n"
" Is this a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> intake? <z 0.7>And this a <#KONJUR>Teffronic</> resonance sensor... and a lapidary tumbler??</>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Good gravy! This is a <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" A what-what-meter?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_welcome_to_town_refiner.ATTRACT0.first_meet.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_welcome_to_town_refiner.ATTRACT0.first_meet.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So this is your <#BLUE>{name.town}</>, huh? And <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> the de-facto leader? \n"
" !think\n"
" <i>Hm.</> Despite that, it appears to be a decentralized collectivist cooperative with a souvenir-based barter system...\n"
" player:\n"
" It's not much, but it's home.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" -- Wait. Is that a <i>community garden?!</> <z 0.7>OMG... food security, knowledge sharing, sustainability...EEK!</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sorry. My \"Been in a Lab Under a Volcano With a Mad Scientist for Too Long\" is showing.\n"
" !point\n"
" Mind if I set up my gear here? Good because it's happening.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, and make sure <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> reads <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> <#RED>Diary</> to see I'm not lying, okay? <i>Not</> that I care... \n"
" player:\n"
" Will do. Y'know, you <i>act</> all cool, but <i>I</> think you--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Look, Hunter. I'm down for open info exchanges, but I've had a looong day.  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Talk to me when you've found some of the three <#RED>Key Fragments</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We need those to stop <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}'s</> <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> from destroying life as we know it. Cool?\n"
" player:\n"
" Cool! Supes cool. Welcome to the, er, non-hippopotamus, collector's edition, desensitized campoperative!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Cool. <z 0.7><i>\"Hunter... bad... at... words...\"</></> He he he."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" It's super important. You've got to follow my instructions <i>exactly</>, okay?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Close your eyes and hold out your hands."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Це дуже важливо. Ви маєте точно виконувати мої інструкції <i>без імпровізації</>, гаразд?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Заплющте очі та простягніть руки."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Perfect! Stay just like that for a second...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Okay, now open your eyes!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" Чудово! Залишайтеся так ще секунду...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Добре, тепер відкрийте очі!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_3A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Hope you like it! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> helped me pick it out!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Сподіваюся, вам сподобається! <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> допоміг мені вибрати!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "What do you need?"
msgstr "Що тобі потрібно?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Okay! <i><#RED><z 0.7>(Close your eyes and hold out your hands)</z></></i>"
msgstr "Добре! <i><#RED><z 0.7>(Заплющити очі та простягнути руки)</z></></i>"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_3A"
msgid "A {name.holiday_winter} present? Wow, thanks {name.npc_armorsmith}!"
msgstr "Подарунок до {2:{name.holiday_winter}}? Вау, дякую, {Name.npc_armorsmith}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_armorsmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Hunteerrrrr, over here! I need you to do something for me!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Мисливцюююю, сюди! Мені потрібно, щоб ви щось зробили для мене!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt} Dinnae mention it. Ever."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt} Не згадуйте про це. Ніколи."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "You got me a {name.holiday_winter} present? Thanks {name.npc_blacksmith}!"
msgstr "Ти дав мені подарунок до {2:{name.holiday_winter}}? Дякую, {Name.npc_blacksmith}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_blacksmith.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Here."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Мисливцю.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Ось."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1AB"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Everyone needs to take it easy now and then. Even you, Hunter.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But if you're not keen on takin' a break, you can take this instead."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Іноді всім потрібно трохи відпочити. Навіть вам, Мисливцю.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Але якщо ви не налаштовані відпочивати, тоді візьміть це."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! Wouldn't you like to know!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ха! Хіба ви не хотіли б знати!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "I can't slow down, there's too much to do!"
msgstr "Я не можу зупинитися, занадто багато роботи!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "Bah. Holidays are just used as an excuse to slack off."
msgstr "Та ну. Свята — це просто привід для байдикування."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2A"
msgid "Aw, thanks {name.npc_dojo_master}! Does this mean I'm your favourite student?"
msgstr "Ой, дякую, {Name.npc_dojo_master}! Це означає, що я твій улюблений учень?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_dojo.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Still workin' hard over {name.holiday_winter}, eh kid?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Працюєте, навіть під час {2:{name.holiday_winter}}, так, друже?"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1A"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" We've all lost a lot these past ten years. I had a feeling you'd understand.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Look at me getting all sappy, I almost forgot! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here. A little something from me to you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Ми всі багато втратили за ці десять років. Я відчував, що ви це зрозумієте.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" О! Дивіться, як я розчулився, мало не забув! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ось. Маленький подарунок від мене для вас."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1B"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Truer words were never spoken.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh! Look at me getting all sappy, I almost forgot! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Here. A little something from me to you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Ніколи не було сказано правдивіших слів.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" О! Дивіться, як я розчулився, мало не забув! \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ось. Маленький подарунок від мене для вас."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_2AB"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Happy Wintertide, Hunter."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Щасливої зимної пори, Мисливцю."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1A"
msgid "Me neither..."
msgstr "Я теж..."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_1B"
msgid "There's nothing like spending {name.holiday_winter} with good friends."
msgstr "Немає нічого кращого, ніж провести {3:{name.holiday_winter}} з хорошими друзями."

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2AB
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2AB"
msgid "Thanks, {name.npc_scout}!"
msgstr "Дякую, {Name.npc_scout}!"

#: Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK
msgctxt "Convo.twn_winter2024_scout.ATTRACT0.winter2024.giver.STATE_0.TALK"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" You know, usually I dread this time of year.\n"
" !think\n"
" It always brings up so many memories. But somehow... this time it feels easier.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I suspect you've got a lot to do with that. You, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I can't remember the last time I was surrounded by so many folks during {name.holiday_winter}."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Знаєте, зазвичай я боюся цієї пори року.\n"
" !think\n"
" Вона завжди приносить стільки спогадів. Але цього разу... усе здається простішим.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Думаю, це багато в чому завдяки вам. Вам, <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_dojo_master}}</>, {3:<#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</>, <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Не можу згадати, коли востаннє мене оточувало стільки істот під час {2:{name.holiday_winter}}."

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_FOXTAILS"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Hold on everyone! We're coming!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ONTHREE
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_ONTHREE"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" Pretty sure you landed <i>directly</> on your brain, but... we'll deal with that later. Let's go rescue our pals!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_FOXTAILS"
msgid "{name_multiple.foxtails}!"
msgstr "{Name_multiple.foxtails}!"

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ONTHREE
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_ONTHREE"
msgid "Did you mean ON three? Or right AFTER three?"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK_INTRO
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON0.game_intro.giver.STATE_0.TALK_INTRO"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! Thank goodness you're alive! How many claws am I holding up?\n"
" player:\n"
" Uh... none. Are <i>you</> okay?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Far from it! Our expedition's barely begun and I've already lost track of half our crew! <z 0.7><i>Grandpa would never have let this happen...</></>\n"
" player:\n"
" It's gonna be alright, {name.npc_scout}. Just breathe. Who's missing?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" While you were out, I flew over and saw <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>, our Battlemaster. He recovered our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> tech and is setting up camp.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" But I couldn't find <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, our <#RED>{name.job_armorsmith},</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, our <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}.</> They don't stand a chance against these <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Okay, you search the forest. The <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>'s still in one piece, so I'll be right above you to scoop up our crew--or you if you, uh, y'know, <z 0.7> \"fall.\"</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Alright now, \"<#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>\" on three. 1... 2... 3! <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].1
msgctxt "Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'll follow from the sky, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" I believe in you."
msgstr ""

#: Convo.wrld_game_intro_sequence.CHAT_DUNGEON1.hurry_up.giver.QUIP.game_start_hurry_up:[in_convo_wrld_game_intro_sequence.chat_dungeon1.hurry_up.giver].2
