#: Quest.after_find_all_keys_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3,in_quest_after_find_all_keys_scout,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_find_all_keys_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3,in_quest_after_find_all_keys_scout,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hunter! I finished my <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> <#RED>Diary</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Мисливцю! Я дочитав <#BLUE>щоденник</> <#RED>дідуся</>."

#: Quest.after_find_first_key_dojo.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_after_find_first_key_dojo,in_town,qc_after_find_first_key_scout,role_dojo]NOT[has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_find_first_key_dojo.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_after_find_first_key_dojo,in_town,qc_after_find_first_key_scout,role_dojo]NOT[has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I can tell you've got something to tell me, kid. Out with it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Я бачу, ви хочете мені щось сказати, друже. Розповідайте."

#: Quest.after_find_first_key_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_after_find_first_key_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_find_first_key_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_after_find_first_key_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_volcanokey2,has_volcanokey3].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" ...\n"
" player:\n"
" Are you reading the Diary {name.npc_refiner} stole from your Grandpa?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Hm? Oh, yes, minus the few <#RED>Pages</> we recovered already. Speaking of...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Remember the <#RED>Page</> about how my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> designed the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> and <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> that our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> tech was meant to run off of?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" ...\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти читаєш щоденник, який {Name.npc_refiner} вкрав у твого дідуся?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Хм? А, так, за винятком кількох <#RED>сторінок</>, які ми вже повернули. До речі...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Пам’ятаєте <#RED>сторінку</> про те, як мій <#BLUE>дідусь</> розробив <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> і <#KONJUR>енергомережу трубопроводу {2:{name.konjur}}</>, від якої мала працювати наша технологія <#KONJUR>Бульбашкового щита</>?"

#: Quest.after_find_second_key_dojo.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,in_quest_after_find_second_key_dojo,in_town,qc_after_find_second_key_scout,role_dojo]NOT[has_volcanokey3].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_find_second_key_dojo.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,in_quest_after_find_second_key_dojo,in_town,qc_after_find_second_key_scout,role_dojo]NOT[has_volcanokey3].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What is it, kid? You look all watery-eyed. Do you need more push-ups?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Що таке, друже? У вас очі мокрі. Потрібно ще віджимань?"

#: Quest.after_find_second_key_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,in_quest_after_find_second_key_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_volcanokey3].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_find_second_key_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,has_volcanokey2,in_quest_after_find_second_key_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_volcanokey3].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" Oh, hey, Hunter. I could use a bit of a break from <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> <#RED>Diary</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !diary_start\n"
" О, привіт, мисливцю. Мені б не завадило трохи перепочити від <#BLUE>щоденника</> <#RED>дідуся</>."

#: Quest.after_insert_heart_5_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_1_zone_2_hearts,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,has_diarypage1,in_quest_after_insert_heart_5_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_insert_heart_5_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_1_zone_2_hearts,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,has_diarypage1,in_quest_after_insert_heart_5_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> Still not enough power to generate the <#KONJUR>Shield</>, and I just don't know why the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> is failing!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" My <#BLUE>Grandpa</> is the key. He <i>invented</> all this. We must save him to save our home from the <#RED>{name.rot}</>, Hunter!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> readings show he's been moved!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I'm glad you have all that <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> power. Prepare yourself, Hunter. We ride at dawn!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.after_insert_heart_6_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,has_diarypage2,in_quest_after_insert_heart_6_scout,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_5_scout,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_3_zone_2_hearts].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_insert_heart_6_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,has_diarypage2,in_quest_after_insert_heart_6_scout,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_5_scout,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_3_zone_2_hearts].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> are toying with us, with Grandpa. But we still have his <#KONJUR>Teffra</> signature, which means he's alive.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" We have them cornered in the <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</>, our old home. There's nowhere left for them to run.\n"
" !point\n"
" This is it. We'll save <#BLUE>Grandpa</>, he'll save us, and everything will go back to how it was."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_3_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_bnd,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_bnd.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_3_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_bnd,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Incredible work, Hunter. We're just <i>one</> <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> shy of powering the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Once we have the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> cleared out and everyone's resettled, I think I'm going to restart my Grandpa's <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> laboratory.\n"
" player:\n"
" That sounds great!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" We'll jump-start the old <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</>, get the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> flowing again, and put our home back to how it was!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_1_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_mt,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_2_zone_1_hearts].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_1_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_mt,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_2_zone_1_hearts].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Did you see that, Hunter? My design... It didn't explode, or implode, or any of the 'plodes!\n"
" player:\n"
" I <i>knew</> it'd work. Did... did it work? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Well, not <i>yet</>. Otherwise the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> would be shining above us. But that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> you deposited got us on our way.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" By my calculations, we'll need just three more to jump-start the old <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> and get the <#KONJUR>Shield</> up and running for good!\n"
" player:\n"
" \"Just\" three? Ha. Haha. Ha. And I'm \"just\" having a heart attack...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Aw, c'mon Hunter! You made quick work of <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>! What's three more <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>? Besides, you got a power boost, didn't you?\n"
" player:\n"
" That <i>did</> feel nice...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Well imagine that times three!\n"
" player:\n"
" Okay, I'm on it!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'm proud to work with you, Hunter!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hm..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_2_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_3_zone_1_hearts].1
msgctxt "Quest.after_insert_heart_scout_owl.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_2_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_3_zone_1_hearts].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Excellent work, Hunter! I've done some calculations--we need two more <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</> to get the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> running. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" The calculations I did were harder than 'four minus two,' by the way."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abadoned_last_run,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abadoned_last_run,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" If a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> was melting <i>my</> face off with hot guitar licks, I'd split, too."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> lab isn't like I remember it from when I was young.\n"
" !think\n"
" It seems smaller. And more hostile."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That was overwhelming for me too, so I don't judge you, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" But we can't delay long--the <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> could still happen any moment!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].3"
msgid "!happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !agree\n"
" Good idea to retreat! Now we can find more <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" The power boost will help us in our next run at <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Smart of you to high-tail it out of there when you did.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There's too much riding on us stopping <#BLUE>Grandpa</> to fail now."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Back so soon? Did you forget to water the plants?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Так швидко повернулися? Ви забули полити квіти?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I guess even Hunters get nervous sometimes.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" That's kind of nice to know, actually."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Гадаю, навіть Мисливці інколи нервують.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Насправді, це навіть приємно знати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!greet\n"
" I've been looking for you!\n"
" !point\n"
" Can you tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> the {name.i_damselfly} should be a community vehicle?"
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Я вас шукав!\n"
" !point\n"
" Чи можете ви сказати <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_scout}}</>, що {Name.i_damselfly} повинен бути спільним засобом пересування?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!greet\n"
" Welcome home!\n"
" !think\n"
" \"Home.\" Huh. It's got a nice mouthfeel."
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Ласкаво просимо додому!\n"
" !think\n"
" \"Додому\" Хах. Це приємне відчуття у роті."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Still alive, I see.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Good."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Все ще живі, я бачу.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Добре."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Back for better weapons, are ye?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wise."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Повернулися за кращою зброєю, так?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Мудро."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!shocked\n"
" Back so soon?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Did you forget to pack a lunch?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Так швидко повернулися?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви забули взяти обід?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's alright Hunter, sometimes you've gotta know when to cut and run.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I ain't gonna fault you for that."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Все гаразд, Мисливцю, інколи треба знати, коли відступити.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я не звинувачуватиму вас за це."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" When you've gotta split, you've gotta split."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Was the {name.c_konjur} just not <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-ing</> in that run?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Better to tuck tail on a bad Hunt than get chomped.\n"
" !agree\n"
" The important thing is we made it back."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Краще підвернути хвоста під час поганого полювання, ніж отримати під зад.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Важливо те, що ми повернулися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[abandoned_last_run,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I respect your tactical decision to retreat.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Very smart."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я поважаю ваше тактичне рішення відступити.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Дуже розумно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_0,friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_0,friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" With some <#RED>{name_multiple.upgrade_ingot}</>, I bet I could learn some new techniques.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Then I could make all your armour way more powerful. Check my shopping list in the <#RED>Armoury</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_0,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_0,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Check out the <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</> over there to see all the <#RED>Armour Upgrades</> we can do for you!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I mean, we do need some <#RED>{name.rot} {name_multiple.material}</> to work with, but that shouldn't be too hard for you to get, right?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Перевірте <#RED>{name.i_station_armorsmith}</>, щоб побачити всі <#RED>покращення обладунків</>, які ми можемо зробити для вас!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Нам, щоправда, потрібні <#RED>{name_multiple.material} {2:{name.rot}}</>, але ж вам не важко буде їх дістати, чи не так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_1,has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_1,has_deposited_2_zone_2_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I think <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I could do more if we upgraded my tools!\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's get those materials for {name.armourtools2}.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Then I bet I could totally upgrade <i>all</> your armour even more!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Думаю, ми з <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_lunn}}</> могли б зробити більше, якщо оновити мої інструменти!\n"
" !point\n"
" Дістаньмо ті матеріали на {name.armourtools2}.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Тоді я могла б покращити <i>усі</> ваші обладунки ще більше!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_1,has_deposited_3_zone_2_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_fortification_level_1,has_deposited_3_zone_2_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" But... doing all those upgrades on that new armour made me realize...\n"
" !point\n"
" I'm definitely gonna need to upgrade my <#RED>{name.armourtools1}</> too.\n"
" !think\n"
" Scratch that--I'll probably need to make a whole new kit to handle working with all that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Trust me, the upgrades I'll be able to do with it will be totally worth it!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Sooooo could you pick up a few materials for me? Pretty please?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[boss_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[boss_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Check <i>you</> out! <#RED>{name.weapon_boss}</> and everything! Strut your stuff, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[broken_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[broken_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Looks like yer <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> needs some repairs, ay?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[broken_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[broken_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hrm. Yer weapon is lookin' a bit worse for wear.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Dunnae worry, I can fix up yer <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> tells me you've completed another challenge!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Go ahead and claim yer <#RED>Mastery</> at the <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</> whenever you're ready."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I hear you finished off one of my challenges, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I've got a little <#KONJUR>Treat</> for you at the <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</>, when you're ready to claim it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Seems like someone went and finished another one of my challenges.\n"
" !point\n"
" If that sounds like you, there's a <#KONJUR>Treat</> for you at the <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</>. Go on. If it's you."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>Masteries</> aren't to be taken lightly, Hunter.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You complete one, you're owed <#KONJUR>Compensation</>. The <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</> is where you claim what's yours."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Any <#RED>Master</> I've known'll take a <#KONJUR>Reward</> that's <i>earned.</>\n"
" !point\n"
" And Hunter, you've earned it. Head over to the <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</>. It's waitin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_claim_mastery,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Nothin' feels better than a well-deserved <#KONJUR>Treat</>, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.i_masteries_station}</>. Think somethin's there with yer name on it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_craft_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[needs_potion].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_craft_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[needs_potion].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Why, my friend! Are you aware your flask is full of <i>inferior product</i>?!\n"
" !think\n"
" Golly, I just hate to see a salt of the earth <#BLUE>{player.species}</> like yourself get ssswindled.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tell you what, why don't you empty that swill out with <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK> and I'll top you up with some bonafide {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Potion</> instead?\n"
" player:\n"
" Wow! You'd do that for me?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Undoubtedly!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Мій друже! Чи ви знаєте, що ваша фляга наповнена <i>низькоякісним продуктом</i>?!\n"
" !think\n"
" Боже, я просто не можу терпіти, коли <#BLUE>{player.species}</> як ви, чесний до кісток, потрапляє у обман.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я вам скажу ось що. Чому б вам не вилити цей жалюгідний напій за допомогою <p bind='Controls.Digital.USE_POTION' color=BTNICON_DARK> і я заповню її справжнім <#RED>зіллям</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}?\n"
" player:\n"
" Вау! Ти зробиш це для мене?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !point\n"
" Безперечно!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Free <#RED>Upgrade</> time?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" It'll make your fight with <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</> more survivable."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Час безплатного <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Це збільшить ваші шанси на виживання в битві проти <#RED>{2:{Name.bandicoot}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You look like you could use an <#RED>Upgrade</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Aren't you lucky? I've got a free one right here for you."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви виглядаєте так, ніби вам потрібне <#RED>покращення</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Вам пощастило! У мене є безплатне для вас."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hey, do you want your free <#RED>Upgrade</> or what?\n"
" !point\n"
" Make it quick, I need to get back to work."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" То ви хочете своє безплатне <#RED>покращення</> чи ні?\n"
" !point\n"
" Не баріться, мені треба повертатися до роботи."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Just the Hunter I was hoping to see.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" I've got some free <#RED>Upgrades</> for you to test out."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Саме на вас я й чекав, Мисливцю.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" У мене є кілька безплатних <#RED>покращень</>, які варто випробувати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Wanna warm up with a free <#RED>Upgrade</>?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" I could use the break."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Хочете зігрітися безплатним <#RED>покращенням</>?\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Мені б не завадило трохи відпочити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" It's your lucky day!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" I've got a free <#RED>Upgrade</> for you to try out."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Вам сьогодні щастить!\n"
" !notebook\n"
" У мене є безплатне <#RED>покращення</>, яке можна випробувати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Oh, hey. Come for some free <#RED>Upgrades</>? Sure, I have time."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You've got some free <#RED>Upgrades</> waiting. Save some precious <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Come to claim your free <#RED>Upgrades</>?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Here for <#RED>Upgrades</>? I could do some for free, this time..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_multiple_free_upgrades,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Got some free <#RED>Upgrades</> for you. You ready?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Oh, hey. Want an <#RED>Upgrade</>? First one's free."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" О, привіт. Хочете <#RED>покращення</>? Перше безплатно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" First <#RED>Upgrade</>'s on the house. After that I'll need some <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Перше <#RED>покращення</> на рахунок закладу. Після цього мені знадобиться<#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" First <#RED>Upgrade's</> always free."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Перше <#RED>покращення</> завжди безплатне."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Want an <#RED>Upgrade</>? First one's on me."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Хочете <#RED>покращення</>? Перше безплатно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_get_single_free_upgrade,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[received_power_upgrade].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" First <#RED>Upgrade's</> on the house."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Перше <#RED>покращення</> за кошти закладу."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_upgrade_weapon,has_killed_megatreemon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_upgrade_weapon,has_killed_megatreemon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You lookin' ta <#RED>Upgrade</> that <#RED>Weapon</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Have a gander at the <#RED>Weapon Rack</>, then."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хочете <#RED>покращити</> цю <#RED>зброю</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Погляньте на <#RED>стійку для зброї</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_upgrade_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[can_upgrade_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That <#RED>Weapon</> o' yours... wanna <#RED>Upgrade</> it?\n"
" !point\n"
" The <#RED>Weapon Rack</> will get ye started. Quit dallyin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Looks like yer <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> is ready to be finished."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Здається, що ваша <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> готова до завершення."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ye did it. Hmph. I knew ye could.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now let's finish yer <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви зробили це. Гмпф. Я знав, що вам під силу.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" А тепер давайте завершімо вашу <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_crystal}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,first_run_in_eggzy_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,first_run_in_eggzy_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What <i>is</> that smell?\n"
" !shock\n"
" This place stinks like a rotten egg.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" That's disconcerting..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_bow].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_bow].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Now <i>there's</> a real Hunter's weapon. Sleek, agile, versatile... not to mention incredibly cool-looking.\n"
" player:\n"
" Which of your teammates used the {name.weapon_bow}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" That would be yours truly! Figured my old Hunting <#RED>{name.weapon_bow}</> might be useful for training new Hunters.\n"
" !think\n"
" Though I have to admit, it doesn't hold a candle to the fancy <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_bow}</> you can make nowadays. Who woulda thought one day we'd be using <#RED>{name.rot}</> parts to make our weapons stronger?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Оце <i>так</> зброя Мисливця. Струнка, спритна, універсальна... і ще й виглядає надзвичайно стильно.\n"
" player:\n"
" Хто з твоїх товаришів користувався {4:{name.weapon_bow}}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Це був я! Подумав, що мій старий мисливський <#RED>{name.weapon_bow}</> може згодитися для тренування новачків.\n"
" !think\n"
" Хоча мушу зізнатися... він і близько не зрівняється з тими розкішними <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.weapon_bow}}</>, які ви тепер можете робити. Хто б міг подумати, що колись ми використовуватимемо частини <#RED>{name.rot}</>, щоб зробити зброю сильнішою?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Heh. I just remembered the time me and my teammates decided we'd throw <#BLUE>Tommy</> a surprise birthday party.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" In retrospect, probably not the best idea to startle the guy with the <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>. What a mess!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Хе-хе. Щойно згадав, як ми з командою вирішили влаштувати <#BLUE>Томмі</> сюрприз на день народження.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Озираючись назад, мабуть, не найкраща ідея була налякати хлопця з <#RED>{4:{name.weapon_cannon}}</>. Який безлад вийшов!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_hammer].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_hammer].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Heh. My old teammate <#BLUE>Nellie</> used to say, 'any problem can be solved with a big enough hammer'.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...It was best not to get on her bad side."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Хе-хе. Моя стара напарниця <#BLUE>Неллі</> любила казати: 'будь-яку проблему можна вирішити достатньо великим молотом'.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Краще було не потрапляти їй під гарячу руку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_polearm].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_polearm].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's a shame you never got to meet <#BLUE>Pike</>. He could make a <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> sail through the air like it was nothing.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...But <i>yeesh,</> the constant puns! Always saying stuff like 'I got the point' and 'I'll spearhead the next Hunt'. It was relentless!\n"
" player:\n"
" Sounds like he was pretty sharp. I think we would've gotten along.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" On second thought, it's probably a mercy you two never met."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Шкода, що ви так і не зустріли <#BLUE>Пайка</>. Він змушував <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> літати в повітрі, ніби то була пір'їнка.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...Але, <i>йой</>, ті нескінченні каламбури! Завжди повторював щось на кшталт 'Я склав список учасників' чи 'Не треба списувати мене з натсупного полювання'. Це було безжально!\n"
" player:\n"
" Звучить, ніби він був досить дотепним. Думаю, ми б з ним порозумілися.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Якщо подумати, мабуть, добре, що ви двоє так і не зустрілися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_shotput].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_shotput].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Heh. I remember when <#BLUE>Rover</> first tried to sell me on using a giant ball as a weapon--truth be told, I thought he was nuts.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But then I saw him in action... took down <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> like it was child's play, looking like he was having the time of his life. Needless to say, I was convinced.\n"
" player:\n"
" So it <i>is</> a ball!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...Hush, you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Хех. Пригадую, як <#BLUE>Ровер</> уперше спробував переконати мене, що гігантська куля може бути зброєю... чесно, я подумав, що він з глузду з'їхав.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Але потім я побачив його в дії... він знищував <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>, наче то були іграшки, ще й виглядав так, ніби отримував від цього суцільне задоволення. Тоді я зрозумів, що помилявся.\n"
" player:\n"
" То це <i>справді</> куля?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...Тс-с, тихіше ви."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[has_teffrometer].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[has_teffrometer].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Did ya feel that? There's somethin' strange goin' on out there...\n"
" !point\n"
" Mind checkin' on <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>? They're looking a mite twitchy."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Відчули це? Там щось дивне відбувається...\n"
" !point\n"
" Перевірте <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_scout}}</>, здається, він трохи нервує."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You should really think about getting a helmet, y'know.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Sorry the expedition didn't provide one."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Вам дійсно варто подумати про шолом.\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Вибачте, що експедиція не надала його."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" You should probably have some head protection.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" That was an oversight on my part. Sorry."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Вам, мабуть, потрібен захист для голови.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Це була моя помилка. Вибачте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" You could probably use a helmet, huh?\n"
" !point\n"
" Maybe you could get one of the forest denizens to sell you one on our next Hunt."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Вам, мабуть, потрібен шолом, так?\n"
"!point\n"
"Можливо, ви зможете купити його в одного з лісових жителів на наступному полюванні."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_bandicoot,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_bandicoot,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Just wait 'til that <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</> takes you on head-to-head! To... head? \n"
" !laugh\n"
" Er, we'll see who gets the last laugh."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Просто зачекайте, поки <#RED>{Name.bandicoot}</> вийде з вами в бій сам на сам! На... сам?\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Емм.. побачимо, хто буде сміятися останнім."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You can't make a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</> omelette without breaking a few eggs.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !angry\n"
" Let's get cracking, Hunter!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Не можна зробити омлет з <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur_heart}}</> не розбивши кілька яєць.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !angry\n"
" Нумо стукаймося, Мисливцю!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Let's get that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>, Hunter!\n"
" !think\n"
" But, um... try not to get any shell bits in it, alright?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Дістаньмо це <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>, Мисливцю!\n"
" !think\n"
" Але, гм... намагайтеся, щоб туди не потрапили шматочків шкаралупи, гаразд?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Don't worry, you've got this.\n"
" !clap\n"
" This fight will be over-easy!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Не хвилюйтеся, у вас все вийде.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Цей бій буде легкий, як яєчня!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" You know what to do, right Hunter?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Get in there and beat that bad egg!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ви ж знаєте, що робити, так, Мисливцю?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ідіть і здолайте це погане яйце!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" This is it.\n"
" !clap\n"
" That oversized <#RED>{name.rot}</> is going to shell out its <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Це воно.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Цей великий <#RED>{name.rot}</> розколеться і віддасть своє <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" That <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> really gives me the creeps.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(sigh)</> But we've come too far to back down now."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ця <#RED>{Name.grimhollow}</> мене лякає.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(зітхає)</> Але ми зайшли надто далеко, щоб відступати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't worry about it, Hunter.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You'll get that <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> next time, I know it!"
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Не переймайтесь, Мисливцю.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ви переможете <#RED>{3:{Name.grimhollow}}</> наступного разу, я впевнений!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" That <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> is standing between us and finding our answers.\n"
" !angry\n"
" We can't let it win!"
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" Ця <#RED>{Name.grimhollow}</> стоїть між нами та відповідями, які ми шукаємо.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ми не можемо дозволити їй перемогти!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_owlitzer,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_owlitzer,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" You promise to take down that <#RED>{name.owlitzer}</>, Hunter?\n"
" !scared\n"
" I hate birds..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ви обіцяєте знищити ту <#RED>{2:{Name.owlitzer}}</>, Мисливцю?\n"
" !scared\n"
" Я ненавиджу птахів..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" If you get cold while fighting <#RED>{name.sedament}</> just um... Think warm thoughts!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Like imagine being next to a warm fire. Mind over matter, right?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Якщо вам стане холодно під час боротьби з <#RED>{3:{Name.sedament}}</>, просто, е-е... Думайте про теплі речі!\n"
"!closedeyes\n"
"Наприклад, уявіть, що ви біля теплого вогнища. Сила думки, так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>{name.sedament}</> better watch out!\n"
" !angry\n"
" We're comin' for that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"<#RED>{4:{Name.sedament}}</> краще стерегтися!\n"
"!angry\n"
"Ми йдемо забирати <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Ready to take down <#RED>{name.sedament}</>?\n"
" !agree\n"
" Personally, I think you're ready."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Готові здолати <#RED>{2:{Name.sedament}}</>?\n"
"!agree\n"
"Особисто я думаю, що ви готові."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1"
msgid "!agree\n"
" Time to face the music.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" By which I mean a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>."
msgstr "!agree\n"
" Час зустрітися з музикою.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Під цим я маю на увазі <#RED>{name.rot_boss}а</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh boy, your expedition-issued gear isn't cutting it anymore, huh?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I'm certain <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> somewhere in the <#RED>{name.treemon_forest}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" If we can rescue her, she can start <#RED>Upgrading</> your <#RED>Armour</>."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Ой, ваша екіпіровка, видана експедицією, вже не витримує, так?\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Я впевнений, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> десь у <#RED>{3:{Name.treemon_forest}}</>.\n"
"!point\n"
"Якщо ми врятуємо її, вона зможе почати <#RED>покращувати</> ваші <#RED>обладунки</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Hey Hunter, your <#RED>Armour's</> looking a little outdated.\n"
" !point\n"
" Why don't you give <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> <#RED>Armour Rack</> a visit and get some <#RED>Upgrades</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!think\n"
"Гей, Мисливцю, ваші <#RED>обладунки</> виглядають трохи застарілими.\n"
"!point\n"
"Чому б не відвідати їх <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> на <#RED>стійку для обладунків</> та не отримати кілька <#RED>покращень</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You should think about getting some better protection, now that you're settled in.\n"
" !think\n"
" I remember seeing an <#RED>Armour</> merchant on our last Hunt, now that I think of it."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Вам варто подумати про кращий захист, тепер, коли ви вже освоїлися.\n"
"!think\n"
"Пригадую, що бачив торговця <#RED>обладунками</> на нашому останньому полюванні, тепер, коли я про це згадав."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hey Hunter, is that <#RED>Armour</> of yours strong enough...?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You might want to start buying some new pieces.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" You've seen that odd purple fellow selling <#RED>Armour</> during your Hunts, right?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Гей, Мисливцю, ваші <#RED>обладунки</> достатньо міцні...?\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Можливо, варто почати купувати нові частини.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!think\n"
"Ви бачили цю дивну фіолетову істоту, що продає <#RED>обладунки</> під час ваших полювань, так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Judging by those bruises, I'm guessing yer having some trouble taking down a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" The thing you gotta remember is that while a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</> hits hard, it's also slow to wind up. Keep an eye out for that wind up, and it'll be easier to {name.tutorial_dodge} when it finally swings.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's better to <#RED>Dodge</> than run away-- you'll stay in range to land a few <#RED>Attacks</> before the <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</> comes at you again.\n"
" !point\n"
" Plus you'll be <#RED>Invincible</> for a split second during the {name.tutorial_dodge}, so even if you're up close and personal, you won't take any <#RED>Damage</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just make sure to time it right.\n"
" player:\n"
" Thanks, teach!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Heh. Go get 'em, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Судячи з цих синців, схоже, що вам важко впоратися з <#RED>{Name.yammo_miniboss}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Пам'ятайте, що хоча <#RED>{Name.yammo_miniboss}</> сильно б'є, він повільно розганяється. Слідкуйте за його розгоном, і тобі буде легше виконати {Name.tutorial_dodge}, коли він нарешті замахнеться.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Краще <#RED>ухилятись</>, ніж тікати — так ви залишишаєтесь в зоні, щоб нанести кілька <#RED>ударів</> перед тим, як <#RED>{Name.yammo_miniboss}</> атакує знову.\n"
" !point\n"
" Крім того, ви будете <#RED>непереможні</> на частку секунди, виконуючи {Name.tutorial_dodge}, тож навіть поблизу ви не отримаєте <#RED>пошкоджень</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Просто подбайте про правильний вибір часу.\n"
" player:\n"
" Дякую, вчитель!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Хе. Вперед, Мисливцю."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Did I hear that right? You didn't know <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> is <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}'s</> grandkid?\n"
" player:\n"
" Hey, that was a private conversation!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You were talking within earshot of my armoury, that's basically <i>inviting</> me to listen in.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I don't blame you, though. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> so unassuming! \n"
" !think\n"
" It's hard to imagine they're related to <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>...\n"
" !bliss\n"
" The <i>silver fox</> who invented {name.c_konjur} power... \n"
" !shock\n"
" Ah! N-now don't tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> I said that, okay? This was a private conversation, after all!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> told you about their famous grandpappy, eh? \n"
" player:\n"
" Do you know anything else about {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Well... he was a genius. He personally designed all of <#BLUE>the Rotwood's</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-powered</> infrastructure.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...And he never let you forget it. He could be a real pain to work with.\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>You</> worked with {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Don't get the wrong idea, it wasn't anything science-y. I am and always have been a proud grunt-for-hire.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...But yeah. A couple years before the eruption, <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> hired me to train a team. We were responsible for keepin' <#BLUE>the Capital</> free of any wayward <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" Wait... there were {name_multiple.rot} <i>before</> the eruption?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Not many--not like today. I'm not surprised you never heard about them, it was kept real hush-hush. <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> was pretty clear that he didn't wanna worry folks.\n"
" !think\n"
" But every so often one would turn up. We'd get a call about a missing pet, or a garden plot that got torn up, and we'd find a <#RED>{name.rot}</> roamin' the streets.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> said they must've come from the sea, swam over from another continent, and wandered into town.\n"
" player:\n"
" But you have a different theory?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...Yeah. I do. But a gut feeling ain't proof. And it's not like it makes a difference now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Отже, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> розповів вам про свого знаменитого дідуся, га? \n"
" player:\n"
" Ти щось ще знаєш про {Name.npc_grandpa}а {Name.flitt_lastname}а?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ну... він був генієм. Особисто спроектував всю інфраструктуру <#BLUE>Ротвуда</>, що працювала завдяки <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</>.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...І ніколи не давав забути про це. Працювати з ним було непросто.\n"
" player:\n"
" <i>Ти</> працював з {3:{Name.npc_grandpa} {3:{Name.flitt_lastname}}?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Не думайте нічого наукового. Я завжди був простим найманцем.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Але так, за пару років до виверження <#BLUE>{Name.flitt_lastname}</> найняв мене тренувати команду. Ми слідкували, щоб <#BLUE>столиця</> була чиста від будь-яких некерованих <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" Стоп... тобто {name_multiple.rot} були ще <i>до</> виверження?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Не багато... не як зараз. Не дивно, що ви про них не чули, все трималося в таємниці. <#BLUE>{Name.flitt_lastname}</> чітко сказав, щоб ніхто не хвилювався.\n"
" !think\n"
" Але час від часу з'являлися. Дзвонили про зниклих домашніх тварин або пошкоджені городи, і ми знаходили <#RED>{2:{name.rot}}</>, що бродив вулицями.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.flitt_lastname}</> казав, що вони, мабуть, прийшли з моря, перепливли з іншого континенту і забрели до міста.\n"
" player:\n"
" Але ти маєш іншу теорію?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...Так. Маю, але передчуття... не доказ. І зараз це вже не має значення."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You beat up an old fox a year ago. Feel good? \n"
" !think\n"
" Everyone feels more settled after you did it.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" And that feels good to me."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>. Makes everything so... quiet.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" No wind. No bugs. No birds... \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Sometimes I stand in the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> with my <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Make a little opening, let the wind and bugs and birds in. \n"
" !angry\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> yells at me. I don't let <#RED>{name.rot}</> in!\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Just enough Wilds in. We need it. To feel connected.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" We can't live in a \"tek-mo-cricket del-oo-shun.\"\n"
" player:\n"
" \"Technocratic delusion\"? Wait... you've been hanging out with {name.npc_refiner}, haven't you?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Yes. Do I smell like nerd?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>. He made the <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>. \n"
" !agree\n"
" He loves <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>. My Granny did too. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" She kept a lot of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</> around our hut. Told me all about their powers. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" I never believed her. But I can see it now, with the <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" A lot of things Granny said feel more true now than ever."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Since you beat the old fox. Things have changed.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" When I roam the Wilds now, I actually gotta be careful. \n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.rot}'s</> changed. Meaner. Smarter, too.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" They can see through my invisibilty trick! \n"
" !angry\n"
" {name.apothecary_hiss}\n"
" !point\n"
" Now I have to be regular-sneaky-but-better."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> says since it's been a year, he's ready to congratulate you on beating <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> and saving us all. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, gee, thanks {name.npc_lunn}!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !agree\n"
" Well, it's from the both of us, but I already thanked you a year ago. I think."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Having the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> up and running this past year's made me feel a lot safer. \n"
" !point\n"
" And I have it on good authority most of the camp feels safer too! \n"
" !shrug\n"
" If their diary entries and their just-too-loud conversations are any indication."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hunter! Have you been ignoring <#BLUE>Cassandra</>? \n"
" player:\n"
" ... \"Cassandra\"? Sorry, but who's \"Cassandra\"?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" HUN-<i>TER!</> Keep it down! She'll hear you!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know Cassandra. Cassy! Cassafrass! Cassarole! \n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>The Bubble Shield!</>\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh? Oh! Oh... \"Cassandra\" is what you named the Bubble Shield.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" She's nearly a year old, so it's important! She'll start recognizing her name any moment now..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I wonder how <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}'s</> is doing out in the Wilds these days. \n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" I wish he'd come inside the <#KONJUR>Bubble</> but he'd <i>never.</>\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Bad for his brand, y'know."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Mm. I'm proud o' the work done to get the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> up. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" A crumb o' redemption on a table laden with a feast o' regret. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" But I'll take a crumb. Aye. A crumb'll do."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Talented kids, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> are. \n"
" !think\n"
" Workin' alongside 'em on the ol' <#KONJUR>{name.town_grid_cryst}</>... reminded me o' the old days... \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Good ta know this generation takes pride in their work. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Even ifn I cannae ken the patter comin' out their gobs halfa the time."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" How's yer <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</> workin', Hunter? \n"
" player:\n"
" Good! Still letting me pass through the Bubble Shield, no problem.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Och. Bein' a Gemologist comes in handy now 'n' again. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Particularly with <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, who keeps losin' her <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Tho I reckon she just wannae gab 'bout romance novels 'n' the like."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" A year gone by. We're safer, aye, but <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}'s</> in the wind. I dunnae like it. \n"
" !dubious\n"
" Even without <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> pullin' his strings, <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> was a sleekit one. \n"
" !point\n"
" Ye cannae trust the sort, 'specially when cornered. And I'd count this as bein' cornered."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" What, are ye tryin' ta blind me?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Feh."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Och! Did <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> sell ya \"invisible armour\"?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.7>Psst! Put some clothes on, Hunter. For our sake, at least.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <z 0.7>I dinnae even want t'ask.</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <z 0.7>Я навіть не хочу питати.</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Is this what comedy's come ta?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I ken wantin' ta feel a breeze, but could ya do it <i>away</> from me?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Been a year under the big pink bubble and I gotta say, I feel snug as a bug in a rug!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It's like I'm a shiny lil' jewel, nestled all safe-like in, well, a safe! Locked in tight! \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Locked in... like in a... a jail...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Y'know what, hun? We're just <i>not</> gonna dwell on that. Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> makes me feel safer, sure it does, hun. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" But don't think I forgot about <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> Grampy. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I've seen a lot of crooked types try and straighten out, only to spring back to their usual shape...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's as they say: once a crook, always a crook...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Er, well, which isn't <i>always</> true, in <i>every</> case, mind. Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Chalk it up to my years of leapin' from one, ah, kitchen to another...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I ain't never been much fer the feelin' of security. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" Always feels like the other shoe's set to drop, y'know?\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Or in this case, the bubble's set to pop! \n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ah, eh... Anyway... Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You uh, testin' a new intimidation tactic?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ви, е-е, випробовуєте нову тактику залякування?\n"
"!gesture\n"
"{Name.dojo_cough}"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Err... {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" You forget to finish dressing this morning?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Е-е... {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
"!point\n"
"Ви забули закінчити одягатися цього ранку?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\t\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" If it isn't the hero of the Battle of <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>. \n"
" player:\n"
" It feels like it <i>just</> happened... \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Heh. Yeah. That's normal, Hunter. As they write the songs and epic poems, shaping your deeds into jaunty tunes and fancy words...\n"
" !think\n"
" ... we live with the very real memories themselves. They lay in wait around corners, in shadows, in sudden noises--then we're right back there, heart racing and blades flashing.\n"
" !point\n"
" You faced something none of us ever has, Hunter. Remember that. And remember you survived it, and you're here now because of it.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Be proud. Be humble. And be ready. More challenges await. The {name.run} is never over."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Was it validating to have my read on the beloved <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</> as a bad guy confirmed? Uh, <i>YEAH.</> \n"
" !shrug\n"
" But it sucked all the same. Especially for <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>.\n"
" player:\n"
" No longer referred to as the \"precious grandchild,\" I see...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Look, I was mad at them. But they're a legit genius in their own right. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" The <#RED>{name.damselfly}</>? Running <i>without</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>? Amazing. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Makes a good case for a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-free world after all this. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" If we can put this Primeval genie back in its bottle. And that's a BIG \"if.\""
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Hunter! I'm thinking about starting a punk band!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield's</> given me some bandwidth--literally. \n"
" !think\n"
" I'm thinkin' <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> on percussion. Plays mostly the anvil, but still...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> on strings--mainly the bow. Me on lead guitar, obvs. \n"
" !point\n"
" And I was thinkin'--stay with me--<#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> on lead vocals!\n"
" !clap\n"
" All that grunting and growling and hissing? She's <i>perfect!</>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Attitude is like 90% of punk music, so I figure this group'll be, like 80% of the way there."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Visited my dad recently. In the year since you took Doc down, the woods've gotten dodgier...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But my dad seems good! I mean, good as he's been since Doc let <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> change him.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I've brought my <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> a couple times. And his <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature, it shares a similar frequency to the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>...\n"
" !think\n"
" Probably why the <#RED>{name.rot}</> leaves him alone. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Needs more research, but... It's hard to see him sometimes, so I gotta space out my visits, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I've been thinkin', my dad's connected to <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>, but still I don't know why it doesn't possess him like it did <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" It's like the connection's reversed. My dad is connected <i>to</> it, plugged into its chaotic, creative <#KONJUR>Teffressence</>, without letting its consciousness flow back into him...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" If only I could find a way for him to shut that connection off--if even temporarily..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Looking up at the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> at night... it almost looks like pink stars twinkling, doesn't it? \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Still, I can't help but wonder about the <i>real</> stars, twinkling somewhere beyond it..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Thanks to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}'s</> <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulets</> mounted into the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> body, we soar straight through the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" And the <#KONJUR>Amulets</> dampen my allergies, too! I keep one on me at all times, now-ow-AOH-AH--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" AH-<i>CHOO!!</>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That was just pollen. I think."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Nearly a year of the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, and it's holding strong, thanks to you and the team of course...\n"
" player:\n"
" How was it, working with <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" It was hard at first. Her father's madness was caused by <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>... on <i>my</> account. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" But after pouring our blood, sweat, and tears into the the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, the resentment, confusion, and strangeness--it all melted away. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" We're bonded as scientists now, and friends. We're now tuning her <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> with <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> she stole from the lab.\n"
" !think\n"
" With it, we hope to find some way to cure her father, and maybe even cure my... maybe even cure <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>. Someday."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter. It's hard to express my thanks for all you've done for us. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You've put your life on the line day-in, day-out for our quest to make a better world. \n"
" !think\n"
" Defeating <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>, stopping the <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</>, fueling the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I hesitate to think where we'd be without you.\n"
" player:\n"
" Of course, {name.npc_scout}. But it's given me purpose. That's gift enough. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-a gift? Oh dear, I... I wasn't building up to a gift. Just saying thank you. \n"
" player:\n"
" Oh! Oh. I'm sorry. Wow. I'm really embarrassed. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Oh my... well thanks for all you've done, including making this awkward, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" This scarf belonged to my... to <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>. \n"
" !think\n"
" In the year since we last saw him, I kept wearing it--out of habit, I suppose. But the hurt, betrayal, and anger lingered...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I've wanted to throw it away so many times.  \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" But I couldn't. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Perhaps this old scarf is a reminder of my hope--threadbare as it is--that he'll come back to himself, and come back to us.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Is that naive? Foolish? Maybe. Or maybe it's the same hope that keeps me fighting for our future.  \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" And we must hold onto hope--even if it's in tatters. Especially so. I believe that to my core."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hello, Hunter. Or should I say, \"The Hero of the Battle of <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>\"! \n"
" !clap\n"
" I hear your legend's even spread to <#BLUE>The Brinks</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Rousing people from their torpor to join the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> in our epic quest!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I even hear <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> is selling anniversary edition brown cloaks!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Uhh.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're not going out like that, are you?"
msgstr "!neutral \n"
"!shocked \n"
"Е-е. \n"
"!dubious \n"
"Ви ж не збираєтесь виходити в такому вигляді?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I don't think you're going to enjoy the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> ride dressed like that.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" There's a lot of wind up there..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!point\n"
"Не думаю, що вам сподобається їзда на <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</> в такому вбранні.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Там дуже вітряно..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Hunter, I know we're very casual around here.\n"
" !point\n"
" But, um. Maybe not <i>that</i> casual?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Мисливцю, я знаю, що ми тут дуже невимушені.\n"
"!point\n"
"Але, е-е. Можливо, не <i>настільки</i> невимушені?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What happened to your chest <#RED>Armour</>?\n"
" !point\n"
" You can go over to <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> <#RED>Armour Rack</> to put it back on y'know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Що сталося з вашим нагрудним <#RED>обладунком</>?\n"
"!point\n"
"Ви можете підійти до <#RED>стійки для обладунків</> <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> та повернути їх."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Um! Hunter?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Y-you're not wearing any pants."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Ем! Мисливцю?\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!point\n"
"Ви не носите штанів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ah! Um. Hunter?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Would you mind putting on some pants, please?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Ах! Е-е. Мисливцю?\n"
"!happy\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Чи не могли б ви надіти штани, будь ласка?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith]bath.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith]bath.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" It just occured to me <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> haven't bathed since we last saw them...\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm... <z 0.7>Maybe I'll add an air freshener to the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> dash.</z>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh! I didn't mean to say that out loud!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Мені здається, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> і <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> не купалися відколи ми востаннє бачили їх...\n"
" !think\n"
" Хмм... <z 0.7>Можливо, я додам освіжувач повітря в приладову панель <#RED>{2:{Name.i_damselfly}}.</z>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ой! Я не хотів сказати це вголос!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" W-why, my good <#BLUE>{player.species}</>... don't tell me you're d-d-d...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Dessstitute!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Чому ж, мій дорогий <#BLUE>{player.species}</>... не кажіть мені, що ви...\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Бінессенький!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmmm....\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Lossst a bet, did you?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Хммм....\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Програли парі, так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" No ssshirt?? No ssshoes??\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Still ssservice."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Немає сссорочки?? Немає сссандалів??\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Все одно обссслуговую."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[is_wearing_body].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmmm....\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well I guess I won't be taking the ssshirt off your back today!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Хммм....\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Ну, думаю, сьогодні я не зніму з вас сссорочку!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.7>(sniff sniff)</z> Don't you just love the smell of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</> in the morning?\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ha</i>-CHOO."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.7>(нюх, нюх)</z> Ви ж любите вранці запах <#KONJUR>{2:{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}}</>?\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ап</i>-ЧХИИ."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout,struggling_on_eggzy]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout,struggling_on_eggzy]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Okay, okay. This is serious. I promise I'm out of egg yolks.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Egg jokes! I meant to say egg jokes!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Err... sorry.\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>Come on {name.npc_scout}, get it together! You're better than this!</z>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Гаразд, гаразд. Це серйозно. Обіцяю, що більше не буде жарених яєць.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Жартів про яйця! Я мав на увазі жартів про яйця!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ем... вибачте.\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.7>Зберись, {Name.npc_scout}, ти кращий за це!</z>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" There's something sparkling deep into this cavern.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !angry\n"
" Let's get cracking, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shock\n"
" The Anti-<#RED>{name.rot}</> Security Systems my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> built are still active.\n"
" !point\n"
" They can't discern between <#RED>{name.rot}</> and not, so stay on guard.\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm. Not his <i>best</> design..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" The <#BLUE>City Center</> used to be so full of life.\n"
" !point\n"
" Now it's so full of <#RED>{name.rot}</>!\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Let's do something about that, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano_r2,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Pipeline Energy Grid</> still works here.\n"
" !think\n"
" Maybe because it's close to the <#BLUE>Volcano</>? Hmm..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Good luck out there, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" Don't let the <#RED>Wind</> push you around."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Удачі вам, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Не дозволяйте <#RED>вітру</> зіштовхнути вас."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Err... Just a heads up.\n"
" !point\n"
" I think you might get a little chilly in there, friend."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Е-е... Просто попередження.\n"
"!point\n"
"Я думаю, що вам може там стати трохи холодно, друже."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Haha, uh...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Don't you look sufficiently, um. Breezy."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ха-ха, е-е...\n"
"!happy\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Ви виглядаєте достатньо, е-е. Прохолодно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I keep flying over the woods but no sign of <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Where on earth could he be?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> should be somewhere ahead.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" He's tough, but not \"never get rescued\" tough."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Hunter! Look out for <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm sure I smelt smelting. <i>Smelled</> smelting. You know what I mean."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>?? Are you in there? \n"
" !think\n"
" Silence. Classic <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>. Go find him!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].5"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !scared\n"
" I'm sure <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>'s okay. But he'd be okayer with us!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I usually like the c-cold. \n"
" !angry\n"
" But this? Th-th-this is a m-mean cold."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh, uh... Hunter? I know it's <#BLUE>Cold</> out here no matter what, but...\n"
" !point\n"
" I think you are going to be <i>particularly</i> cold.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" If you catch my... <i>drift</> ..."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!nervous\n"
"О, е-е... Мисливцю? Я знаю, що тут завжди <#BLUE>холодно</>, але...\n"
"!point\n"
"Думаю, що вам буде <i>особливо</i> холодно.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Якщо ви розумієте, про що я... <i>маю на увазі</>..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I swear! Someone's playing music!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" You believe me... right?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Let's get goin', Hunter!\n"
" !agree\n"
" There's <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</> to be had."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ходімо, Мисливцю!\n"
" !agree\n"
" Тут є <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" If you see <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</>, keep an eye out for her roots.\n"
" !clap\n"
" That bark's got bite!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Sorry. I'll stay here."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'm trusting you to avenge my <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>, Hunter.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" <#RED>{name.megatreemon}</> can't get away with this."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я довіряю вам помститися за мій <#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}</>, Мисливцю.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" <#RED>{Name.megatreemon}</> так просто не втече."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I think <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> near. Why? I heard sewing. \n"
" !agree\n"
" Very vigorous sewing."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !scared\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> ahead, I just know it. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, I hope it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter, <#RED>Ber</>--EEP! \n"
" !nervous\n"
" Well, my <i>foot</> found one of <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> sewing needles. Keep an eye out for her!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'm certain <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> near. Please, Hunter, find her!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].5"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> must be near. \n"
" !scared\n"
" If she's been eaten, oh! She'll be SO mad!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It's such a relief to have <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> back safe and sound.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I just hope we find <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> soon..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Яке полегшення, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> повернулася ціла і неушкоджена.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Сподіваюся, ми скоро знайдемо <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hey Hunter... you don't think Hamish is <i>avoiding</> us, do you?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No, that's crazy.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I-I'm a good boss! You think so, right...?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю... ви ж не думаєте, що Гаміш <i>уникає</> нас?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ні, це безглуздо.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я хороший бос! Ви ж так думаєте, чи не так...?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I hope <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> alright.\n"
" !scared\n"
" She could be halfway through a <#RED>{name.yammo}'s</> digestive tract by now!"
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я сподіваюся, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> в порядку.\n"
" !scared\n"
" Вона вже могла пройти половину харчового тракту <#RED>{Name.yammo}</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I keep flying over the woods but I haven't seen <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> anywhere.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" There's no way she got <i>that</i> far!"
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я продовжую літати над лісом, але ніде не бачив <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Вона ж не могла зайти <i>так</i> далеко!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Let's get back out there and search for <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The sooner we find her, the sooner I can sleep again."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Повернімося туди та пошукаємо <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Чим швидше ми її знайдемо, тим швидше я зможу заснути."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !sigh\n"
" Things to do, people to save.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We should get back to the search."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !sigh\n"
" Справа купа, мешканців рятувати треба.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Повертаймося до пошуків."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].5"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I hired <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> to do upkeep and modifications for the whole camp.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Our Hunters won't stand a chance against the <#RED>{name.rot}</> without her."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я найняв <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> для обслуговування та модифікації всього табору.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Наші Мисливці не матимуть жодних шансів проти <#RED>{name.rot}</> без неї."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].6"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !scared\n"
" I hope <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> confidence doesn't get her into any trouble out there.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" She's, uh, not the best at risk assessment."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !scared\n"
" Я сподіваюся, що впевненість не втягне <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> в проблеми.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Вона, е-е, не найкраща в оцінці ризиків."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_armorsmith].7"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Don't forget, we've got people to go rescue.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" We should get back to it."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Не забувайте, у нас є кого рятувати.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Потрібно повертатися до справи."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I hope <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> is alright.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" He looks tough, but he's not a fighter, y'know."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я сподіваюся, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> в порядку.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Він виглядає крутим, але він не боєць, знаєте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" I think I spotted some of <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}'s</> tools from up in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" But... no <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" Мені здається, я помітив деякі інструменти <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> літаючи на <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</>...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Але... не <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" Let's get back out there and look for <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Next time I lead an expedition, I'm giving everyone flare guns."
msgstr "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" Повернімось туди та пошукаємо <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Наступного разу, коли я очолю експедицію, я роздам усім сигнальні пістолети."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" As expedition leader, it's my job to make these {name_multiple.run} as smooth as I can for you."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Everything you teach me is gonna make this {name.run} better, for you <i>and</i> the other Hunters!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Don't worry. I monitor all your {name_multiple.run} to support you the best I can."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith]tea.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith]tea.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> are getting hungry about now.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'll see if I can scrounge up some tea before they get back."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Цікаво, чи <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> і <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> зараз голодні.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я подивлюсь, чи зможу знайти чай, перш ніж вони повернуться."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> is lookin' mighty empty."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ця <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> виглядає занадто порожньо."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner]NOT[has_charged_corestone_weapon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner]NOT[has_charged_corestone_weapon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Your <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> isn't charged.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> says that's like walking around with no pants on."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[corestone_weapon_equipped,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[charged_corestone_weapon_equipped,has_any_boss_weapon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> needs to be <#RED>Charged</> before I can finish it.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Killin' a <#RED>{name.elite_prefix} {name.rot_boss}</> with it'll do the trick."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Цю <#RED>{2:{name.weapon_crystal}}</> потрібно <#RED>зарядити</>, перш ніж я зможу її завершити.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Убивство нею <#RED>{4:{name.elite_prefix}} {2:{name.rot_boss}}</> має допомогти."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[drunken,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[drunken,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" [TEMP] I might have a cure for your affliction..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" [TEMP] У мене, можливо, є ліки проти вашої недуги..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Good memories in this lab...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ... bad ones, too. Hm. Let's go see the old fox, huh?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I doubt <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</> is gonna be stoked to see me."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If you're taking requests, I'd like to see the old fox get thumped but good."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Why keep the old fox waiting?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_tefframech_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Watch out for <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> in there. \n"
" !think\n"
" It's gonna get... emotional."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_thatcher_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner]NOT[has_seen_thatcher].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[first_run_in_thatcher_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner]NOT[has_seen_thatcher].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You heard <i>guitar</> in <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp}</>? <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> rocking? That rules."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith} was really impressed with the stitching on my cowl!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...She looked a little greener than usual after I told her how I made it, though."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> була вражена швами на моєму капюшоні!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Але вона виглядала трохи зеленішою після того, як я розповів, як його зробив."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm getting a lot better at talking to folks.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" But I still need to take a break sometimes."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" У мене вже краще виходить спілкуватися з іншими.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Але іноді мені все ще треба перепочити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Taking care of plants is easy.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" They tell you what they need without talking."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Доглядати за рослинами легко.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Вони кажуть, що їм потрібно, без слів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> never seems to run out of things to say.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Maybe that's because she repeats what <i>other</> people say, too."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" У <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> ніколи не вичерпується теми для розмов.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" ...Можливо, це тому, що вона повторює те, що говорять <i>інші</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I miss Granny's hut. And our garden.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...But it's overrun with <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> now. So."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Я сумую за хатинкою бабусі. І нашим садом.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Але тепер його заполонили <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>. Ну що ж."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" I like watching the plants grow.\n"
" !agree\n"
" They're doing such a good job."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" Я люблю спостерігати, як ростуть рослини.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Вони чудово справляються."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> keeps talking about a place called 'the Brinks'?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Is that where the sky ships took everybody?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> постійно говорить про місце, яке називається 'Брінкс'?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Це туди небесні кораблі відвезли всіх?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" There's nothing wrong with dirt. It's natural.\n"
" !angry\n"
" What's <i>weird</> is everyone telling me to 'wash my hands' and 'stop wiping dirt in your armpits'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Everyone here talks so much.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" It's so tiring..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Усі тут так багато говорять.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Це так втомлює..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you ever feel bad for the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I do sometimes. It's not really their fault they're like that."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Вам коли-небудь було шкода <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Мені іноді буває. Вони ж не винні, що такі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].9"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I was just thinking...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...about how much I want to take a nap."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Я щойно думала...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" ...як би добре було подрімати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I really miss my Granny. Even though I know a part of her is always close by.\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean her spirit?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, no. Her pelt. Granny left me instructions for how to prepare it when she passed. I like knowing she'll always be close, even now that she's gone.\n"
" player:\n"
" Her... <i>pelt</>? You mean... your cowl is...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" She turned out really well, didn't she? I think she'd be proud of my work.\n"
" player:\n"
" I... um... excuse me, I think I need to go for a walk...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Okay."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Дуже сумую за своєю бабусею. Хоча знаю, що частинка її завжди поруч.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ти маєш на увазі її дух?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" О, ні. Її шкуру. Бабуся залишила мені інструкції, як її підготувати після смерті. Мені подобається відчувати, що вона й досі поряд.\n"
" player:\n"
" Її... <i>шкуру</>? Ти маєш на увазі... твоя накидка це...?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Вона вийшла чудово, чи не так? Думаю, вона була б мною горда.\n"
" player:\n"
" Я... е-е... вибач, мені, мабуть, треба пройтися...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Гаразд."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_apothecary_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I <i>want</> to like being around people. But it's hard sometimes.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...What if I never get used to it?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я <i>хочу</> подобатися іншим. Але це складно.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...Що як я так і не звикну?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know what makes me a good friend? I'm a great secret-keeper.\n"
" !point\n"
" For example, I've never told anyone that <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> self-conscious about their snout."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Знаєте, що робить мене хорошим другом? Я чудово вмію зберігати таємниці.\n"
" !point\n"
" Наприклад, я ніколи нікому не казав, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> комплексує через свій ніс."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You wouldn't believe the kinds of juicy secrets people will just write down for anyone to see!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I mean sure, they write it in a 'diary' or whatever, but what's to stop someone from taking a little peek when no one's around?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви не повірите, які пікантні секрети просто записують, щоб їх міг побачити кожен!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ну, вони називають це 'щоденником' чи якось так, але що завадить комусь підглянути, коли нікого поруч немає?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!dejected\n"
" Ugh. {name.rot} stains just never wash out right...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" It's better to just cut around the stain and sew on a new patch of fabric."
msgstr "!dejected\n"
" Уф. Плями від {2:{name.rot}} ніколи не відпираються як слід...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Краще просто вирізати пляму та пришити нову латочку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Hey, Hunter! What's a juicy secret you've never told anyone before?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Aww, don't give me that look. I was just <i>asking!</>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю! Яку соковиту таємницю ви нікому не розповідали?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Не дивіться на мене так. Я просто <i>спитала!</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Some people say I won't amount to anything, then other people say I'm 'too much'.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Well which is it? Make up your minds!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Дехто каже, що я ні на що не здатна, інші — що я 'занадто' вміла.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" То як же насправді? Вирішіть нарешті!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Why would I ever be lonely when I've got <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> for company?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Чому я маю відчувати себе самотньою, якщо у мене є <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I think the fact that I have better conversations with my leather cutter than with most people says more about most people than it does about me."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я думаю, що той факт, що я краще спілкуюся зі своїм різаком для шкіри, ніж з більшістю істот, більше говорить про більшість істот, ніж про мене."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and Balki are still going strong. I feel kinda silly for getting so worked up over thinking they wouldn't want me around. We still hang out all the time!\n"
" !think\n"
" But I think it's good that <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I aren't spending <i>all</> our time together anymore.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" It was like we shared a brain! I guess there <i>is</> such a thing as being too close."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> та Балкі досі разом. Мені трохи соромно, що я так переживала, думаючи, що я буду зайвою. Ми все ще проводимо час разом!\n"
" !think\n"
" Але добре, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> і я більше не проводимо <i>весь</> час разом.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Було наче ми ділили один мозок! Мабуть, існує таке поняття, <i>як</> занадто близькі стосунки."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> was a little jealous of Balki at first, but they seem to be getting along better now.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I think with a little time, they'll be great friends!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Спочатку <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> ревнував до Балкі, але зараз вони ладнають краще.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Думаю, з часом вони стануть чудовими друзями!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_armorsmith_is_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Sorry <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> been giving you the silent treatment, Hunter.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" I think he's still a little upset about the whole whetstone thing."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Вибач, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> ігнорує тебе, Мисливцю.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Думаю, він ще трохи засмучений через точильний камінь."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Maybe I've got time ta read one more page... <z 0.7>It's sure nice havin' something ta mark my spot-- I can finally stop re-reading the first chapter...</z>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Och-- err, Hunter! ...How long have ye been standin' there?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ye wanna know where I got this scar, eh?\n"
" !think\n"
" Ah... just a wee 'workplace accident'... It happens in my line o' work.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" 'Specially when a customer and I didnae see eye-to-eye on a payment plan."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хочете знати, де я отримав цей шрам?\n"
" !think\n"
" Ах... просто маленький \"виробничий інцидент\"... Таке трапляється в моїй роботі.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Особливо коли клієнт і я не дійшли згоди щодо плану оплати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Here's a free bit of advice, Hunter-- ye'll sleep better knowin' ye got a sharp blade within arm's reach.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I like ta keep mine under the pillow, meself."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Ось маленька порада, Мисливцю... спати буде спокійніше, знаючи, що гострий клинок під рукою.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я тримаю свій під подушкою."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...<z 0.7>'Henri'? Sure doesnae look like an 'Henri' ta me...</z> Oi, Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" Would ye tell yer <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> she cannae name other people's tools?!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" ...<z 0.7>'Генрі'? Не виглядає як 'Генрі', як на мене...</z> Ой, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Скажи своєму <#BLUE>{2:{name.job_armorsmith}}</>, що вона не може називати інструменти інших?!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. Looks like ye've been in a scrape or two.\n"
" !point\n"
" Mind yerself out there."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хм. Схоже, ви мали пару неприємностей.\n"
" !point\n"
" Бережіть себе."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_fortification_level_0].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_4,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_fortification_level_0].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Want to upgrade yer weapons even more?\n"
" !point\n"
" I'll need materials. Check my list on the <#RED>Weapon Racks</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" They called me 'Hamish the Hammer' back in the Guild.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" On account o' my soft touch 'n way with words."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" В гільдії мене називали 'Гаміш-Молот'.\n"
" !gesture \n"
" Завдяки моєму м'якому підходу та вмінню спілкуватися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" The Blacksmith's Guild was like a big family.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye never turn yer back on family... gives 'em too clear of a shot at yer vital parts."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Гільдія ковалів була як велика родина.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ніколи не відвертайтесь від родини... це дає їм змогу поцілити у ваші життєво важливі органи."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ye think a <#RED>{name.yammo}'s</> got a mean mug?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ye shoulda met my old Guildmaster."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви думаєте, що у <#RED>{Name.yammo</> сердите обличчя?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Бачили б ви мого старого майстра гільдії."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph. Nice racket <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> got goin' here. Coulda make a mighty lucrative business haulin' {name.konjur} back ta <#BLUE>the Brinks</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Heh. 'Course, the kit's got much loftier goals than that."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Хм. Гарна справа у <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_scout}}</>. Можна було б добре заробити, перевозивши {name.konjur} у <#BLUE>Брінкс</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Але, звісно, у цього хлопця є набагато більш амбітні цілі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" The Blacksmith's Guild takes care o' its own.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" 'Course, if ye cross 'em, they'll 'take care' of ye in a more permanent sorta way."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Гільдія ковалів піклується про своїх.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Але якщо перейти дорогу, вони 'попіклуються' про вас... назавжди."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" A lot's happened in the last ten years...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I cannae help but wonder if things really can go back ta the way they were."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" За останні десять років сталося багато чого...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Цікаво, чи можна все повернути як раніше."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmph. <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> was goin' on about how I'm 'unapproachable'.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Doesn't seem ta stop her from comin' over and talkin' my ear off, though."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Хм. <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> казала, що я 'недоступний'.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" ...Але це не заважає їй приходити і теревенити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>. A <i>romantasy</> fan?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Beneath his iron exterior lies a soft molten core. Should've known."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" I suppose I'd call us... friends. \n"
" !points\n"
" Dunnae tell anyone I said that."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_6,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_blacksmith_is_level_6,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" All <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> does is grunt and work.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" He's the perfect collaborator!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, uh, sorry I'm just a bit busy with... vegetable sorting.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Gotta make sure all those sneaky veggies are in order, y'know?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ой, вибачте, я трохи зайнята... сортуванням овочів.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Треба ж стежити, щоб усі підступні овочі були на своєму місці, ви ж знаєте?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2"
msgid "!angry\n"
" Hey, wouldya tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> to stop pokin' her nose around my kitchen?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Doesn't she have more important things to do?"
msgstr "!angry\n"
"Гей, скажіть <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</>, щоб не пхала носа на мою кухню!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Невже в неї немає важливіших справ?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hunter... <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me somethin' awful.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" He said that on your Hunts you find <#KONJUR>Teffra Crystals</> and... <i>smash them?!</>\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Tell me it ain't true! Do you have any idea how much those'd be worth in <#BLUE>the Brinks?!</>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Er, I mean, how <i>pretty</> they are when they're all big and whole?!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You haven't overheard any gripin' about my cookin' have you?\n"
" !point\n"
" Comments flyin' about the likes of 'she don't know a fritter from a flambé'?\n"
" !angry\n"
" I know what I'm doin'! Some folks just don't appreciate simple, unassumin', country-style food, is all."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" As soon as I'm done cookin', there's all these dishes to clean.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Then when I'm done cleanin' the dishes, it's time to cook again.\n"
" !scared\n"
" Where does it end?!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Щойно закінчу готувати – одразу треба мити посуд.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" А щойно закінчу мити посуд – знову треба готувати.\n"
" !scared\n"
" Де цьому кінець?!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_2,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I just found <#RED>{name.blarmadillo}</> spit is a decent replacement for butter when you're in a pinch.\n"
" !think\n"
" Amazin' what you learn when you run out of butter..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_9,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_at_least_level_9,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know, I tried ta backtrack some fibs I told <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, tryin' ta rile him up some. Y'know, sowing discord 'n' the like.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" But he just laughed! Said nothin' riles him up no more--'cept a pretty face? Pretty sure he gave me a wink, too!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Is <i>he</> prone ta fibbin'? <z 0.7>And is he single?</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'd say my cookin's a might bit improved in the past year, wouldn't you, Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" It's certainly gotten hotter!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ya think cookin's all about the food, but it's <i>also</> about turnin' the grill on."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> levels in yer meals up to your likin', Hunter?\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, yes. Powers are still popping, {name.npc_cook}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ah good, good. I haveta remember to <i>not</> put it in everyone else's meals, such that I wrote it on my hand...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh! Seems like I washed it off. Strange. I never wash my hands before cookin'..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Nice of my sister Marigold to leave me with this cookery cart, at least.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Though I hope she gave the original owner just a <i>mild</> concussion to steal it..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Hey Hunter! Wanna taste-test this new recipe I've been workin' on?\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'm experimentin' with <i>salt!</>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю! Хочете спробувати новий рецепт?\n"
" !clap\n"
" Експериментую з <i>сіллю!</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did ya know there's a kitchen tool made <i>just</> for beatin' eggs? Crazy stuff!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви знали, що є кухонний інструмент створений <i>саме</> для збивання яєць? Дивовижно!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I had a crazy dream last night--a blue mountain goat in a bonnet was teachin' me how ta cook so as to feed a giant mouth in the sky.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I gotta eat more cheese right before bed! It was a HOOT!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did ya notice anything special about the last dish I gave you?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It wasn't raw in the center! I'm thinkin' of callin' that \"a la Glorabelle.\""
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви помітили щось особливе в останній страві?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Вона не була сирою всередині! Думаю, назву це \"а-ля Ґлорабель\"."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know, <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> seems scary and gruff, but he's really just a big pussycat when you get to know him.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ulp--Don't tell him I said that."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Знаєте, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> страшний і суворий, але насправді ласкавий, коли знаєте його.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" Ой...Не кажіть йому цього."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].7"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Who wants to lick the batter from this bowl?\n"
" player:\n"
" I will!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Great! One less dish to clean."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Хто хоче злизати тісто з миски?\n"
" player:\n"
" Я можу!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Чудово! На одну миску менше мити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].8"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" While I'm gettin' everythin' out in the open... I guess I oughta tell ya the <#RED>Secret Ingredient</> I've been puttin' in your lunches.\n"
" player:\n"
" Well we already know it's {name.konjur}, right?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Yeeeaaahhh... that, and leftover <#RED>{name.rot}</> parts.\n"
" player:\n"
" Ah. That... explains a lot.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I could stop adding it, if'n ya wanted?\n"
" player:\n"
" Nah. Now I think I'd miss the flavour."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hey! W-where's the <#RED>Brooch</> I always keep next to my cot?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" My Granny gave that to me..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ей! Де <#RED>брошка</>, що завжди біля ліжка?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Її мені дала бабуся..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" It's the weirdest thing... I'm <i>sure</> I left some extra <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}</> next to my workbench...\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>, you didn't borrow them, did you?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Дивно... Я <i>точно</> залишила трохи <#KONJUR>{2:{name_multiple.konjur_soul_lesser}}</> біля мого верстата...\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>, ти ж їх не брав, правда?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Haven't seen my satchel of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</> around, have ye, Hunter?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Mark me words. There's somethin' fishy goin' on around here..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви не бачили мою сумку з <#KONJUR>{2:{name_multiple.gem}}</>, Мисливцю?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Кажу вам, тут щось дивне..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> keeps askin' about my marigold flower... did you tell her 'bout my sister?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Y'know, I told ya about her in strictest confidence, now. Don't. Betray. Me. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Now who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Huh. My bag of <#KONJUR>Treats</> is feeling a bit light.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>Someone's</> been helpin' themselves while I wasn't looking..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Хм. Моя сумка з <#KONJUR>смаколиками</> здається полегшала.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>Хтось</> відсипав, поки я не дивився..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_cook_is_level_7,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Where are those <#KONJUR>Ingots</> I've been saving? I could have <i>sworn</> I put them right over here...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I-I'm sure they must be around here somewhere. I just need to keep looking!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Де ті <#KONJUR>злитки</>, що я зберігав? Я міг би <i>присягнутися</>, що поклав їх саме тут...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я-я впевнений, що вони десь тут. Потрібно тільки продовжувати шукати!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_refiner_is_level_1,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_refiner_is_level_1,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know, I thought the <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> I stole from the Lab was the only one.\n"
" !point\n"
" But <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> claimed he could forge another right here!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I told him he was nuts! <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</> famously can't be forged--it's forge fuel! <i>I</> told <i>him</> that!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But the mad cat, he did the thing. And when you showed me that button pin <#RED>Souvenir</>, imbued with <#KONJUR>Teffressence</>?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It confirmed my theory of how the <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> worked.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you took down a <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</> with the <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>, its <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</> would leap into it, charging it with its chaotic power! \n"
" !notebook\n"
" I've since discovered that the <#KONJUR>Primeval \"Entity\"</> possesses <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> by imbuing their <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</>-like Hearts with its <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</>.\n"
" !agree\n"
" That <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffressence</> is a conduit back to the <#KONJUR>Primeval Source</> itself, allowin' it to strum the strings and make 'em dance, so to speak. \n"
" !think\n"
" Thing I can't figure out is, why wouldn't it leap into <i>you?</> You down enough <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> to be like 99% <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_soul_lesser}</> by now...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're a conundrum, Hunter... A lucky conundrum indeed."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Always glad to see you in one piece, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" Stay that way, okay?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Завжди радий бачити вас в цілості, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Залишайтеся таким, добре?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" It's so eerie hearing the <#RED>Rot</> calls at night.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I had a hard time sleeping the first couple nights we camped here."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Моторошно чути крики <#RED>гнильця</> вночі.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Перші кілька ночей, які ми провели тут, мені було важко заснути."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget to stop and smell the flowers every now and then.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Unless they're <#RED>Rot-infected</>. I wouldn't recommend smelling those."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не забувай інколи зупинятися і нюхати квіти.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Якщо тільки вони не <#RED>заражені гниллю</>. Я б не радив їх нюхати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't let the pressure get to you, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" We're all in this fight together!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Не дозволяйте тиску впливати на вас, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ми всі в цій боротьбі разом!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_3,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm... <z 0.7>How will I wash my mug without accidentally wiping off the Hunter's writing?</z>\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ohh... <z 0.7>This truly is a dilemma.</z>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Хмм... <z 0.7>Як мені помити кухоль, щоб випадково не стерти напис Мисливець?</z>\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ох... <z 0.7>Це справжня дилема.</z>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hey Hunter... when this expedition is over, do you think we'll all still stay in touch?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ah, I'm thinking too far ahead. We need to stay focused on the mission in front of us!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю... як думаєте, коли ця експедиція закінчиться, ми й надалі спілкуватимемось?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ага, забігаю надто далеко. Треба зосередитися на поточному завданні!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_at_least_level_5,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I've been thinking about giving the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> a new coat of paint, but there's so many colours to choose from! Should I paint it a sky blue? Burnt orange? Forest green?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" And then there's the trim to consider! Should it match or contrast?!\n"
" !angry\n"
" C'mon, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>! A leader needs to be ready to make these kinds of important decisions!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Думаю над тим, щоб перефарбувати <#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}</>, але стільки кольорів на вибір! Може, небесно-блакитний? Палений помаранчевий? Лісово-зелений?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" А ще ж є обрамлення! Воно має бути однакового кольору чи контрастного?!\n"
" !angry\n"
" Та ну, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</>! Лідер має бути готовий ухвалювати такі важливі рішення!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[friend_npc_scout_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hunter, when all this is over... let's take the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> up above the smog-cover and see the stars.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What do you think?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Мисливцю, коли все це завершиться... нумо піднімімося на <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</> вище за туман і подивимося на зорі.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Як вам така ідея?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_blarmadillo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_blarmadillo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You really have nerves of steel, Hunter.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Not many folks could've faced that <#RED>{name.blarmadillo_miniboss}</> head-on and come out on top!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" У вас справді залізні нерви, Мисливцю.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Не багато хто зміг би вийти переможцем після зустрічі з <#RED>{Name.blarmadillo_miniboss}</> лоб в лоб!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_cabbageroll_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_cabbageroll_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" You took down the <#RED>{name.cabbageroll_miniboss}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder... does that make you the new <#RED>{name.cabbageroll}</> ruler by default?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We'll see if they send an emissary."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ви перемогли <#RED>{2:{Name.cabbageroll_miniboss}}</>!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Цікаво... чи робить це вас новим правителем <#RED>{3:{Name.cabbageroll}}</> за замовчуванням?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Побачимо, чи надішлють вони свого представника."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_floracrane_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_floracrane_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Bingo, bango, bongo! That foul fowl is gonezo!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Sorry for the outburst. I just really don't like birds."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_gnarlic_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_gnarlic_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" That right there is the sweet smell of victory!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Err, well... maybe 'sweet' isn't the right word... but the <i>pungent stink</> of victory doesn't quite roll off the tongue the same way."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Ось воно — солодкий запах перемоги!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ем, що ж... можливо, 'солодкий' — не зовсім точне слово... але <i>пекучий сморід</> перемоги не звучить так елегантно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_gourdo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_gourdo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Twice the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot_boss}</>, and you still came out on top! You're really something else, Hunter.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" It's almost a little scary sometimes!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Двоє <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot_boss}}</>, і ви все одно перемогли! Ви дійсно особливі, Мисливцю.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Іноді це навіть трохи лякає!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hunter. <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}'s</>. Been sniffing around my garden.\n"
" player:\n"
" She was really excited about it. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" A bit too excited. Buzzing around me like an aphid. Do I do this? Have I tried that? \n"
" !dubious\n"
" Is it her <#BLUE>Grandpa</> that wants to kill everything?\n"
" player:\n"
" Er, no. Her dad's the weird guy in the woods, though. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh! Him. ...Maybe I like her, then."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Gemsmiths such as meself rub elbows with miners from time to time. \n"
" !agree\n"
" I know <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}'s</> pa. <i>Knew,</> rather. Not closely, mind. \n"
" player:\n"
" What was he like... before?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" A studious 'n' serious {name.species_ogre}. Adored his wee lass somethin' fierce. Och, poor <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Never put two and two together he was the feller in the woods. Math were never me strong suit. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" Seein' that... Who knows what a <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> of <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra'd</> do. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Careful, Hunter. Who knows what toll it's taken on <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</>..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A <#KONJUR>Second Eruption's</> going to come and wipe everyone out?\n"
" !angry\n"
" I just got to know them!\n"
" player:\n"
" Um, you'd... y'know what? Nevermind.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ugh. Fine. Yes, I'd... I'd <i>miss</> them. Gross. Gross you made me say it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Whenever I was a bad little kid, Granny'd tell me the story about a dragon named <#KONJUR>Teffrey</>. \n"
" !point\n"
" <#KONJUR>Teffrey's</> breath turned bad kids into <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" I never got scared, but Granny <i>did</> say <#KONJUR>Teffrey'd</> turned into <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>. \n"
" player:\n"
" Guess Teffrey had been naughty himself. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" No. He just held in a sneeze."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" My fingertips are tingling... Is... is there a new <#RED>Diary</> nearby?\n"
" player:\n"
" Weird but yes. {name.npc_refiner} gave {name.npc_scout} Grandpa's Diary.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" WHAT?! <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> kept a <#RED>Diary</>?! And it's HERE?!\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Y-you're right, <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> my friend. We don't steal friends' diaries... \n"
" !angry\n"
" Even if it's <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>, your admittedly-weird-crush's diary... \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Woooo-SHAAAAhhhh....\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's passed. Phew! Am I glad I have friends like you and <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> to talk me down. \n"
" player:\n"
" Uh, yeah. Don't mention it.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh, I <i>won't.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Word on the unpaved paths is <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> is trying to cause a <i>Second</> Eruption?\n"
" player:\n"
" That's right. Don't worry--we won't let that happen.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" IF that's happening. I mean, <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> said this, right? Who is she, again? \n"
" !shock\n"
" I heard she got fired for theft! Stole that <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</>. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Disgruntled employees will say anything. I once said an old boss dyed some of my hair white! \n"
" !shrug\n"
" I was just getting older but... I just can't believe sweet, handsome <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</> would do something evil.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" He wouldn't... right?\n"
" player:\n"
" Either way, we have to find out.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !think\n"
" I guess that's better than wondering..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hunter! Did you hear about this new kind of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>? \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" \"<#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>,\" they're calling it. Strong stuff, they're saying. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" I even heard it's the putrified remains of a long-dead ancient dragon god named something like <#KONJUR>'Teffrey'</>? \n"
" !scared\n"
" And that if it's awoken from its slumber, it will rain fury down upon our land, sparing none? \n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Good thing it's just a rumour, huh?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Dunnae worry about <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>, Hunter. They're made o' tougher steel than ya think.\n"
" !think\n"
" Than <i>they</> think, even. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" When hammer meets anvil, and they're snout ta snout with the old fox, they'll hold up. \n"
" !point\n"
" 'Course, should it come ta fisticuffs--get in there, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" (Preferably with a solid piece of kit.)"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Where does all this power come from, Hunter? <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>, <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>--the lot of it.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" No one--<#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> included--stopped for a second ta think o' that.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We all just started usin' it. Meself included. Like 'twas ours ta wield as we saw fit. \n"
" !think\n"
" Stands ta reason we oughta pay a price. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" But a <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> o' <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</>? That's a bill I refuse ta pay.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Go get 'em, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Do I look like a roast <#RED>{name.meowl}</> to you?\n"
" player:\n"
" Uh... no? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Then why're y'all pullin' my juicy, succulent leg like one with all this \"<#KONJUR>Second Eruption</>\" bunkum?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Y'all don't like my cookin' and want me to run for the hills? Well it won't work! \n"
" !point\n"
" I know a liar when I am one--er, see one! \n"
" player:\n"
" We're not lying, {name.npc_cook}! We... <z 0.7>love...</> your cooking!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Well that's all you had ta say, darlin'!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" What would you say to a nice last meal before headin' off to certain death in <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>, darlin'?\n"
" player:\n"
" We're... gonna be fine... I think?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Why, that's the spirit, hun!\n"
" !point\n"
" Tell you what: I'll cook it, and you just give it to <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> for <i>his</> last meal, if'n it swings that way. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'll make sure it's got a real soft texture for the ol' boy, to boot."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm. <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</>... Sounds mighty old, mighty rare, and mighty... <i>expensive</> ...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" A gal could think of a lotta things it could buy her...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" ... <#BLUE>{name.town}</>. For her <#BLUE>{name.town}</>, I mean. Besides, me, the <#BLUE>{name.town}</>--what's the difference, anymore? Hahaha.\n"
" !point\n"
" You oughta think about nabbin' some on your heist in <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>. Just sayin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Look. I gave <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> extra inhalers for the Hunt into <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Said I'd tell you to get 'em out of there if their health took a hit around all that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>. \n"
" !cough\n"
" But the darn fool fox said no! {name.dojo_cough} \n"
" !point\n"
" Said you'd <i>have</> to go on and stop their grandpappy. \n"
" player:\n"
" They're right, but... \n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Darn right they're right! So you go on, and you end this. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" ...no matter what."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Before you head off on the Hunt to end all Hunts, I wanna say somethin'. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" It's been an honour trainin' you. You've grown into one of the truest Hunters my remainin' eye has seen. \n"
" player:\n"
" Stop it, {name.npc_dojo_master}, before you make me cry!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" I'm a bit ashamed to admit this next bit, but day one, I was dead sure you were gonna be <#RED>{name.rot}</> food.\n"
" !point\n"
" In fact, I even called you \"<#RED>{name.rot}</>-Food\" in my head for a while 'cause I plum forgot your name. \n"
" player:\n"
" Stop it, {name.npc_dojo_master}, before you make me <i>actually</> cry!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Alls I'm sayin' is, I'm very happy to be proven wrong, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,wf_town_has_refiner]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" A tip, Hunter. Do <i>not</> underestimate <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>. \n"
" !disagree\n"
" He may be a frail, old fox, but dumb, he is not. \n"
" !point\n"
" He knows you're comin'. Knows <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> is comin'. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" And with the unknown of <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</> in his corner?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Be ready for anythin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Dad and I used to work in here together. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I miss those times."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I thought I'd made it big when I got this job. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Big mistake, more like it. Hm."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What, did we come here for the sights?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'll never get sick of you whoopin' that old tin can's can. Get at 'er!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_refiner,room_type_hyperoom]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Warrior versus giant robot? Pretty metal. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" Prog metal, at <i>least.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't let your guard down, Hunter.\n"
" !scared\n"
" Even though he's gone, <#BLUE>Grandpa's</>... \"creations\" still roam the lab."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" My <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> gone, but this place is still dangerous."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Steel yourself, Hunter. <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</> is nothing new. \n"
" !scared\n"
" Still, those robo-<#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> give me the shivers."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You're brave, Hunter. <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</> isn't for the faint of heart."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A-ah-AH--All that loose <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> in there <i>really</> triggers my ah-ah-aaAAAH! \n"
" !point\n"
" Allergies.  \n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> makes me carry his inhaler."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Out of the fire, into the Cauldron, eh, Hunter?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Huh. I sounded like <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> just then."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" My <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> influence is all over this room."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> mess won't clean itself up, I suppose."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just like this volcano, my Grandpa's mistakes just keep burbling up.\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you think I should write poetry?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Whatever's waiting ahead, it's not my <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. \n"
" !angry\n"
" Though he did unleash it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_zucco_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_zucco_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're getting really good at this, Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" That <#RED>{name.zucco_miniboss}</> never stood a chance!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви стаєте справжнім майстром у цьому, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Той <#RED>{Name.zucco_miniboss}</> навіть не мав шансу!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Oh, <#BLUE>Grandpa</>... What have you done...?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" If we can just get him out of that <#RED>Mech</>...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ... maybe we can reason with him. <z 0.7>Maybe.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" It hurts, seeing him <#BLUE>Grandpa</> taken over by <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</>...\n"
" !think\n"
" Though it's as if the stuff is literally speaking <i>for</> him..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" We can't give up, Hunter. I know you can beat him."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[has_seen_tefframech,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" We won't let <#BLUE>Grandpa</> spread this to others. We <i>can't.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ha</i>-CHOO!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Whew. My allergies are acting up all of the sudden."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ап</i>-ЧХИИ!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Фух. Моя алергія раптово посилюється."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh hey, don't forget about that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart_shard}</> in your bag.\n"
" !point\n"
" Go pop it in the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> when you get a chance, okay?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ha</i>-CHOOoo!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Whewie. Do you have a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart_shard}</> on you or something?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4"
msgid "!greet\n"
" Heya Hunter, how's it--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" <i>ha</i>-CHOOoo!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ah. Have a <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart_shard}</> on you, do ya?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[holding_any_heart,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hey. You planning to put that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart_shard}</> in the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</> or--\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We could use the power, y'know."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_bonejaw_miniboss,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_bonejaw_miniboss,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <#RED>{name.bonejaw_miniboss}</> needs a dentist after meeting you! \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Also because I think it had a <i>bit</> of an underbite."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_blarmadillo_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_blarmadillo_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" You know, as a fellow allergy sufferer I had a bit of sympathy for <#RED>{name_multiple.blarmadillo}</>...\n"
" !point\n"
" ...until now, that is."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Як той, хто страждає на алергію, я трохи співчував <#RED>{Name_multiple.blarmadillo}</>...\n"
" !point\n"
" ...до цього моменту, звісно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_bonejaw,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_bonejaw,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" How are you feeling, Hunter?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" That <#RED>{name.bonejaw}</> really did a number on you."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Як Ваше самопочуття, Мисливцю?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Той <#RED>{Name.bonejaw}</> дійсно вас пошкодив."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_cabbageroll_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_cabbageroll_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't worry about it, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" That <#RED>{name.cabbageroll_miniboss}'s</> days are numbered!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не хвилюйтеся, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Дні <#RED>{2:{Name.cabbageroll_miniboss}}</> пораховані!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Things got a little rocky on that last fight, huh?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" S-sorry! I didn't mean to make a joke!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Та остання бійка була трохи складною, правда?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" В-вибачте! Я не хотів жартувати!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" I'm <i>still</> thawing out from our run-in with that <#RED>{name.crystroll}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" At least you had the option of hacking the ice off those <#RED>Braziers</> down there!\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Sorry, Hunter, I know you had your hands full, but... it's not a bad idea..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_crystroll,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brrr...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I don't know if I've got the shivers from the cold, or from how that last fight turned out."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Бррр...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я не знаю, чи мене трусить від холоду, чи від того, як закінчився останній бій."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_eggzy,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_eggzy,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" So... I guess that nest wasn't <i>completely</> abandoned.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Though in my defense, that <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> was technically just a hatchling.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" But look on the bright side! We were able to gather valuable data that will serve us well on the next Hunt!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_embison,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_embison,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Are you sure you're okay, Hunter?\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <i>I</> sure wouldn't be after taking a right-hook from a <#RED>{name.embison}</>..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви впевнені, що все гаразд, Мисливцю?\n"
" !nervous\n"
" <i>Я</> б точно не був після правого хука від <#RED>{2:{Name.embison}}</>..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>Ugh.</i>\n"
" !point\n"
" I hate that bird."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dejected\n"
"<i>Ух.</i>\n"
"!point\n"
"Я ненавиджу цю пташку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I didn't realize that <#RED>{name.floracrane}</> could hit so hard.\n"
" !point\n"
" This is why I hate birds."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dejected\n"
"Я не думав, що <#RED>{Name.floracrane}</> може так сильно вдарити.\n"
"!point\n"
"Ось чому я ненавиджу птахів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I was bit really hard by a seagull once.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I know exactly what you're going through."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Мене якось дуже сильно вкусила чайка.\n"
"!agree\n"
"Я точно знаю, що ви переживаєте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Got knocked out by a <#RED>{name.floracrane}</>, huh? Was it a pink one or a green one?\n"
" !think\n"
" Those colours look great together, don't you think?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!clap\n"
"Вас збив з ніг <#RED>{Name.floracrane}</>? Він був рожевий чи зелений?\n"
"!think\n"
"Ці кольори мають чудовий вигляд разом, ви так не думаєте?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_floracrane,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Isn't a <#RED>{name.floracrane}</> just a big bird?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh! I know! You should try throwing french fries in the opposite direction."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Хіба <#RED>{Name.floracrane}</> не просто велика пташка?\n"
"!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"О! Я знаю! Спробуйте кинути картоплю фрі в протилежному напрямку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gnarlic_miniboss,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gnarlic_miniboss,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I can still smell that old <#RED>Gnarlic's</> stench...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Um, Hunter? Maybe you could wash off a bit before we get back in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>...?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Я досі відчуваю сморід від старого <#RED>Часнирога</>...\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Е-е, Мисливцю? Може, ви б трохи освіжилися, перш ніж ми повернемося в <#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}</>...?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gourdo,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gourdo,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I've had just about enough of those two <#RED>{name_multiple.gourdo}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Since when did <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> learn to team up?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gourdo,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_gourdo,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Fighting two <#RED>{name_multiple.gourdo}</> at once...\n"
" !point\n"
" Watch how you use your <#RED>Potions</>. They've got twice the coverage with their clubs!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I don't know about you, but I'm getting really tired of getting attacked by angry trees.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Just saying..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Не знаю як ви, але мені набридло постійно отримувати атаки від сердитих дерев.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Просто кажу..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,role_refiner,struggling_on_grimhollow].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,role_refiner,struggling_on_grimhollow].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" C'mon, Hunter. Are you gonna let a <#RED>computer tree</> best you?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Because it bested me, and it irritates me to this day."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,role_refiner,struggling_on_grimhollow].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_grimhollow,role_refiner,struggling_on_grimhollow].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" See? <#RED>{name.grimhollow}'s</> sneaky for a heap of lumber and circuitry."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_groak,last_run_was_bandi_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_groak,last_run_was_bandi_swamp_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" If a <#RED>{name.groak}</> ever swallowed me I think I'd shave off all my fur.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Yuck!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Якщо <#RED>{Name.groak}</> коли-небудь проковтне мене, я думаю, що збрию всю свою шерсть.\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Фу!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_groak,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_groak,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You look like you've seen the inside of a <#RED>{name.groak}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Wait, is that what got you?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Ви виглядаєте так, ніби бачили нутрощі <#RED>{2:{Name.groak}}</>.\n"
"!think\n"
"Зачекайте, це він вас дістав?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_sedament,last_run_was_sedament_tundra,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_sedament,last_run_was_sedament_tundra,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" The <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> is a bunch of rocks?! I'm no <#BLUE>{name.job_konjurist}</>, but I thought <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> only affected living things...\n"
" !point\n"
" Let's get back out there, Hunter! This calls for further investigation."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" <#RED>{Name.rot_boss}</> — це купа каменів?! Я не <#BLUE>{name.job_konjurist}</>, але я думав, що <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> впливає тільки на живих істот...\n"
" !point\n"
" Повернімося туди, Мисливцю! Потрібне подальше розслідування."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_swarmy_miniboss,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_swarmy_miniboss,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r1,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" That <#RED>{name.swarmy}</> gunk is impossible to wash out...\n"
" !think\n"
" I might need to replace the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> seat cushions after this is all over."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Та гидота з <#RED>{2:{Name.swarmy}}</> взагалі не відмивається...\n"
" !think\n"
" Можливо, після всього доведеться міняти сидіння у <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !disagree\n"
" It's not my <#BLUE>Grandpa</> attacking you, Hunter. It's the <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</>.  \n"
" !gesture\n"
" What I'm saying is... <i>(sigh)</> Don't pull your punches next time, okay?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dejected\n"
" The <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</> is so <i>strong!</>\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" But I know we can beat it, Hunter. We have to."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" We have to fight <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> with <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>!\n"
" !think\n"
" We might need more <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</> to beat <#BLUE>Grandpa</>..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Do you think there's some piece of <#BLUE>Grandpa</> left in there? \n"
" !nervous\n"
" I... I have to believe there is..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout].5"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !point\n"
" We're down, but the <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</> is scared of us, Hunter. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Let's go remind it why!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].1"
msgid "!happy [keep-for-room]\n"
" !think\n"
" An emergency rescue <i>inside</> a volcano was pretty impressive! Not that I'm bragging. \n"
" !shocked\n"
" I'm not!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !nervous\n"
" That was a close one, Hunter. \n"
" !shocked\n"
" Those machine-<#RED>{name.rot}</> things are on another level!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !scared\n"
" Threading the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> between pipes and <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-falls with a near-lifeless Hunter dangling from its claw is <i>stressful!</>\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Oh! B-but not as stressful as fighting those hoards of lab-grown <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, of course."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_tefframech,last_run_was_tefframech_volcano,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_tefframech].4"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Maybe more <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.i_konjur_heart}</> could keep you in the fight longer?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I only suggest it because the fate of the world is at stake, of course."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_thatcher,lost_last_run,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_thatcher,lost_last_run,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" So <#RED>{name.thatcher}</> shreds, huh? And not just your ego."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r3,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>(sigh)</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I used to really like yams..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <i>(зітхає)</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Раніше я дуже любив батати..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_zucco_miniboss,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_zucco_miniboss,last_run_was_owlitzer_forest_r2,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You'll get that <#RED>{name.zucco_miniboss}</> next time, Hunter!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We all believe in you!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Наступного разу ви спіймаєте <#RED>{Name.zucco_miniboss}а</>, Мисливцю!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ми всі віримо у вас!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_crystroll_miniboss,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_crystroll_miniboss,last_run_was_sedament_tundra_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You put <#RED>{name.crystroll_miniboss}</> on ICE! Because of the cold!\n"
" !think\n"
" Or you brought the HEAT? Because of the <#RED>Braziers</>. You did great, is what I mean."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_embison_miniboss,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_embison_miniboss,last_run_was_eggzy_tundra_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" You gave <#RED>{name.embison_miniboss}</> a bit o' that sweet chin music!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" A crash course in that sweet science!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" The ol'... one-two... buckle-my-shoe?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me to say those things. I have no idea what they mean."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_groak_miniboss,last_run_was_bandi_swamp_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_groak_miniboss,last_run_was_bandi_swamp_r2,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" You really <i>suck</> now, <#RED>{name.groak_miniboss}</>! \n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's not here but I just wanted the chance to say my little pun."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_swarmy_miniboss,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_swarmy_miniboss,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp_r1,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Nice work cleaning up <#RED>{name.swarmy_miniboss}</>, Hunter! \n"
" !dubious\n"
" You <i>could</> clean the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> seats that you sat on after...\n"
" !agree\n"
" Buuuuut I'll just flip them over. All good."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_yammo_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r3,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_yammo_miniboss,last_run_was_treemon_forest_r3,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Bet you that yam wishes it was a sweet potato today!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Wait... are yams also sweet potatoes? No, right? This feels insensitive."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thumped Grimhollow again just for funsies?\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'm here for it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You fed that <#RED>cyborg tree</> to the <i>wood-micro-chipper!</>\n"
" ...\n"
" !angry\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> assured me that would go over better."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_refiner,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks again for the assist with {name.grimhollow}.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Even though I didn't need it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <#RED>{name.thatcher}</> should've known better than to get in the pit with you.\n"
" !clap\n"
" You floor-punching, two-stepping, wall-of-death beast!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_thatcher_swamp,role_refiner,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" So {name.c_konjur} mutated a <#RED>{name.rot}</> to rock?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" That rules."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Don't feel bad, Hunter. You did your best."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Не засмучуйтесь, Мисливцю. Ви зробили все можливе."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Granny used to say that making mistakes is just as important as winning.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Learning from mistakes makes us stronger."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Моя бабуся завжди казала, що помилки так само важливі, як і перемоги.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Вчитися на помилках – це шлях до сили."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Welcome home!\n"
" !point\n"
" I hear you gave almost as good as you got."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Ласкаво просимо додому!\n"
" !point\n"
" Я чув, що ви віддали майже стільки ж, скільки отримали."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].10"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" I know what it's like to get my butt kicked.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I had a family once."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Я знаю, як це - отримати під зад.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Колись у мене була сім'я."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].11"
msgid "!wavelunn\n"
" Folks think I won <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> in a leg-wrestling match against three {name_multiple.cabbageroll}.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Truth is, I stole him off the jerk who laughed at me for losing."
msgstr "!wavelunn\n"
" Усі думають, що я виграла <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}а</> у матчі з боротьби на ногах проти трьох {2:{Name_multiple.cabbageroll}}.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Насправді я вкрала його у придурка, який сміявся з моєї поразки."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].12"
msgid "!point\n"
" It's not a loss as long as you learn something.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Even if all you learn is that you need better <#RED>Armour</>."
msgstr "!point\n"
" Це не втрата, якщо ви щось вчитеся.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Навіть якщо все, що ви вивчите, це те, що вам потрібні кращі <#RED>обладунки</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].13"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" WOAH!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, sorry. I thought you were a ghost."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!shocked\n"
"ВООУ!\n"
"!happy\n"
"!think\n"
"О, вибачте. Я подумав, що ви привид."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I really admire your grit.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...and your ears."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я справді захоплююся вашою твердістю.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" ...і вашими вухами."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" When I've had a rough run, I like to go scream into a tree.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" The trees don't mind. I asked."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Коли в мене важкий день, я люблю піти покричати в дерево.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Дерева не проти. Я питав."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Heya, welcome back.\n"
" !point\n"
" Glad you made it out with all your limbs!"
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Гей, ласкаво просимо назад.\n"
" !point\n"
" Я радий, що ви вибралися з усіма кінцівками!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].5"
msgid "!wave\n"
" Hey Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" Those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> are in for a <i>big</i> surprise next time."
msgstr "!wave\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Наступного разу цих <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</> чекає <i>великий</i> сюрприз."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].6"
msgid "!greet\n"
" Hey Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" You really gave those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> a run for their... rottenness."
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Ці <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> отримали від вас доброго прочухана за свою... гнилість."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].7"
msgid "!greet\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> says he's got a good feeling about your next run!\n"
" !point\n"
" !agree\n"
" You're scrappy, like us."
msgstr "!greet\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> каже, що має хороші передчуття щодо вашого наступного забігу!\n"
" !point\n"
" !agree\n"
" Ви боєць, як і ми."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].8"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" It's not just about winning.\n"
" !point\n"
" It's about putting up a fight."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Справа не лише в перемозі.\n"
" !point\n"
" Йдеться про боротьбу."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_armorsmith].9"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Yowza... those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> are tough!\n"
" !point\n"
" And so are you."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Йо, ці <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> міцні!\n"
" !point\n"
" І ви також."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Y'alright?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ye look like somethin' <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> dragged in."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Усе гаразд?\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ви виглядаєте, наче вас <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> приніс."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Listen, Hunter. Yer not the first to get knocked down a peg. \n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Dust yerself off, an' go show 'em what fer."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Mark my words, Hunter.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Those boggin' <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}'ll</> get theirs."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Запам'яте мої слова,Мисливцю.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ті бридкі <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, отримають своє."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {name.job_dojo}'s been askin' after ye.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {Name.job_dojo} питав про вас.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I've got th' forge fired up if ye need.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Don't let a weary weapon take ye down."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_blacksmith].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Failin' means yer playin'."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Якщо ви програєте, значить, ви граєте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hoo-whee, looks like somethin' gave you a real shiner.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I heard slappin' a slab of steak on it helps. Except we don't got any steak... maybe a bag of frozen beans, then?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ох, здається, вам добре дісталося.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Чув, що прикладений шматок м'яса допомагає. Але в нас немає м'яса... може, пакет заморожених бобів?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_cook].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't you worry your little head over it, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" You'll get that varmint next time!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не хвилюйтеся, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Наступного разу ви точно впораєтесь!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>Healing's</> scarce on Hunts.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Best not to get hit if you can help it."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>Зцілення</> на полюваннях рідкість.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Краще уникати ударів, якщо можете."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Listen up, Hunter.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Failed Hunts are just learning experiences."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Слухайте, Мисливцю.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Невдалі полювання — це також навчання."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Welcome back.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm prouda you for getting out there."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ласкаво просимо назад.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я пишаюся вами за те, що ви вибралися звідти."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Get yer butt whupped?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ain't no shame in a loss. It's part of the process."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Отримали під зад?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Програти не соромно. Це частина процесу."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Chin up, kid.\n"
" !point\n"
" You aren't gonna let those rotten monsters win, are ya?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Підійміть голову, друже.\n"
"!point\n"
"Ви ж не дозволите цим гнилим монстрам перемогти, чи не так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Why the long face?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You went down swingin'."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Чому таке похмуре обличчя?\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Ви билися до кінця."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_dojo].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hey kid.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Took some down with ya, I hope?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ей, друже.\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Сподіваюсь, ви взяли кількох із собою?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner,struggling_on_thatcher].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner,struggling_on_thatcher].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Dang. <#RED>{name.thatcher}</> rocked your little socks off, huh?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hey, at least you survived to overthink all your mistakes. He he he."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't get down, Hunter. That last run was just the warm-up.\n"
" !point\n"
" Now for the headliner."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Is it time to gives those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> a lesson in retribution?\n"
" !point\n"
" Yes. Yes it is."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't sweat that last Hunt. Failure's necessary for progress, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" Still, it sucks a big one. Tough break."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't worry, Hunter. No one's keeping track of your failures.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Oh this? I'm just keeping track of... other stuff."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Hey, everyone gets their butts destroyed by nasty vegetables now and then.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Though usually it's due to food poisoning. He he he. Sorry."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_refiner].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Don't give up. My dad's out there, alone."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].1"
msgid "!shrug\n"
" You win some, you lose some, right Hunter?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No one said it'd be easy."
msgstr "!shrug\n"
" Ви виграєте, десь програєте, чи не так, Мисливцю?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ніхто не казав, що це буде легко."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].2"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Glad to see you up.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ready to get back to it?"
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Радий вас бачити.\n"
" !point\n"
" Готові повернутися?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,lost_last_run,role_scout].3"
msgid "!greet\n"
" Hey, Hunter.\n"
" !agree\n"
" No lasting damage from that last Hunt, I hope."
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Сподіваюся, що останнє полювання не залишило серйозних ушкоджень."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Doin' us all proud."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ми всі пишаємось."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !point\n"
" 'Tis an honour to fight alongside yer pals."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...\n"
" !point\n"
" Для мене честь битися разом зі своїми друзями."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Remember that you and other Hunters are working together."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Пам'ятайте, що ви та інші Мисливці працюєте разом."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" By the way, if yer fighting with allies and get knocked out try hitting the <#RED>Attack</> and <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> buttons.\n"
" !cough\n"
" Ghe-he-he."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
"До речі, якщо ви боретеся з союзниками й вас збили, спробуйте натиснути кнопку <#RED>Атаки</> і <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>.\n"
"!cough\n"
"Хе-хе-хе."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo]NOT[using_gamepad].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo]NOT[using_gamepad].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" If you learn something useful out there, share the tip with your fellow Hunters."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Якщо ви дізнаєтеся про щось корисне, поділіться порадою з іншими мисливцями."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo]NOT[using_gamepad].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,multiplayer,role_dojo]NOT[using_gamepad].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" By the way, you can communicate with other Hunters by pressing <p bind='Controls.Digital.TOGGLE_SAY' color=BTNICON_DARK> to chat."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" До речі, ви можете спілкуватися з іншими Мисливцями, натиснувши <p bind='Controls.Digital.TOGGLE_SAY' color=BTNICON_DARK>, щоб розпочати чат."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" No more beatin' around the bush, Hunter. \n"
" !point\n"
" You got new <#RED>Recipes</>, a <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</>, and a functionin' stomach. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" And I got a grill, a buncha cookin' tools and whatsits, and time on my hands. \n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Whaddaya say we get this party started, ay, hun?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" I've been practicin' the meals what're on that there new {name.cook_rotating_recipe} menu.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Reckon I've got 'em down pat, so I offer you my Solid Gold 'No Tummyache' Guarantee!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ahem. <z 0.7>Guarantee does not cover inverted eye waterin', downstairs winds, the deep knee bends, or spontaneous hair braidin'.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Well? Grill ain't gettin' any hotter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" You're gonna ignore all these new <#RED>Recipes</> I done dug up for ya? \n"
" !dejected\n"
" After I made sure they'd give ya helpful powers 'n' the like?\n"
" !point\n"
" Shooooot. Don't come bellyachin' to me 'bout yer belly achin' on account of you not askin' me to pack you a meal, now, y'hear?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Look at all thems new <#RED>Recipes</> goin' uncooked!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Guess <i>someone</> doesn't like <i>someone else's</> cookin'! \n"
" !angry\n"
" Guess that <i>someone else</> could get offended 'n' such, should they not be asked to pack one of 'em up in the <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</> sooner 'n' later...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Psst! <z 0.7>I'm talkin' about me. I'll get offended. I <i>will,</> dadgummit!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_cook_rotatingmenu_unlocked,role_cook]NOT[pf_made_rotatingmenu_food].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You've been readin' that there new <#RED>{name.cook_rotating_recipe}</> menu like there's gonna be a test, hun!\n"
" !angry\n"
" Well there is: TESTIN' MY GALL-DURN PATIENCE!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm just kiddin'.\n"
" !angry\n"
" OR AM I?\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Go on and <i>pick</> somethin', already! I promise, it's all made with love.\n"
" !angry\n"
" OR SPITE!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_corestone_weapon_crafting_unlocked,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Working with the <#BLUE>{name.job_blacksmith}</>, he's so aloof, antisocial, and assiduous to a fault.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" A+. 10 out of 10. Would recommend."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_gave_cookingtools,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_gave_cookingtools,role_cook].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Now, we don't want ya goin' hungry on a {name.run}, Hunter. \n"
" !point\n"
" Look fer the <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</> next to the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> when next you're in the wilds. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" This scrum-diddly-umptious somethin'-or-rather'll be waitin' for ya.\n"
" !angry\n"
" And <i>no,</> it won't go <i>bad,</> <z 0.7>I don't reckon.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_gave_cookingtools,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,pf_gave_cookingtools,role_cook].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Don't tell ol' <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</> you don't like her cookin', now!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Your <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</> has some home-cooked, power-packed meals waitin'... \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Find it by the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> next time you land in the wilds. Them powers'll do you good."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_gems_intro_blacksmith,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_gems_intro_blacksmith,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!bliss\n"
" Oooohoho, I can smell a secret from a mile away! What were you and <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> whispering about?\n"
" !think\n"
" Does it have something to do with that <#RED>{name.gem}</> you showed him?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" C'mon, spill! You can tell me! <i>Pleeeeaaaase?</>"
msgstr "!bliss\n"
" Оооохохо, я відчуваю секрети за милю! Про що ви з <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> шепотілися?\n"
" !think\n"
" Це пов'язано з тим <#RED>{name.gem}ом</>, який ви йому показали?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ну ж бо, зізнавайтесь! Ви можете мені сказати! <i>Будьлаааааааска?</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_gems_intro_blacksmith,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_gems_intro_blacksmith,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Have you ever noticed how big and shiny <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}'s</> eyes get whenever he sees a <#RED>Gem</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I asked him about it and he just grunted at me... but I swear it was a <i>nervous</> grunt.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Uuuugh why does he have to be so secretive!!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви колись помічали, які великі й блискучі очі у <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>, коли він бачить <#RED>самоцвіт</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я запитала його про це, а він лише рикнув на мене... але я клянуся, це був <i>нервовий</> рик.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ууууух, чому він такий таємничий!!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_specialeventhost].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_twn_second_key_refiner,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_specialeventhost].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Did you see my dad on your last Hunt? How was he?\n"
" player:\n"
" He looked good, {name.npc_refiner}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervousddd\n"
" Did he... did he ask about me? Say my name at all... ?\n"
" player:\n"
" ... Sorry, he wasn't--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook_start\n"
" No it's fine. Thanks anyway. See ya."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,weapon_type_polearm].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,weapon_type_polearm].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That's a weird-looking scythe.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You can't harvest crops with that."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Це дивна серпоподібна коса.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" З цим не зібрати врожай."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I don't like the smell of those potions you've been getting from the potion-seller.\n"
" !think\n"
" I can't pick up a single natural ingredient."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Мені не подобається запах того зілля, що ви купуєте у продавця.\n"
" !think\n"
" Я не відчуваю жодного природного інгредієнта."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Eww...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You're covered in <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> stink. Hope that means you beat it."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff} Фу...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ви покриті смородом <#RED>{2:{name.rot_boss}}</>. Сподіваюся, це означає, що ви його здолали."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> said you beat the <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" They seemed really proud."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> сказав, що ви перемогли <#RED>{2:{name.rot_boss}}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Він виглядав дуже гордим."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !point\n"
" You smell weird."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" {name.apothecary_sniff}\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви дивно пахнете."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(yawn)</> Do you know any good napping spots?\n"
" !think\n"
" The <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</> gets mad when I sleep next to his forge. But it's so warm and cozy..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <i>(позіхання)</> Ви знаєте хороші місця для сну?\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{Name.job_blacksmith}</> злиться, коли я сплю біля його кузні. Але там так тепло і затишно..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" There's so many people here...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Are they here <i>all</> the time?!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Тут так багато істот...\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Вони тут <i>завжди</>?!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Shh. I'm practicing being invisible."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Тсс. Я тренуюся бути невидимою."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Was <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> really a Hunter too?\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if he knew... never mind."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Невже <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> теж був Мисливцем?\n"
" !think\n"
" Цікаво, чи він знав... неважливо."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" Um. How have you lasted this long without a <#RED>{name.job_blacksmith}</>?"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
" Ем. Як ви протрималися так довго без <#RED>{2:{name.job_blacksmith}}</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,weapon_type_polearm].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,weapon_type_polearm].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I knew it was a <#RED>{name.rot}</> kebab kind of day!\n"
" !point\n"
" Just watch where you point that thing."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Я знав, що сьогодні день шашлику з <#RED>{2:{name.rot}}</>!\n"
" !point\n"
" Просто дивіться, куди ви направляєте цю штуку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I got a free mouthwash sample from a slippery salesman out there once...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...turned out to be a <i>very</i> powerful burping potion."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Одного разу я отримав безплатний зразок рідини для полоскання рота від слизького продавця...\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ..виявилося, що це було <i>дуже</i> потужне зілля для відрижки."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_seen_npc_potionmaker_dungeon].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You're not talking to <i>strange</i> strangers out there, are you?\n"
" !clap\n"
" You could be home talking to strange friends instead!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви ж не розмовляєте з <i>дивними</i> незнайомцями, чи не так?\n"
" !clap\n"
" Натомість ви можете залишитись вдома та розмовляти з дивними друзями!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>'s sonnets are so lyrical.\n"
" !point\n"
" You didn't hear it from me."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Сонети <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> такі ліричні.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви не чули цього від мене."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" You know some folks call <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> \"HAM-ish\" instead of \"HAY-mish\"?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" He's really not much of a ham."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви знаєте, що дехто називає <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> \"ГАЙ-міш\" замість \"ГАМ-іш\"?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Насправді він не дуже схожий на гай."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" They say that <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> gave <i>himself</i> that tattoo.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Okay, nobody says that. But it could be true!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Кажуть, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> зробив <i>собі</i> це татуювання.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Гаразд, ніхто це каже. Але це може бути правдою!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}'s</> hammer just called <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> <i>dull</i>.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" What a tool."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Молоток <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> щойно сказав що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> <i>тупий</i>.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Що за інструмент."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> is <i>so weird</i> about accepting help.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I spent all morning suggesting names for his hammer, and he told me to go <i>boil my head!</i>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> <i>так дивно</i> приймає допомогу.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Я провела весь ранок, пропонуючи назви для його молотка, а він сказав, щоб я йшла <i>кип'ятити голову!</i>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Does <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> seem okay to you?\n"
" !think\n"
" He seems gruntier than usual."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Вам здається, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> в порядку?\n"
" !think\n"
" Він здається більш буркотливим, ніж зазвичай."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I tried to help <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> come up with some names for his tools, and do you know what he said?\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>'Och, me tools need names like I need a hole in the head!'</> Can you believe that?!\n"
" !think\n"
" Why would <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> think he needs a hole in his head?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я намагалась допомогти <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> з назвами для його інструментів, а він що сказав?\n"
" !angry\n"
" <i>'Ох, моїм інструментам потрібні імена як мені потрібна діра в голові!'</> Ви уявляєте?!\n"
" !think\n"
" Чому <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> думає, що йому потрібна діра в голові?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</> says superheating food releases the nutrients.\n"
" !point\n"
" That's why she makes sure to burn everything."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</> каже, що перегрівання їжі вивільняє поживні речовини.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ось чому вона все обов'язково спалює."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Some <#RED>{name.rot}</>-tainted jerk called <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> food \"slop\"!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" !angry\n"
" They're not <i>wrong</i>. But still."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Якийсь дурень, одурманений<#RED>{3:{name.rot}}</>, назвав їжу <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</> \"помиями\"!\n"
" !dubious\n"
" !angry\n"
" Вони не <i>помиляються</i>. Але все ж."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Smell that?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It's mystery mash casserole night!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Відчуваєте запах?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Сьогодні вечеря з таємничою кашею касероль!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know what's worse than food poisoning?\n"
" !point\n"
" !agree\n"
" Eating raw <#RED>{name.gnarlic}</> out of a shoe. Trust me."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви знаєте, що гірше харчового отруєння?\n"
" !point\n"
" !agree\n"
" Їсти сирий <#RED>{Name.gnarlic}</> із черевика. Повірте мені."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" A few more weeks with <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</>, and you'll have a cast-iron gut!\n"
" !point\n"
" That's like <#RED>Armour</> for your insides."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ще кілька тижнів з <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</>, і у вас буде чавунний кишківник!\n"
" !point\n"
" Це як <#RED>обладунок</> для ваших нутрощів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,wf_town_has_cook].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I added a flame-retardant lining to <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> apron.\n"
" !clap\n"
" She said she's already getting lots of use out of it!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я додав вогнестійку підкладку до фартуха <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</>.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Вона сказала, що вже активно її використовує!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!greet\n"
" I've been hearing a <i>lot</i> of chatter about you...\n"
" !point\n"
" ...folks are saying you're a natural!"
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Я чув <i>багато</i> балачок про вас...\n"
" !point\n"
" ...інші кажуть, що у вас талант!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Even if you <i>do</i> wipe out all the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" ...you'll need <#RED>Armour</> to stay safe from all your fans."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Навіть якщо ви <i>зітрете</i> всіх <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" ...вам знадобляться <#RED>обладунки</>, щоб захиститися від усіх своїх шанувальників."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!clap\n"
" Way to slay, Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" Get it? 'Cause you slayed all those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr "!clap\n"
" Молодець, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Зрозуміло? Бо ви знищили всіх цих <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].4"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" If you ever run outta <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> to hunt...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" ...<#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> could teach you to be an {name.job_armorsmith}!"
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Якщо у вас колись закінчиться <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> для полювання...\n"
" !laugh\n"
" ...<#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> може навчити вас бути {4:{name.job_armorsmith}}!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].5"
msgid "!greet\n"
" That last run was <i>killer!</i>\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Hooyah!"
msgstr "!greet\n"
" Останній забіг був <i>убивчим!</i>\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Юху!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].6"
msgid "!point\n"
" All your training is really paying off.\n"
" !think\n"
" D'you think I could train myself to be taller?"
msgstr "!point\n"
" Усі ваші тренування дійсно окупаються.\n"
" !think\n"
" Як ви думаєте, я міг би потренуватися, щоб стати вищим?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].7"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" !disagree\n"
" You're not a Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" !clap\n"
" You're a DECIMATOR! Hooyah!"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
"!disagree\n"
"Ви не Мисливець.\n"
"!point\n"
"!clap\n"
"Ви — ЗНИЩУВАЧ! Хііяя!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,won_last_run].8"
msgid "!notebook\n"
" <i>Dear Diary, many <#RED>{name.rot}</> butts were kicked today.</i>\n"
" !think\n"
" Do you think <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> minds that I borrowed his diary?"
msgstr "!notebook\n"
" <i>Дорогий щоденнику, сьогодні було надерто багато задів <#RED>{2:{name.rot}}</>.</i>\n"
" !think\n"
" Як ви думаєте, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> не проти, що я позичив його щоденник?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Find you're dying a bunch out there?\n"
" !point\n"
" The right kind of <#RED>Armour</> could change that..."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Здається, ви там часто вмираєте?\n"
" !point\n"
" Правильні <#RED>обладунки</> можуть це змінити..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].10"
msgid "!notebook\n"
" Says here you've been voted \"Most Likely To Sleep Through A Natural Disaster.\"\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Honestly, same."
msgstr "!notebook\n"
" Тут написано, що тебе обрали \"Тим, хто найімовірніше проспить природний катаклізм\".\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Якщо чесно, то я теж."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].11"
msgid "!wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> once carved my initials into a <#RED>{name.gourdo}'s</> leg.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" He got almost halfway through the \"B\" before it woke up."
msgstr "!wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> одного разу вирізав мої ініціали на нозі <#RED>{Name.gourdo}</>.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Він майже завершив \"Б\", перш ніж він прокинулася."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].12"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" D'you think <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> would let me borrow the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Як ви думаєте, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> дозволив би мені позичити <#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].13"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You'll never guess who came by my workshop today!\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Oh wait, I promised not to say."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ви ніколи не вгадаєте, хто завітав до моєї майстерні сьогодні!\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ой, зачекайте, я обіцяв не казати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].14"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Hahaha! Ohmygosh Lunn you are such a <i>riot!</> How do you come up with this stuff?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh, sorry Hunter, it's an inside joke."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Хаха! О боже Лунн, ти такий <i>бунтівник!</> Як ти вигадуєш таке?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ой, вибачте Мисливцю, це внутрішній жарт."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].15
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].15"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> once killed a <#RED>{name.rot}</> by slapping it in the face with a sandwich.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" And then ate the sandwich!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> одного разу вбив <#RED>{2:{name.rot}}</>, вдаривши його по обличчю бутербродом.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" А потім з'їв бутерброд!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].16
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].16"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> mutters in his sleep.\n"
" !think\n"
" It'd be nice if he spoke up a little."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> бурмоче уві сні.\n"
" !think\n"
" Було б добре, якби він трохи розмовляв."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].17
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].17"
msgid "!shocked\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> you were a gut biter!\n"
" !think\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Or maybe it was \"good fighter.\" Lip-reading is hard."
msgstr "!shocked\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> сказав <#BLUE>{3:{Name.npc_scout}}</>, що ви кусаєтеся!\n"
" !think\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Або, можливо, він сказав \"хороший боєць.\" Читати по губах важко."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].18
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].18"
msgid "!greet\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> has never stayed in one place this long.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" He must <i>really</i> like my work."
msgstr "!greet\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> ніколи не залишався на одному місці так довго.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Мабуть, йому <i>справді</i> подобається моя робота."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].19
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].19"
msgid "!wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I would be great {name.job_dojo}s!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" We just don't wanna step on <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</>'s toes. He's already missing a few."
msgstr "!wavelunn\n"
" Я і <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> були б чудовими {3:{name.job_dojo}}!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ми просто не хочемо наступати на пальці <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}а</>. Він вже втратив кілька."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Skin too soft?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Protect it with <#RED>Armour</>!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Шкіра занадто м'яка?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Захистіть її <#RED>обладунками</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Been feeling unlucky on the Hunt?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" With the right <#RED>Armour</>, you don't <i>need</i> luck!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Почуваєтеся невдалим на полюванні?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" З правильними <#RED>обладунками</> вам не <i>потрібна</i> удача!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" People's voices really carry in this camp. \n"
" !bliss\n"
" I love it!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Голоси істот справді добре чутно в цьому таборі.\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Мені це подобається!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> would take <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> as an apprentice.\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}'s</> very studious."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Цікаво, чи <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> узяв би <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_lunn}}</> учнем.\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> дуже старанний."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Information is the best <#RED>Armour</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" That's why I'm <i>always</i> listening!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!point\n"
"Інформація — найкращий <#RED>захист</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
"Ось чому я <i>завжди</i> слухаю!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].7"
msgid "!greet\n"
" !point\n"
" You're looking sharp!\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Almost as sharp as <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</>."
msgstr "!greet\n"
"!point\n"
"Ви чудово виглядаєте!\n"
"!wavelunn\n"
"Майже так само чудово, як <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].8"
msgid "!shocked\n"
" D'you ever think about singing your feelings?\n"
" !point\n"
" I think you'd be good at it."
msgstr "!shocked\n"
" Чи думали ви коли-небудь про те, щоб оспівувати свої почуття?\n"
" !point\n"
" Я думаю, у вас це добре вийде."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith].9"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" Folks say I talk too much.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But then when I listen, they call it eavesdropping."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Люди кажуть, що я занадто багато говорю.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Але коли я слухаю, вони називають це підслуховуванням."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!nervous\n"
" Do you think <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> has made new friends elsewhere?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Not that I'd care.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" But <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> misses him."
msgstr "!nervous\n"
" Як ви думаєте, <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}</> знайшов нових друзів?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Не те щоб мене це хвилювало.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Але <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> сумує за ним."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!nervous\n"
" You're still looking for <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, right?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" He's not as tough as he thinks."
msgstr "!nervous\n"
" Ви все ще шукаєте <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>, правда?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Він не такий сильний, як думає."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[wf_town_has_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!nervous\n"
" It's not that I miss <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>, it's just...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...no one's grunted angrily at me in ages."
msgstr "!nervous\n"
" Не те щоб я сумував за <#BLUE>{Name.npc_blacksmith}ом</>, просто...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...ніхто на мене сердито не бурчав вже дуже давно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,struggling_on_miniboss].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,struggling_on_miniboss].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hm... Listen, Hunter.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yer mind is yer best weapon."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Хм... Слухайте, Мисливцю.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ваш розум — ваша найкраща зброя."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_fortification_level_0].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_fortification_level_0].1"
msgid "!gruffnod\n"
" Me an' my forge will get the job done.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" All ye've gotta do is go out into the wilds an' get the goods I need.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ye ken?"
msgstr "!gruffnod\n"
" Моя кузня і я впораємося з роботою.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Все, що треба — це піти в дику місцевість і принести мені потрібні матеріали.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Зрозуміли?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_type_hammer,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_type_hammer,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Th' <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</>'s a good, honest weapon.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"<#RED>{Name.weapon_hammer}</> — це гарна, чесна зброя.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}'s</> not one for bletherin'.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Makes fer a nice change."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_apothecary}</> не любить балакати.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Це приємна зміна."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_apothecary].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {name.town}'s gettin' crowded.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <i>(hmph)</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {Name.town} стає переповненим.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <i>(хмпф)</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Och, th' scullery reeks o' burnt porridge again.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(hmph)</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ой, з їдальні знову тхне пригорілою кашею.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(гмпф)</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" The <#BLUE>{name.job_cook}'s</> been after me biscuit recipe.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Good luck. I'm a steel trap."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.job_cook}</> уже давно хоче мій рецепт печива.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Удачі. Я сталева пастка."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Th' dinner around here's like a Guild initiation rite.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(hmph)</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Ця вечеря схожа на обряд посвячення в гільдію.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(хмпф)</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,wf_town_has_cook].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Och. Yer <#BLUE>{name.job_cook}'s</> mince and tatties'd kill a <#RED>{name.groak}</> faster'n a <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hrm.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Yer showin' promise."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хм.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ви подаєте надії."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Och, well done.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I've not smiled like this in years."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" О, добре зроблено.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Я так не посміхався багато років."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ye almost gave <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> a wee heart attack that time.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Того разу ви ледь не спричинили у <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}а</> серцевий напад.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Yer wee {name.job_armorsmith}'s been snoopin' round me forge again.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(hmph)</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Ваш маленький {name.job_armorsmith} знову шастає навколо моєї кузні.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <i>(гмпф)</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].10"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {name.blacksmith_grunt} I'm busy. Bother someone else."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {Name.blacksmith_grunt} Я зайнятий. Заважайте комусь іншому."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].11"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Ye keep standin' there, ye'll grow moss."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Якщо будете стояти тут, виросте мох."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" There's always work that needs ta be done.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Don't ye have somewhere ta be, Hunter?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Завжди є робота, яку треба виконати.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...У вас немає куди піти, Мисливцю?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].13"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Want somethin' forged?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...No? Then why are ye botherin' me?!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Хочете щось викувати?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Ні? Тоді навіщо мене турбуєте?!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].14"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" That {name.job_dojo}'s got some battle scars.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I'd wager he's got some tales to tell."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" {Name.job_dojo} має чимало бойових шрамів.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Закладаюся, у нього є цікаві історії."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].15
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].15"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I had a square go wit' yer {name.job_dojo}.\n"
" !point\n"
" Fierce fella."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Я мав сутичку з вашим {2:{name.job_dojo}}.\n"
" !point\n"
" Лютий хлопець."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Hrm. Ye've got naught for me, I see.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Хм. Я бачу, у вас для мене нічого нема.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 'Tis a fine forge ye've got here."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" У вас тут чудова кузня."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Have ye e'er ate a good, hot mustard?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Me mind's been spinnin' on a good, hot mustard."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Ви коли-небудь їли гарячий гірчичний соус?\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"У мене весь час в голові вертиться думка про хороший, гарячий гірчичний соус."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I'm here ta work, not chat."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Я тут працювати, а не базікати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" There's always work that needs ta be done."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Завжди є робота, яку треба зробити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What are ye gawkin' at? Never seen a smithy ponderin' before?\n"
" !point\n"
" I cannae work with folks peerin' over me shoulder."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Och. I see how it is.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye think I'm not busy? Got all the time in th'world for a wee blether? Feh."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith].9"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" That wee <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}'s</> been snoopin' round me forge again.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ye'd better tell her ta keep her nose outta other folks' business.\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Lots o' <i>accidents</> can happen 'round a forge. Nasty accidents."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Той маленький <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> знову тиняється навколо моєї кузні.\n"
" !point\n"
" Краще скажіть їй не лізти в чужі справи.\n"
" !think\n"
" ...Багато <i>нещасних випадків</> може трапитися біля кузні. Неприємні випадки."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Hoooo-whee! Heard you gave 'em a real thrashing out there!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" All thanks to that faaaan<i>tastic</> lunch I packed for you, right?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Ого-го! Чула, що ви дали їм справжнього прочухана!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" І все завдяки тому фааанта<i>смачному</> обіду, що я вам приготувала, правда?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Nice going, Hunter!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did you get lots of good loot from beating that oversized <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Чудова робота, Мисливцю!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви отримали багато хорошої здобичі після битви з цим велетенським <#RED>{name.rot_boss}ом</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Well howdy there, Hunter!\n"
" !point\n"
" Feelin' a bit peckish?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Ну, привіт, Мисливцю!\n"
" !point\n"
" Відчуваєте голод?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" There's nothin' I love more in this world than whipping up big tasty batches of grub!\n"
" !point\n"
" Hooo-wee! Boy howdy!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Немає нічого кращого за приготування смачних, ситних страв!\n"
" !point\n"
" Ого-го! От це так!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Howdy! Everything's right as rain here--\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I sure do love choppin' and fryin' and all that other cookin' stuff!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Привіт! Тут все гаразд...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Люблю нарізати, смажити і всілякі інші кулінарні штуки!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].4"
msgid "!laugh\n"
" Well, someone's lookin' ready for adventure!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Best get a move-on, don't ya think?"
msgstr "!laugh\n"
" О, хтось виглядає готовим до пригод!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Краще вирушайте якнайшвидше, згодні?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Aw shucks, I can't find my flipper-flapper... er... turner-over...er...?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Splatula! I definitely meant splatula."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ой леле, не можу знайти свою лопаточку... ку... переверталочку... ку...?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Лопатка! Я безумовно мала на увазі лопатку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Hoo-boy, I sure am workin' hard in this here kitchen! Yes-siree!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Here I am, cookin' up a storm!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Mixin' and stirrin' away!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Are you gonna be standin' there for much longer, Hunter?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Ох-хо, я так завзято працюю на цій кухні! Точно!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Ось я, готую на повну!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Мішаю та помішую!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Ви ще довго тут стоятимете, Мисливцю?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Yeep! Don't sneak up on me like that!!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...Uh, sorry, guess I got a mite jumpy there. Good to see ya!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ой! Не підкрадайтеся так!!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" ...Ух, вибачте, здається, я трохи злякалася. Рада вас бачити!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].8"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Findin' lots of rare stuff on your adventures?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just curious!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви знаходите багато рідкісних речей у своїх пригодах?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Просто цікаво!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook].9"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Whew, the stuff in that big chest sure would fetch a pretty penny back in <#BLUE>the Brinks</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" N-not that I was snoopin' or nothin'!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Ух, оце добро у тій великій скрині коштувало б чималі гроші в <#BLUE>Брінкс</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Н-ні, я не лазила в неї, чесно!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Way to go.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You put the fear in 'em out there."
msgstr "!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Так тримати.\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"На полі бою ви всіх налякали."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" There's my star pupil.\n"
" !think\n"
" It'd be nice if the rest of my students learned a thing or two from you."
msgstr "!happy\n"
"!point\n"
"Ось мій найкращий учень.\n"
"!think\n"
"Було б добре, якби решта моїх учнів навчилася чогось від вас."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" There's the Hunter of the hour.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Whatcha need?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!gruffnod\n"
"Ось він, Мисливець цього часу.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Що вам потрібно?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" A+, kid.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Now. You need a lesson review?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" 5+, друже.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Тепер. Вам потрібен огляд уроку?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,won_last_run].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I'm glad at least <i>one</i> of my students pays attention in class.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Whatcha need?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Радий, що принаймні <i>один</i> з моїх учнів уважно слухає на заняттях.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Що вам потрібно?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" It's easy to regret a swing, but you'll never regret a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" So, y'know. <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Легко пошкодувати про удар, але ви ніколи не пошкодуєте про <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Тому, знайте, <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].10"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Didja know smacking objects in the environment keeps yer <#RED>Hit Streak</> going?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" 'Thought it was a good tip."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Чи знали ви, що удари по предметах в навколишньому середовищі підтримують вашу <#RED>серію влучань</>?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Мені здалося, що це гарна порада."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].11"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" A <#RED>{name.beets}</> is dazed after a head slam.\n"
" !point\n"
" Bait and <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</> before going in for the kill."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{Name.beets}</> приголомшений після удару головою.\n"
" !point\n"
" Приманюйте та виконуйте <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>, перш ніж його вбити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" You can swap your equipped gear at the <#RED>Armoury</> here in town."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви можете поміняти одягнуте спорядження на <#RED>манекені з обладунками</> тут, у місті."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].13"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You can't change your gear once you set out on a Hunt.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Dress wisely before you leave."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви не можете змінити своє спорядження, вирушивши на полювання.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough} Думайте що одягнути, перш ніж піти."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].14"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Don't forget, it's more important to stay alive than it is to strike.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" This is yer daily reminder to <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Не забувайте, що важливіше залишитися в живих, ніж завдати удару.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" <#RED>{Name.concept_dodge}</ > це ваше щоденне нагадування."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].15
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].15"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Remember, all <#RED>Weight</> builds are viable.\n"
" !point\n"
" You just gotta find what build works for you."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Пам'ятайте, усі <#RED>вагові категорії</> є життєздатними.\n"
" !point\n"
" Вам просто потрібно знайти той варіант, який вам підходить."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].16
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].16"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" All great Hunters started off as newbies trying stuff out."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Усі великі Мисливці починали як новачки, які пробують різні речі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].17
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].17"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" If you ever feel stuck, try changing up your gear.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" If nothing else, you'll feel snazzy."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Якщо ви коли-небудь відчуєте, що застрягли, спробуйте змінити спорядження.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Якщо вже нічого іншого, то принаймні будете виглядати круто."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].18
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].18"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Gettin' stuck is just an opportunity to try new things.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Try experimenting with your tactics."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Застрягти - це лише можливість спробувати нові речі.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Спробуйте поекспериментувати зі своєю тактикою."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].19
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].19"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> have melons for brains.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.yammo}'ll</> hit their own pals if you bait a swing right."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{Name_multiple.rot}</> мають дині замість мізків.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Якщо правильно підставитись, <#RED>{Name_multiple.yammo}</> вдарять своїх."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You can check yer <#RED>Weight Class</> over at the <#RED>Armoury</>.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви можете перевірити свою <#RED>вагову категорію</> на <#RED>манекені з обладунками</>.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].20
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].20"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Hey.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Be wary of the folks in the woods."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough} Гей.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Будьте обережні з істотами в лісі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].21
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].21"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" You done any training lately?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You can practice <#BLUE>Focus Hits</> on the dummies here in town."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Ви нещодавно тренувалися?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви можете практикувати <#BLUE>фокусні удари</> на манекенах тут, у місті."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].22
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].22"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> only last for one Hunt.\n"
" !point\n"
" Experiment with yer combinations."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{Name_multiple.concept_relic}</> тривають лише одне полювання.\n"
" !point\n"
" Експериментуйте зі своїми комбінаціями."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].23
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].23"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Listen up, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You'll know yer <#RED>Luck</> stat swayed a sitchy-ation if you see a <#RED>Lucky Clover Icon</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Слухайте, Мисливцю.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви дізнаєтеся, що ваша <#RED>удача</> вплинула на ситуацію, якщо побачите <#RED>значок щасливої конюшини</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].24
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].24"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Gusts of <#RED>Wind</> aren't so bad if you're a <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} Class</> build.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{name.light_weight} Class</> build? Different story."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Пориви <#RED>вітру</> не такі вже й страшні, якщо у вас <#RED>клас: {name.heavy_weight}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#RED>{Name.light_weight} клас</>? Це вже інша історія."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].25
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].25"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Listen up, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" Every <#RED>Enemy</> is predictable, if you learn to read them."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Слухайте, Мисливцю.\n"
" !point\n"
" Кожен <#RED>ворог</> передбачуваний, якщо ви навчитесь їх читати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].26
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].26"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Study your foes. Watch their moves.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Soon you'll see the openings."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Вивчайте своїх ворогів. Слідкуйте за їхніми рухами.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Незабаром ви побачите можливості."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].27
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].27"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Didja know you can get a <#RED>Critical</> <#BLUE>Focus Hit</>?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Powerful stuff."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Чи знали ви, що можете отримати <#RED>критичний</> <#BLUE>фокусний удар</>?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Сильна штука."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].28
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].28"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Need a lesson?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough} \n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture \n"
" Потрібен урок?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].29
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].29"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" How're yer studies going?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Як проходить навчання?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You can check yer <#RED>Weight Class</> over at any <#RED>Weapon Rack</>.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви можете перевірити свою <#RED>вагову категорію</> на будь-якій <#RED>стійці для зброї</>.\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].30
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].30"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Need anything explained?\n"
" !cough\n"
" Ask away."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Потрібно щось пояснити?\n"
" !cough\n"
" Запитуйте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].31
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].31"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Hmph.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm in a teachin' mood today."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Хмпф.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Сьогодні я в настрої викладати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].32
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].32"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget to review the fundamentals."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не забудьте переглянути основи."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].33
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].33"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Need me to explain anythin'?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {Name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Мені потрібно щось пояснити?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Be thoughtful when yer trying new <#RED>Armour</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Changing your gear might change your <#RED>Weight Class</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Будьте уважні, коли одягаєте нові <#RED>обладунки</>.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Зміна спорядження може змінити вашу <#RED>вагову категорію</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's easier to fight when you're comfy.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Try mixin' and matchin' <#RED>Armour</> sets to get your favourite <#RED>Weight Class</>."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Легше битися, коли вам зручно.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Спробуйте комбінувати набори <#RED>обладунків</>, щоб отримати вашу улюблену <#RED>вагову категорію</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Kids these days can't get enough of them <#RED>'Emote Rings'</> <p bind='Controls.Digital.SHOW_EMOTE_RING' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I prefer to never express myself."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Some <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> is more powerful than others, y'know.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You can tell <#RED>Fabled {name_multiple.concept_relic}</> apart by the fancier frames around their icons."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Деякі <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> потужніші за інші.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ви можете відрізнити <#RED>легендарні {name_multiple.concept_relic}</> за більш витонченими рамками навколо їхніх значків."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Listen up.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" You can do <#RED>Dodge Cancels</> to keep up your <#RED>Hit Streak</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Слухайте.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Ви можете виконувати <#RED>скасовування ухилення</>, щоб продовжити свою <#RED>серію влучань</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo].9"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" How's yer gear treatin' you?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Gettin' new equipment's just as important as upgrading your old stuff. Maybe even more."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Як ваше спорядження?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Отримання нового обладнання так само важливо, як і покращення старого. Можливо, навіть більше."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Team trainin's progressin' well. Everyone's showin' up and puttin' in the work. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" Sure, the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> is good 'n' all, but we can't rest on laurels. Should it fail, we need to be ready. \n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> surprised me. I'd swear she's had combat trainin' before, but she says her cookin' skills are just \"transferable\"... \n"
" !shrug\n"
" And here I am, can't toast a toadstool without burnin' down the woods."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Been a year since <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> disappeared. Could be darn near anywhere with that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur} Staff</> of his. \n"
" !point\n"
" But that don't scare me, Hunter, and I'll tell ya why: he's still got love in his heart. \n"
" !think\n"
" Think about it, Hunter. If he'd really wanted to hurt us, the smart move woulda been to play nice, gain our trust, then attack from within. \n"
" !gesture\n"
" But to hear y'all tell it, he teleported away because he feared he might still hurt <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>.\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" So I choose to believe <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}'s</> out there, workin' on changin', healin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Just got back from a tour of the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield's</> perimiter. \n"
" !shrug\n"
" I know it aggravates my cough somethin' fierce, but old habits, y'know. Got to make sure it's secure--\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Most <#RED>{name.rot}</> act like they just don't like the smell of the <#KONJUR>Shield</> 'n' turn away before gettin' too close.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" But I've seen some <#RED>{name.rot}</>, they seem taken by a darker energy. They <i>test</> the <#KONJUR>Shield</>, Hunter. \n"
" !think\n"
" Poke at it. Press on it. Claw, even. They can't get through, mind you, but it's enough to keep me patrollin'. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Can't give these <#RED>{name.rot}</> an inch, Hunter. Not. One. Inch."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !think\n"
" I don't think I've told you how proud I am of you for defeating <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> in the Battle of <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>...\n"
" player:\n"
" Aw, thanks, {name.npc_dojo_master}. And it only took a year!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Hmph. Well I still haven't. Let's see if I tell you next year."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ran into <#BLUE>{name.npc_konjurist}</>, huh? I'd know her work anywhere."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I bet <#BLUE>{name.npc_konjurist}</> is snitching on you to <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" But you probably knew that already."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_konjurist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_konjurist}</> doesn't see people. She sees {name.c_konjur} auras.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" At least, that's what she told me. And I believe her."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_specialeventhost]refiner_seen_wanderer.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_seen_npc_specialeventhost]refiner_seen_wanderer.1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Your {name.c_konjur} signature is...\n"
" !point\n"
" Did you run into that mysterious kind of wandering kind of guy on your last Hunt? How did he seem?\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh... yeah. He seemed, y'know, mysterious and... wander-ous...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Yeah, but did he seem happy?\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh. He's kind of hard to read...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Oh.\n"
" player:\n"
" But yeah, he seemed happy. For sure.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" ... Appreciated, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> is some kind of plant whisperer.\n"
" !agree\n"
" And not <i>just</> because I've clocked her whispering to plants."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}'s</> <i>such</> a dyed-in-the-wool anarchist.\n"
" !clap\n"
" Like, to the point she doesn't even subscribe to <i>that</> ideology. She's an inspiration to us rebels everywhere."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,wf_town_has_apothecary].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Do you think <#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> likes me?\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Not that I care, obvs."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Nice work, Hunter. Dad's a bit safer with you thrashing <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Nice run, Hunter. I sanction your reckless use of {name.c_konjur}. He he he."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" The way you rock those <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> rules."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.c_konjur} made the Rot what they are, but <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> made you what <i>you</> are so...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Lose, win... draw?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" You're the one instance of environmental devastation I can get on board with."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Good Hunt? You're glowing!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" That <i>could</> be the {name.c_konjur}, though..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,won_last_run].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm. <i>Do</> <#RED>{name.rot}</> have butts?\n"
" !point\n"
" If they do, you've kicked 'em. If they don't, you've kicked 'em off. Case closed."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You eat {name.c_konjur} all the time, right?\n"
" player:\n"
" \"Eat\" isn't quite right. \"Absorb\"?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" And you're good? No visions of thirsty ghosts or a desire to flip coins?\n"
" player:\n"
" No... Should I?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" No, no. Just checking."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].10"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Did you know <i>every one of us</> has about a shoe's worth of {name.c_konjur} in their bodies?\n"
" !angry\n"
" Yeah, I said 'shoe's worth'.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Look, we make do with what measurement tools we've got in the field, alright? Science is DIY, OK? NBD."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].11"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Loving my setup here. <i>Except</> for the smells from <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> grill. Yeesh."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}'s</> not some miracle goo.\n"
" !angry\n"
" It's useless at spiking up my hair, for example."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].13"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" To me, science is like music--you just bash things together and see what happens!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].14"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Is <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> afraid to talk to me?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I mean, <i>I</> would be."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].15
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].15"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I learned a lot working with <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>.\n"
" !think\n"
" Like \"Don't work with mad scientists,\" for example."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].16
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].16"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Am I worried about all the {name.c_konjur} you consume? No.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Am I worried about all of <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> cooking <i>I</> consume? Yes.\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.7> What does she PUT in that stuff? I can't stop eating it...</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].17
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].17"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Do I think having worked for <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</> makes me a sellout?\n"
" !dejected\n"
" All. The. Time."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].18
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].18"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I really admire your commitment to direct action, mutual aid, and water conservation.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm assuming the 'water conservation' one, since I've never <i>once</> seen you bathe.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" N-not that I'm trying to watch you bathe! He. He. Eh... <z 0.7>Dang it, {name.npc_refiner}! You're so AWKWARD!</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].19
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].19"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Is it weird you're not sick, given all the {name.c_konjur} you're exposed to?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Yes, it is very weird. You're a big weirdo. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" That <i>is</> my scientific opinion."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Nothing like some loud music and getting lost in {name.c_konjur}-based mutation data, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].20
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].20"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}'s</> precious grandchild is bigger than I'd imagined.\n"
" !think\n"
" I guess I <i>did</> imagine they'd be a baby, for whatever reason."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].21
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].21"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" It's reckless, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> being here.\n"
" !angry\n"
" It'll aggravate their illness <i>and</> their <#BLUE>Grandpa</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].22
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].22"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I know <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> trying to do what's right.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Even though so much wrong has been done in their name..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You weren't about to tell me what I can and can't do, were you?\n"
" !laugh\n"
" I'm just pulling your chain, Hunter. I wouldn't have listened anyway."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I'm concurrently parsing {name.c_konjur}'s mutagenic factors while coming up with names for a new punk band and-- Ooh--\n"
" !happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" \"Mass In-parse-ration.\"\n"
" \"Factoress.\"\n"
" \"Lottie and The Muta-Genies.\"\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ugh. Those suck. Maybe less multitasking..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I don't have a problem with authority. Authority has a problem with <i>me</>.\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Mainly because of withering comments like that one."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" So you're all just misfits and losers from <#BLUE>The Brinks</>, huh? \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Very cool. Very cool."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I've never been to <#BLUE>The Brinks</>. I always imagined it like this, though.\n"
" !think\n"
" Hardscrabble people, pulling together, makin' something better out of what they have...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" But, for some reason, I thought there'd be a lot more hats."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Careful with all that {name.c_konjur}. We still don't fully understand it..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].9"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" {name.c_konjur}'s here to stay, like it or not.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Like <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> weird foot rash, which she keeps showing me despite my telling her I'm not that kind of doctor."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner]refiner_twin.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner]refiner_twin.1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Uh, what're you staring at?\n"
" player:\n"
" Do... Do you have a twin?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Uh, no?\n"
" player:\n"
" You sure? While you were kidnapped, you were somehow simultaneously <i>here,</> in Camp...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Are you feeling okay? You eat a lot of {name.c_konjur}, don't you?\n"
" !think\n"
" It <i>has</> been known to cause hallucinations... You also get hit in the head a lot...\n"
" player:\n"
" Huh. Yeah... that could be it, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's nice to have <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> around.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I think she brightens up the camp."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Приємно коли <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> поруч.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Мені здається, вона скрасить табір."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Feel free to chat with folks around town.\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's good for morale."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не соромтеся спілкуватися з іншими в місті.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Це добре для моралі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Take some time to socialize with the other <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" It's good for team cohesion."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> truly doesn't care what others think of her.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I can't relate. But I admire it."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> дійсно не хвилює, що інші думають про неї.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я не в захваті."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm glad I hired <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I can trust him to be honest with me."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я радий, що найняв <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я вірю в те, що він буде чесним зі мною."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</> is an interesting character, isn't she?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There's <i>something</> about her..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" If you're taking a <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</>, make sure it's packed before we leave.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I don't wanna have to fly all the way back for a sandwich."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Якщо ви берете <#RED>{name.i_lunchbox}</>, переконайтеся, що він запакований, перш ніж ми підемо.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я не хочу летіти назад заради бутерброда."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You'll get some good <#RED>Buffs</> from <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}'s</> cooking.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I guess that's just my way of saying \"don't forget to eat\"."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ви отримаєте гарні <#RED>бафи</> від кулінарії <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Мабуть, це мій спосіб сказати \"не забудьте поїсти\"."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].1"
msgid "!closedeyes\n"
" Ahh. I love a victory flight home, don't you?\n"
" !agree\n"
" The air just <i>feels</i> headier."
msgstr "!closedeyes\n"
" Ахх. Я люблю переможний політ додому, а ви?\n"
" !agree\n"
" Навіть повітря <i>відчувається</i> легшим."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].2"
msgid "!clap\n"
" Another hunt well done, Hunter.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Not that I had any doubts."
msgstr "!clap\n"
" Ще одне вдале полювання, Мисливцю.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не те щоб у мене були сумніви."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].3"
msgid "!gesture\n"
" There are few things more refreshing than the wind rushing through my fur.\n"
" !think\n"
" I have to brush it kinda thoroughly afterwards to prevent matting, though."
msgstr "!gesture\n"
" Немає нічого більш освіжаючого, ніж вітер, що проноситься крізь моє хутро.\n"
" !think\n"
" Хоча потім доводиться ретельно його розчісувати, щоб не утворювалися ковтуни."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,won_last_run].4"
msgid "!laugh\n"
" I bet you enjoy the flight home more when you're conscious, huh?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I bet you remember more of the scenery at least."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Remember to prioritize <#RED>Dodging</> over <#RED>{name.concept_damage}</> out there.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !nervous\n"
" I don't mean to tell you how to Hunt. I just don't want anyone getting hurt."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].10"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No pressure, but let me know when you're ready.\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm itching to get back in the air!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].11"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ready for another {name.run}?\n"
" !point\n"
" Just hop in the ol'<#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Готові до ще одного {name.run}?\n"
" !point\n"
" Просто застрибніть у старий <#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].12"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" There's training dummies here in town if you'd like a chance to practice.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" If you can bring yourself to hit them, anyway. They're kinda cute.\n"
" !happy"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" У місті є тренувальні манекени, якщо ви хочете потренуватися.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Якщо ви взагалі зможете змусити себе їх вдарити. Вони ж такі милі.\n"
" !happy"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].13
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].13"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget, you can practice your moves on the training dummies around town.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's a good way to get the hang of a new weapon."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не забувайте, що ви можете відпрацьовувати свої рухи на тренувальних манекенах по всьому місту.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Це хороший спосіб навчитися володіти новою зброєю."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].14
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].14"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ready to {name.run}?\n"
" !point\n"
" The <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> aren't ready for you, I'll tell you that for free."
msgstr "!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Готові до {name.run}?\n"
"!point\n"
"<#RED>{Name_multiple.rot}</> не готові до вас, можу вам це гарантувати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Rest here as long as you need, Hunter.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It's not like the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> are going anywhere."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Відпочивайте тут, скільки потрібно, Мисливцю.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Не думаю, що <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> кудись дінуться."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Make sure to double check your gear before we head out.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I don't want to have to fly back, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget, you can't change your <#RED>Armour</> once we leave!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" It'd be unwieldy to pack <i>all</i> the <#RED>Armour</> you own for every flight, y'know?\n"
" !happy"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не забувайте, що ви не зможете змінити свої <#RED>обладунки</>, коли ми підемо!\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Важко взяти <i>всі</i> <#RED>обладунки</>, які у вас є, на кожен політ, знаєте?\n"
" !happy"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" We can head out whenever you're ready.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" No rush."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Коли ви будете готові, ми можемо вирушати.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не спішіть."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Nice day, isn't it?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" My allergies are only moderately debilitating today!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Гарний день, чи не так?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Сьогодні моя алергія лише помірно виснажлива!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].7"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Take a load off, Hunter. We're safe here in camp.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" At least I think we're safe.\n"
" !happy"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].8"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Make yourself at home.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" This <i>is</i> your home for the foreseeable future, after all.\n"
" !happy"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Почувайтесь як вдома.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Зрештою, <i>це</i> ваш дім у найближчому майбутньому.\n"
" !happy"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout].9"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ready to head out?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !thinking\n"
" I think I'm ready. Wait, did I pack my--"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Готові вирушати?\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !thinking\n"
" Я думаю, що я готовий. Зачекайте, я забрав свій..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith]armoursmith_itch_cream.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith]armoursmith_itch_cream.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I found <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> anti-itch cream in some debris.\n"
" !scared\n"
" She's probably missing that by now."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Я знайшов крем <#BLUE>{4:{Name.npc_armorsmith}}</> від свербіння серед уламків.\n"
"!scared\n"
"Вона, мабуть, уже почала його шукати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]bonion_cry.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]bonion_cry.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Every time I see a <#RED>{name.cabbageroll}</> die I end up crying a little bit.\n"
" !think\n"
" But I'm not sure if that's because I feel bad for it, or because of the <#RED>{name.cabbageroll}</> stink."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Кожного разу, коли я бачу смерть <#RED>{2:{Name.cabbageroll}}</>, я трохи плачу.\n"
" !think\n"
" Але я не впевнений, чи це через те, що мені його шкода, чи через смердючий запах <#RED>{2:{Name.cabbageroll}}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]dojo_toe_nails.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]dojo_toe_nails.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" I wish <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> wouldn't clip his toenails in the common area.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" He <i>insists</> they're a natural <#RED>Rot</> repellant, but there's no way that's true... right?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Я б хотів, щоб <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> не стриг собі нігті на ногах у спільній зоні.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Він <i>наполягає</>, що вони є природним засобом від <#RED>гнильців</>, але це ж не може бути правдою... чи не так?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]gathering_data.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]gathering_data.1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's a lot easier to scout when you've got a fighter on the ground!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I'm gathering so much info from your {name_multiple.run}!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Набагато легше розвідувати, коли на землі є боєць!\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Я збираю так багато інформації під час вашої {name_multiple.run}!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]playing_cards.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]playing_cards.1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Oh hey! My pack of playing cards survived the crash!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Well at least we have the essentials! Haha."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" О, привіт! Моя колода гральних карт пережила аварію!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ну, принаймні, у нас є найнеобхідніше! Ха-ха."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]smushed_rations.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]smushed_rations.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hm... our food got pretty smushed in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> crash.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I hope no one's picky."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Гм... наша їжа трохи пом'ята після аварії <#RED>{2:{Name.i_damselfly}}</>.\n"
"!happy\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Сподіваюся, ніхто не буде вибагливим."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,konjur_rich,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,konjur_rich,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Whewie, you're <i>ripe</i> with <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> stink-- need an <#RED>Upgrade</>?"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Фуф, ви пахнете <i>дозрілим</i> <#KONJUR>{3:{name.i_konjur}}</>... потрібне <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Need another <#RED>Upgrade</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" <#RED>{name_multiple.mothball}</> are more dangerous than they look, you know."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Потрібно ще одне <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
"!shrug\n"
"<#RED>{Name_multiple.mothball}</> набагато небезпечніші, ніж здаються."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The samples I collect in this swamp are quite interesting.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" If you've got nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>, I'd like to get back to them."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!think\n"
"Зразки, які я збираю в цьому болоті, досить цікаві.\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Якщо у вас немає нічого для <#RED>покращення</>, я б хотів повернутися до них."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> been teaching me all about skincare lately.\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if the goop here would make a good mask."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</> останнім часом навчає мене всього про догляд за шкірою.\n"
" !think\n"
" Цікаво, чи підійде ця мазь як маска."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oooh. I stepped in something goopy.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Gross."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ооох. Я втрапив у щось неприємне.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Фуу."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmmmm..... Yeah.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I'll <i>definitely</i> need to hose down the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> floor mats when we get home."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Хмммм..... Так.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Мені <i>безумовно</i> потрібно буде промити килимки <#RED>{2:{Name.i_damselfly}}</> зі шланга, коли ми повертаємось додому."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" How d'you think the <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</> gets her fur so silky?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" I-I'm not jealous!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Як, гадаєте, як <#RED>{Name.bandicoot}</> досягає такої шовковистої шерсті?\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Я-я не заздрю!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" This whole place is caked top to bottom with fungus.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" And where there's fungus, there's <#RED>Spores</>. They're mostly benign, but they <i>can</i> cause some weird effects.\n"
" !point\n"
" I'd suggest learning to identify them by sight."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> in this area is something called an <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</>.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" It's huge, and seems to delight in tormenting people with its tricks.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" This'll be a very different fight from the last <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>. Steel yourself."
msgstr "!agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#RED>{Name.rot_boss}</> у цій місцевості — <#RED>{Name.bandicoot}</>.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Вона величезна і, здається, насолоджується тим, що мучить істот своїми витівками.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Це буде зовсім інший бій, ніж минулий <#RED></>. Переконайтеся, що ви готові."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't <i>muck</i> about with inferior products, my friend.\n"
" !point\n"
" For the discerning ssshopper, it's {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand or bust!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Не <i>зв'язуйтеся</i> з неякісними продуктами, мій друже.\n"
"!point\n"
"Для вибагливих покупців є тільки бренд {Name.npc_doc_lastname}, або нічого!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_travelling_salesman].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_travelling_salesman].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't get <i>bogged down</i> with inferior products!\n"
" !point\n"
" Buy {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</>, for all your recovery needs!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не <i>зациклюйтеся</i> на неякісних продуктах!\n"
" !point\n"
" Купуйте <#RED>лікувальні {name.potion}</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}, і ваші потреби у лікуванні будуть втамовані!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1"
msgid "!think\n"
" If the cold's starting to get to you...\n"
" !point\n"
" You could always try warming up with a new <#RED>Upgrade</>."
msgstr "!think\n"
" Якщо холод починає дошкуляти вам...\n"
" !point\n"
" Можливо, варто зігрітися новим <#RED>покращенням</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!think\n"
" I need to get back to analyzing my samples.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" They'll freeze if I leave them out too long."
msgstr "!think\n"
" Мені потрібно повернутися до аналізу зразків.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Вони замерзнуть, якщо я залишу їх надовго."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout,wf_town_has_cook]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" It's a shame <#BLUE>{name.npc_cook}</> can't see this place.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" She likes things that sparkle. Or at least that's what <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</> told me."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Шкода, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_cook}</> не може побачити це місце.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Вона любить блискучі речі. Принаймні так мені сказала <#BLUE>{Name.npc_armorsmith}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lucky for us, this cavern is wide enough for me to fly the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> through.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <z 0.7>(sigh)</z> I'll be missing the open sky, though."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" На наше щастя, ця печера досить велика, щоб я зміг пролетіти крізь неї на {3:<#RED>{Name.i_damselfly}}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" <z 0.7>(зітхає)</z> Я буду сумувати за відкритим небом."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Look at those giant walls of ice!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" It's a good thing I'm not claustrophobic.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Haha... <z 0.7>ha...</z>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Подивіться на ці величезні стіни льоду!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Добре, що я не клаустрофоб.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Хаха... <z 0.7>ха...</z>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" You know... this place is actually kind of beautiful. In its own way.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Not that I'd like to stick around too long."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Знаєте... це місце насправді гарне по-своєму.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Хоча я б не хотів тут надовго залишатися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brrr...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Note to self: next expedition, pack extra thick socks."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Бррр...\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Нотатка для себе: наступного разу взяти ще товстіші шкарпетки."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me he lost one of his toes to frostbite.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Let's... try to avoid that, shall we?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> розповідав, що втратив один із пальців через обмороження.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Спробуймо цього уникнути, гаразд?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Stay on your toes, Hunter. <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> counting on us."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Don't think about what we've lost, but what we'll rebuild."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_region,qc_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Whatever he might've done, we need <#BLUE>Grandpa</> to fix our <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>. \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Let's go save him."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1"
msgid "!shrug\n"
" Sure it's a little eerie out here, but you get used to it after a while.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Mostly."
msgstr "!shrug\n"
" Так, тут трохи моторошно, але з часом звикаєш.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" ...Майже."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Those old security systems can be a real pain to get around, huh?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" An <#RED>Upgrade</> or two might help with that."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Ці старі охоронні системи справжній головний біль, чи не так?\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Можливо, кілька <#RED>покращень</> допоможуть."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" This is my old home. It's... It's all gone now."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scout_rummage\n"
" Maybe something of mine is still here..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" <#BLUE>Grandpa</> and I lived here. Seems like ancient history now. \n"
" !dejected\n"
" Maybe it is."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" So many memories growing up here. All gone now."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,room_type_quest]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" It's surreal, to see your childhood home suddenly in ruins."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,received_power_upgrade,role_scout,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,received_power_upgrade,role_scout,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" How are those <#RED>Upgrades</> treating you?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Let me know if you experience any dizziness or shortness of breath.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ha! Kidding! ...But let me know if you do."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Як вам ваші <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Дайте знати, якщо відчуєте запаморочення чи задишку.\n"
" !point\n"
" Ха! Жартую! ...Але якщо щось буде – дайте знати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It's so peaceful here.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Almost makes you forget how crazy the rest of the world is... almost."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Тут так спокійно.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Майже змушує забути, який божевільний інший світ... майже."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if the old fishing hole still exists. I always meant to go...\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just assumed it'd always be there, or <i>I'd</> always be here to go. Hm."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Can you believe this little grove was tucked away in the forest?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I bet it'll make a great camping spot one day, once we've saved <#BLUE>the {name.rotwood}</>!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Чи можете ви повірити, що цей маленький гай був захований у лісі?\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Б'юсь об заклад, що одного разу це стане чудовим місцем для кемпінгу, коли ми врятуємо <#BLUE>{Name.rotwood}</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The <#RED>Wind</> here is strong and constant enough to actually blow away some of the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> smog.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" At night, you can actually see the stars!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Тутешній <#RED>вітер</> настільки сильний і постійний, що може розганяти трохи туману з <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</>.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Уночі справді видно зорі!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" I hope you're warm enough in that.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It gets pretty <#RED>Windy</> out here."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я сподіваюся, що вам тут достатньо тепло.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Тут буває досить <#RED>вітряно</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{name.owlitzer_forest}'s</> full of <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> with <#RED>Wind</> abilities.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you've got <#RED>{name.heavy_weight} Class</> gear it won't bother you much, but anything lighter and you might find it hard to keep your footing."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#RED>{Name.owlitzer_forest}</> повний <#RED>{2:{name_multiple.rot}}</> зі здібностями <#RED>вітру</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Якщо у вас є спорядження класу <#RED>{name.heavy_weight}</>, це вас не дуже турбуватиме, але будь-що легше, і вам може бути важко втриматися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].7"
msgid "!point\n"
" I've only spotted the <#RED>{name.owlitzer}</> outside its nest a few times, but I saw enough to know it's a <i>massive</i> bird with crazy sharp talons!\n"
" !scared\n"
" A single flap of its wings creates huge blasts of air!"
msgstr "!point\n"
" Я бачив <#RED>{2:{Name.owlitzer}}</> біля гнізда лише кілька разів, але я бачив достатньо, щоб знати, що це <i>масивна</i> пташка із божевільно гострими кігтями!\n"
" !scared\n"
" Один помах її крил створює величезні вихори повітря!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[in_town].8"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The <#RED>Wind</> here presents a fun challenge flying the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> overhead.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh, don't worry though! It won't affect my ability to come to your rescue in an emergency!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Тутешній <#RED>вітер</> створює цікаві виклики для польоту на <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</>.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Але не хвилюйтеся! У надзвичайній ситуації я все одно прилечу на допомогу!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ugh, this stupid wind...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" I lost half a day's worth of notes because I forgot to weigh them down with a paperweight."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Ох, цей клятий вітер...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Я втратив половину своїх записів, бо забув їх скріпити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Chilly out.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Need an <#RED>Upgrade</>?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Прохолодно.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Потрібно <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}'s</> good for blood circulation, you know.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? <#RED>Upgrade</> time?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"<#KONJUR>{Name.konjur}</> чудово підходить для покращення кровообігу.\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Так що? Час для <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>, huh?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Don't freeze out there."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!dubious\n"
"Нічого не потрібно <#RED>покращувати</>, так?\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Не замерзніть там."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brr...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" My fur's double-coated and I can <i>still</i> feel that chill!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Брр...\n"
"!gesture\n"
"В мене подвійне хутро, і я все <i>ще</i> відчуваю цей холод!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].10"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" If you see a <#RED>Brazier</> that's frozen over, a few good whacks should shake the ice off and get it burning again."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Якщо побачите <#RED>жаровню</>, покриту льодом, ударте декілька ударів — і вона знову запалиться."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].11"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Remember Hunter, even if you get frozen solid, you can still wiggle your way out.\n"
" player:\n"
" How do I do that?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" This may be an odd analogy, but I like to imagine I have a keyboard in front of me, and I'm mashing a bunch of buttons.\n"
" player:\n"
" Your mind works in mysterious ways, {name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ha! I suppose you're right."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Пам'ятайте, Мисливцю, навіть якщо замерзнете, ви все одно можете звільнитися.\n"
" player:\n"
" Як мені це зробити?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Може здатися дивним, але уявляю перед собою клавіатуру і товчусь по клавішах.\n"
" player:\n"
" Твій розум працює загадковим чином, {Name.npc_scout}.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ха! Мабуть, ви праві."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brrr... boy, am I glad I installed a seat warmer in the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</>..."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Бр-р-р... як добре, що я встановив підігрів сидіння в <#RED>{3:{Name.i_damselfly}}</>..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brrr! Sure wish I was an arctic fox about now."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Бррр! Зараз я точно хотів би бути арктичним лисом."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Hey, don't lick any metal while you're out there.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" If you like having a tongue, anyway."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!point\n"
"Гей, не облизуйте метал, коли будете там.\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Якщо вам подобається мати язик."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Keep an eye out for <#RED>Heat Sources</> out there so you don't <#RED>Freeze</> solid!\n"
" !scared\n"
" Boy, I'm glad I packed my scarf."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
"Слідкуйте там за <#RED>джерелами тепла</>, щоб не <#RED>замерзнути</>!\n"
"!scared\n"
"Ох, як добре, що я взяв шарф."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" This snow's kinda pretty, huh?\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I swear it sparkles a little from different angles. Haha. Neat."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
"Цей сніг трохи гарний, чи не так?\n"
"!happy\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Я присягаюся, він трохи виблискує під різними кутами. Ха-ха. Класно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" I think my entire nose is turning into an ice cube.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Hunter? Is my nose still there? Tell me the truth."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Здається, весь мій ніс перетворюється на крижинку.\n"
"!nervous\n"
"Мисливцю? Мій ніс все ще на місці? Скажіть мені правду."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !scared\n"
" Brr!!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" My <i>coat</i> needs a coat in this <#BLUE>Cold</>!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!scared\n"
"Брр!!\n"
"!shocked\n"
"Моє <i>хутро</i> потребує ще одного шару на такому <#BLUE>холоді</>!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].8"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" This place used to be a granite quarry, back in the day. It supplied the whole <#BLUE>Rotwood</> with stone to build our homes.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Maybe when this is all over, we'll be able to get it up and running again. We'll have a lot of rebuilding to do, after all."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Колись тут був гранітний кар'єр. Він забезпечував увесь <#BLUE>Ротвуд</> каменем для будівництва наших домівок.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Може, коли все це скінчиться, ми зможемо знову його відкрити. Бо роботи з відбудови буде чимало."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[in_town].9"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Whew! Sorry for the bumpy flight, Hunter. I had to shake off a particularly territorial flock of crows on the way over."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Фух! Вибачте за хиткий політ, Мисливцю. Прийшлося відлякувати дуже територіальну зграю ворон по дорозі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" You know, this scarf was my <#BLUE>Grandpa's</>. \n"
" !think\n"
" I wonder if he'll recognize it... Or me..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" I'll be ready to pull you out, even in there. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" I've flown <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> in tighter spaces, sure!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I've been inside the lab, but it was well over 10 years ago...\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I was little. I'm sure it's changed. Like everything."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" <#KONJUR>Primeval Teffra</>--what is it, even?\n"
" !disagree\n"
" And could <i>anything</> be worth all this suffering?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" Ah-ah-AH-AH---Oh. I think it's gone--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" -<i>CHOOO!!</>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ow. That one kind of <i>hurt</> ..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_entrance]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I'm ready to face him. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" I'll <i>be</> ready once we face him."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I'm ready. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" It's time to face <#BLUE>Grandpa</>. Together."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It's okay Flitt. He loves you. He'll listen to you."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" All this <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-a-ah--</>\n"
" !shocked\n"
" --ah-AH-<i>CHOO!</>\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Oh dear. <z 0.7>Do you think he heard that?</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> a fox of science. He'll listen to reason."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" You look like you could use an <#RED>Upgrade</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...And a bath. How long have you been wading through swamp muck?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Ви виглядаєте так, ніби вам потрібно <#RED>покращення</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...І ванна. Як довго ви бродили болотами?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Lovely day for a walk through the swamp, huh?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...For you, anyway. I'm up to my ears in samples that need labeling."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Чудовий день для прогулянки болотом, правда?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" ...Принаймні, для вас. А я по вуха в зразках, які потрібно маркувати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I didn't think to pack bug spray for this Hunt.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I regret that."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я не подумав взяти з собою спрей від комах для цього полювання.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я шкодую про це."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'know, I think <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> grew up around here actually.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe I'll find him a neat rock to bring back as a souvenir."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Знаєте, я думаю, що <#BLUE>{Name.npc_dojo_master}</> насправді виріс тут.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Можливо, я знайду йому гарний камінь, щоб повернути як сувенір."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Oh hey, remember not to stand in the <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" You'd be surprised how many Hunters forget."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !point\n"
" Ой, пам'ятайте, що не варто стояти в <#RED>{5:{name.concept_toxic}}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Ви будете здивовані, скільки мисливців забувають."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Ah geez, I hope I don't get any <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</> on my watch.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Why didn't I leave it at camp?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" О боже, я сподіваюся, що <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</> не потрапить на мій годинник.\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Чому я не залишив його в таборі?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Watch your step--unless you like <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</> between your toes."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[in_town].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" The bog was always home to a lot of toxic creatures, even before the volcano erupted. But the introduction of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> certainly didn't help matters.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Remember, with <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</> there's only one rule--don't touch it. If something spits at you or leaves a <#RED>{name.concept_toxic}</> trail, don't stand around in it.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Unless you're looking to do some industrial-strength exfoliation."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_treemon_forest,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" This here tonic is made from the finest, freshest ingredientsss east of the <#RED>{name.treemon}</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Don't misss out!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Цей тонік зроблено з найкращих, найсвіжіших інгредієнтів на схід від цих <#RED>{2:{Name.treemon}}</>.\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Не пропустіть!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh my, your pocketsss seem lighter than usual today.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" As the single father of four plucky eruption orphansss, I'm afraid I simply can't give my <#RED>Potions</> away for free.\n"
" !scared\n"
" A little <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> is all I ask. It's for their college fundsss.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm sure you understand."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ой, здається, ваші кишені сьогодні легші, ніж зазвичай.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Як єдиний батько чотирьох спритних сиріт виверження, боюсь, я просто не можу роздавати свої <#RED>зілля</> безплатно.\n"
" !scared\n"
" Трішки <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</> — це все, про що я прошу. Це для їхнього фонду на навчання.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Сподіваюся, ви мене розумієте."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,needs_potion,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[can_craft_potion].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Good gravy, maybe Ma wasss right about this venture.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hm? Oh my friend, I didn't realize you were lissstening!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Хороша підлива, можливо, мама мала рацію щодо цієї справи.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Гм? О мій друже, я не знав, що ви слухаєте!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Need another <#RED>Upgrade</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Next one'll cost you."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Потрібне ще одне <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
"!shrug\n"
"Наступне за ваш рахунок."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Don't forget, only the <i>first</i> one's free."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Не забувайте, лише <i>перше</i> безплатно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I can do more <#RED>Upgrades</> if you don't mind paying."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я можу зробити більше <#RED>покращень</>, якщо ви не проти заплатити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I'm out spare <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>, so you'll have to pay if you want another <#RED>Upgrade</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" У мене більше нема <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</>, тому вам доведеться заплатити, якщо ви бажаєте ще одне <#RED>покращення</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for letting me do a free <#RED>Upgrade</>. It's a nice break."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Дякую, що дозволили мені зробити безплатне <#RED>покращення</>. Гарна перерва."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,run_has_free_upgrades,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Hope that free <#RED>Upgrade</> does you some good."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Сподіваюся, безплатне <#RED>покращення</> принесе вам користь."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Need anymore <#RED>Upgrades</>?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Потрібні ще <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" If you need any more <#RED>Upgrades</>, I'm your <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Якщо вам потрібні ще якісь <#RED>покращення</>, я ваш <#KONJUR>{name.job_konjurist}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" I can do another <#RED>Upgrade</> if you've got the <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Я можу зробити ще одне <#RED>покращення</>, якщо у вас є <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" So? How's the <#RED>Upgrade</> feel?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ну, як відчувається <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Did you want to look at the <#RED>Upgrade</> options again?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви хочете ще раз переглянути варіанти <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" If you want some more <#RED>Upgrades</>, I'll need some <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Якщо ви хочете ще <#RED>покращень</>, мені знадобиться <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,received_power_upgrade,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Need something else?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Потрібно щось ще?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_apothecary]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_apothecary]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!closedeyes\n"
" Hmm. Other people..."
msgstr "!closedeyes\n"
" Хм. Інші істоти..."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> and I are gonna take a big nap the second we get home.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Can't wait."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" <#BLUE>{Name.npc_lunn}</> і я збираємось подрімати, як тільки повернемося додому.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Не можу дочекатися."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't let any monsters bite your butt while you're out here.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Or do. Who am I to give orders."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Не дозволяйте жодним монстрам кусати вас за зад, поки ви тут.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Або ж дозволяйте. Хто я такий, щоб віддавати накази."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" It'll be nice to get to camp and take a load off.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Maybe a warm foot bath."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Буде чудово прибути в табір і відпочити.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Можливо там є тепла ванна для ніг."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].4"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" So tell me more about how <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> was worried about me.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Heehee."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Що ж розкажи мені більше про те, як <#BLUE>{Name.npc_scout}</> хвилювався за мене.\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Хі-хі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I can't wait to see who else joins our camp!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" What can I say? I'm a people person."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Не можу дочекатися, щоб побачити, хто ще приєднається до нашого табору!\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Що я можу сказати? Я дуже соціальний."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" I'll be at the camp if you need me!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" See you there!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Я буду в таборі, якщо я вам знадоблюся!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" До зустрічі!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].7"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Come say hi after your Hunt!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" We have so much to chat about."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" Приходьте передати привіт після свого полювання!\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Нам так багато про що є побалакати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_armorsmith]NOT[in_town].8"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" See you at home... <i>neighbour!</i>\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Heehee."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" До зустрічі вдома... <i>сусід!</i>\n"
" !wavelunn\n"
" Хіі-хіі."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Ye ain't watchin' me get grabbed by the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}'s</> claws. Get goin'."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_blacksmith]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Off with ye, then."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Тоді йдіть."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_cook]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_cook]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Happy trails, Hunter. Seeya at camp!"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wave\n"
" Щасливих дороги, Мисливцю. Побачимося в таборі!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Oh. Is it <#RED>Upgrade</> time?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"О, вже час для <#RED>покращення</>?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Sorry, I've got no <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> to spare.\n"
" !point\n"
" If you want an <#RED>Upgrade</>, you're gonna have to pay up."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Вибачте, але в мене немає жодного запасного <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" Якщо хочете отримати <#RED>покращення</>, вам доведеться заплатити."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" No free <#RED>Upgrades</> this time around."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Цього разу немає безплатних <#RED>покращень</>."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist,upgradable_powers]NOT[can_get_free_upgrade,run_has_free_upgrades]no_freebie.3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Hey. This has been a great experiment and all, but...\n"
" !point\n"
" Maybe you should just turn back. Forget all of this."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Гей. Це був чудовий експеримент і все таке, але...\n"
" !point\n"
" Може, вам краще повернутися. Забути все це."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" The raw <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> is pretty potent here.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It's great."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Необроблений <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> тут досить потужний.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Це чудово."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].10
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].10"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" You're welcome to hang.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" The <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> fumes are wonderfully fragrant this time of day. Or so I'm told."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Ви завжди можете залишитися.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Пари <#KONJUR>{2:{name.i_konjur}}</> чудово пахнуть у цей час дня. Принаймні, так кажуть."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].11
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].11"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" How do I move from room to room?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Very carefully."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Як мені перейти з локації в локацію?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Дуже обережно."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].12
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].12"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What's it like to be full of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</>?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Does it... hurt?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Як це бути сповненим <#KONJUR>{3:{name.i_konjur}}</>?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Це... боляче?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't you love the sting of <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> hitting your nostrils?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" No, I'm genuinely asking. You won't catch me running around out here bare-faced."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Вам подобається відчуття коли <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur}</> пече в ніздрях?\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ні, я серйозно питаю. Ви мене тут без маски не побачите."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !thinking\n"
" Now what if...?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" No, no, that won't work."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !thinking\n"
" А що, якщо...?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Ні, ні, це не спрацює."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Haha, I knew you were headed this way.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" My equipment's been going nuts."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
"!point\n"
"Ха-ха, я знав, що ви прямуєте сюди.\n"
"!gesture\n"
"Моє обладнання божеволіє."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Watch your step.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I've got a bunch of gadgets and crystals strewn about."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Дивіться під ноги.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" У мене розкидано купу гаджетів і кристалів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Well, I didn't expect <i>that</i> result.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" That's research for you."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Ну, я не чекав <i>такого</i> результату.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Ось що таке дослідження."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].7"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Hmm...\n"
" !think\n"
" How interesting."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Гмм... \n"
" !think\n"
" Як цікаво."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Making a note of that...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Huh? Sorry, I was distracted."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Занотувати це...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Га? Вибачте, я відволікся."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist].9"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Kinda hard to work when you're making my equipment go haywire.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Not that you can control it, I guess."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Досить важко працювати, коли ви змушуєте ламатись моє обладнання.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Хоча, думаю, ви не можете це контролювати."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" No <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> to <#RED>Upgrade</> today?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Too bad."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Сьогодні немає <#RED>{name_multiple.concept_relic}</> для <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Шкода."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Eh? Oh. You've got nothing for me to <#RED>Upgrade</> today.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Well, I'll be here when you need me."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" А? Ох мені нема чого <#RED>покращувати</> сьогодні.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ну, я буду тут, коли я вам знадоблюся."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Aw, you've got nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" I was looking forward to a break."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Ой, вам нема чого <#RED>покращити</>.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Я з нетерпінням чекав перерви."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Eh? You've got nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" What a bummer."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" А? Вам нема що <#RED>покращувати</>.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Що за облом."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</> today, huh?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Maybe you'll get a <#RED>{name.concept_relic}</> in the next room."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Сьогодні нічого для <#RED>покращення</>, га?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Можливо, ви отримаєте <#RED>{2:{name.concept_relic}}</> у сусідній галявині."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_konjurist]NOT[upgradable_powers].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Nothing to <#RED>Upgrade</>?\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Just as well, I'm behind on data entry."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Немає нічого для <#RED>покращення</>?\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Крім того, я відстаю від введення даних."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Queeeeeeee.</>\n"
" <z 0.8>Chorp!</>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <z 0.8>Квіііііііііііііііі.</>\n"
" <z 0.8>Чорп!</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.8>Squet.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Ca-ca-ca-ca!</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" <z 0.8>Скет.</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Ка-ка-ка-ка!</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Queh?</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Cheh! Cheh!</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Ке?</>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Чех! Чех!</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <z 0.8>Coooo.</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Quaw.</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" <z 0.8>Коооо.</>\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <z 0.8>Кву.</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Queep... quaw.... <i>Squet.</i></>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Ca-ca-ca-ca.</>"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Квіп... кву.... <i>Скет.</i></>\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" <z 0.8>Ка-ка-ка-ка.</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_magpie].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Quort.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.8>Quee, quee.</>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" <z 0.8>Кворт.</>\n"
" !think\n"
" <z 0.8>Кві, кві.</>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" What a privilege for you, browsing my wares.\n"
" !wink\n"
" You're welcome."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" Яка честь для вас переглядати мої товари.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Будь ласка."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Peruse at your leisure, culver.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I'm not going anywhere."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !wink\n"
" Розглядай на свій розсуд, голубе.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Я нікуди не йду."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Handcrafted, artisanal pieces at reasonable prices.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Made from local materials."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" Вироби ручної роботи за розумними цінами.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Виготовлено з місцевих матеріалів."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" All pieces are guaranteed to be one-size-fits-all.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" The material is <i>deceptively</i> elastic."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Гарантовано, що всі деталі універсальні.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Матеріал <i>оманливо</i> еластичний."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].5"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !smirk\n"
" Hand-hammered, hand-forged.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" And, if you desire, hand-delivered."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !smirk\n"
" Власноруч кований, власноруч виготовлений.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" І, якщо ви бажаєте, власноруч доставлений."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_market_merchant].6"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Oh yeah. I hath what the Hunters crave.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Enjoy."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" О так. Я маю те, чого прагнуть Мисливці.\n"
" !wink\n"
" Насолоджуйтесь."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" I'm glad we're doing another Hunt here.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I love flying over the treetops."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !agree\n"
" Я радий, що ми проводимо тут ще одне полювання.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Я люблю літати над верхівками дерев."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Y'think there are any squirrels left in this forest?\n"
" !point\n"
" Squirrels are neat."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
" Ви думаєте, що в цьому лісі залишилися білки?\n"
" !point\n"
" Білки гарні."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,treemon_region]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" When I was a kid my grandpa and I used to pick berries around here.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Anyway. Be safe on your Hunt."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Коли я був дитиною, ми з дідусем збирали тут ягоди.\n"
" !gesture\n"
" У будь-якому випадку. Будьте обережними на полюванні."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" You know what <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}'d</> say about the <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> in there.\n"
" !scared\n"
" If one looks like it's about to <#RED>Attack</>, <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK> <#RED>Dodge</> out of the way."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Don't forget, a <#RED>Dodge</> will always get you out of harm's way quicker than running.\n"
" !point\n"
" As Toot would say, \"You can <#RED>Dodge</> with <p bind='Controls.Digital.DODGE' color=BTNICON_DARK>.\" I usually dodge with my legs."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !agree\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says, time a <#RED>Dodge</> <i>just</> right after starting an <#RED>Attack</> to do what's called a <#RED>{name.concept_dodge} Cancel</>.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Longer or heavier <#RED>Attacks</> usually have smaller <#RED>Cancel Windows</>, though. <z 0.7>All of <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}'s</> weird terms...</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_cannon]NOT[in_town,weapon_type_cannon].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Oh, <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> said when you <#RED>{name.concept_dodge}</>, you'll roll a short distance and even be <#RED>Invincible</> for a little bit.\n"
" !agree\n"
" Masters can even do a <#RED>Perfect Dodge</> by waiting until the last moment to roll away. <#RED>Dodging</> is a science, an art, <i>and</> a little roll!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me to remind you of <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" And I quote, \"One way is to do 'em is to hit <#RED>two or more Targets</> at once with your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</>.\" End quote."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> told me to remind you of <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</>.\n"
" !point\n"
" And I quote, \"One way to do 'em is to fully charge your <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}'s</> <#RED>Skill</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.SKILL' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\""
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_hammer]NOT[in_town].3"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Oh, Hunter, do you know what it takes to do a <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>? <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> asked me to ask.\n"
" !point\n"
" He said, \"One way to do 'em is with a fully charged <#RED>{name.weapon_hammer}</> <#RED>Heavy Attack</> (<p bind='Controls.Digital.ATTACK_HEAVY' color=BTNICON_DARK>).\""
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_polearm]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout,weapon_type_polearm]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !thinking\n"
" <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> today, huh?\n"
" !point\n"
" You know what <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says, \"Hit with the very tip, do a scary <#BLUE>{name.concept_focus_hit}</>.\""
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Don't forget to keep <#BLUE>{name_multiple.concept_focus_hit}</> in mind out there.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> says they do increased <#RED>Damage</>, which appears in <#BLUE>Blue</>, whatever <i>that</> means?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_scout]NOT[in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Hey, Hunter... I just wanted to say I appreciate all the work you do for the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}'</> expedition.\n"
" !nervous\n"
" That's... that's all. Didn't mean to get all mushy."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
