" !angry\n"
" Немає безплатних зразків!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hey!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Гей!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].3"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" What are you doing over there, my fine friend?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Що ви там робите, мій добрий друже?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].4"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Keep your paws out of that!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Тримай свої лапи якомога далі від цього!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].5"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Did I hear something?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я щось почув?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].6"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" What was that?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Що це було?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].7
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].7"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hm?"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Хм?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].8
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].8"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Like I need another health code violation."
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" Ніби мені потрібно ще одне порушення санітарних норм."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].9
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman,steal_five_finger_brew].9"
msgid "!dubious\n"
" What's going on over there?"
msgstr "!dubious\n"
" Що там відбувається?"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It'sss not easy to brew this stuff up, you know.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" I've only got so much oil."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Непросто зварити це, ви ж знаєте.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Я маю лише обмежену кількість олії."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thanks for stopping by the finest little caravan this ssside of the volcano!\n"
" !point\n"
" Be sure to tell your friendsss... <z 0.7>(with money.)</z>"
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Дякуємо, що зупинилися біля найкращого маленького каравану на цьому боці вулкана!\n"
" !point\n"
" Обов'язково розкажіть своїм друзям... <z 0.7>(з грошима.)</z>"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].3"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand <#RED>Health {name.potion}s</>!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Restore your mojo on the go-go!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!greet\n"
"<#RED>Лікувальні {name.potion}</> бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname}! Відновлюйте свій настрій на ходу!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Those nasssty Rots have been getting into my <#RED>Potion</> supply. I'm sure of it.\n"
" !point\n"
" But don't fret-- now I'm storing my brew somewhere safe from their ssssticky fingers.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Got to make sure there's plenty for honest, hard-working Hunters like yourself to buy!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ті сссмердючі гнильці лізли в мої <#RED>зілля</>! Я впевнений у цьому.\n"
" !point\n"
" Але не хвилюйтес... тепер я зберігаю свої напої в безпечному місці, подалі від їхніх сссслизьких пальців.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Треба переконатися, що їх буде достатньо для чесних, важко працюючих Мисливців, як ви!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman]NOT[run_has_five_finger_brew].2"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Can't just leave my famoussss {name.npc_doc_lastname}-brand brew out in the open anymore.\n"
" !angry\n"
" I'm certain some low-life's been ssssswiping it!"
msgstr "!neutral\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Не можу більше залишати своє знамените зілля бренду {Name.npc_doc_lastname} на виду.\n"
" !angry\n"
" Я впевнений, що якийсь покидьок сcccтащив його!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.generic_fallback:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.generic_fallback:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback].1"
msgid "Have a good day!"
msgstr "Гарного дня!"

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[cant_craft_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[cant_craft_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Come back later, my friend."
msgstr "!happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Повертайтесь пізніше, друже мій."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[has_refilled_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[has_refilled_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].1"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Thank-you for your patronage."
msgstr "!agent:\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Дякую вам за вашу підтримку."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[has_refilled_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[has_refilled_potion,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,role_travelling_salesman].2"
msgid "!point\n"
" You're my favourite cussstomer."
msgstr "!point\n"
" Ви мій улюблений ссспоживач."

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,wf_town_has_refiner,won_last_run]scout_first_grimhollow.1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_run_was_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout,wf_town_has_refiner,won_last_run]scout_first_grimhollow.1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Who is she? And where is <#BLUE>Grandpa</>...?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].1"
msgid "!neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Gah! You made me lose my train of thought! Aaand here comes a new one."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.nothingtosay:[in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner].2"
msgid "!happy\n"
" !think\n"
