" !dubious\n"
" (sniff sniff)...\n"
" !dejected\n"
" Kid. We gotta stop meeting like this."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!dubious\n"
"(нюх-нюх)...\n"
"!dejected\n"
"Друже. Ми повинні припинити ось так зустрічатися."

#: Quest.dgn_understand_nimble_market.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_understand_nimble_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market_magpie,role_market_merchant].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_understand_nimble_market.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_dgn_understand_nimble_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market_magpie,role_market_merchant].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !smirk\n"
" Hail, culver, a moment of your time?\n"
" !eyeroll\n"
" This art <i>obviously</i> a ridiculous question for 'tis plain the answer's \"no,\" but--\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !point\n"
" Can you, perchance, <i>understand</> <#BLUE>{name.shop_magpie}</>?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.dgn_whats_nimble_market.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_dgn_whats_nimble_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market,role_market_merchant].1
msgctxt "Quest.dgn_whats_nimble_market.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_dgn_whats_nimble_market,qc_dgn_firstmeeting_market,role_market_merchant].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Welcome back, culver."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Ласкаво просимо назад, голубе."

#: Quest.died_to_boss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_died_to_boss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_megatreemon,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon].1
msgctxt "Quest.died_to_boss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_died_to_boss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_megatreemon,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" I can't believe how quick your progress has been!\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Just think--a few weeks ago you were training in <#BLUE>the Brinks,</> now you're taking on a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</> head to head!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_died_to_miniboss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_megatreemon].1
msgctxt "Quest.died_to_miniboss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_died_to_miniboss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,lost_last_run,role_scout]NOT[has_seen_megatreemon].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
" You did great out there!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !clap\n"
"Ви там чудово попрацювали!"

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.QUIP.chitchat:[bandicoot_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd.QUIP.chitchat:[bandicoot_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_bnd,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter! I--<I>(Heyeurrk)</> Oof. Wow. I nearly--Phew! \n"
" !nervous\n"
" I haven't poked my nose into <#BLUE>{name.bandi_swamp}</> in a bit. Mmph. The stench is VILE!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Try not to breab trough your nobe! H-hab you smelled here beforb? <z 0.7>(Gasp!) I-I can't keep that up.</>"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Мисливцю! Я...<I>(Пчхі)</> Уф. Ого. Я ледь не...Фух!\n"
" !nervous\n"
" Я давно не сував носа в <#BLUE>{Name.bandi_swamp}</>. Ммф. Сморід ЖАХЛИВИЙ!\n"
" !happy\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Спробуйте не дихати носом! В-ви тут уже нюхали раніше? <z 0.7>(Ах!) Я-я так довго не витримаю.</>"

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.QUIP.chitchat:[eggzy_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy.QUIP.chitchat:[eggzy_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_eggzy,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !wave\n"
" So this is <#BLUE>{name.eggzy_tundra}</>...\n"
" !disagree\n"
" I haven't been able to scout ahead here. This is the first time I've been able to bring the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> this far down into the cavern itself.\n"
" !notebook\n"
" It's a maze-like network of tunnels. My readings show <#BLUE>Grandpa</> must be <i>somewhere</> down here... I just don't know <i>where</> ...\n"
" !think\n"
" But from the shape of the cavern itself, I'd say something <i>big</> lived down here. And because we're still alive, I'd say it's long gone."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.QUIP.chitchat:[grimhollow_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow.QUIP.chitchat:[grimhollow_region,in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_grimhollow,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" I had to check the <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> twice but this <i>is</> <#BLUE>{name.grimhollow_volcano}</>. What's left of it, anyway.\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" It feels so strange to be back..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl,owlitzer_region,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl,owlitzer_region,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I hope you're warm enough in that.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" It gets <#RED>Windy</> in there."
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Я сподіваюся, що вам тут достатньо тепло.\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Там стає <#RED>вітряно</>."

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_has_hamish.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_has_hamish,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout,wf_town_has_blacksmith]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_has_hamish.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_has_hamish,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout,wf_town_has_blacksmith]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" I recognized the same trail of debris I saw before. This is where <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> was stranded.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" I'm glad he's safe now.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Good luck, Hunter--and watch your footing, it's <#RED>Windy</> out there."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_mention_hamish.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_mention_hamish,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_mention_hamish.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_owl_mention_hamish,location_owlitzer_forest_r1,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Based on the disturbed trees and the trail of debris I saw, I'm hopeful that <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> is in these woods.\n"
" !point\n"
" I wasn't able to spot him from the air, but you might have more luck gathering clues on the ground.\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Good luck, Hunter--and watch your footing, it's <#RED>Windy</> out there."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt,role_scout,sedament_region]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_sdmnt,role_scout,sedament_region]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Phew! Th-th-that <#BLUE>{name.sedament_tundra}</> air is chilly even h-here at the foot of the mountains. W-watch out for ice, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech,role_scout,tefframech_region]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_tefframech,role_scout,tefframech_region]NOT[has_killed_tefframech,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !bliss\n"
" <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}'s</> <#RED>Key Pieces</> worked! <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> Lab doors are open. \n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Now, according to <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>, <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> mining machines could trigger the <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</> any moment now. \n"
" !nervous\n"
" To shut them down, we need to get to the <#RED>Control Panel</> in <#BLUE>Grandpa's</> lab. Where he'll be waiting..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr,role_scout,thatcher_region]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_first_dgn_visit_scout_thchr,role_scout,thatcher_region]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hmm... it seems we're in a bit of a predicament.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" [sound:Event.MX_Thatcher_DistantGuitar] 1\n"
" I've scouted all over, but I haven't been able to locate <#BLUE>{name.thatcher_swamp}'s</> <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>. All I've seen is a--\n"
" !shocked\n"
" ...! Um... did you hear music just now?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Хмм… здається, ми в скрутному становищі.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" [sound:Event.MX_Thatcher_DistantGuitar] 1\n"
" Я розвідав усюди, але так і не зміг знайти <#RED>{2:{name.rot_boss}}</> <#BLUE>{2:{Name.thatcher_swamp}}</>. Все, що бачив... це…\n"
" !shocked\n"
" …! Ем… Ви теж щойно чули музику?"

#: Quest.hype_room_first_visit_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_hype_room_first_visit_scout,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.hype_room_first_visit_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_hype_room_first_visit_scout,location_tefframech_volcano,role_scout,room_type_hype]NOT[in_town].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !nervous\n"
" This is the employee lab. That means <i>his</> lab is just through those doors. \n"
" player:\n"
" Don't worry. He's still your Grandpa. He'll listen to you and stop his mad plan. \n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral [keep-for-room]\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" You're right, Hunter. You're right. <i>(deep breath)</> \n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I'm ready when you are."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.pop_quiz_dodge.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_pop_quiz_dodge,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.pop_quiz_dodge.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_pop_quiz_dodge,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ghe-he-he. 'Ey Hunter! \n"
" !point\n"
" Don't think you've wriggled out of your first {name.pop_quiz} just 'cause I was lost in the woods!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!laugh\n"
"Ге-хе-хе. Ей, Мисливцю!\n"
"!point\n"
"Не думайте, що ваша перша {Name.pop_quiz} не відбудеться, тільки тому, що я заблукав у лісі!"

#: Quest.pop_quiz_focus_hit.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_pop_quiz_focus_hit,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.pop_quiz_focus_hit.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_pop_quiz_focus_hit,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" 'Ey, Hunter!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" {name.pop_quiz}!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Гей, Мисливцю!\n"
" !laugh\n"
" {Name.pop_quiz}!"

#: Quest.struggling_on_miniboss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_struggling_on_miniboss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,lost_last_run,role_scout,struggling_on_yammo_miniboss]NOT[has_seen_megatreemon].1
msgctxt "Quest.struggling_on_miniboss_scout_mt.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_struggling_on_miniboss_scout_mt,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,lost_last_run,role_scout,struggling_on_yammo_miniboss]NOT[has_seen_megatreemon].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !angry\n"
" Yeesh, that <#RED>{name.rot_miniboss}</> is a real piece of work!\n"
" player:\n"
" I don't know what's more bruised, my body, or my pride...\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't let it get to you, Hunter. Even <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> had his off days.\n"
" !think\n"
" Speaking of, you could always go talk to him if you need a little extra guidance. I'm sure he's got some strategies for taking that <#RED>{name.rot_miniboss}</> down."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_from_market,armour_rarity_rare,in_quest_twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[armour_rarity_legendary].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith.QUIP.chitchat:[armour_from_market,armour_rarity_rare,in_quest_twn_alphonse_zone2_armorsmith,in_town,role_armorsmith]NOT[armour_rarity_legendary].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Got some new armour from <#RED>him</> again, huh?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Знову отримали нові обладунки від <#RED>нього</>, хмх?"

#: Quest.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_from_market,weapon_rarity_rare].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_alphonse_zone2_blacksmith,in_town,role_blacksmith,weapon_from_market,weapon_rarity_rare].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" I see ye got yer mitts on a new weapon. From the Market, aye?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gruffnod\n"
" Бачу, ви дістали нову зброю. З ринку, так?"

#: Quest.twn_ascensions_explainer.QUIP.chitchat:[frenzy_unlocked,in_quest_twn_ascensions_explainer,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,qc_twn_weather_intro_scout,role_dojo]NOT[done_any_frenzy].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_ascensions_explainer.QUIP.chitchat:[frenzy_unlocked,in_quest_twn_ascensions_explainer,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,qc_twn_weather_intro_scout,role_dojo]NOT[done_any_frenzy].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" How's it lookin' out there, kid?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Як там справи, друже?"

#: Quest.twn_bandages_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_bandages_scout,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_bandages_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_bandages_scout,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Let's see... grease the rotor... replace the oil... shine the headlights...\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" Oh, hey, Hunter."
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!neutral\n"
"!notebook\n"
"Подивимось... змастити ротор... замінити масло... натерти фари...\n"
"!happy\n"
"!greet\n"
"О, привіт, Мисливцю."

#: Quest.twn_beautiful_future_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_beautiful_future_scout,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_beautiful_future_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_beautiful_future_scout,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Y'know... even though they're riddled with <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>, the woods still look beautiful from the air.\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" I wonder what it'll look like after we've saved the world..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_berna_and_hamish_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_berna_and_hamish_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_berna_and_hamish_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith,wf_town_has_blacksmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Hey, Hunter. Ready to get back out there?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !greet\n"
" Ей, Мисливцю. Готові повернутися?"

#: Quest.twn_cannon_explainer.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_cannon_explainer,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_cannon_explainer.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_cannon_explainer,in_town,pf_unlocked_masteries,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !greet\n"
" {name.dojo_cough} Eyy, Hunter.\n"
" !point\n"
" That a <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</> I see? Need any tips?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
"!happy\n"
"!greet\n"
"{Name.dojo_cough} Ей, Мисливцю.\n"
"!point\n"
"Це <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>? Потрібні якісь поради?"

#: Quest.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_at_least_1_hearts,in_quest_twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout,in_town,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_at_least_1_hearts,in_quest_twn_canttouch_heartstone_scout,in_town,role_scout].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !closedeyes\n"
" Hmm... <z 0.7><i>I wonder what it feels like... putting the <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</> in the <#KONJUR>{name.i_town_grid_cryst}</>...</></>\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Oh. Hey Hunter! You... you didn't hear that, did you?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.twn_dojo_cough.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_dojo_cough,in_town,qc_twn_mastery_explainer,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_dojo_cough.QUIP.chitchat:[in_quest_twn_dojo_cough,in_town,qc_twn_mastery_explainer,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !very_sick\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(cough, cough, HACK, cough)</z></i></>\n"
" player:\n"
" Um... are you okay?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Just peachy. Why d'ya ask?"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !cough\n"
" {name.dojo_cough}\n"
" !very_sick\n"
" <#KONJUR><i><z 0.8>(кашель, кашель, КХЕК, кашель)</z></i></>\n"
" player:\n"
" Ем… з тобою все гаразд?\n"
" agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Просто чудово. А чому питаєте?"

#: Quest.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_twn_find_first_key_blacksmith,in_town,qc_after_find_first_key_scout,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_find_first_key_blacksmith.QUIP.chitchat:[has_killed_grimhollow,has_volcanokey1,in_quest_twn_find_first_key_blacksmith,in_town,qc_after_find_first_key_scout,role_blacksmith]NOT[has_killed_tefframech].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Hmph. What is it? Ye've got a weird look about ye. \n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_scout}'s reading their Grandpa's diary, and your name came up.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" Och. 'Course it did. Bloody heck...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" How's the kiddo holdin' up?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.twn_finish_boss_weapon.QUIP.chitchat:[has_charged_corestone_weapon,in_quest_twn_finish_boss_weapon,in_town,role_refiner]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_finish_boss_weapon.QUIP.chitchat:[has_charged_corestone_weapon,in_quest_twn_finish_boss_weapon,in_town,role_refiner]NOT[has_any_boss_weapon].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Hunter--my equipment went nuts the second you touched down from your last {name.run}...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" You didn't... did you?\n"
" player:\n"
" You mean this {name.weapon_crystal} that I <i>CHARGED,</> then, uh, <i>YEAH,</> I <i>DID,</> DIDN'T I? BOOYEAH!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" You really did. Wow. I'm impressed, Hunter. Like, very, VERY impressed.\n"
" !think\n"
" Now take that to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> so he can re-forge it into a permanently-charged, <i>unbreakable</> <#RED>{name.weapon_boss}</>!\n"
" player:\n"
" Oh, riiiight. Cuz if I fall while using <i>this</>--\n"
" agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" It's goodbye <#RED>{name.rot_sf_boss}</> <#KONJUR>Teffressence</>, <i>and</> goodbye <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" Don't forget: <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</> repair costs are now <i>on you,</> per the terms of our deal.\n"
" player:\n"
" About that, um, a-are you <i>sure</> that was the deal...? \n"
" agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Don't you start, Hunter. You've cost me a <i>lot</> of <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Y'know, everyone in camp took bets on whether or not you'd <i>actually</> charge the thing...\n"
" player:\n"
" Really? Well I'm Glad to have made you some {name.konjur} <i>back,</> then.\n"
" agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" Oh, nonono--I bet against you.\n"
" player:\n"
" {name.npc_refiner}! What the--?!\n"
" agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Tsk. Don't take it personally--I'm a pessimist! He he he.\n"
" !point\n"
" And as a pessimist, I say go see <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>--now!"
msgstr "agent:\n"
" !neutral\n"
" !think\n"
" Мисливцю - моє обладнання збожеволіло в ту ж секунду, як ви повернулися з останнього {name.run}...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Ви ж не... так?\n"
"player:\n"
" Ти про цю {2:{name.weapon_crystal}}, яку я <i>ЗАРЯДИВ,</> тобто, е-е, <i>ТАК,</> Я <i>ЦЕ ЗРОБИВ,</> ПРАВДА Ж? БУМ!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Ви справді це зробили. Вау. Я вражена, Мисливцю. Дуже, ДУЖЕ вражена.\n"
" !think\n"
" А тепер віднесіть це до <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</>, щоб він перекував її в постійно заряджену, <i>неламку</> <#RED>{3:{name.weapon_boss}}</>!\n"
"player:\n"
" А, точно. Бо якщо я впаду з <i>нею</>...\n"
"agent:\n"
" !disagree\n"
" То прощавай <#KONJUR>Тефресенція</> <#RED>{2:{name.rot_sf_boss}}</> , <i>і</> прощавай <#RED>{name.weapon_crystal}</>.\n"
" !shrug\n"
" І не забувайте: ремонт <#RED>{3:{name.weapon_crystal}}</> тепер <i>за ваш рахунок,</> за умовами нашої угоди.\n"
"player:\n"
" До речі, е-е, ти <i>впевнена</>, що ми саме так домовлялися...?\n"
"agent:\n"
" !angry\n"
" Тільки не починайте, Мисливцю. Ви вже винні мені <i>чимало</> <#KONJUR>{2:{name.konjur}}</>...\n"
" !gesture\n"
" Знаєте, у таборі всі ставили ставки, чи ви <i>взагалі</> зможете її зарядити...\n"
"player:\n"
" Справді? Ну, радий тоді був повернути тобі трохи {2:{name.konjur}} <i>назад,</>.\n"
"agent:\n"
" !notebook\n"
" О, ні-ні-ні - я ставила проти вас.\n"
"player:\n"
" {Name.npc_refiner}! Та що за...?!\n"
"agent:\n"
" !laugh\n"
" Ц-ц. Не сприймайте близько до серця - я песимістка! Хе-хе-хе.\n"
" !point\n"
" І як песимістка, я кажу: йдіть до <#BLUE>{2:{Name.npc_blacksmith}}</> - зараз!"

#: Quest.twn_first_alphonse_armor.QUIP.chitchat:[equipped_any_armour_from_market,equipped_any_uncommon_armour,in_quest_twn_first_alphonse_armor,in_town,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.twn_first_alphonse_armor.QUIP.chitchat:[equipped_any_armour_from_market,equipped_any_uncommon_armour,in_quest_twn_first_alphonse_armor,in_town,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n"
" !happy\n"
" !shocked\n"
" Hunter... that new armour...\n"
" !dubious\n"
" Where did you get it?"
msgstr ""

