#: Quest.twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout.QUIP.chitchat:[has_deposited_3_zone_1_hearts,holding_any_zone_1_heart,in_quest_twn_fourth_heart_handin_scout,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts].1
