#: STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.speed_demon.desc
msgctxt "STRINGS.ITEMS.POWERS.PLAYER.speed_demon.desc"
msgid "Constantly build up to a maximum of <#RED>+{max_speed}% {name.concept_runspeed}</>.\n\n"
"Resets when you <#RED>Dodge</>."
msgstr "Постійно накопичуйте до максимуму <#RED>+{max_speed}% {name.concept_runspeed}</>.\n\n"
"Скидається, коли ви <#RED>ухиляєтеся</>."

