#: STRINGS.UI.MECHANIC_TUTORIALS.LOADOUTS_UNLOCKED_2.DESC
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.MECHANIC_TUTORIALS.LOADOUTS_UNLOCKED_2.DESC"
msgid "After a loadout is created, you can quickly switch between them using any <#RED>Mannequin</>.\n\n"
