#: STRINGS.UI.MOUSE_AIMING_POPUP.BODY
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.MOUSE_AIMING_POPUP.BODY"
msgid "In Rotwood, your character will always face your mouse cursor. Use your <#RED>Mouse</> to aim your attacks.\n\n"
"We recommend playing this way because you'll have an easier time doing more complicated combos later, but if you would prefer to aim your attacks with your <#RED>Keyboard</>, please say so below!.\n\n"
"You can always change your mind in the <#RED>Options Screen</>."
